data: {"type":"search_strategy","strategy":{"queries":["speech coaching app","public speaking practice","communication skills trainer","presentation coach app","speaking confidence builder","debate practice app","impromptu speaking trainer","conversational pressure simulator","interview preparation speaking","pitch practice app","Orai speech coach","Speeko public speaking","talk coach AI","overcome speaking anxiety","articulation fluency trainer"],"categories":["6017","6000"],"reasoning":"Cognitize sits at the intersection of education and business productivity — users are professionals, students, and aspiring speakers seeking real-world communication improvement. Queries span direct competitor names (Orai, Speeko), feature-level searches (impromptu speaking, pressure simulation), problem-level searches (speaking anxiety, fluency), and adjacent solutions (interview prep, pitch practice). Categories 6017 (Education) and 6000 (Business) capture the primary store shelves where speech coaching apps are listed. Filters reflect a mainstream market with moderate install thresholds since public speaking apps have meaningful but not massive audiences, and maxRating of 4.5 targets users who may be dissatisfied with existing solutions — revealing gaps Cognitize can exploit.","filters":{"minInstalls":10000,"maxRating":4.5,"minRatings":100}}}

