data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1071468459","title":"Speeko: AI for Public Speaking","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.7336,"ratings":4,"reviewCount":4302,"installs":"N/A","description":"Instant feedback on your speaking style. Speak confidently everywhere. \n\nTransform your speaking skills with real-time feedback on your pace, tone, and fillers. Benefit from our cutting-edge technology that adapts to your specific needs and intelligently recommends tailored lessons and exercises.\n\nSpeeko is more than just a public speaking app — it's a complete communication coach. Whether you're preparing for a job interview, a virtual meeting, or a wedding toast, Speeko will give you the confidence and skills you need to speak with authority and impact.\n\nAnd with the added expertise of America's top voice coach, Roger Love, our app takes your learning experience to the next level.\n\nJoin the hundreds of thousands of people who have improved their speaking skills with Speeko. Try it now for free and experience the difference for yourself.\n\n------------------------------------------------\n\nSubscription Pricing and Terms:\n\nSpeeko offers two auto-renewing subscription options:\nMonthly: $24.99 per month\nYearly: $7.49 per month (One payment of $89.99 billed every 12 months)\n\nThese prices are for United States customers. Pricing in other countries may vary, and actual charges may be converted to your local currency depending on the country of residence.\n\nYour iTunes Account will be charged when the purchase is confirmed.\n\nYour Speeko Pro subscription will automatically renew unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current period.\n\nYour account will be charged for the renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period, and the cost of the renewal will be identified. \n\nYou can go to your iTunes Account Settings to manage your subscription and turn off auto-renew.\n\nIf you have any comments or questions, email info@speeko.co. \n\nRead our terms and conditions here:\nhttps://www.speeko.co/terms-and-conditions\n\nRead our privacy policy here:\nhttps://www.speeko.co/privacy-policy","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/47/1b/ff/471bffce-3106-4e80-d5df-f99d86d2b1d9/AppIcon-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-0-85-220-0.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/speeko-ai-for-public-speaking/id1071468459?uo=4","developer":"SPEEKO Tech, LLC","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":66,"2":28,"3":148,"4":502,"5":3558}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1253443132","title":"Astound - Voice & Speech Coach","store":"app_store","genre":"Health & Fitness","score":4.71331,"ratings":1,"reviewCount":1322,"installs":"N/A","description":"*Featured App of the Day*\n\nFind your voice with Astound.\n\nSpeaking with confidence doesn’t come naturally to most of us. Whether it’s leading a meeting, pitching an idea, teaching a class, or recording a podcast—your voice carries more weight than you think.\n\nAnd yet, very few of us ever receive real training on how to use it. That’s why we built Astound.\n\nWith 100+ bite-sized exercises, guided breathwork, voice recordings, affirmations, and progress tracking, Astound makes daily practice simple, approachable, and even fun.\n\nWe know public speaking can feel nerve-racking—even when it’s not a big stage. That shaky feeling before you speak? You’re not alone. Astound helps you turn those nerves into calm energy and presence.\n\nOur approach is different. Instead of obsessing over filler words, we focus on how your voice makes you—and your listeners—feel. You’ll learn to breathe with intention, speak with authenticity, and adapt your voice to fit any situation.\n\nTeachers. Podcasters. Salespeople. Remote professionals.\nAstound was built for anyone who wants to communicate with more confidence and clarity.\n\nMost users report feeling a shift in just a few days of practice—greater calm, more confidence, stronger presence. And with daily recordings, you can hear your own progress.\n\nYour voice is your power. With Astound, you’ll learn how to use it.\n\n-----------------------\n\n*Content*\n- Astound offers an extensive library of 100+ easy-to-follow video tutorials\n- A 30 Day Challenge, which gradually strengthens your voice over time for your chosen goal\n- Bite-sized practice packs for different occasions, like preparing for an interview or presentation on stage.\n\n*Features*\n- Audio Voice Recorder\n- Audio feedback and analytics on your speaking tempo, pitch modulation, and volume\n- Create a list of 'Favorite' exercises to watch together easier\n- Reminders to help you build a healthy habit.\n\n*Subscription pricing*\nIf you want to get the souped-up version, you can pay less than your monthly coffee budget. The two auto-renewing subscription options:\n- $12.99/month\n- $69.99/year  (55% savings)\n\nThese prices are for United States Customers. Pricing in other countries may vary and actual charges may be converted to your local currency depending on the country of residence. \nYour Astound subscription will automatically renew, and your credit card will be charged, unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period. Any unused portion of a free trial period, if offered, will be forfeited when you purchases your subscription. You can turn off auto-renew at any time from your iTunes account settings, but refunds will not be provided for any unused portion of the term.\n\nIf you have any feedback, questions, or comments, please email us at: \nrobin@astoundthem.com\nWe'd love to hear from you.\n\nRead more about our Terms & Conditions: \nhttp://astoundthem.com/terms.html\n\nRead more about our Privacy Policy:\nhttps://www.iubenda.com/privacy-policy/8180900","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/d8/1d/e0/d81de0b9-d794-7d5b-da9a-68c2d29c1fa8/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-8-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/astound-voice-speech-coach/id1253443132?uo=4","developer":"Astound Inc","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":39,"2":13,"3":36,"4":112,"5":1122}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1567841142","title":"BoldVoice: Accent Training","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.8166,"ratings":51,"reviewCount":51080,"installs":"N/A","description":"BoldVoice is the top-rated English speaking and pronunciation app, with over 2 million global users. Our Hollywood accent coaches and AI-powered feedback will help you achieve clear, confident pronunciation, with only 10 minutes of daily practice.\n\nWHY CHOOSE BOLDVOICE: \nLearn from professional accent coaches who train Hollywood actors\nRecord your voice and receive instant, AI-powered pronunciation feedback\nPractice with daily-life scenarios and professional conversations\nMonitor progress through comprehensive analytics\nDevelop confidence for presentations, meetings, and interviews\nPractice only 10 minutes a day to see improvement\n\nFEATURES:\nProfessional video tutorials for mastering English sounds\nReal-time pronunciation assessment and correction with AI\nVoice recording and native speaker comparison tools\nSound-by-sound analysis of every word you pronounce\nInteractive mouth diagrams that show how sounds are made\nBite-sized daily learning tasks that only take 5-10 minutes\nComprehensive assessment that identifies your focus areas\nCustomized learning paths based on your assessment and native language\nAI Chat for free-flowing conversations with an AI conversation partner\nExtensive business vocabulary and professional phrases\nSmart learning journey that adapts to your progress\nEngaging interface that makes learning fun\n\nIDEAL FOR:\nBusiness professionals and executives\nInternational employees in multinational companies\nJob seekers preparing for interviews\nGraduate students and academics\nPublic speakers and presenters\nESL/EFL learners advancing their skills\nTOEFL, IELTS, and English certification candidates\n\nAWARDS:\nDesigned by a team of Hollywood accent coaches with experience including: Harvard University, Yale University, Netflix, Marvel, CBS, NBC, Broadway\nFeatured as one of Apple’s Top #10 Education Apps\nSelected as a Best New App of the Year by Google\nFeatured on TechCrunch as \"the app that helps non-native English speakers find their voice\"\nRecognized as a top Education app by Forbes\n\nFOCUS AREAS:\nBoldVoice expertise includes: English pronunciation, accent reduction, business English, professional development, speech training, accent coach, ESL, EFL, language learning, pronunciation app, accent modification, speech clarity, communication skills, professional speaking, American accent, English fluency, voice training, pronunciation software, Artificial Intelligence, accent training app, English speaking skills.\n\n\nSUBSCRIPTION\nTo access BoldVoice, you will be asked to subscribe to one of the subscription options that will be shown to you in the app.\n\nA subscription will unlock all the lessons from accent coaches, practice materials, and features of the app. Without a subscription, you will only be able to access the first lesson for free.\n\nPayment for the subscription will be charged to your Apple ID account upon confirmation of purchase. Subscriptions will automatically renew unless canceled 24 hours prior to the end of your current subscription. To cancel your subscription or manage auto-renewal settings, go to your device settings by accessing your Apple ID from the Settings app and choosing Subscriptions.\n\n\nConnect With Us\nEmail: support@boldvoice.com\nWebsite: https://boldvoice.com\nTerms of Service: https://boldvoice.com/terms\nPrivacy Policy: https://boldvoice.com/privacy","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/cd/13/ca/cd13ca02-d0c8-56ef-5a81-c51579621414/BoldVoice-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-0-sRGB-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/boldvoice-accent-training/id1567841142?uo=4","developer":"Wellocution Inc.","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":618,"2":278,"3":1003,"4":4056,"5":45125}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"894460403","title":"Speak4Me Text to Speech Reader","store":"app_store","genre":"Utilities","score":4.54817,"ratings":12,"reviewCount":12965,"installs":"N/A","description":"Looking for an app to read things out loud? Search no more! Speak4Me allows you to convert any text into audio, no matter the length. Just pick a language and a voice–and you’re all set.\n\nSpeak4Me is a powerful text to speech app designed to read aloud any text with natural sounding voices. \n\nSpeak4Me is the perfect app for you if:\n- you’re looking forward to reading faster and saving time;\n- you’d like to improve your productivity and comprehension;\n- you aim at doing more at once: take your reading wherever you go – to the gym, the park, or the couch;\n- you suffer from vocal problems such as dyslexia or you sometimes struggle to express yourself (don’t worry, we’ve got you covered!);\n- you need to create voice overs for any videos, customer support, podcasts etc.\n- you’d like to trick your friends–everyone loves a good prank ;)\n\nHere’s all the magic you can do with Speak4Me:\n- Speak and say anything.\n- Convert any text into speech by inputting or pasting your own text.\n- Choose between male or female natural sounding voices in over 20 different languages and accents.\n- Adjust the voice speed and the font size.\n- Enable the dyslexia font.\n- Save your phrases as favorites.\n- Download your speech as an audio file and share it with your friends via iMessage, WhatsApp, Facebook Messenger, TikTok, Instagram, Snapchat, e-mail etc.\n\nWhat are you waiting for? Join thousands of people who use Speak4Me every day to read, speak and improve their comprehension!\n\nThe complete list of all the supported voices you can find on Speak4Me:\nArabic; Chinese (China, Hong Kong, Taiwan); Czech; Danish; Dutch (Belgium, Netherlands); English (Australia, Ireland, South Africa, United Kingdom, United States); Finnish; French (Canada, France); German; Greek; Hindi; Hungarian; Indonesian; Italian; Japanese; Korean; Norwegian; Polish; Portuguese (Brazil, Portugal); Romanian; Russian; Slovak; Spanish (Mexico, Spain); Swedish; Thai; Turkish.\n\nDon’t forget to check out our updates. New content is added regularly.\n\nIf you’re enjoying Speak4Me, then please leave a review! You’ll make us happy and help others discover your favorite text to speech app. \n\nHave a feature request you would like to see in a future version of the app? Do not hesitate to contact us at support@bakeryscent.com\n\nSUBSCRIPTION INFO\n\n• Subscription length: monthly, yearly.\n• Your payment will be charged to your iTunes Account as soon as you confirm your purchase.\n• You can manage your subscriptions and turn off auto-renewal from your Account Settings after the purchase.\n• Your subscription will renew automatically, unless you turn off auto-renew at least 24 hours before the end of the current period.\n• The cost of renewal will be charged to your account in the 24 hours prior to the end of the current period.\n• When canceling a subscription, your subscription will stay active until the end of the period. Auto-renewal will be disabled, but the current subscription will not be refunded.\n• Any unused portion of a free trial period, if offered, will be forfeited when purchasing a subscription.\n\nPlease, make sure to read our Privacy Policy and Terms Of Service:\nhttps://speak4me-3ac5f.web.app/policy/policy.html\nhttps://speak4me-3ac5f.web.app/policy/terms.html","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/cc/ee/c4/cceec443-e1b2-8c23-850c-1225e59cabf4/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-11-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/speak4me-text-to-speech-reader/id894460403?uo=4","developer":"Bakery Scent","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":638,"2":297,"3":597,"4":1221,"5":10212}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1627501632","title":"Stimuler- English Speaking App","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.84877,"ratings":5,"reviewCount":5105,"installs":"N/A","description":"Ever wondered how you can ace the IELTS Speaking section or practice your English speaking skills with just your smartphone?\n\nEnter Stimuler! Dive deep into the realm of English speaking practice, meticulously crafted by a team of IITians, a World Public Speaking Champion, and multiple IELTS 8.5 Band achievers.\n\nDOWNLOAD STIMULER NOW! Boasting a community of 300,000+ users from 200+ countries and a glowing 4.8/5* rating, Stimuler isn’t just another English learning app – it's an English-speaking revolution!\n\nWhy is Stimuler the talk of the town?\n\n *   60-Second Magic: Record a 60-second speech and get instant feedback on your pronunciation, fluency, vocabulary, and more in less than 20 seconds. Plus, an immediate IELTS band score to gauge your progress.\n *   Real-life IELTS Simulation: Industry-first Live Video Mock Tests that mirror the real IELTS experience with our proprietary AI Interviewer. Engage, speak, and receive exhaustive performance insights instantly alongside your overall IELTS Speaking band!\n *   Speak Your Mind: With over 100 diverse speaking topics, you're spoilt for choice. Perfect for IELTS, TOEFL, or just some casual English conversation practice.\n *   Speech Insights: Dive deeper than scores. From filler words, pace, and tone to awkward pauses, get a 360-degree view of your speaking prowess.\n *   Tailored Tips After Every Session: We believe feedback is the breakfast of champions. Get personalized pointers after every session, crafted just for you.\n\nFeatures that set us leagues apart:\n\n *   Global Recognition: We're not just loved by our users. We've been spotlighted as one of the top 100 promising apps of 2023 and have the backing of top-tier VCs from Silicon Valley, Japan, and India.\n *   Proprietary Voice AI Technology: Our state-of-the-art voice AI has been refined using millions of user speeches, spanning every single country on the planet. This ensures unparalleled feedback accuracy and insights.\n *   Fast and Flexible: Whether you've got hours or just 10 minutes a day, see tangible results with Stimuler. What's more? Every speech gets comprehensive feedback in less than 30 seconds!\n *   Affordable Premium Perks: At a nominal price of less than $5/month, unlock a universe of features. A tailored practice roadmap of speaking exercises, 15+ full-length IELTS Speaking mock tests, and much more awaits you.\n\nHere's the best part: Stimuler is FREE for everyone. Dive in, practice speaking, gather feedback, and watch yourself transform day by day. For those aiming for the stars, our premium suite is your rocket ship.\n\nFrom rigorous IELTS speaking preparation to breezy English conversation sessions – Stimuler is your pocket mentor. Flexible, blazing fast, and proven, with users witnessing a whopping 20% enhancement in speaking and conversational skills in just a month!\n\nSo, why wait? Whether you're gearing up for your IELTS speaking test or just looking to brush up on your English conversation skills, Stimuler is too good to miss out on. Remember, real progress happens when you practice, not just watch. It's free to download, and it's high time you took your English speaking to the next level.\n\nSpeak, Evolve, Triumph!\n\n\nTerms of Use- https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/82/47/34/824734af-7ca1-c40a-b354-e340fe24cf74/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-8-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/stimuler-english-speaking-app/id1627501632?uo=4","developer":"Stimuler Private Limited","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":62,"2":25,"3":73,"4":303,"5":4642}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6468764490","title":"SpeakApp AI: Voice Notes","store":"app_store","genre":"Productivity","score":4.6422,"ratings":7,"reviewCount":7099,"installs":"N/A","description":"SpeakApp AI: Voice-to-Text\n\nSpeakApp captures your voice with a single tap and transforms it into text.\nRecord and summarize meetings, take voice notes, write emails or create content with your voice. SpeakApp simplifies your workflow by seamlessly converting voice to text.\n\nFrom a spontaneous brainstorm to a structured blueprint, your spoken ideas are transcribed swiftly and accurately, thanks to our cutting-edge AI.\nSpeakApp is your reliable companion, instantly delivering clean, ready-to-use text. \nIt works perfectly to record and transcribe:\n•  meetings\n•  voice notes\n•  lectures\n•  brain storm new ideas\n•  write emails and other important communication with your voice on the go\n\nRecord and Transcribe\n• Record Voice Notes and Meetings: Easily record your thoughts and SpeakApp will transcribe them into text in real-time.\n• High-Quality Transcription: Grammatically correct and punctuated text that is free of filler words and repetitions.\n• AI Length Adjustment: Modify the transcribed text to be shorter or longer, using advanced AI technology.\n\nImport and Transcribe Recordings\n• Import recordings from other apps, files, or YouTube\n• Import voice messages from messengers including WhatsApp and Telegram\n• Import and transcribe YouTube videos\n• Get instant summaries and translations for your recordings, audio messages, and even YouTube videos\n\nAI Text Editing\n• Summarize & turn into bullet notes: Extract the essence of your notes with summaries and bullet points.\n• Email & Task Conversion: Turn your text into a ready-to-send email or a structured task.\n• Tone Adjustment: Change the tone of the text to suit your needs - from professional to casual, or even add a touch of humor with funny AI-rewrite options.\n\nLanguage & Translation Features\n• Multiple Language Support: Choose from a range of languages for instant voice translation.\n• Ideal for multilingual users or those learning a new language.\n\nEfficient Sharing\n• Share your notes directly from the app.\n\nPrivacy & Security\n• We take your privacy seriously. Your data remains confidential and is never shared with third parties.\n• Full Data Control: Easily manage and delete your data as needed.\nPrivacy Policy: https://speakapp.com/privacy\nTerms of Use: https://speakapp.com/terms\n\n\nGet SpeakApp today and turn your voice into your most powerful tool!","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/93/28/af/9328af25-6218-7cf4-d1cc-4f513fcbbac5/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007ephone-0-1-0-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/speakapp-ai-voice-notes/id6468764490?uo=4","developer":"VoicePop Inc.","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":289,"2":118,"3":245,"4":540,"5":5907}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1429704005","title":"Peech: Text to Speech Reader","store":"app_store","genre":"Magazines & Newspapers","score":4.58784,"ratings":6,"reviewCount":6512,"installs":"N/A","description":"Peech – Turn Anything Into Audiobooks!\n\nMeet Peech, your personal AI-powered reading sidekick that transforms all your text - PDFs, web articles, physical books, and more - into crystal-clear audiobooks. Whether you’re racing through study notes, catching up on blog posts, or diving into that spicy new novel, Peech has you covered.\n\nThe Magic of AI Voices\n\t• Smart Voice Matching: Peech’s advanced AI picks the perfect voice for each genre - whether it’s serious academic reading or a lighthearted romance.\n\t• Natural & Lifelike: Our voices are so real, you might forget you’re listening to an app.\n\nEffortless Content Scanning\n\t• Lightning-Fast OCR: Snap a pic of any page or book, and Peech instantly converts it to audio. No more manual typing!\n\t• Web & PDF Parsing: Just paste a link or upload a file to start listening - perfect for busy pros, students, and anyone who prefers ears over eyes.\n\nSpeedy Reading, On-the-Go\n\t• High-Speed Playback: Devour your favorite content up to 5x faster - perfect for power-learners or those who want to binge-listen on the run.\n\t• Playlists & Autoplay: Build custom playlists to keep the stories rolling, so you can multitask like a boss.\n\nOne App, All Languages\n\t• Automatic Language Detection: Peech seamlessly identifies and narrates in 60+ languages.\n\t• Global Accessibility: Great for language learners, busy professionals, and anyone with reading challenges.\n\nWhy Peech?\n\t• Students: Turn textbooks into engaging audio lectures - study smarter, not harder.\n\t• Busy Professionals: Catch up on news, memos, or trade articles during your commute.\n\t• Accessibility: An empowering reading solution for users with visual or reading impairments.\n\t• Content Lovers: From classics to your favorite steamy novels - Peech reads it all.\n\nFree Trials & Subscriptions\n\nExperience Peech with our flexible subscription plans, some offering free trials. Dive into unlimited content and see how Peech revolutionizes your reading routine - no commitment, no hassle.\n\nReady to transform your reading life? Give Peech a try and unlock the power of AI-driven audio today!","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/54/90/8b/54908b44-b73a-259c-84ae-981762763641/AppIcon-composed-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-0-sRGB-85-220-0.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/peech-text-to-speech-reader/id1429704005?uo=4","developer":"Dopefin Limited","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":374,"2":91,"3":215,"4":485,"5":5347}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1610386353","title":"Transkriptor - Speech to Text","store":"app_store","genre":"Productivity","score":4.71698,"ratings":954,"reviewCount":954,"installs":"N/A","description":"Transkriptor: The Ultimate AI-Powered Speech-to-Text App and Productivity Tool\n\nSave time with Transkriptor, your all-in-one AI assistant for transcription and AI note-taking. Easily transcribe meetings, convert voice notes and memos to text, and transform videos into written notes. Transkriptor combines powerful AI features with convenience and speed for a seamless experience.\n\nKey Features of Transkriptor:\nAI Assistant: Transkriptor’s AI assistant enhances your workflow by generating AI summaries, drafting emails, and converting voice memos into text, helping you efficiently manage and interact with your transcripts.\n AI Chat: Interact directly with your transcripts using AI chat. Ask questions, extract important details, and get summaries—all through a user-friendly chat interface that saves time and boosts productivity.\n AI Voice Memos: Automatically transcribe voice memos with AI-powered precision. Capture every detail from your voice recordings, turning them into easy-to-read text that saves time and keeps your notes organized.\nConvert Voice Notes to Text: Effortlessly convert voice notes to text with high accuracy, supporting various formats like MP3, WAV, and M4A. Ideal for transcribing voice memos, meetings, lectures, interviews, and more.\nConvert Video to Text: Perfect for creating captions, transcribing video content, or generating notes from webinars and Youtube videos ensuring nothing is missed.\nTake Notes with Voice:Use Transkriptor’s integrated audio recorder to capture lectures, personal thoughts, or any spoken content directly from your device. Easily take notes with voice, then navigate your recordings and transcripts with AI chat for quick access to key points.\nTranscribe Voice Memos to Text:  Convert voice memos into clear, organized notes with exceptional accuracy. Use our meeting assistant to capture every detail and create knowledge bases from transcriptions, ensuring all important information is documented and accessible.\n\nWhy Choose Transkriptor?\n1. Save Time and Enhance Efficiency: Transkriptor’s AI features like the AI assistant, AI chat, and voice memo transcription reduce the time spent on manual note-taking and transcription. Let our AI handle the details while you focus on what matters most.\n2. Versatility Across Formats: Whether transcribing voice notes, converting audio to text, or converting video to text, Transkriptor provides a comprehensive solution for all your transcription needs in one intuitive app.\n3. Flexible and Affordable Plans: Start with our free plan, offering 90 minutes of transcription to explore our features, including AI chat and AI summary.\n4. Secure and Private: Transkriptor ensures your data is securely stored and kept confidential, never shared with third parties.\n\nAdditional Features to Enhance Your Experience:\nImport and Transcribe: Easily upload audio and video files for transcription. Transkriptor supports multiple formats, catering to a variety of use cases.\nExport in Multiple Formats: Download your transcripts in formats like PDF, DOCX, TXT, and SRT, perfect for documentation, sharing, and archiving.\nSpeaker Identification: Automatically tag different speakers in your transcripts, making it easier to follow conversations with multiple voices.\nTranslation and Language Support: Transkriptor supports transcription in over 40 languages, making it perfect for global users and multilingual environments.\nOrganize with AI: Efficiently manage your transcripts with AI-powered folders, tags, and search features to quickly locate what you need.\nGet Started with Transkriptor Today!\n\nCan I transcribe for free?\nYes! Sign up to receive free transcription credits. Easily transcribe audio or video files like Amberscript, Otter, Temi, Notta, SoundType AI Rev.com, or HappyScribe!\n\nConvert audio to text: https://transkriptor.com\n\nTerms of Use: https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/9d/59/76/9d597680-9217-00d0-4a2a-d6307ae8f7ce/GlassIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-0-sRGB-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/transkriptor-speech-to-text/id1610386353?uo=4","developer":"Torapp","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":52,"2":8,"3":5,"4":28,"5":861}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1203178170","title":"Orai - Improve Public Speaking","store":"app_store","genre":"Productivity","score":4.61747,"ratings":3,"reviewCount":3375,"installs":"N/A","description":"We're on a mission to help you overcome your fear of public speaking. So you can express confidence and be more compelling!\n\nPractice Presentations, Speeches, Sales Pitches, and much more using instant driven feedback to improve your professional speaking style. \n\nWe also have world-class gamified lessons to guide you on your journey to improving your pacing, filler words (um, you know basically) energy, conciseness, clarity, confidence, facial expressions, and much more!\n\nOrai allows you to record anytime anywhere so if you can't make it to the toastmasters meeting or if you are feeling nervous 20 mins before your presentation. Just open Orai and practice your speech!\n\nIN THE NEWS\n\n• FastCompany • - “Orai will coach you to add fewer filler words, speak clearly, and at a good pace. It helped its young inventors pitch their way to funding.”\n• TechCrunch • - “An app … to make you a better public speaker!”\n\nKEY FEATURES\n\n• Instant speech feedback using AI:\n- Filler words (um, uh, you know, so)\n- How fast you speak\n- You energy level\n- Confidence\n- Conciseness\n• Micro-lessons on public speaking\n• Detailed performance tracking\n• Audio recording and playback\n• Accurate transcript of what you say\n• Save your previous recordings\n• Ability to share your recording and transcript with friends/colleagues\n• Freestyle mode to practice anytime, anywhere\n• And more!\n\nIf you have any comments or questions, please email support@orai.com\n\nWe love to hear what you think!\n\n~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~\n\nFollow and like us at \n\nTwitter - twitter.com/oraiapp\nFacebook - facebook.com/oraiapp\nInstagram - https://www.instagram.com/orai___\nLinkedIn - linkedin.com/company/orai\nVisit us - orai.com\nSay hi - support@orai.com\n\nPrice may vary by location. Subscriptions will be charged to your iTunes account. Subscriptions are offered for either 1-month ($9.99) or 1-year ($39.99) periods, and will automatically renew unless cancelled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. Any unused portion of a free trial will be forfeited if you purchase a subscription.\n\nManage your subscriptions in Account Settings after purchase.\n\nTerms of Use: https://www.orai.com/tos","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/27/95/1b/27951b85-44a9-206e-aea0-2017d92e5a5d/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-6-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/orai-improve-public-speaking/id1203178170?uo=4","developer":"Orai","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":115,"2":55,"3":154,"4":358,"5":2693}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1127349155","title":"Speech Central AI Voice Reader","store":"app_store","genre":"Productivity","score":4.56749,"ratings":1,"reviewCount":1415,"installs":"N/A","description":"Speech Central is the ultimate text-to-speech app, transforming any text into clear, natural-sounding speech. Listen to articles, eBooks, PDFs, web pages, and documents effortlessly—perfect for productivity, accessibility, and multitasking.\n\nWHY CHOOSE SPEECH CENTRAL?\n\n•  Exceptional Text-to-Speech Experience: \nProprietary engine enhances Apple and AI voices (OpenAI, Azure, Google) with emotion and variation for superior realism.\n\n•  Best PDF Experience: \nAI intelligently removes distractions like footnotes, headers, citations, and web links, preserving your reading flow. Even scanned PDFs import seamlessly with recognized titles.\n\n•  Superior Web Integration:\nListen to full articles and headlines (including RSS feeds). Easily add content by sharing from Safari or browsers.\n\n•  Comprehensive Document Support: \nPDFs (scanned and regular), Microsoft Word (.docx), PowerPoint (.pptx), OpenOffice (.odt, .odp), .html, .mhtml, .webarchive, .txt, .rtf, .md, and ePub eBooks.\n\n•  Hands-Free Convenience:\nListen during commuting, exercise, or daily chores and save valuable time.\n\n•  No Subscription Required:\nUnlock all premium features with a simple, one-time upgrade—no hidden fees.\n\n•  Customizable Experience:\nExtensive options for adjusting reading speed, voice preferences, playback controls, and appearance.\n\n•  Accessibility First:\nFully accessible and free with VoiceOver, ideal for visually impaired, dyslexic users, and those managing ADHD or reducing screen time.\n\n•  Multi-Device Sync:\nSeamlessly synchronize playlists and reading positions across Apple devices, including macOS.\n\n• CarPlay Integration:\nEnjoy effortless listening and convenient control directly from your car’s media dashboard.\n\n•  Built-In Knowledge Tools:\nAnnotate and enhance your texts effortlessly, perfect for studying and deep reading.\n\n•  Independent Apple Watch App:\nListen without needing your iPhone nearby.\n\n•  Document Export:\nAnnotated texts exportable to .docx format; text also exportable to audio files.\n\n•  Enhanced Privacy:\nAbsolutely no data collection, even with sync enabled.\n\n•  Health Integration:\nTrack mindfulness time in the Health app.\n\nACCESSIBILITY PROFILES FOR DYSLEXIA, ADHD & VISUAL IMPAIRMENTS\nIndustry-leading, scientifically designed profiles instantly adapt the app, providing a distraction-free, reading-friendly environment specifically tailored for dyslexic users, people managing ADHD, and those with visual impairments. Featuring hundreds of detailed, evidence-based adjustments, Speech Central is the only text-to-speech app that deeply customizes the reading experience to these needs.\n\nFREE FOR SCHOOLS\nCommitted to empowering every child to unlock their full potential, Speech Central is completely free when deployed through Apple School Manager as a managed app. Research shows up to 40% of students can improve academic performance with text-to-speech solutions. Speech Central brings these powerful accessibility tools directly into classrooms, benefitting all students.\n\nWHO BENEFITS FROM SPEECH CENTRAL?\n- Busy professionals converting articles and reports to audio.\n- Students and researchers listening to textbooks, papers, and PDFs.\n- Users requiring assistive technologies for dyslexia, visual impairment, or ADHD.\n- Anyone preferring hands-free, distraction-free multitasking.\n\nDownload now and unlock the ultimate text-to-speech experience!\n\nNotes:\n- Free version limited by the number of daily articles; unlimited access available with Pro upgrade.\n- Some features require the latest OS version.\n- License valid only on iOS/watchOS; separate licenses required for other platforms.\n- DRM-protected books (e.g. Kindle) are incompatible.\n- AI features may occasionally perform unexpectedly.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/e9/ae/b4/e9aeb4b1-dfb9-3d5c-8fa3-f76a64064ea2/SCIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-sRGB-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/speech-central-ai-voice-reader/id1127349155?uo=4","developer":"Labsii","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":58,"2":26,"3":64,"4":174,"5":1093}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1061319002","title":"Narrator's Voice","store":"app_store","genre":"Productivity","score":4.54517,"ratings":9,"reviewCount":9874,"installs":"N/A","description":"New version of Narrator’s Voice: AI Text to Speech\n• New ultra-realistic AI voices with professional dubbing quality\n• ElevenLabs integration for human-like narration\n• App fully rebuilt from scratch: faster, lighter, and more stable\n• Simpler, more intuitive interface to create audio in seconds\n\nDownload now and turn any text into professional-quality voice.\nGo check it out - it’s absolutely amazing!\n\nNarrator’s Voice app lets you create and share amusing messages using a narrator’s voice of your choice.\nWith a wide range of languages and reliable, pleasant sounding voices.\nSimply speak or type a message, then choose the language, voice and any special effects for the app to use.\nThe end result is a customized narration of your original message, which you can share as desired.\nVideos are one of the hottest projects for Narrator’s Voice, letting the narrator explain or comment on whatever’s happening on the screen. In fact, many people have been using the Narrator’s Voice app to add audio to their YouTube and TikTok videos, giving them a distinct voice that enhances the overall video’s vibe.\nCan be equally successful when used with still images, slide shows, e-learning projects, or anything else that could benefit from useful commentary or clarification.\nCreate voiceovers for your videos easily.\nPeople are sharing it in droves.Millions are using it, and many are thrilled with it.\n\n==FEATURES==\n- Convert text to audio file MP3 or video MP4 and share on social networks\n- Create or open text file, read aloud it, or export/share text as audio/video file.\n- Your phone will speak what you type.\n- With many voices with effects in many languages.\n- Provides expressive and natural sounding voices.\n- Make funny messages with your friends TIMELINE.\n- Best text to voice and text to speech (TTS) app\n- Include pinksheep voice (pink sheep), MLG voice - Daniel UK, CORTANA voice and others...\n- Recommended by YouTubers [they uses this app]\n- Works offline after save audio\n- Great for YouTube and TikTok videos\n- Text to Speech, Read Aloud TTS\n- Create voiceovers for your videos.\n- Voice your texts naturally and realistically\n- ElevenLabs voices\n- Now you have access to the world’s most advanced AI voices - with professional dubbing quality!\n\nTerms of use: https://escolhatecnologia.page.link/terms\nPolicy privacy: https://www.escolhatecnologia.com.br/privacy-policy/privacy.html","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/12/93/e4/1293e436-98e4-2e9c-2b89-456a547ae05e/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-11-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/narrators-voice/id1061319002?uo=4","developer":"Escolha Tecnologia LTDA - ME","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":495,"2":217,"3":400,"4":1060,"5":7702}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1139762358","title":"Speech Assistant AAC","store":"app_store","genre":"Medical","score":4.5914,"ratings":93,"reviewCount":93,"installs":"N/A","description":"Speech Assistant AAC is a text-to-speech app designed for people who are speech impaired, for example due to Aphasia, MND/ALS, Autism, Stroke, Cerebral Palsy or other speech problems.\n\nWith the app you can create categories and save phrases on buttons for quick access and easy communication. You can also type messages using the iOS keyboard.\n\nThe app is affordable with a one-time payment and no subscription.\n\nKey features\n• Easy to use and fully customizable to your needs and preferences.\n• Categories and subcategories to organize your phrases.\n• History feature to quickly access previously entered phrases.\n• Option to add symbols, emoji or photos to the buttons.\n• Full screen mode to display your messages in large font.\n• Autocomplete feature to display phrase suggestions in a drop-down list.\n• Tabs for multiple conversations.\n• Designed for iPhone and iPad, supports both portrait and landscape orientation.\n• Supports Apple Watch.\n• Backup to iCloud, Mail or AirDrop.\n\nVoices\n• You can choose a voice from any of the iOS system voices.\n• Supports ElevenLabs voices, giving you the option to use highly realistic AI professional voice clones.\n• Supports Apple's Personal Voice.\n• Option to create voice recordings for the buttons and to import voice recordings.\n\nPhone calls\n• The app can also be used while making Phone and FaceTime calls.\n• This works with iOS system voices and with iOS 18 also with ElevenLabs voices and regular recordings (app setting).\n\nCategories and phrases\n• Add, change or delete your own (sub)categories and phrases.\n• You can create an unlimited number of categories to organize your phrases for quick access.\n• Create user profiles with their own categories, phrases and settings for multi-language support or different individuals.\n• Easily edit category and phrase buttons with a long press.\n• With Backup to iCloud or AirDrop you can transfer your categories and phrases to another iPhone/iPad.\n\nFully Customizable\n• The size of the buttons, the textbox and the text can be adjusted.\n• The app has various color schemes and you can also create a personal color scheme.\n• You can change the order of the buttons with drag and drop.\n\nFull screen\n• Show your message full screen with a very large font.\n• Useful for communicating in a noisy environment.\n• You can rotate the text to show your message to the person opposite of you.\n\nSpeech\n• The rate and pitch of the speech can be adjusted.\n• Option to speak each Word or Character directly while typing.\n• Optional highlighting of the spoken words.\n• Pause and resume speaking by tapping the speak button (optional setting).\n\nApple Watch\n• The Watch app can especially be useful for communicating short messages.\n• On the go, you don't have to pick up your phone and can quicky communicate with the app on your wrist.\n\nOther features\n• Button to share your message to mail, text and social media.\n• Connect a bluetooth keyboard and create shortcuts for actions.\n• A custom keyboard can be enabled in the settings with customizable size, color and layout. \n• Abbreviations expansion to reduce keystrokes.\n• Attention sound button on Main and Full screen.\n• Option to select symbols from the set of 3400 Mulberry Symbols (mulberrysymbols.org).\n\nAbout the app\n• This app is developed by ASoft.\n• The app does not collect any data, so all your conversations stay private.\n• One-time payment, there is no subscription fee.\n• The app has won an innovation award: The Vodafone Mobiles For Good Challenge.\n• The app does not require an internet connection.\n• For feedback or questions, please contact: speechassistant@asoft.nl.\n• On www.asoft.nl you can find more information such as a user manual.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/c9/dd/34/c9dd34ec-a0cb-aedc-0338-498bc3e37d9f/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-10-0-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/speech-assistant-aac/id1139762358?uo=4","developer":"Ton Schalke","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":24.99,"free":false,"histogram":{"1":1,"2":3,"3":7,"4":11,"5":71}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6745208857","title":"Communication Skills: PatterAI","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.56515,"ratings":2,"reviewCount":2187,"installs":"N/A","description":"PatterAI is your all-in-one communication coach, helping you become more articulate, clear, and confident in how you speak.\n\nPatterAI is more then just a public speaking app. It’s for those who want to improve their communication skills, public speaking, and voice delivery. PatterAI offers a structured, habit-forming way to sharpen how you express yourself with just a few minutes a day.\n\nThink of PatterAI as your personal guide to better speaking. In just a few minutes each day, you can practice exercises designed to make your voice clearer and your words more impactful.\n\nKey features:\n\nDaily Vocal Training:\nVoice is a powerful tool. We’ll give you simple, expert-designed exercises to improve how you sound. Work on speaking more clearly, strengthen your voice, and find a natural rhythm in your speech. It’s like having a voice coach in your pocket.\n→ Improve your pronunciation, articulation, and vocal range\n→ Build a stronger presence with your voice training routine\n→ Perfect your speech with a smart AI voice coach and trainer in your pocket\n\nImpromptu Speaking Challenges:\nThink fast, speak well. Daily impromptu challenges give you fun and interesting topics to talk about. This is a great way to get comfortable with spontaneous conversations, whether you’re at a party or in a job interview.\n→ Perfect for improving social skills, especially in unplanned moments\n→ Strengthen your ability to speak eloquently under pressure\n\nReal-Life Conversation Practice:\n\nPractice realistic scenarios and develop better flow, word choice, and delivery. Whether it’s making small talk, giving feedback, or leading a team, PatterAI helps you get better with real conversation starters.\n→ Learn how to start a conversation with confidence\n→ Get better at icebreakers, conversation shakers, and social cues\n\nWhy Choose PatterAI?\nMany apps focus on just learning new words. We believe the best way to improve is by actually speaking. Whether you want to feel more confident in social situations, prepare for a big presentation, or simply be a more effective communicator, PatterAI is here to support you.\n\nPatterAI is for you if you want to:\n- Feel more confident when you speak.\n- Get your point across more clearly.\n- Prepare for interviews or public speaking events.\n- Improve your social skills and conversation skills.\n- Speak with a stronger and calm voice.\n- Cut down filler words like “ums” and “ahs.”\n\nWhat You’ll Improve With PatterAI\n- Communication skills for professional and personal life\n- Everyday conversations and structured responses\n- Public speaking with confidence and grace\n- Sharpening articulation, tone, and vocal warmth\n- Elevating your presence through a strong vocal image\n- Reducing overused fillers and building thoughtful flow\n\nKey Features\n- Speech feedback using AI\n- Filler words detection\n- Vocal clarity detection\n- Role play to improve small talks\n- Lessons on public speaking\n- Performance and streak tracking\n- Accurate transcript of your session\n- Access to community of public speakers\n- and much more!\n\nPatterAI includes both free and premium content. You can start practising for free and explore foundational lessons designed to build confidence in everyday interactions. A subscription unlocks access to advanced lessons, personalized feedback, and deeper conversation challenges tailored to your goals. Premium users also gain access to exclusive practice scenarios, detailed progress tracking, and adaptive learning paths that adjust based on your performance.\n\nDownload PatterAI and start your journey to becoming a more confident, articulate communicator. Our users report significant reductions in social anxiety and enhanced professional presence.\n\nPractice. Improve. Speak Better.\n\nPrivacy Policy: https://patterai.app/privacy-policy\nTerms of Service: https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/\nContact us: support@patterai.app","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/ba/b7/4d/bab74db3-08d4-5e0c-261f-f56d55fc7140/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-11-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/communication-skills-patterai/id6745208857?uo=4","developer":"Het Thummar","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":77,"2":35,"3":152,"4":234,"5":1689}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"917672170","title":"WebOutLoud - Text to Speech","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.625,"ratings":736,"reviewCount":736,"installs":"N/A","description":"Listen to websites, PDFs, EPUBs, any text using text to speech.\n\nNow with a powerful new Safari extension where you can listen to websites without leaving the browser.\n\nOther features include premium voices from Amazon Polly, Microsoft Azure and more, custom pronunciations, AI summaries, PDF text-to-speech, offline capabilities, desktop integration, iCloud sync and Dark Mode.*\n\nYou can save articles, e-novels, PDFs and EPUBs to read later, or listen to them one after another in a playlist.\n\nNo Longer Limited to Websites!\n\n- Use WebOutLoud to listen to EPUBS and PDFs*. It highlights words as it reads.\n- Use WebOutLoud to read aloud any text on your device.\n- Organize your saved content into collections.\n- Custom substitutions including regular expression support\n- AI content summaries. Instantly summarize documents and websites up to 300 pages in length.*\n\nAbout WebOutLoud's Leading Website Reader:\n\nIt's simple! Just navigate to any web page using the in-app web browser and touch play. Web Out Loud will read web pages using a wide selection of voices, from those freely available on your device to the high quality premium voices from Amazon Polly, Microsoft Azure, Google Cloud and others.\n\nReading requires way too much of your attention. Multitask like a champ! Listen to articles in your car or while you work.\n\n- Reads any web page, PDF or text document\n- Highlights words as it reads\n- Scrolls the page automatically as you follow along\n- Tell the app where to begin reading using Touch Assist, or enable the powerful Reader View to eliminate ads and isolate readable content automatically.\n- Dozens of supported languages, each with their own unique voice\n- Chrome and mobile Safari browser integration\n- Custom pronunciations and word substitution\n- AMP link blocking\n- Custom pronunciations and substitutions\n\nBut how does it know what to read!?!? WebOutLoud uses hand-crafted AI to read web pages to you Out Loud.\n\n----------------------\n\n* PLEASE NOTE:\n\nPDF Text to Speech requires, and custom substitutions require a Basic subscription. \n\nA Premium subscription is required for AI content summaries and premium voices (i.e. voices by Amazon Polly, Microsoft Azure and others).\n\nListening to web pages and text using the voices that are built-in to your device is free with an occasional ad.\n\n----------------------\n\nWebOutLoud Full Version is a 1-year auto-renewable subscription\nPayment will be charged to iTunes Account at confirmation of purchase.\nSubscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period.\nAccount will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period.\nYou can turn off auto-renew up to 24 hours before your next subscription payment is due via your App Store settings page.\nSubscriptions may be managed by the user and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the user's Account Settings after purchase.\n\nTerms of Service\nhttp://wol.bretlester.com/terms_of_service.html\n\nPrivacy Policy\nhttp://wol.bretlester.com/privacy_policy.html","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/04/c8/43/04c84350-b978-9756-06c6-133774d1b74a/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-0-sRGB-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/weboutloud-text-to-speech/id917672170?uo=4","developer":"Bret Lester","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":35,"2":15,"3":16,"4":59,"5":611}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1158877342","title":"Grammarly: AI Keyboard & Notes","store":"app_store","genre":"Productivity","score":4.66085,"ratings":208,"reviewCount":208966,"installs":"N/A","description":"Instantly and easily create smart, polished writing with the Grammarly Keyboard. Designed to deliver real-time writing feedback and provide AI assistance, the Grammarly Keyboard works directly in your iPhone and iPad apps, no copy and paste required. \n\nWhen you join the millions of people using the Grammarly Keyboard, you’ll benefit from: \n\nAn easy-to-use AI keyboard that works in all your apps\n    - Spelling, grammar, and conciseness suggestions in English, Spanish, French, German, Portuguese, and Italian\n    - Vocabulary and clarity recommendations (Premium only)\n    - Tone detection\n    - Tone transformations (Premium only)\n    - Multi-word text predictions\n    - Smart autocorrect, synonyms, and swipe typing\n    - Emoji predictions and search bar\n\nGenerative AI rewrites\n    - New versions of your entire message in a couple of taps\n    - Versions adjust for length, fluency, tone, and more\n    - Rewrites are supported in 19 different languages\n    - Works in all your favorite apps\n\nA document editor for long-form writing and notes\n    - Comprehensive writing feedback\n    - Cloud-based document management\n    - Personal writing statistics\n    - Plagiarism and AI detection\n    - Compatible with hardware keyboards\n\nA Safari extension for typing on websites\n    - Spelling and grammar checker\n\nFurther Improve Your Writing With Grammarly Premium\nGrammarly Premium makes your writing more engaging and effective with advanced suggestions for clarity, conciseness, tone, and vocabulary. Premium works across all your devices; just sign in to enjoy its benefits.\n\nIf you upgrade to a Premium subscription, payments will be charged to the account associated with your Apple ID. Your subscription will automatically renew unless you cancel at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. After purchase, you can manage your subscription by going to your account settings in the App Store.\n\nPrivacy Is Our Priority\nGrammarly practices privacy by design. Your words are your own; we will never rent or sell your data. \n\nUser Trust Guidelines: https://www.grammarly.com/trust\nTerms of Service: https://www.grammarly.com/terms\nPrivacy Policy: https://www.grammarly.com/privacy-policy\nCalifornia Privacy Notice: https://www.grammarly.com/privacy-policy#for-california-users","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/30/49/e3/3049e313-43a9-fb18-7121-dbd4cc58b93d/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-sRGB-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/grammarly-ai-keyboard-notes/id1158877342?uo=4","developer":"Grammarly, Inc","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":8233,"2":3011,"3":6091,"4":16721,"5":174910}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"806819422","title":"Speak • Speech Synthesizer","store":"app_store","genre":"Utilities","score":4.6158,"ratings":3,"reviewCount":3178,"installs":"N/A","description":"Speak brings typed words and sentences to life using your iPhone, iPod or iPad!\n\nFeatures\n• Beautiful, modern and sleek user interface.\n• Sliders to adjust the Volume, Pitch and Rate of the voice.\n• Option to change the accent/language of the voice.\n• Favourite Phrases and Phrase History.\n• Repeat feature let's you specify how many times your would like your phrase repeated.\n• Share Audio feature allows you to send an audio output recording to your friends and family.\n• Loads of settings to allow you to tweak Speak to behave just how you like.\n• Support for Slide Over and Split Screen (on appropriate devices).\n• Background Audio so you can continue listening to your text whilst your device is locked or you're working on something else.\n• VoiceOver support.\n• Connect Speak to a Bluetooth speaker/headphones to broadcast your text even further.\n\nIf you enjoy using Speak, please consider supporting its development by removing remove ads (in-app purchase from the Settings screen).\n\nQuick Tip: If a word doesn't sound quite right, try spelling it phonetically.\n\nMany of Speak's users have lost their ability to speak (often after surgery) and Speak helps to give them a voice again.\n\nSpeak does not require an internet connection, and is always optimised for the latest and greatest devices and software.\n\nHave fun! And feel free to drop me an email with any suggestions or comments: loic@loic.tech\n\nIf you find Speak useful or fun please take a moment to give it a quick review!","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/19/59/0a/19590a4d-d401-2ec4-2f8b-c4c7123da1cc/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-11-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/speak-speech-synthesizer/id806819422?uo=4","developer":"Loic Verrall","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":128,"2":41,"3":136,"4":314,"5":2559}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6502340091","title":"Text to Speech - Listen AI","store":"app_store","genre":"Productivity","score":4.44198,"ratings":3,"reviewCount":3577,"installs":"N/A","description":"Listen AI: Unveiling the Power of Text-to-Speech\n\nTurn Text into Speech and Open Your Ears to the Written Word\n\nListen AI isn't just a text-to-speech tool, it's your effortless companion for a world of information, narrated at your pace. Here's how Listen AI elevates your experience:\n\nUnmatched Vocal Majesty: Immerse yourself in a variety of crystal-clear, expressive voices that blur the line between human and machine. Choose from a range of accents and personalities to find the perfect narrator for any content, be it a casual blog post or a formal report.\n\nCustomization at Your Fingertips: Tailor your listening experience to your preferences. Adjust the speaking rate to match your comprehension speed, or fine-tune the volume for optimal comfort.\n\nEffortless Integration: Forget copy-pasting. Listen AI seamlessly converts text from documents and web pages into spoken content. Highlight a passage on a website, a section in a PDF, or an entire document, and Listen AI will bring it to life with its captivating narration.\n\nMultitasking Masterclass: Free up your eyes and ears for other activities. Listen to articles, web pages, and PDFs while you exercise, commute, cook, or complete chores. Listen AI lets you learn and stay informed while you conquer your to-do list.\n\nAccessibility Champion: Listen AI is a game-changer for those with visual impairments or learning disabilities. Reading lengthy documents or educational materials can be a challenge. Listen AI transforms text into an engaging audio experience, making learning and information access more accessible than ever before.\n\nListen AI: It's not just reading, it's experiencing.\n\nTerms and Conditions: https://static.listenai.app/terms-conditions-en.html\nPrivacy Policy: https://static.listenai.app/privacy-en.html\nCommunity Guidelines: https://static.listenai.app/community-guidelines-en.html","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/e0/65/93/e06593e5-01b1-4198-c57c-3c3a679c3bce/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007ephone-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/text-to-speech-listen-ai/id6502340091?uo=4","developer":"DEEP FLOW SOFTWARE SERVICES","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":336,"2":71,"3":105,"4":229,"5":2836}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1488071175","title":"Stamurai: Stuttering Treatment","store":"app_store","genre":"Health & Fitness","score":4.67478,"ratings":781,"reviewCount":781,"installs":"N/A","description":"**SUPPORTED BY** Google for Startups, Prosus, Mphasis, Accel, ZS and Social Alpha, Stamurai is a one-stop stuttering treatment app for all ages. \nStuttering aka stammering is a speech disorder that demands persistence and practice. Stamurai provides the motivation and engagement you need to persevere on the journey towards fluent and confident speech. \nSet a daily reminder and practice your speech exercises without fail! \nIt is an app for people who stutter by people who stutter, complete with guidance from speech language pathologists and speech therapists. \nLearn all there is to know about stuttering causes, stuttering treatment and speech therapy. Practice and apply stuttering modification techniques and fluency shaping strategies in your speech during day-to-day conversations. \nStamurai comes with the complete tutorial for over 30 speech exercises including pausing, pull outs, preparatory sets, cancellations, light articulatory contacts, easy onsets, diaphragmatic breathing and slowed speech. \nHere’s what you can do with Stamurai –\n1. You can practice reading aloud, record your voice and observe the disfluencies. \n2. Relax with guided meditations. These will teach you coastal breathing techniques ubiquitous for fluency. \n3. Practice breathing exercises and controlled exhalation while speaking. \n4. Understand function and challenges of your speech mechanism by answering simple questions.  5. Use delayed auditory feedback (DAF) to compensate for auditory processing defects6. Log daily ratings such as those used in Lidcombe Program\nJoin moderated Group Sessions for discussing the new techniques you have learned and connecting with other Stamurai users from across the globe. Perform real life practice but in a safe environment.\nHow to use Stamurai – Stammering & Stuttering Speech Therapy\n1. Download and launch the stuttering therapy app\n2. Answer a few questions about your speech disorder to customise therapy regimen\n3. Start daily speech exercises personalized for you \n4. Learn about the stammering treatment, perform daily speech practice and learn to speak fluently\n5. Follow your progress based on your daily performance\nFeatures of Stamurai – Stammering & Stuttering Speech Therapy\n1. Simple and easy speech-language therapy app design\n2. Assessment options for evaluating the severity of stuttering  \n3. Customized stammering treatment plans based on your speech disorder\n4. Engaging speech exercises designed by speech pathology experts \n5. Overview of personalized weekly and monthly language therapy plans \n6. Estimated speech therapy timeline for seeing results\n7. Progress monitoring options based on your daily app use8. Tools such as delayed auditory feedback (DAF), meditation, breathing exercises for stuttering, counselling strategies.\nDownload and use Stamurai – Stammering & Stuttering Speech Therapy today!\nSTAMURAI SUBSCRIPTION TERMS\nStamurai offers a 7-day free trial as well as a basic free version.\nIf you choose to subscribe, you will be charged a yearly or monthly subscription fee as per your choice according to your country. The subscription fee will be shown in the app before you complete the payment. Your subscription will automatically renew at the end of each subscription term, unless auto-renewal is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the term. Subscription renewals cost the same as the original subscription, and your credit card will be charged through your iTunes account at confirmation of purchase.\nYou may manage your subscription and turn off auto-renewal at any time after purchase by going to your iTunes Account Settings. Refunds will not be given for any unused portion of the term.\nFor additional information, please read our Terms of Service (https://stamurai.com/terms-service.html) and Privacy Policy (https://stamurai.com/privacy-policy.html).","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple126/v4/36/39/ad/3639ad4c-272d-cf80-887a-7a5956d949db/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-10-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/stamurai-stuttering-treatment/id1488071175?uo=4","developer":"Stamurai","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":31,"2":8,"3":20,"4":66,"5":656}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1149425482","title":"Noted: Record & AI Transcribe","store":"app_store","genre":"Productivity","score":4.47413,"ratings":3,"reviewCount":3421,"installs":"N/A","description":"Meet Noted: Your Essential Audio Note-Taking Study Tool & Meeting Companion\n\nUnlock the power of Noted, the ultimate voice recorder and note app, designed to simplify your study and work life. Record, transcribe, and organize all in one place. Don’t let important details slip away—Noted captures every word, so you can focus on what really matters.\n\n\nKEY FEATURES:\n\n• Audio Transcription: Convert audio or video files into precise text\n• Time-Stamped Notes: Link important moments in your audio to specific points in your notes for quick access\n• Intelligent Playback: Skip silences and unwanted noise with advanced Machine Learning features\n• Voice Typing: Dictate your notes and convert speech to text instantly\n• Crystal-Clear Recording: Capture audio with background noise reduction, even in busy places\n• Easy Sharing: Share via iCloud, PDF, TXT, M4A, or web links\n• Cross-Device Sync: Access notes on iPhone, iPad, Mac and even Apple Watch via iCloud. \n• Reminders: Schedule revision alerts for meetings, lectures, or exams\n• Custom Themes: Personalize your experience with unique theme options\n• Quick Access Widgets: Record right from your home screen\n• Secure Notes: Lock notes for extra privacy\n• Multi-Language Support: Available in 18 languages and counting\n\nWhy Noted? \nWhether you’re a student capturing every lecture or a professional aiming to stay organized, Noted keeps all your notes in one searchable, secure place. Say goodbye to scattered notes and missed details.\n\nBoost Your Productivity Today!\nTry Noted for free with a 7-day trial and experience note-taking without the hassle. Download now and see why it’s the app you’ll rely on daily!\n\nNoted offers the following subscription options (prices may vary by location):\n• Free 7-Day Trial with Yearly plan\n• Monthly Plan: Auto-renews, Flexible with full access (no trial)\n• Lifetime Access: One-time purchase for permanent full access (no trial)\n\nManage Subscriptions:\n• Payment charged to your App Store account after the free trial ends\n• Subscriptions auto-renew unless canceled 24 hours before the period ends\n• Unused trial periods are forfeited when the subscription starts\n• Manage your subscription in Noted Account Settings or App Store Account Settings\n\nFamily Sharing:\n• Available on Yearly plans\n\nFor support, reach out at support@notedapp.io.\n\nFollow Us:\nTikTok: @notedapp\nX: @EverythingNoted\nInstagram: @notedapp\nFacebook: everythingnoted\n\nPrivacy Policy: https://www.notedapp.io/privacy-policy/\nTerms of Service: https://www.notedapp.io/terms-of-use/","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/e2/b2/e6/e2b2e6c7-4a80-b2a2-c829-21fa76db65b3/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-0-0-1-0-0-0-85-220-0.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/noted-record-ai-transcribe/id1149425482?uo=4","developer":"Digital Workroom Ltd","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":248,"2":78,"3":128,"4":317,"5":2650}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1239150966","title":"Voice Dictation - Speechy Lite","store":"app_store","genre":"Business","score":4.62586,"ratings":2,"reviewCount":2908,"installs":"N/A","description":"Speechy is the powerful, real-time dictation solution you’ve been looking for! Based on the latest artificial intelligence and using a powerful speech recognition engine, Speechy will easily transcribe your words and thoughts, helping you accomplish more in less time!\n\nUsing Speechy, your words will be magically transcribed into text without your ever needing to touch a keyboard. Save yourself hours of repetitive stress, elbow and wrist injuries brought on by endless and tedious typing. Now you can use the power of your voice to create your words! It also helps pronunciation practice of foreign language learning and minutes of meeting memo.\n\n\nSpeechy not only transcribes your words, but also records your VOICE so you can refer to the original recording later! Plus, you can easily share your text and audio files later! (Works with Evernote, Dropbox, Google Drive, OneDrive, Facebook, Twitter, Snapchat, WhatsApp and other iOS supported sharing apps.)\n\nWhether you’re a professional writer, doctor, lawyer, disabled or somehow prevented from traditional typing, Speechy will swiftly solve your transcription problems and help you achieve your writing goals today!\n\nAnd Speechy doesn’t stop there! Speechy is global-focused, and will not only recognize your native language (currently more than 88 languages supported, and growing), but it will also TRANSLATE your dictated texts into other languages! So no matter where you are in the world or who you need to communicate with, Speechy will help make it happen!\n\n \n\nTop Speechy Benefits:\n\n・Unlimited recognition duration (Speechy won’t time out like Siri or some “other” voice recognition apps)(Pro Version)\n\n・Records your audio simultaneously\n・Immediate playback of recordings\n・Unlimited save & edits\n・Easy, unlimited sharing of text and audio\n・Transcribed text can be edited directly\n・Ideal for both individual and group transcription\n・Background support for voice recognition\n・Translates your speech into other languages\n・Allows you to add custom vocabulary words\n・Voice-to-text by audio files.\n・On-device Speech Recognition\n\nWho Should Use Speechy?\n\n1. Reporters: Interviews, conversations and more are easily recorded and transcribed, preserving the original audio.\n\n2. Writers: Novelists, Authors, Wattpad and fanfiction users can all write in their true voice, capturing their moments of inspiration anytime, anywhere.\n\n3. Professionals: Doctors, lawyers, managers, etc. Easily transcribe your daily tasks, notes, conference calls, letters and more! Your voice makes it happen!\n\n4. Elderly or Disabled: Eliminates slow typing, commonly misspelled words or embarrassing composition mistakes. Speechy makes it convenient and easy to send and share your words with those you love.\n\n5. Language Students: Easily learn and master new words and languages by practicing dictation with Speechy!\n\n► Speechy’s Currently Supported Speech Recognition Languages: Arabic, Cantonese, Catalan, Chinese, Croatian, Czech, Danish, Dutch, English, Finnish, French, German, Greek, Hebrew, Hindi, Hungarian, Indonesian, Italian, Japanese, Korean, Malay, Norwegian, Bokmål, Polish, Portuguese, Romanian, Russian, Shanghainese, Slovak, Spanish, Swedish, Thai, Turkish, Ukrainian, Vietnamese.\n\nOffers one auto-renewing subscription options:\n$4.49 per month\n\nThese prices are for United States customers. Pricing in other countries may vary and actual charges may be converted to your local currency depending on the country of residence.\n\nPayment will be charged to iTunes Account at confirmation of purchase. Subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. Account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period at the rate of the selected plan. Subscriptions and auto-renewal may be managed by going to Account Settings after purchase\n\nTerms of service: http://speechy.app/privacy_policy.html\nPrivacy policy: http://speechy.app/terms_of_use.html","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple116/v4/be/4e/53/be4e5320-d456-6850-3f88-bbe44fb0b6b8/AppIcon_Lite-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/voice-dictation-speechy-lite/id1239150966?uo=4","developer":"吉华 郑","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":74,"2":26,"3":122,"4":470,"5":2216}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6738028828","title":"Public Speaking AI","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":5,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":4,"installs":"N/A","description":"Master the art of speaking with confidence and clarity! Our app is designed to help you improve your communication and public speaking skills with real-time, AI-powered feedback. Simply record or upload a video of your speech or presentation, and receive detailed insights into your performance.\n\nFeatures:\n\nVocal Analysis: Get personalized feedback on your vocal tone, pace, and pitch to ensure you're delivering your message effectively.\nVisual Feedback: Improve your body language and eye contact with actionable advice on non-verbal communication.\nDetailed Transcripts: Access an accurate transcript of your speech, complete with key highlights and suggestions for improvement.\nPerfect for students, professionals, and anyone looking to polish their speaking skills, our app helps you become a more impactful, confident communicator.\n\nTerms: https://enginesstudio.tech/terms/speaking\nPrivacy: https://enginesstudio.tech/privacy/speaking","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/0d/a9/59/0da95941-4776-87ea-90bf-fbc8c1885455/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-11-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/public-speaking-ai/id6738028828?uo=4","developer":"Saad Belfqih","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6746377369","title":"Public Speaking Coach: Babli","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.58333,"ratings":12,"reviewCount":12,"installs":"N/A","description":"SPEAK WITH CONFIDENCE IN EVERY SITUATION\n\nBabli is an AI-powered public speaking and speech coach for speech practice, presentation practice, and everyday communication. Choose a scenario, record your answer, and get instant AI feedback to reduce filler words, improve clarity, and build confidence for job interviews, leading meetings, toasts, on-camera speaking, and closing deals.\n\nPRACTICE ACROSS REAL LIFE CATEGORIES AND EARN CERTIFICATES\nBabli includes 100+ guided role play scenarios designed for practical use cases. Master any category to unlock a shareable public speaking certificate of completion.\n\nSOCIAL EVENTS: Toasts, celebrations, and cultural events\n\nJOB INTERVIEWS: Master common questions with strong answer structures\n\nEDUCATION & TEACHING: Explain subjects clearly from school to university\n\nDEBATES & NEGOTIATIONS: Win arguments, express opinions, and handle tough questions\n\nMEDIA & CONTENT CREATION: Press, vlogs, and on-camera speaking for creators and influencers\n\nCAREER & LEADERSHIP: Leading meetings, managing teams, and professional communication\n\nSALES & PITCHING: Pitching products, promotions, and closing deals\n\nSPEECH OF THE DAY\nEvery day you get a unique Speech of the Day with a fresh, interesting scenario, often outside these categories. It keeps training consistent, fun, and challenging.\n\nCUSTOM PRACTICE\nHave an upcoming presentation, job interview, meeting, toast, sales pitch, or difficult conversation? Create your own scenario and practice for your exact situation.\n\nAI FEEDBACK THAT HELPS YOU IMPROVE\nRecord your speech and get instant analysis of filler words (like “um” and “you know”), grammar, pacing, and content clarity, plus targeted suggestions and example rewrites.\n\nOVERCOME SPEAKING ANXIETY IN PRIVATE\nPractice in a pressure-free environment so you can organize your thoughts, stay calm, and improve steadily.\n\nLANGUAGE SUPPORT\nBabli supports English, French, German, Italian, Spanish, Portuguese, Turkish, Japanese, Polish, Czech, and Slovak for both the app interface and speaking practice.\n\nTerms of Use: https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/81/8b/bf/818bbf83-5fcf-b65f-dce9-8a2b588084f3/AppIcon-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-sRGB-85-220-0.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/public-speaking-coach-babli/id6746377369?uo=4","developer":"Sebastian Poliak","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":1,"2":0,"3":0,"4":1,"5":10}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1588273723","title":"MicMentor: Public Speaking","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":4,"installs":"N/A","description":"MicMentor is app that helps you to learn how to become better in public speaking and improve communication skills by using different speech techniques. You will do it faster than you ever thought is possible! Improve pronunciation, and articulation - Start with our accent training & presentation coach!\n\nOur mirror speaker feature with caption-based video from YouTube will make you a better and more confident speaker by getting you constant feedback on what you should improve. With a teleprompter for videos, everything is easier!\n\nHOW DOES IT WORK?\n- Choose Video - Choose a video of your favorite public speaker. Search for a specific thought leader, or explore our video collection.\n- Mark Starting Point - Decide the starting point of the video. You can hit Caption or use the timeline to scroll to your preferred starting time.\n- Mark Ending Point - Set the ending point of the video.\n- Start Mirroring Chosen Speaker - You will be sharpening your presentation in no time! Build your charisma and set goals to keep you motivated.\n\nThe mirror speaker tool is the best way to become a more confident and skilled speaker. Practice presentation speaking in any language!\n\nMAIN FEATURES:\n- Goal Setting - Set your weekly goals for time, sessions, and videos.\n- Goal Tracking - Track your goals and meet them. Keep track of your progress and cultivate habits through daily practice.\n- Achievements - Earn achievements from practicing every week.\n- Search & Explore - Search from a list of YouTube videos or explore from a collection of videos.\n- Recent Videos - View your recent videos to start practicing.\n- Learn Faster - Turn hour-long speech practice into bite-size practice sessions. Practice presentation speaking fast & easy!\n- Captions In Videos - Caption support within videos to read and speak. There is multi-language support.\n- Mirror Speaker Tool - Mirror influential speakers on YouTube. Learn how to present your ideas like a pro.\n- Reduce Anxiety - Speak to a customizable imaginary audience to reduce anxiety.\n- Recording Tool & Teleprompter For Videos - Use a recording tool with a teleprompter feature to practice your speech.\n\nLearn to speak with confidence in any language & improve your communication skills. Have the accent training, and practice presentation speaking - Increase your speaking power!\n\nTAKE ADVANTAGE OF ALL BENEFITS:\n- Learn From the Best - Explore our international video collection of CEO interviews, comedian performances, and TedTalk speeches.\n- Master Different Accents - Instantly pick up the vowel sounds with accent training. Refine and perfect your chosen accent or dialect by mirroring the public speaker or personality that inspires you most. \n- Increase Speaking Confidence - You can take our app with you anywhere. Train and master your public speaking skills, anytime and anywhere.\n- Build a Habit To Practice Consistently - Set weekly goals and track your progress. MicMentor is the ultimate new mobile coaching system to deliver fast results.\n\nUSE YOUR VOICE TO WIN PEOPLE OVER\n\nNow you can hack public speaking and conversation as a non-native speaker with a simple and effective tool. Practice presentation speaking anytime, anywhere with MicMentor.\n\nThis isn’t a language learning app. It’s about helping you to communicate with confidence in your non-native workplace. You’re in the right place if you want to wow an audience, win a promotion, or apply for that new position you’ve had your eye on.\n\nDownload MicMentor, the best tool to practice and improve your public speaking & communication skills in one place! Accent training & presentation speaking coach at your fingertips - Increase your speaking power!\n\nPrivacy Policy: https://micmentor.app/privacy-policy.html\nTerms of Use: https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/a3/14/68/a3146866-687e-4c8b-aaf5-0d8c86ff85cf/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/micmentor-public-speaking/id1588273723?uo=4","developer":"Honu Lab LLC","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6739273196","title":"SayNow AI: Speech, Voice Coach","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":5,"ratings":5,"reviewCount":5,"installs":"N/A","description":"SayNow AI is your ultimate Public Speaking and Communication companion. Transform your voice, boost your confidence, and master professional presentations—all through interactive AI-powered training. Whether you’re preparing for a job interview, honing your accent, or aiming to deliver a flawless speech, SayNow AI helps you speak with clarity and impact!\n\nKey Features\n\n1. Personalized Learning  \n   - Choose scenarios or frameworks that match your goals  \n   - Practice in short bursts or in-depth sessions  \n   - Receive instant AI recommendations to refine each attempt\n\n2. Structured Scenarios  \n   - Public Speaking & Job Interviews  \n   - Salary Negotiations & Business Pitches  \n   - Daily Social Conversation & Networking  \n   - Advanced Presentation Skills for Professionals\n\n3. Framework-Based Guidance  \n   - STAR Method for interview prep  \n   - AIDA Model for persuasive messaging  \n   - Pyramid Principle for logical structures  \n   - 5W1H for comprehensive analysis\n\n4. AI-Powered Analysis  \n   - Live feedback on filler words, fluency, and articulation  \n   - Suggestions for confident tone and body language cues  \n   - Speech metrics for deeper insights\n\n5. Track Your Growth  \n   - Detailed performance metrics over time  \n   - Identify patterns, set milestones, and celebrate wins  \n   - Perfect for ongoing personal and professional development\n\n\nHow It Works\n\n1. Select a Scenario or Framework  \n   Target the exact skill or situation you want to improve.\n\n2. Start Practicing  \n   Speak freely or follow guided prompts and outlines.\n\n3. Instant AI Feedback  \n   Identify strengths, fix weaknesses, and iterate on the spot.\n\n4. Progress & Analytics  \n   Monitor your improvements with in-app stats and unlock advanced insights.\n\n\nWho Benefits\n\n- Job Seekers: Stand out in interviews and negotiate with poise  \n- Professionals: Excel in meetings, sales pitches, and leadership roles  \n- Students: Sharpen oral exam or debate performance  \n- Speakers & Trainers: Refine every aspect of your presentation  \n- Language Learners: Enhance English fluency and reduce accent barriers\n\n\nWhy Choose SayNow AI\n\n- Real-Time AI Feedback  \n  Get immediate insights on pacing, tone, and clarity to pinpoint your strengths and areas for growth.\n\n- Speech & Communication Skills  \n  Tackle a wide range of scenarios—from casual conversations to formal business presentations.\n\n- Accent & Voice Coach  \n  Improve pronunciation and accent with targeted exercises designed by communication experts.\n\n- Professional Frameworks  \n  Learn proven methods like STAR, Pyramid Principle, 5W1H, and AIDA to structure compelling talks.\n\n- Customized Practice Paths  \n  Tailor your training according to your level—beginner, intermediate, or advanced—and track your progress.\n\n\nReady to Speak with Confidence?\nDownload SayNow AI and embark on your journey to fearless public speaking and effective communication today!\n\nSupport: support@saynow.ai\nWebsite: https://saynow.ai\nPrivacy Policy: https://saynow.ai/privacy-policy\nTerms of Service: https://saynow.ai/terms-of-service","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/ea/9a/7f/ea9a7f8f-286a-4ff5-d942-9343b6a76811/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-11-0-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/saynow-ai-speech-voice-coach/id6739273196?uo=4","developer":"Geekclo Co., Ltd.","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":5}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1081494198","title":"Call Simulator-Speech Practice","store":"app_store","genre":"Utilities","score":4.54974,"ratings":28,"reviewCount":28224,"installs":"N/A","description":"This app is a scenario-based tool for eloquence practice. \n\nIt simulates various phone call situations to help you hone your telephone communication skills. \n\nIf you get nervous during phone interviews, try this app to consistently improve your eloquence across different scenarios.\n\n\nAuto-Renewable subscription Note：\nThis app is free but you can also upgrade to VIP for full access to  features through an auto-renewing subscription.Price may vary by location.\n\nSubscriptions for VIP will be charged to your credit card through your iTunes account. Your subscription will automatically renew unless canceled at least 24-hours before the end of the current period. You will not be able to cancel a subscription during the active period. You can manage your subscriptions in the Account Settings after purchase.\n\nTerms of Use : https://yuedong56.github.io/2019/01/02/Terms%20of%20VIP%20Service/\nPrivacy Policy : https://yuedong56.github.io/2019/01/02/Privacy%20Policy/","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/e7/69/bb/e769bb75-a11a-5099-78f3-318cb75d905f/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007ephone-0-1-0-sRGB-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/call-simulator-speech-practice/id1081494198?uo=4","developer":"雪景 潘","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":937,"2":596,"3":1667,"4":3838,"5":21186}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1604386676","title":"Lola Speak: English Practice","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.78206,"ratings":14,"reviewCount":14706,"installs":"N/A","description":"Practice speaking English in real life situations! Be the hero in our interactive series. Move the story forward by speaking English.\n\n—\n\nHow does Lola Speak help me learn English?\n\nMany English learners already know a lot of grammar and vocabulary, but are afraid to actually speak English. Why? Many are embarrassed to make mistakes, or mispronounce words. \n\nLola Speak provides a safe environment to practice real life conversations. You can repeat as many times as you like. You can practice communicating in a life-like setting, but without the pressure and stress. You can build confidence to communicate in English. \n\n—\n\nHow will I know if I am speaking correctly?\n\nOur AI provides instant feedback on your pronunciation. \n\nAlso, you can listen to your own audio and recordings by native speakers to learn to sound more like a native.\n\n—\n\nIs this going to be fun?\n\nFrom plot driven stories (Welcome to Hollywood) to series helping you navigate specific situations (Job Interview) you will be immersed in American English and culture. We think you won't want to stop - all while speaking English to move the stories forward!\n\n—\n\nHow often is the content updated?\n\nWe expect to release new series monthly covering different topics & English speaker levels from basic to advanced.\n\n__\n\nSUBSCRIPTION PRICING AND TERMS\n\nThe subscription will automatically renew unless turned off in your iTunes Account Settings at least 24 hours before the current period ends. You can go to your iTunes Account settings to manage your subscription and turn off auto-renew. Your iTunes Account will be charged when the purchase is confirmed. If you subscribe before your free trial ends, the rest of your free trial period will be forfeited as soon as your purchase is confirmed.\n\nRead the terms and privacy policy here:\n\nhttps://lolaspeak.com/terms","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/f3/6f/63/f36f63c3-f262-1c59-27b1-7f5e0002bf47/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007ephone-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/lola-speak-english-practice/id1604386676?uo=4","developer":"Wiseport Ltd","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":249,"2":156,"3":407,"4":927,"5":12967}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6744645684","title":"Public Speaking Coach","store":"app_store","genre":"Productivity","score":4.68966,"ratings":29,"reviewCount":29,"installs":"N/A","description":"Master Public Speaking with AI-Powered Coaching\n\nNervous about speaking in front of a crowd? Want to boost your confidence in meetings, presentations, or interviews? Public Speaking: AI Coach is your personal communication trainer—built to help you speak clearly, confidently, and effectively.\n\nDesigned for all skill levels, our app offers smart, guided practice sessions, AI feedback, and custom lessons that grow with you.\n\nTop Features\n\nDashboard Overview\nTrack your lesson progress, speaking trends, and daily prompts—all from a clean, easy-to-use dashboard. See your growth at a glance.\n\nProgressive Lesson Plans\nFollow structured learning paths designed to improve your speaking skills—from beginner tips to advanced public speaking techniques.\n\nAI-Powered Analysis\nReceive instant, personalized feedback after every practice session. Our AI breaks down your performance across key metrics like:\n- Filler words\n- Pauses\n- Confidence\n- Energy\n- Speech pace\nand more....\n\nReal-Life Practice Scenarios\nTrain in practical situations like:\n- Job interviews\n- Business meetings\n- Pitches\n- Keynote speeches\n- Daily conversations\nand more...\n\nEach scenario includes curated prompts to help you get started on your journey of sounding natural and professional.\n\nCompare Your Progress\nGet a visual view of your improvement. See how your current session compares with previous ones. Track confidence, delivery, and clarity over time.\n\n\nWhy Users Love Public Speaking?\n- Easy to use\n- Instant AI feedback\n- Personalized lessons\n- Real results over time\n- Helps reduce stage fright\n- Great for professionals, students, job seekers and anyone that wants to improve their public speaking skills\n\n\n\nWho Is It For?\nWhether you're preparing for a TED-style talk or just want to sound more confident on Zoom calls, this app is for:\n\n- Professionals & leaders\n- Job seekers\n- ESL learners\n- Students & educators\n- Anyone who wants to speak better\n\n\nStart Speaking Better Today\nDownload Public Speaking now and take the first step toward becoming a more confident, persuasive communicator. Practice daily. Improve continuously. Impress always.\n\nSubscription Information\n\n\n– Public Speaking sessions are limited and you need a subscription for unlimited access\n– Subscription Length: Weekly and Yearly\n– Free Trial: If offered, it will automatically convert to a paid subscription unless canceled.\n– Payment: Charged to your Apple ID account at confirmation of purchase.\n– Auto-Renewal: Automatically renews unless canceled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period.\n– Renewal Charge: Your account will be charged within 24 hours before the end of the current period, based on the selected plan.\n– Managing Subscription: Users can manage subscriptions and turn off auto-renewal in Account Settings on the App Store.\n– Free Trial Policy: Any unused portion of a free trial will be forfeited upon purchasing a subscription.\n\n\n Terms of Use: https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/\n\n Privacy Policy: https://drawingdata.io/privacy-policy","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/75/c5/6e/75c56e60-fde9-5d2f-1a43-beca7175a3e6/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-sRGB-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/public-speaking-coach/id6744645684?uo=4","developer":"DrawingData, Inc.","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":0,"2":1,"3":1,"4":4,"5":23}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6740540874","title":"SpeakUp - Public Speaking App","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.71429,"ratings":7,"reviewCount":7,"installs":"N/A","description":"You know that feeling. The moments before you present. Your heart races. Your mind goes blank. You wonder if you'll sound competent, if your team will respect you, if you'll actually say what you mean.\n\nPublic speaking anxiety doesn't discriminate. It affects talented professionals, strong leaders, brilliant minds. And that fear costs you: opportunities you don't take, voices you don't raise, ideas you don't share.\n\nTHE TRUTH ABOUT NERVOUSNESS\nFrom 25,000+ speakers worldwide, we've learned something powerful: the nervousness doesn't disappear. But something changes when you practice.\nWith honest feedback and deliberate practice, you stop being controlled by that nervousness. You learn to move through it. You discover that articulation, presence, and impact are skills—not talents. And skills can be built.\n\nWHAT CONFIDENT SPEAKERS ACTUALLY HAVE\nThey're not people who never feel nervous. They're people who speak with clarity despite the nerves, manage their pace and tone intentionally, command a room with their words, and articulate ideas so well people listen, remember, and act.\nThat's the difference. Between being heard and being dismissed. Between getting the promotion and being overlooked. Between leading teams and managing them.\n\nHOW SPEAKUP WORKS\n\n1. Practice in a Safe Space\nRecord your presentations, pitches, meetings—anything that matters. No judgment. No audience. Just you, freedom to try, stumble, and improve.\n2. Get Honest AI Feedback\nOur AI analyzes what's actually working: your vocal variation, your pacing, your clarity, your confidence. Real insights about the specific areas that need work.\n3. Learn from Bite-Sized Lessons\nExpert-crafted lessons on articulation and delivery, managing nervousness, commanding presence, storytelling and impact. Short enough to fit your week. Practical enough to apply immediately.\n4. Practice Again\nThis is where transformation happens. Practice. Get feedback. Adjust. Practice again. Each time, you're building muscle memory. Each time, you're becoming more articulate, more composed, more effective.\n\nYOU'RE NOT ALONE\n25,000+ professionals and leaders worldwide are already practicing on SpeakUp. They're preparing for board meetings, client presentations, team standups, job interviews, and important conversations. They're investing in the one skill that compounds: being heard.\n\nSTART PRACTICING TODAY\nYour next big presentation doesn't have to be the moment you discover you're nervous. It can be a moment you're prepared for. Download SpeakUp and start building your confidence: practice your speech, get instant AI feedback, track your improvement, ace your next presentation.\n\nWHY CHOOSE SPEAKUP?\n\n* AI-Powered Speech Analysis: Get detailed feedback on filler words, vocabulary, content coherence, and delivery.\n* Progress Dashboard: Track improvements with metrics and replay past recordings.\n* Custom Scenarios: Practice elevator pitches, TED-style talks, interviews, or casual conversations.\n\nKEY FEATURES\n\n* AI Speech Analysis: Detailed feedback on language, wording, filler words (like \"um\" or \"ah\"), vocabulary, and content coherence.\n* Progress Dashboard: Track improvements with metrics, and replay past recordings to see how far you've come.\n* Custom Scenarios: Practice for real-world situations—elevator pitches, TED-style talks, job interviews, or casual conversations.\n* 15+ Skills Analyzed: Speech clarity, content structure, vocal delivery, filler words and more.\n\nDownload SpeakUp now and start practicing your speech.\n\n---\n\nTerms of Use: https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/\nPrivacy Policy: https://sumukhah.github.io/SpeakUp_Privacy_Policy/\nSupport Email: sumukha@practicepublicspeaking.com","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/17/f0/39/17f0390d-9351-d39f-e788-db6975ea84d9/AppIcon-1x_U007emarketing-0-7-0-85-220-0.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/speakup-public-speaking-app/id6740540874?uo=4","developer":"Sumukha Hegde","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":1,"4":0,"5":6}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6470220669","title":"Credible: Speech Coach","store":"app_store","genre":"Productivity","score":4.41026,"ratings":234,"reviewCount":234,"installs":"N/A","description":"Stop saying \"like,\" \"um,\" \"you know,\" and other distracting filler words that make you sound unprofessional. Credible is the only app that provides immediate feedback during everyday conversations to help you speak with confidence and clarity.\n\nWHY CREDIBLE WORKS (When Other Apps Fail)\n\n•\tReal-Time Feedback: Credible works in the moment, when you need it most – not just during isolated practice sessions.\n•\tEffortless Improvement: No time-consuming practice drills. Credible works immediately, making you aware of your speech habits instantly and discreetly.\n•\tFast Results: Awareness based training is the only way to improve, enhancing job prospects and personal communication.\n•\tTrack Your Progress: Stay motivated and track your progress with our new streak tracking feature.\n\nKEY FEATURES:\n\nUnlike other speech improvement software that requires regular training or provides feedback after you speak, Credible is designed to increase your awareness of filler word use immediately, the only way to solve the problem. With Credible, you don't need to spend hours practicing; it works effortlessly to help you improve your speech.\n\n•\tReal-Time Alerts: Discreetly alerts you of filler words as you use them while speaking on your iPhone and Apple Watch.\n•\tCustomization: Choose common filler words or add any phrases you want to reduce, and the notification frequency.\n•\tStreak & Progress Tracking: Monitor your improvement over time with detailed progress reports.\n•\tPrivacy First: Audio is processed on your device, never stored or shared.\n\nPERFECT FOR:\n\nBreak the habit of saying \"like\"  with Credible, the easy-to-use solution that works instantly without any effort, time, or practice. As you become more aware of your speech, you'll naturally stop using \"like.\"\n\n•\tJob Interviews\n•\tConversations\n•\tMeetings\n•\tPresentations\n•\tAnyone who wants to communicate more effectively!\n\nGet Noticed for What You Say – Not How You Say It\n\nHOW TO USE:\n\nCredible requires microphone, speech recognizer, and notification access. Also, you will need to read a short paragraph to train Credible to only listen to you.\n\n•\tProvide access to your microphone, speech recognizer, and notifications.\n•\tSelect the filler word you want to stop saying.\n•\tSelect your notification frequency.\n•\tSet up the speaker verification tool by reading a short paragraph.\n•\tHit “Tap to Start.”\n\nLeave Credible on during any conversation to increase your awareness of filler words as you say them. Real time feedback is the only way you can become aware and improve your speech.\n\nDATA PRIVACY:\n\nWe take your data privacy seriously! Audio data is processed on-device in real time, it is never sent to the cloud or saved. Credible listens only when you activate it.\n\nPURCHASE OPTIONS:\n\nCredible offers a free demonstration of all included features with unlimited use, without interruptions or advertisements.  Subscription options are for 1-week, 1-month, 3-months, 1-year, 1-year non-renewing access, or purchase of lifetime access. The cost varies by country of residence and will be shown before confirming the purchase. Subscriptions automatically renew unless auto-renewal is disabled at least 24 hours before the end of the billing cycle. Users can manage subscriptions by going to the App Store, going to AppleID Account Settings, and scrolling down to Subscriptions. Cancellations are allowed during the active subscription period but no partial refund will be given. For refund inquiries, users must contact the Apple App Store directly.\n\nCONNECT:\n\nFor more information, questions, or concerns, please visit our website https://soundcredible.com/contact-us/ or email info@soundcredible.com\n\nPrivacy Policy: https://soundcredible.com/privacy-policy\nTerms of Service: https://soundcredible.com/terms-conditions","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/cf/f4/94/cff49464-c1d2-9f54-7ed7-d17d3e74acb7/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007ephone-0-1-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/credible-speech-coach/id6470220669?uo=4","developer":"WearableSoft","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":25,"2":5,"3":5,"4":13,"5":186}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1135012670","title":"Rhetoric Public Speaking Game","store":"app_store","genre":"Games","score":5,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":2,"installs":"N/A","description":"Public speaking. The mere thought of it can set hearts pounding! And yet, being able to communicate one’s ideas in public is an important and sought-after skill. With Rhetoric - The Public Speaking Game™, you will become a better speaker.\n\nRHETORIC is an educational game created by Florian Mueck and John Zimmer that will help you improve your public speaking skills and have a great time in the process.\n\nDesigned for up to 8 players, RHETORIC will challenge and engage you with a series of public speaking tasks. You and your fellow players will step onto the stage and deliver a series of short speeches, as determined by the squares on which you land.\n\nWhen you play RHETORIC, you will learn:\n\n• to speak with minimal preparation;\n• to control your nerves;\n• to structure a speech;\n• to speak with conviction;\n• to love public speaking.\n\nRHETORIC can be played in English, Spanish, French, Russian, German and Catalan, and will soon be available in other languages. There are three themes: Classic, Business and Family. More will be added.\n\nNow, it’s your turn to speak!\n\n•••••\n\nTo bring you the app version of Rhetoric - The Public Speaking Game™, John and Florian worked with Blowing Minds, a terrific indie game studio based in Barcelona, Spain, that designed and developed the app.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple123/v4/39/6c/a3/396ca314-3aaa-ce28-5f23-378e9d2ae16b/AppIcon-1x_U007emarketing-0-7-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/rhetoric-public-speaking-game/id1135012670?uo=4","developer":"John Zimmer","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":1.99,"free":false,"histogram":{}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"355391184","title":"The Art of Public Speaking!","store":"app_store","genre":"Book","score":0,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"Enjoy reading The Art of Public Speaking ebook with auto-scrolling, day and night viewing modes, bookmarks, multiple font sizes, full screen viewing in portrait and landscape orientations, and more!\n\nFEATURES: \n• AUTO-SCROLL: Hands free reading with our advanced variable speed auto-scrolling. \n• FULL SCREEN VIEW: No tab, navigation, or toolbars to get in your viewing way. \n• BOOKMARK CONTROLS: Bookmarking lets you start up where you left off fast. \n• MULTIPLE FONT SIZES: Increase or decrease the text size quickly and easily. \n• DAY & NIGHT MODES: Switch from day to night mode at the touch of a finger. \n• PORTRAIT & LANDSCAPE: Read your eBook in portrait or landscape position. \n• AUTO SETTINGS: Your viewer settings are automatically saved and loaded. \n• COPY & PASTE: Copy and paste selected text to other apps. \n• TEXT MAGNIFICATION: Magnify text for easier reading. \n• And more!\n\neBook Media Viewer Series #43\n\nTitle: The Art of Public Speaking\n\nAuthor: Dale Carnegie\n\nGenre: Non-fiction, Instructional\n\nPages: 467\n\nDescription: Training in public speaking is not a matter of externals--primarily; it is not a matter of imitation--fundamentally; it is not a matter of conformity to standards--at all. Public speaking is public utterance, public issuance, of the man himself; therefore the first thing both in time and in importance is that the man should be and think and feel things that are worthy of being given forth. Unless there be something of value within, no tricks of training can ever make of the talker anything more than a machine--albeit a highly perfected machine--for the delivery of other men's goods. So self-development is fundamental in our plan.\n\nTable of Contents:\nTHINGS TO THINK OF FIRST--A FOREWORD\nCHAPTER I--ACQUIRING CONFIDENCE BEFORE AN AUDIENCE\nCHAPTER II--THE SIN OF MONOTONY\nCHAPTER III--EFFICIENCY THROUGH EMPHASIS AND SUBORDINATION\nCHAPTER IV--EFFICIENCY THROUGH CHANGE OF PITCH\nCHAPTER V--EFFICIENCY THROUGH CHANGE OF PACE\nCHAPTER VI--PAUSE AND POWER\nCHAPTER VII--EFFICIENCY THROUGH INFLECTION\nCHAPTER VIII--CONCENTRATION IN DELIVERY\nCHAPTER IX--FORCE\nCHAPTER X--FEELING AND ENTHUSIASM\nCHAPTER XI--FLUENCY THROUGH PREPARATION\nCHAPTER XII--THE VOICE\nCHAPTER XIII--VOICE CHARM\nCHAPTER XIV--DISTINCTNESS AND PRECISION OF UTTERANCE\nCHAPTER XV--THE TRUTH ABOUT GESTURE\nCHAPTER XVI--METHODS OF DELIVERY\nCHAPTER XVII--THOUGHT AND RESERVE POWER\nCHAPTER XVIII--SUBJECT AND PREPARATION\nCHAPTER XIX--INFLUENCING BY EXPOSITION\nCHAPTER XX--INFLUENCING BY DESCRIPTION\nCHAPTER XXI--INFLUENCING BY NARRATION\nCHAPTER XXII--INFLUENCING BY SUGGESTION\nCHAPTER XXIII--INFLUENCING BY ARGUMENT\nCHAPTER XXIV--INFLUENCING BY PERSUASION\nCHAPTER XXV--INFLUENCING THE CROWD\nCHAPTER XXVI--RIDING THE WINGED HORSE\nCHAPTER XXVII--GROWING A VOCABULARY\nCHAPTER XXVIII--MEMORY TRAINING\nCHAPTER XXIX--RIGHT THINKING AND PERSONALITY\nCHAPTER XXX--AFTER-DINNER AND OTHER OCCASIONAL SPEAKING\nCHAPTER XXXI--MAKING CONVERSATION EFFECTIVE\n\nAPPENDIX A--FIFTY QUESTIONS FOR DEBATE\nAPPENDIX B--THIRTY THEMES FOR SPEECHES, WITH SOURCE-REFERENCES\nAPPENDIX C--SUGGESTIVE SUBJECTS FOR SPEECHES; HINTS FOR TREATMENT\nAPPENDIX D--SPEECHES FOR STUDY AND PRACTISE\n\nGENERAL INDEX","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple116/v4/b5/43/9a/b5439aa2-176f-4905-ba68-4efbc9829162/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-0-0-7-0-0-sRGB-0-0-0-GLES2_U002c0-512MB-85-220-0-0.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/the-art-of-public-speaking/id355391184?uo=4","developer":"Procypher Software Co.","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":4.99,"free":false,"histogram":{}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"371562064","title":"Public Speaking with AJ","store":"app_store","genre":"Business","score":4,"ratings":5,"reviewCount":5,"installs":"N/A","description":"Public speaking, delivering a presentation, making a speech - these seemingly simple tasks can be nerve-racking for many people. A high percentage of people feel some anxiety about speaking in public, in fact, it is commonly thought that this phobia is many peoples number one fear. \n\nThe overwhelming physical and emotional symptoms are all too real to those who suffer from it. \n\nThis Public Speaking app has been designed to help you overcome your public speaking anxiety by using the amazing resources of your unconscious mind. Deliver a professional performance with confidence, motivation and self-control are restored and new positive thoughts, habits and behaviours and created. \n\n  • Positive suggestions within this app. \n  • Build your confidence. \n  • Remain centred, calm, and relaxed.\n  • Experience wonderful feelings of success.\n\nDestress, improve your mindset, sleep better, grow your confidence and be healthier with guided meditations, mindfulness sessions and positive messages – and much more.\n\nMindfulness expert, coach and therapist Andrew Johnson has been helping people deal with life’s challenges with guided relaxations, meditations, self-care tools and breathing exercises for many years. \n\nHis best-selling range of mindfulness apps have a variety of content to help you, whether you are looking for ways to reduce stress and anxiety, lose weight, improve your health & confidence, learn relaxation techniques, etc.\n\nKey features:\n\n  • Short meditations you can do anywhere: at work, commuting, at home, walking.\n\n  • Inspirational sessions to help you tackle life’s challenges, to be calm and find clarity.\n\n  • Mindfulness stories and talks to help you build better, healthy habits.\n\nMeditations to help you feel inspired and find motivated to eat well, workout and stay healthy both in body and mind.\n\nRelaxation techniques and tools to help you sleep better every night, to wake feeling energised and refreshed.\n\nBreathing exercises and calming meditations for anxiety, panic attacks and stress relief.\n\nMeditation sessions to stop anxiety in its tracks and release stress.\n\nHow do I get more?\n\nStart your day mindfully, keep feeling positive and be inspired throughout the day with a range of guided meditations to help during tough or stressful moments. Boost your energy with a Power Nap, stay focussed to Beat Procrastination, and then drift off using a Deep Sleep meditation for a restful night.\n\nThink of Andrew as your personal mindfulness coach, always there to help when you need him most.\n\nSearch for Andrew Johnson to unlock more daily mindfulness and guided meditation sessions.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple116/v4/b7/a5/c2/b7a5c25c-a48a-7542-2628-7cc6d9ef02a3/contsched.lgxiatfh.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/public-speaking-with-aj/id371562064?uo=4","developer":"Universal Relaxation Ltd","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":2.99,"free":false,"histogram":{"1":0,"2":1,"3":1,"4":0,"5":3}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1621935264","title":"FluentJoy: Speak English","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.76909,"ratings":6,"reviewCount":6366,"installs":"N/A","description":"FluentJoy: Learn English with Real-Life Practice\n\nFluentJoy helps you improve your English through video-based lessons, conversation practice, and pronunciation training. Whether you're preparing for IELTS or TOEFL, working in an English-speaking environment, or simply want to feel more confident in conversations, FluentJoy makes learning effective and fun.\n\nKey Features:\n- Video Lessons: Learn grammar, vocabulary, and useful phrases through short, engaging videos.\n- AI-Powered Conversations: Chat with a smart virtual assistant tailored to your level.\n- Pronunciation Practice: Get instant feedback to improve your accent.\n- Quizzes: Test your listening and grammar with interactive quizzes.\n- Personalized Learning: Your learning path adapts to your goals and progress.\n- Email & Business English Tips: Communicate clearly and professionally.\n- Mobile-Friendly: Learn anywhere, anytime.\n\nFluentJoy is for students, professionals, travelers, and anyone who wants to speak English confidently. Join a global community and take your English to the next level.\n\n-------------------\nTerms of Service: https://www.fluentjoy.com/terms-of-use\nPrivacy Policy: https://www.fluentjoy.com/privacy-policy","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/79/2a/9b/792a9b99-8284-69a8-6677-3ad20a26fcd7/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-11-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/fluentjoy-speak-english/id1621935264?uo=4","developer":"Fluentjoy, Inc","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":71,"2":90,"3":211,"4":494,"5":5500}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6476445866","title":"SimLive - Public Speaking","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":0,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"Step into the spotlight with SimLive, the app that helps you practice public speaking and get comfortable in front of the camera through simulated livestreams.\n\nWhether you’re preparing for a presentation, interview, livestream or just want to build confidence, SimLive gives you a safe, judgment-free space to practice and improve.\n\nHow it Works\n\t•\tSimulated Livestreams: Experience the feeling of going live without the pressure of a real audience.\n\t•\tCustomizable Audiences: Practice in front of smaller or bigger crowds.\n\t•\tEngaging Topics: Warm up with quick exercises or dive into full practice sessions.\n\nWhy SimLive?\n\t•\tBuild real confidence in a safe space\n\t•\tOvercome stage fright step by step\n\t•\tImprove clarity, presence and delivery\n\t•\tPrepare for public speaking, interviews and livestreaming\n\nWhether you’re a student, professional, creator or anyone looking to improve their speaking skills, SimLive makes practicing public speaking fun, effective and stress-free.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/b4/98/2e/b4982e40-52fe-230b-6c76-7bcc7e1b8a0d/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-11-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/simlive-public-speaking/id6476445866?uo=4","developer":"Aventurin International","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6751936053","title":"Radiant: Speaking Challenges","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.52941,"ratings":34,"reviewCount":34,"installs":"N/A","description":"Radiant helps you improve articulation, speech clarity, and speaking confidence through short, guided speaking challenges. \n\nPractice speaking in a calm, supportive space designed to help you slow down, speak clearly, and feel more confident using your voice. Each challenge is simple, focused, and easy to fit into your day. Instead of trying to “fix” your voice, Radiant helps you understand how you speak and make natural improvements that add up over time.\n\nWhat Radiant helps you improve:\n\n- Everyday clarity:\nPractice speaking the way you actually talk—not scripted speeches. Learn how to express your thoughts more smoothly and clearly in real conversations.\n\n- Sound more thoughtful, effortlessly:\nSee patterns in pacing, pauses, and common habits like overusing “like” or “um,” so your words land with more confidence and credibility.\n\n- Pause without awkwardness:\nLearn how to slow down and think mid-sentence without losing your place or sounding unsure.\n\n- Polished, not robotic:\nRadiant helps you sound put-together while still sounding like yourself.\n\n- Progress you can feel:\nWatch your everyday speaking become calmer, clearer, and more intentional—one session at a time.\n\nYou already know what you want to say.\nRadiant helps you say it better.\n\nBeyond the first challenge, all other challenges will require the customer to utilize a free trial (expires within 3 days and transitions to a paid plan) or a paid plan (post-trial).\nThis means to access any app features the user must purchase a weekly or annual subscription.\n\nThe following do not require a purchase:\nOnboarding Flow\n\nThe following do require a purchase:\nSpeaking Challenges\nReading Challenges\nProgress Tracking\n\nTerms of Use (EULA): https://radiant-app.vercel.app/terms-of-service\nPrivacy Policy: https://radiant-app.vercel.app/privacy-policy","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/5c/f8/78/5cf87887-99bb-811d-077c-b80d285c6685/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/radiant-speaking-challenges/id6751936053?uo=4","developer":"Loshi Technologies, LLC","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":2,"2":2,"3":1,"4":0,"5":29}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6476082170","title":"Speak Up - Public Speaking","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":0,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"Speak Up helps you become a better public speaker by increasing your confidence, reducing anxiety, and improving your skills. If you want to overcome your fears and wow your audience, Speak Up is what you need. \n\nThis app contains journal prompts to help you boost your confidence, meditation exercises to help you reduce anxiety, and a full guide to public speaking to help you overcome your fears.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple116/v4/22/1b/00/221b0093-04e1-be80-ec94-1e36e1316c78/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-7-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/speak-up-public-speaking/id6476082170?uo=4","developer":"Marek Blazik","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6751113792","title":"Pause - Public Speaking Coach","store":"app_store","genre":"Productivity","score":0,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"The mindful public speaking coach in your pocket — practice anytime, get instant feedback, and speak with confidence. Perfect for presentations, pitches, or keynotes, the app gives you a safe space to rehearse and grow. With AI-powered analysis, it tracks filler words, pacing, clarity, and tone, then delivers actionable tips to improve your delivery. Mindful coaching helps you pause, breathe, and speak with intention, while progress tracking keeps you motivated as you build lasting habits. Features include:\n\n- Practice Mode to rehearse speeches in your own personal comfort.\n- Instant speech analysis on delivery\n- Progress tracking over time\n\nTurn public speaking into a mindful practice and step onto any stage with clarity, presence, and confidence.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/90/6e/c6/906ec66d-cc79-1283-d46c-e0d0c87378ee/productionAppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-8-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/pause-public-speaking-coach/id6751113792?uo=4","developer":"Pooja Bhaumik","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"957491370","title":"DSST Public Speaking Buddy","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":0,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"Master the DSST Public Speaking Exam\n\nFeatures:\n\n1. DSST Public Speaking Practice Exams\n\n2. Vocabulary Flashcards \n\n\nWith information at our fingertips, it is necessary for students to feel confident when approaching any exam.  Being that most everyone has a device of some kind, education should always be available inside and outside of the classroom.  \n\n\nDSST Public Speaking Buddy is the ultimate tool for learning about the DSST Public Speaking Exam. The features of this app makes studying extremely convenient.  Utilize this app at any time and from anywhere in order to master your knowledge and ace that exam!  Good Luck on testing!","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple126/v4/2a/e8/bc/2ae8bc0c-f725-6db0-eb75-64c8fafcb748/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-0-0-7-0-0-sRGB-0-0-0-GLES2_U002c0-512MB-85-220-0-0.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/dsst-public-speaking-buddy/id957491370?uo=4","developer":"Feraco media Inc.","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":1.99,"free":false,"histogram":{}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6755646238","title":"Charisma Lab: Speaking Coach","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":5,"ratings":7,"reviewCount":7,"installs":"N/A","description":"Speak Out Loud. Hear Yourself. Get Better.\n\nYou know what to say. Charisma Lab teaches you how to say it.\n\nMost people lose impact through uptalk, monotone delivery, filler words, and nervous energy. They're competent professionals who sound unsure. Charisma Lab is the private practice room where you fix that — before the board meeting, the sales pitch, or the interview.\n\nHOW IT WORKS\n\nPick a mode. Speak out loud about anything. Hear your voice played back. Get your own AI speaking coach to analyze how you come across. Practice again. Watch yourself speak confidently.\n\nThe secret is simple: speak often enough that you get used to your own voice. When speaking feels natural, confidence follows.\n\nFOUR MODES FOR EVERY SITUATION\n\nWarm Up — Get your voice and body ready before any big moment. Quick 60-second energy boosts. Vocal warm-ups and body exercises to shake off nerves. Your pre-game ritual.\n\nTrain — Build speaking skills one at a time. Storytelling. Pausing. Projection. Presence. Practice until each one becomes second nature.\n\nSpeak — Talk about anything. The app listens, plays back what you said, and your AI coach gives you specific, tactical feedback. No scripts. No pressure. Just you, your voice, and real reps.\n\nMindset — Your thoughts shape how you speak. Record power statements. Flip negative beliefs into confident ones. Build the mental foundation for every big moment.\n\nWHO IT'S FOR\n\nProfessionals preparing for presentations, pitches, and interviews. Sales teams who close deals on the phone. Lawyers building courtroom presence. Managers building executive presence and leading meetings with authority. Entrepreneurs pitching to investors. Anyone who wants to stop being nervous and start being heard.\n\nWHAT YOUR AI COACH FIXES\n\nUptalk — statements that sound like questions. Monotone delivery — your voice staying on one note. Filler words — um, uh, like, so. Soft trailing voice — losing power at the end of sentences. Rushed pacing — flying past your key points. Hedging language — \"I think\" instead of \"I am.\"\n\nWHAT MAKES THIS DIFFERENT\n\nOther apps teach you what to say. Charisma Lab makes you practice saying it. Out loud. With real feedback. Over and over until it feels natural.\n\nReading tips about charisma will not make you charismatic. You have to actually speak. You have to hear yourself. You have to do the reps.\n\nFEATURES\n\n• Four practice modes for every situation\n• Hands-free speaking practice\n• Hear your own voice played back\n• AI coaching on delivery, not just content\n• Tactical feedback: pace, pitch, volume, pauses\n• Practice public speaking, presentations, pitches, and interviews\n• Works in multiple languages (speak mode only)\n• Practice anytime, anywhere\n\nThe best speakers are not lucky. They just practiced more.\n\nTerms of Use: https://www.signal1st.com/terms/charisma-lab\nPrivacy Policy: https://www.signal1st.com/privacy/charisma-lab\nSupport: https://www.signal1st.com/support","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/1b/24/be/1b24beb2-fc9d-82f5-d8fb-4ff1bf0ac772/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/charisma-lab-speaking-coach/id6755646238?uo=4","developer":"Signal1st","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":7}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6468866021","title":"Public Speaking Made simple","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":0,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"Everyone, at some stage in their life, is going to have to say something in public, whether it be at an interview, at a business meeting, at a formal occasion or just when you are asked to “say a few words” at the end of an event.\n\nBased upon the excellent book “Public Speaking Like a Military Operation”, this app allows you to create your speech, however long or short, simple or complex. It leads you through the stages and automatically converts your speech into the notes you may need to help you deliver it.\n\n\nMaking use of the keyboard or voice to text facility on your phone or tablet, producing a speech could not be simpler and quicker.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/7c/dd/a7/7cdda7f1-3acb-e8e0-34c5-725b3ebd2f58/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-7-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/public-speaking-made-simple/id6468866021?uo=4","developer":"Peter Pearson","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6747023517","title":"English Learning - Easy Speak","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.64541,"ratings":2,"reviewCount":2338,"installs":"N/A","description":"Easy Speak is the #1 English learning app designed to help you speak English with confidence. Engage in real-time, speaking scenarios to practice job interviews, presentations, meetings, and more. Practice pronunciation & words by joining our community of 3 million happy users!\n\nHighlighted Features:\n\n- Improve English Communication -\nCareer-Specific Focus – Learn vocabulary and communication styles tailored to your field\nConfident Exam Preparation – Prepare for IELTS, TOEFL, TOEIC, EIKEN, and more with targeted practice in our bilingual app to boost fluency.\n\n- Personalized Learning Paths -\nPersonalized language learning – Learn to succeed in workplace interviews, giving presentations, interacting in meetings, succeeding at client calls, and daily conversations.\nAI-Driven Conversations & Open-Ended Dialogues – Personalized language learning through practicing realistic conversations.\n\n- Instant Feedback & AI Coach for Conversations -\nQuantitative Progress Tracking – Monitor your improvement with data-driven insights.\nPronunciation & Word Stress Guidance from our AI English Coach – Receive real-time corrections to sound more natural.\n\n- Real-Life Conversation Practice -\nGrammar & Vocabulary – AI-driven conversation helps you build a solid foundation in English grammar and expand your vocabulary with everyday, practical words. The adaptive AI adjusts to your progress, ensuring you always learn exactly what you need.\nConversation Practice – Improve fluency with role-plays, open-ended dialogues, and real-life scenarios. Learn to speak English confidently and with clarity. Leave language misunderstandings behind, whether in the workplace or the classroom.\nPronunciation Training – Practice speaking English and conquer tricky sounds, learn nuanced English pronunciation.\nPersonalized Study Sets – Save words, phrases, or sentences from lessons or create your own, explore and share sets, and improve your pronunciation with real-time feedback\n\n- What You'll Get -\nEnhanced Global Collaboration: Bridge language gaps and foster seamless teamwork with international colleagues or friends.\nCareer Potential: Boost your career by impressing clients and colleagues with polished English communication\nExpand Your Network: Build meaningful relationships and explore global opportunities with confidence.\nBeyond Pronunciation: Learn grammar, vocabulary, and communication techniques to succeed academically, personally, or professionally.\n\nGet unlimited access with Easy Speak Premium!\nEasy Speak AI offers both weekly and annual auto-renewing subscriptions. Become a Easy Speak AI Premium member to gain unlimited access to all courses, review material, and other content within Easy Speak AI.\nThe subscription will automatically renew unless turned off in your iTunes Account Settings at least 24 hours before the current period ends. You can go to your iTunes Account settings to manage your subscription and turn off auto-renew. Your iTunes Account will be charged when the purchase is confirmed. If you subscribe before your free trial ends, the rest of your free trial period will be forfeited as soon as your purchase is confirmed.\n\nTerms of service: https://static-cdn-f.mifeng.plus/policy/EasyTalk_AI/service_en-us.html\nPrivacy policy: https://static-cdn-f.mifeng.plus/policy/EasyTalk_AI/privacy_en-us.html","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/47/66/8e/47668e68-7e92-fbcb-1c8c-2e6c3c79a69d/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007ephone-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/english-learning-easy-speak/id6747023517?uo=4","developer":"INTSIG PTE. LTD.","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":83,"2":56,"3":88,"4":153,"5":1958}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"734412264","title":"IELTSpeaking","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.62814,"ratings":1,"reviewCount":1116,"installs":"N/A","description":"IELTSpeaking - Designed to boost your IELTS Speaking score.\nExperience full IELTS Speaking mock tests, 1-on-1 AI examiner feedback, and precise band scoring that help you quickly break through your speaking barriers.\nAccess the complete and up-to-date IELTS Speaking question bank, covering every topic from the latest test seasons, with detailed Band 6 and Band 7 sample answers and explanations. Prepare smart and see rapid progress before your next exam.\n\n1. Full IELTS Speaking Mock Test & Score Report\n\nSimulate the real IELTS Speaking test from start to finish.\nAfter each mock test, you’ll instantly receive a professional IELTS Speaking score report that evaluates grammar, fluency, vocabulary, and pronunciation.\nUnderstand your current Band level and get clear AI-powered suggestions to move up to the next level — all in just 10 minutes a day.\n\n2. Comprehensive Question Bank & High-Score Samples\n\nGet access to a massive and ever-growing IELTS Speaking question library, updated in real-time with new and predicted topics.\nEvery question includes detailed Band 6 and 7 sample answers so you can learn how top candidates respond.\nDuring topic-change seasons, new questions are updated hourly to ensure you never miss a single real question.\n\n3. AI Practice & Instant Feedback\n\nPractice Part 1, Part 2, and Part 3 separately.\nAfter every answer, the AI examiner provides instant feedback — grammar correction, pronunciation scoring, and fluency tips — so every practice session counts.\nEach exercise includes scoring and improvement guidance to make your training efficient and goal-driven.\n\n4. Progress Tracking & Improvement Curve\n\nAutomatically generate detailed progress charts to visualize your improvement and spot weaknesses for targeted review.\nAll practice sessions are saved for easy review, helping you continually refine fluency and accuracy.\n\n5. Who Is It For\n\nPerfect for test-takers aiming to improve their IELTS Speaking scores quickly, experience real mock tests, and stay updated with new question sets.\nEspecially recommended for learners around Band 5.0–5.5 who want to break through to Band 6 or higher.\n\nStart your full IELTS Speaking mock training today — get familiar in 3 days and see improvement in 7 days!\n\nFor support: support@ieltspeaking.com\nTerms of Use: https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/c8/57/54/c8575497-b836-bd71-e001-d3b0925eb7fc/AppIcon-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-0-85-220-0.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/ieltspeaking/id734412264?uo=4","developer":"Gravity Tech, Inc.","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":22,"2":17,"3":54,"4":168,"5":855}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1630658468","title":"Communication skills 2025","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.54458,"ratings":415,"reviewCount":415,"installs":"N/A","description":"◆ Ever find it tough to make a great first impression, whether it's at work, on a date, or meeting new friends?\n◆ Do you struggle to show empathy and connect deeply in conversations?\n◆ Find it hard to stand up for yourself and get your point across effectively?\n◆ Wish you were better at persuading or negotiating in various situations, not just at work?\n◆ Feel lost in how to handle difficult talks with family, friends, or even strangers?\n\nWith this app, you'll:\n▶ Get stronger, more meaningful relationships in all areas of your life\n▶ Boost your influence and persuasion skills, making every interaction count\n▶ Grow your confidence in managing tricky conversations anywhere\n▶ Master key communication skills that make you stand out in any setting\n▶ Leave lasting, positive impressions on everyone you meet\n\nCommunication skills app: your go-to for becoming a communication pro. This app is for everyone who wants to up their game in making connections, understanding others, and expressing themselves. It’s packed with fun and personalized ways to improve your communication skills, whether with your boss, your date, or your pals.\n\nFeatures:\n- Real-Life Role-Play Challenges: Test your communication chops in varied scenarios, from family dinners to networking events. Learn to dodge common mistakes and navigate smoothly through all kinds of chats.\n- Fun Games & Rewards: Keep your learning streak alive with exciting rewards, levels, and achievements. Watch as your communication skills level up in a way that feels more like play than work.\n- Tailored Learning Journeys: Set up your learning path based on what you're looking to improve, from making friends to acing job interviews. ChatMaster adapts to your pace and goals, offering feedback that’s just right for you.\n- All-Around Communication Training: Pick up vital skills like empathy, assertiveness, and negotiation. Make a positive impact on anyone you interact with, no matter the context.\n\nStart your transformation now!\n\nTerms of Service: https://boatneck-silver-df1.notion.site/Terms-of-Service-1a49078858554153a23096e55ffc973d\nPrivacy Policy: https://boatneck-silver-df1.notion.site/Privacy-Policy-c44d9a76979c4814a898e29092b62904","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/aa/ce/27/aace27a4-638e-0050-61f6-ae44b9952670/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007ephone-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/communication-skills-2025/id1630658468?uo=4","developer":"Jan Krmela","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":20,"2":10,"3":15,"4":49,"5":321}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6749287368","title":"Talklet: AI English Coach","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.70629,"ratings":1,"reviewCount":1127,"installs":"N/A","description":"Your AI coach for real-world English. Practice job interviews, daily conversations, and speak with confidence. Get fluent in just 10 minutes a day.\n\n◆ How Talklet Works: The 10-Minute English Lesson ◆\n\nOur unique two-part lessons are fast, effective, and fit into your busy schedule.\n\nLearn English with an AI Teacher: First, your AI tutor teaches you the key English vocabulary, grammar, common phrases, and pronunciation for a specific real-world scenario, like ordering coffee or introducing yourself.\n\nPractice to Speak English: Next, you immediately put your new English skills to the test! Have a real-time, voice-to-voice conversation where the AI roleplays as a barista, hiring manager, or new friend. You talk, and the AI responds, just like in real life.\n\n◆ For Every Goal: English Scenarios for Your New Life ◆\n\nStop learning English phrases you'll never use. We have hundreds of lessons covering the situations that matter most to you.\n\n For Your New Life: Master essential life skills. Practice talking to a doctor in English, attending a parent-teacher meeting, or opening a bank account with confidence.\n\n For Your Career: Ace your job interview, present ideas in meetings, and master professional small talk. Get the job and succeed at work.\n\n For Your Studies: Excel in an academic environment. Practice participating in class discussions and collaborating with classmates on projects—all in English.\n\nFor Travelers: Navigate any situation with ease. Learn to check into a hotel, ask for directions, and order from a menu using practical English.\n\n◆ Your Personal AI Coach: Patient, Smart & Always On ◆\n\nTalklet is more than an app; it’s your 24/7 English speaking partner who is always there to help you improve without judgment.\n\nInstant, Real-Time English Feedback: Don't just practice, practice perfectly. If you make a mistake, your AI tutor provides gentle, immediate corrections on your English grammar, word choice, pronunciation, and accent.\n\nKey Features:\n\nAI-powered English conversation practice with a virtual tutor\n\nReal-time voice and grammar feedback\n\nHundreds of real-life English language scenarios for work, school, and daily life\n\nBite-sized lessons designed to take only 10 minutes\n\nEnglish vocabulary, pronunciation, and fluency training\n\nPersonalized English learning paths from beginner to advanced\n\nAvailable 24/7 for on-demand practice\n\nThis is the English language app you need.\n\nStop just learning English—start speaking English. Download Talklet today and find your voice!","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/3e/d9/c5/3ed9c597-f304-1673-33ca-ce50ea37db72/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-11-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/talklet-ai-english-coach/id6749287368?uo=4","developer":"Talklet AI Limited","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":30,"2":24,"3":43,"4":53,"5":977}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"417882424","title":"Visuals2Go","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.30279,"ratings":1,"reviewCount":1364,"installs":"N/A","description":"CREATE - COMMUNICATE - PRINT!\n\nVisuals2Go is founded by a Special Education teacher and developed in collaboration with speech pathologists and parents. Our mission is to have an accessible tool that is user friendly, simple to use and effective in the teaching of Alternative and Augmentative Communication (AAC)\n\nVisuals2Go is an ALL-IN-ONE Educational app created to support people with communication and learning difficulties. Research shows that Augmentative and Assistive Communication systems are highly beneficial for people who are non-verbal or have difficulties with speech.\n\nVisuals2Go is designed to support you as an Educator, Therapist, Support Worker or Parent so that you can give the person in your care a voice. It is distinct from other Augmentative and Alternate Communication (AAC) in it’s versatility. It is designed to support people with a range of different communicative needs: from students with high support needs who needs a single message communication system, to choice making using two or more images, to sentence building to extend vocabulary. It also supports those who needs hands-on visuals so the app allows users to PRINT their visuals on a range of different templates.\n\nThe app has a Simple-to-use interface and beautifully designed images that will encourage regular access to communication and learning.\n\nWe believe that if the Educators, therapists, support workers or parents are actively using a software that is highly beneficial, then the person with a communication need will most likely be using it as well.\n\nThe app is useful for verbal and non-verbal learners, it can be used for individuals in the Autism Spectrum, individuals with Down Syndrome or other diagnosis.\n\nHere are some of the ways you can use Visuals2Go:\n\n* Use it as communication device for those struggling with speech. Users can make choices directly or use the ‘Sentence Strip’ feature to communicate in sentences;\n\n* Use it for Visual Prompts, our new 'Card Search' feature allows you to easily search for thousands of images to provide a visual prompt for directions or for learning;\n\n* For students with Higher Support needs, you can use the App as a one button (or one message) communication device;\n\n* Use it as a lanyard - carrying all your symbols on your device, with an easy SWIPE-TO-SCROLL through cards feature;\n\n* Create countless number of visual cards in various sizes to print off and laminated for hands-on learning (Optional Upgrade);\n\n* Print cards on a range of customised visual boards from our templates for a variety purposes including choice boards, shopping lists, flash cards and more (Optional Upgrade);\n\n* Create stories for learning - You can use to create stories to learn social skills and step-by-step recipes or procedures.\n\n* Or simply use it as a photo album with text and voice. Store albums of family members; friends; favourite toys; characters; etc. Your child will love scrolling to see each Visual!\n\nThe app is constantly updated with new images and albums. You have a choice to upgrade the app with added features with individual inApp purchases or with a subscription. \n\nPlease note: If you purchase a monthly or yearly access to the online library, payment will be charged to your iTunes account. Your account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period, and identify the cost of the renewal. Subscriptions may be managed by the user and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the user's Account Settings after purchase.\n\nPrivacy Policy: https://www.visuals2go.com/app-privacy-policy\n\nTerms of Use: https://www.visuals2go.com/app-terms-of-use","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/f0/65/40/f0654037-e8ac-d50d-fa23-da64f138833d/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-10-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/visuals2go/id417882424?uo=4","developer":"Bo Innovations","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":68,"2":59,"3":125,"4":252,"5":860}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6753739129","title":"Conversly: Communication Coach","store":"app_store","genre":"Productivity","score":5,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":3,"installs":"N/A","description":"Conversly is your all-in-one AI coach for real-life communication. It helps you improve what you say, how you sound, how you come across, and how you handle people, so every conversation feels easier and more in your control.\n\n\nPick a situation—meeting, date, party, presentation, or tough talk—and practice it with the AI. Conversly listens like a real person, then breaks down your words, voice, and decisions in simple language.\n\n\nTrain every layer of your communication:  \n• Content – organize your thoughts, be clear, stop rambling.  \n• Voice – fix tone, pace, volume, and energy.  \n• Nonverbal vibe – how you come across and make people feel.  \n• Social reading – pick up cues, subtext, and context.  \n• Interaction flow – keep talks going, ask better questions, avoid awkward silences.  \n• Relationships & influence – build trust, respect, and better outcomes over time.  \n• Norms & culture – handle boundaries, professionalism, and different settings.  • Channels – in-person, calls, video, text, and voice notes.  • Confidence & nerves – manage anxiety, overthinking, and mental spirals.  \n• Substance – bring better stories, examples, and knowledge into your talks.\n\n\nAs you practice, Conversly gives you:  \n• Instant feedback on each conversation.  \n• Targeted drills for your weak spots.  \n• Prompts and examples for what to say next.  \n• Progress tracking so you can see your growth over time.\n\n\nYou don’t need to be naturally outgoing or “smooth.” Conversly gives you reps, feedback, and structure so talking to people stops feeling like a guessing game and starts feeling like a skill you actually own.\n\nTerms of Use (EULA): https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/07/be/2b/07be2b44-9b42-05ad-afb2-48cef0769bed/AppIcon-1x_U007emarketing-0-11-0-85-220-0.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/conversly-communication-coach/id6753739129?uo=4","developer":"Alaevski LLC","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6745815058","title":"Gleam: Social Intelligence","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.8025,"ratings":2,"reviewCount":2805,"installs":"N/A","description":"Improve your social fluency and emotional intelligence (EQ) with Gleam.\n\nGleam is a fun, science-backed coach for mastering communication skills and social skills, whether it's talking to girls on dates, getting better at conversation, or preparing for an interview or networking.\n\nGleam delivers bite-sized, interactive lessons to help you become more confident and charismatic. You can learn to flirt better, ace a job interview, or improve your public speaking.\n\nMASTER ESSENTIAL SKILLS:\n\n* Communication & Social Skills\n* Emotional Intelligence (EQ)\n* Networking & Interview Skills\n* Public Speaking & Small Talk\n* Negotiation & Conflict Resolution\n* Active Listening & Empathy\n* Autism Communication\n* Leadership\n\nHOW GLEAM WORKS:\n\n• Interactive Learning: Learn by doing with scenario-based lessons, quizzes, and practice conversations designed by communication experts.\n\n• Personalized AI Feedback: Receive instant feedback on your communication style to spot hidden blind spots and ensure every message lands perfectly.\n\n• Real-world Confidence: Build \"social muscle memory\" in safe simulations tailored to your goals—from professional networking and dating to everyday conversations.\n\n• Track Your Growth: Monitor your self-improvement journey, set personal goals, and celebrate milestones to build better habits and stay motivated.\n\n• Expert Advice: Access insights from communication coaches, psychologists, and authors of top self-help books, right from your phone.\n\nSkip the pricey workshops and awkward seminars. Gleam is your mobile coach for communication, relationships, and personal growth. Download today and start your journey to a more confident you.\n\nGLEAM MEMBERSHIP\n\nGleam offers both monthly and annual auto-renewing subscriptions. Become a Gleam Member to gain unlimited access to all courses, singles, review material, and other content within Gleam.\n\nThe subscription will automatically renew unless turned off in your iTunes Account Settings at least 24 hours before the current period ends. You can go to your iTunes Account settings to manage your subscription and turn off auto-renew. Your iTunes Account will be charged when the purchase is confirmed.\n\n---\n\nTerms of Service: https://gleam.so/terms  \nPrivacy Policy: https://gleam.so/privacy","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/ae/ac/27/aeac27ad-e262-d0e6-f46f-b9be4268a388/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/gleam-social-intelligence/id6745815058?uo=4","developer":"Gleam Labs Inc.","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":35,"2":15,"3":78,"4":213,"5":2464}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6752822613","title":"Wellspoken: Articulation Coach","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.68966,"ratings":87,"reviewCount":87,"installs":"N/A","description":"Tired of replaying conversations in your head, losing your words mid-sentence, and staying quiet when you shouldn't? \n\nYou are at the right place. Wellspoken helps you build the speaking skills you've always wanted. It trains you to speak clearly and confidently in just 5 minutes a day.\n\nYou have great ideas but struggle to express them clearly. Your thoughts come out jumbled, you search for the right words, and people look confused when you explain things you know well.\n\nWellspoken uses brain science to target the real barriers to clear communication:\n- Multiple practice modes tailored to your communication goals\n- AI speech analysis that identifies exactly where you lost focus\n- Vocabulary activation to access words you know but can't use under pressure\n- Safe base phrases that make anyone sound articulate\n\nHow it works:\n- Choose from multiple practice modes tailored to your goals\n- Get AI feedback on your speech patterns and word choice\n- Learn precise vocabulary to replace filler words\n- Build your \"safe base\" of go-to transition phrases\n\nBuilt on cognitive science research into speech production and skill acquisition. Our approach targets the proven systems that help you find words and speak clearly under pressure.\n\nJoin thousands improving their communication skills daily.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/f6/f4/53/f6f453b1-752a-a939-807c-f0dc311b8003/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/wellspoken-articulation-coach/id6752822613?uo=4","developer":"Carbon Studio LLC (Apps)","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":5,"2":0,"3":0,"4":7,"5":75}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6749592243","title":"Social Skills Builder - Convo","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.40217,"ratings":92,"reviewCount":92,"installs":"N/A","description":"Build Better Conversation Skills\n\nConvo is a social skills builder designed to help you speak better, connect faster, and feel confident in conversations.\nWhether you struggle with social anxiety, small talk, or knowing what to say, Convo helps you practice real conversation skills daily.\n\nHow Convo Works\n\nShort daily speaking exercises\nGuided conversation practice\nReal-world scenarios\nClear feedback on how you speak\nLessons designed to build confidence\nNo pressure. No awkward roleplay.\nJust simple speaking practice that works.\n\nWhat You’ll Practice\n\nConversation skills\nSocial skills & communication\nConversation starters\nSpeaking clearly & confidently\nCharisma and presence\nSocial anxiety relief\n\nWho Convo Is For\n\nAnyone working on social skills\nPeople with social anxiety\nProfessionals who want to speak better\nAnyone who wants stronger conversations\n\nSocial Skills Are Learnable\n\nSpeaking well isn’t a personality trait.\nIt’s a skill.\nConvo helps you build conversation skills through daily practice—so real conversations feel easier.\n\nCONVO MEMBERSHIP\n\nConvo offers monthly and annual subscriptions that unlock full access to premium lessons and conversation practice.\nSubscriptions renew automatically unless canceled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. Payment is charged to your iTunes Account at confirmation. You can manage or cancel your subscription anytime in your Account Settings.\n\nPrivacy & Terms of Use\n\nTerms of Use: https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/\nPrivacy Policy: https://www.tryconvo.app/privacy-policy","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/ce/56/85/ce56858c-28e5-e959-3eda-03fce80a49e3/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-P3-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/social-skills-builder-convo/id6749592243?uo=4","developer":"Thomas Snycerski","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":6,"2":1,"3":6,"4":16,"5":63}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1387373941","title":"BurlingtonEnglish","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.17703,"ratings":209,"reviewCount":209,"installs":"N/A","description":"What is BurlingtonEnglish?\n\nBurlingtonEnglish is a unique blended English program for adults. It offers comprehensive General English Courses as well as a wide range of Career Courses, and provides a complete language-learning solution. Students get any time-anywhere access to state-of-the-art online interactive courses.\nBurlington’s cutting-edge speech technology, the SpeechTrainer®, provides individualized feedback and instruction in pronunciation. \n\nWith BurlingtonEnglish, students effectively improve their pronunciation, vocabulary and overall fluency, giving them the confidence to communicate successfully in any situation.\n\nSpecial Features:\n\n- SpeechTrainer®\nIndividualized Pronunciation Feedback and Instruction \nThis patented speech processing technology helps learners perfect their pronunciation and listening skills.  The SpeechTrainer® analyzes students’ spoken English, adapts to a wide variety of accents to discern specific difficulties, and corrects mispronunciations through individualized training. This will help improve students’ pronunciation, comprehensibility, and confidence to successfully communicate in English.\n\n\n- Mobile Vocabulary Practice\nVocabulary Practice Any Time, Anywhere! \nMobile Vocabulary Practice allows students to get additional vocabulary practice on the go. Students can access wordlists for their courses to reinforce their language learning whenever and wherever they are.\n\n- Using Your Computer\nThrough a series of short animated videos, students develop basic digital literacy skills such as maneuvering the mouse and using the keyboard, as well as gain a basic understanding of a computer. It is designed for learners with limited English proficiency and limited-to-no digital literacy, using easy-to-follow visual demonstrations. \n\n- Personalized, Data-Driven Learning!\nReal-time feedback and reporting to track, monitor and measure progress encourage students and motivate them to learn.\n\n\nAnd many more unique and exciting features!!!\n\nThis results-driven program, with 24/7 online access, is engaging for English language learners, and helps them to become more productive and successful members of the workforce and their communities.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple123/v4/c1/2c/44/c12c440b-dd0a-701b-f176-910d5c76ccc0/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-0-0-10-0-0-sRGB-0-0-0-GLES2_U002c0-512MB-85-220-0-0.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/burlingtonenglish/id1387373941?uo=4","developer":"Burlington Education Ltd.","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":28,"2":9,"3":8,"4":17,"5":147}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1290974340","title":"Conversation Skills","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":5,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":1,"installs":"N/A","description":"** Happy Frog Apps is a Mom’s Choice Award Winner! Also featured on FunEducationalApps.com, TeachersWithApps.com, and more! **\n\nThe “Conversation Skills” app helps children with autism practice key steps in conversation:\n\n - Identifying a friend's interests, \n - Choosing an appropriate topic, \n - Figuring out what topic is already being talked about,\n - Joining a conversation,\n - Continuing a conversation with appropriate follow-up questions and comments.\n\nThis app provides kids the chance to practice and get supportive feedback in a calm, stress-free environment where they can consider their options.\n\nOnce kids build the skills of how to choose topics and continue conversations, they'll be able to bring these skills to real-life situations.\n\nThe “Conversation Skills” app gives your learner the social conversation skills they need to better manage social situations at home, school and in the community. \n\nWhat parents say about our awesome apps:\n*** 5 stars! Brilliant! An app that understands how kids actually learn. Thank you.\n*** 5 stars! Your social skill apps are excellent!\n\n“Conversation Skills” provides:\n\n - More than 140 situations for a wide variety of practice.\n\n - Students progress to the next level only when mastery of the current skill is demonstrated.\n\n - 'At a glance' reporting shows you instantly how your learner is progressing.\n\n - The fun Reward Center motivates even hesitant learners.\n\nMost exciting, this app offers independent AND therapist mode.  In independent mode, answers are displayed and the learner taps the correct answer. \n\nIn therapist mode, no answers are displayed.  For each question, the student answers orally and the therapist taps whether the learner's oral answer was correct or incorrect.  Both modes earn coins for the Reward Center.\n\nOur apps are designed for and tested by typical and special needs children. Testers include children with Autism and other special needs. Our apps work for them! Our apps are also suitable for adults dealing with aphasia or learning English as a Second Language.\n\nTo evaluate the app, download the lite version, which has 1 free level. Additional levels and additional players can be accessed with in-app purchases.\n\nIf you prefer no in-app purchases, download the paid version of this app, which includes all levels and up to 10 players.\n\nWe take customer service very seriously! If you ever have a problem or find that we've missed something, contact us at our website and we will do our best to fix the problem. \n\nwww.HappyFrogApps.com\n\nOur apps are safe for kids. We collect NO private information in our app. None! Our apps do not allow unrestricted web or social media access. We conform to the Children's Online Privacy Protection Act.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/7c/12/82/7c1282f9-1f55-8020-91b1-a90d327787bc/AppIcon-1x_U007emarketing-85-220-3.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/conversation-skills/id1290974340?uo=4","developer":"Janine Toole","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":11.99,"free":false,"histogram":{}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6502325255","title":"Hedy AI Meeting Coach","store":"app_store","genre":"Productivity","score":4.77419,"ratings":62,"reviewCount":62,"installs":"N/A","description":"Gain confidence in every conversation. Hedy is your personal AI meeting coach, helping you shine in meetings, lectures, and interviews with real-time insights, smart talking points, and perfect notes of every conversation.\n\n\n\"For executives, entrepreneurs, and team leaders, Hedy acts as a personal strategist, note-taker, and communication coach all in one.\" - Entrepreneur Magazine\n\nPERFECT FOR:\n- Professionals who want to stand out in meetings\n- Students aiming to excel in lectures\n- Coaches and mentors guiding development conversations\n- Non-native speakers navigating English conversations\n- Anyone who needs help understanding and remembering important conversations\n- Anyone who wants to contribute more confidently to discussions\n\nTRANSFORM EVERY CONVERSATION\nIn Business Meetings:\n- Get intelligent talking points before others think of them\n- Turn complex discussions into clear action items\n- Get instant transcripts of every meeting\n- Receive AI-powered meeting minutes with key points and action items\n\nDuring Interviews & Journalism:\n- Generate insightful follow-up questions\n- Identify unique angles in real-time\n- Keep complex narratives on track\n\nDuring Recruitment & Hiring:\n- Get tailored insights during candidate interviews\n- Generate insightful follow-up questions to assess qualifications\n- Create comprehensive interview notes automatically\n\nDuring Lectures & Classes:\n- Your intelligent lecture recorder captures every detail\n- Understand difficult concepts in real-time\n- Ask questions that showcase your engagement\n- Get detailed notes and study guides after every class\n\nDuring Coaching & Mentoring Sessions:\n- Generate powerful questions that promote deeper reflection\n- Identify development opportunities your mentee might not see\n- Track growth and progress across multiple sessions\n\nIn Medical Appointments:\n- Get suggested questions you hadn't considered\n- Leave with clear understanding of next steps\n\nSPEAK YOUR LANGUAGE:\n- Join multi-lingual conversations while getting insights in your preferred language\n- Support for 30+ languages including English, Spanish, French, German, Italian, Japanese, Korean, Chinese (Mandarin), Dutch, Polish, Portuguese, Swedish, Vietnamese, Turkish, Malay, Indonesian, Norwegian, Ukrainian, and Russian\n- Perfect for global teams and international students\n\nPOWERFUL KNOWLEDGE CAPTURE:\n- Auto-generated transcripts capture every detail\n- Smart summaries distill key points and decisions\n- Organize highlights in Zettelkasten-style notes\n- Post-meeting chat to explore past discussions\n- Email summaries for easy follow-up\n\nEXCLUSIVE FEATURES:\n- Real-time analysis powered by advanced AI\n- Seamless phone and desktop experience\n- Automatic summaries and action items\n- Meeting and transcript library\n- Import voice memos, audio, and video files into Hedy\n\nWORKS WITH:\n- Zoom, Microsoft Teams, Google Meet\n- Any virtual meeting on your computer\n- In-person meetings and conversations\n\nGETTING STARTED IS SIMPLE:\n1. Press a button to activate Hedy\n2. Let Hedy analyze your conversation\n3. Get brilliant insights via a discrete interface\n4. Review and learn from every interaction\n\nTrusted by 20,000+ professionals, students, and global teams.\n\nAmplify your expertise—with Hedy. Whether you're leading a meeting, attending a lecture, or coaching a client, Hedy helps you be your best. Download now and transform the way you communicate forever.\n\nHedy uses advanced AI including OpenAI's Whisper for speech recognition and Google’s Gemini for conversation analysis.\n\nSubscription pricing and terms:\nHedy offers an auto-renewing monthly subscription at $9.99/month to provide you with unlimited access to Hedy while you maintain an active subscription. Payment will be charged to your iTunes Account when you confirm the initial subscription purchase. Subscriptions automatically renew unless auto-renew is turned off.\n\nTerms of use: https://www.hedy.ai/terms-of-use\nPrivacy policy: https://www.hedy.ai/privacy-policy","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/81/85/6f/81856f68-1c50-668a-fcf3-7ccf95399cdb/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-11-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/hedy-ai-meeting-coach/id6502325255?uo=4","developer":"Hedy AI LLC","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":3,"2":0,"3":0,"4":2,"5":57}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6751140779","title":"Social Sage: Speaking Skills","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":5,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":2,"installs":"N/A","description":"Social Sage is your personal speaking coach — designed to help you become more articulate, confident, and compelling in every conversation.\n\nWhether you're explaining ideas at work, telling stories to friends, navigating difficult conversations, or just want to stop saying \"um\" and start speaking with clarity — Social Sage gives you the tools to transform how you communicate.\n\nWith daily articulation drills, storytelling practice, real-time speech analysis, and personalized coaching available 24/7, you'll finally sound like the person you've always wanted to be.\nSpeak with confidence. Connect with purpose.\n\n\nSOUND SMARTER, SPEAK CLEARER\n\nDaily articulation exercises and speaking drills train your mouth and mind to work together. Stop stumbling. Stop filler words. Start speaking with precision and flow.\n\nNEVER RUN OUT OF WORDS\n\nPractice real conversations across dozens of scenarios — tough talks, interviews, social situations, everyday moments. Build the verbal fluidity that makes speaking effortless.\n\nYOUR 24/7 SPEAKING COACH\n\nMeet the Social Sage: a personal coach who understands communication and gives you instant, practical feedback on how to improve. Like having an expert in your pocket.\n\nBECOME A BETTER STORYTELLER\n\nLearn the structure behind stories that captivate. Practice delivery, timing, and hooks. Be the person people actually want to listen to.\n\nTRACK YOUR PROGRESS\n\nDetailed analytics show your speaking improvement over time — fluency, clarity, filler words, pacing. Watch yourself get better every day.\n\nBUILD REAL CONFIDENCE\n\nEvidence-based techniques help you quiet self-doubt, reframe nervousness, and speak with calm assurance. Confidence isn't born — it's built.\n\nGET INSTANT FEEDBACK\n\nReal-time analysis shows exactly what to fix — tone, pacing, clarity, delivery. Know what's working and what isn't.\n\nREAL STORIES FROM THE SOCIAL SAGE COMMUNITY\n\n“The only app that actually helps…I used to dread social events. Now I actually look forward to them. I’ve learned how to start conversations naturally, be genuinely curious, and never run out of things to say .\"\n\n\"Dating was terrifying. Social Sage helped me overcome my fear of rejection and taught me how to be genuinely interesting. I'm actually enjoying it now and have been told I am a great storyteller.\"\n\n\"The daily drills are addictive. My articulation has improved so much — I sound sharper in meetings and even casual conversations.\"\n\n\"I always thought I was just not a good speaker. Turns out it's a skill, and Social Sage is the only app that has helped so far, I have tried many...”\n\nSUBSCRIPTION INFORMATION\n\nA Social Sage subscription is required to access all features and content after onboarding.\nPricing:\nWeekly: $3.99 for your first week, then $7.99/week\nMonthly: $29.99/month (Save 13%)\n\nPayment will be charged to your Apple ID at confirmation of purchase. Subscriptions automatically renew unless cancelled at least 24 hours before the current period ends. Manage your subscription in your Apple ID Account Settings.\n\nContact: hello@bymeraci.com\nTerms of Service: https://socialsage.social/terms \nPrivacy Policy: https://socialsage.social/privacy","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/d7/33/a7/d733a70d-2227-571c-7008-ddce8038f054/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-8-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/social-sage-speaking-skills/id6751140779?uo=4","developer":"Meraci, LLC","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6755947087","title":"Coco - Communicate Better","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":5,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":2,"installs":"N/A","description":"Coco is a subscription-based AI communication coach that helps you build confidence in everyday\n  conversations.\n\n  SUBSCRIPTION REQUIRED\n  A Coco Pro subscription is required to access all features. Subscription options and pricing are\n   displayed at signup.\n\n  WHAT YOU GET WITH COCO PRO:\n  • Daily AI-powered practice scenarios\n  • Voice-based roleplay conversations\n  • Detailed performance feedback\n  • Personalized improvement tips\n  • Progress tracking & analytics\n\n  Practice real-life situations like ordering coffee, setting boundaries, or handling difficult\n  conversations - all in a safe, judgment-free environment with your AI coach, Coco.\n\n  ---\n  • Payment will be charged to your Apple ID account at confirmation of purchase\n  • Subscription automatically renews unless canceled at least 24 hours before the end of the\n  current period\n  • Manage subscriptions in your Account Settings after purchase\n\nTerms: https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/\nPrivacy Policy: https://ashvinar.github.io/coco-legal/privacy.html","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/8a/f2/5c/8af25cf0-98d2-3c0f-d43b-b62e269f913e/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-8-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/coco-communicate-better/id6755947087?uo=4","developer":"Ashvin Arora","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6742728063","title":"Communication Skill:Talk Maxer","store":"app_store","genre":"Productivity","score":5,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":1,"installs":"N/A","description":"Simulate Conversation\n\nTALK MAXER: MASTER THE ART OF COMMUNICATION: Unleash Your Voice. Perfect Your Speech. Transform Your Connections.\n\nEver found yourself stumbling through important conversations, filling awkward silences with \"um\" and \"uh,\" or struggling to find the right words when it matters most? Talk Maxer is your personal AI communication coach, designed to transform how you speak—and how others perceive you.\n\nYOUR POCKET COMMUNICATION COACH\nTalk Maxer uses advanced speech recognition technology to help you practice real-world conversations in a judgment-free environment. Simply tap to talk, and our AI responds naturally, creating dynamic practice sessions that feel like genuine interactions. Whether you're preparing for a job interview, practicing asking someone out, or just wanting to sound more confident at social gatherings, Talk Maxer is your secret advantage.\n\nPRACTICE ANYWHERE, ANYTIME\nWith Talk Maxer, you can:\n• Master Daily Life Communication: Navigate grocery stores, restaurants, doctor's offices, banks, and more with clear, confident speech patterns.\n• Develop Charisma and Romance Skills: From breaking the ice at first meetings to maintaining long-term relationships, learn to express yourself authentically and charmingly.\n• Enhance Social Communication: Practice telling engaging stories, resolving conflicts, delivering presentations, and shining in group settings.\n• Eliminate Filler Words: Our intelligent system detects and helps you reduce those pesky \"ums,\" \"ahs,\" and \"likes\" that diminish your verbal impact.\n• Track Your Progress: Our intuitive analytics dashboard shows your improvement over time, providing daily scores and highlighting areas for growth.\n\nREAL-WORLD SCENARIOS, REAL RESULTS\nEach lesson plan is carefully crafted to simulate authentic interactions you'll encounter in everyday life. Our AI responds dynamically to your speech patterns, word choices, and conversational approach, providing personalized feedback that helps you refine your communication style.\n\nBACKED BY COMMUNICATION SCIENCE\nTalk Maxer isn't just another practice app—it's built on proven communication principles and techniques used by professional speech coaches. We've studied what makes great communicators stand out and distilled those insights into practical exercises you can use immediately.\n\nPREMIUM FEATURES THAT TRANSFORM HOW YOU SPEAK\nUpgrade to Premium for the full Talk Maxer experience:\n• Unlimited access to all lesson categories and specialized scenarios\n• Advanced analytics and progress tracking\n• Personalized feedback on tone, pace, and clarity\n• No ads for uninterrupted practice sessions\n\nWhether you're a professional looking to advance your career, a student preparing for presentations, or someone who simply wants to communicate more effectively in personal relationships, Talk Maxer provides the practice, feedback, and confidence you need to become a masterful communicator.\nDownload Talk Maxer today and transform how you speak—and how the world responds to you.\n\nhttps://www.rashedslab.com/terms-of-use","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/76/ab/c9/76abc93b-abbf-b93e-5231-7bcd77e9ed51/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007ephone-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/communication-skill-talk-maxer/id6742728063?uo=4","developer":"Risul Rashed","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6746419990","title":"Sociabl: Learn Social Skills","store":"app_store","genre":"Lifestyle","score":4.26087,"ratings":23,"reviewCount":23,"installs":"N/A","description":"Build real-world confidence with Sociabl - the ultimate app for practicing everyday conversations, making new connections, and navigating tricky social moments. Whether you're brushing up on small talk or prepping for a big date, Sociabl gives you a safe space to practice and grow.\n\n\n\nWHY USERS TRUST SOCIABL\n\n\n\nMASTER REAL-LIFE SOCIAL SITUATIONS\n\nPractice realistic conversations with varying stakes, from ordering coffee to confronting others, and even charming your way into VIP events. Speak aloud to interactive AI characters that respond naturally, preparing you for confident interactions in real life.\n\n\n\nPERSONALIZED FEEDBACK & INSIGHTS\n\nAfter each practice session, receive detailed feedback highlighting your strengths and areas for improvement. Gain quantitative scores on confidence, clarity, and empathy, plus actionable qualitative insights to improve the next time around.\n\n\n\nCOMPREHENSIVE LEARNING MODULES\n\nEnhance your skills through short, focused lessons organized by key topics like \"Small Talk Mastery,\" and \"Friendship Building\" Enjoy interactive quizzes, practical techniques, bite-sized challenges, and guides to support your social confidence journey.\n\n\n\nMEET CHATTO - YOUR AI SIDEKICK\n\nChatto’s got your back - anytime, anywhere. Whether you’re overthinking a text, nervous about a date, unsure how to handle a tough conversation, or just need a little pep talk, Chatto gives personalized advice for your situation. It’s like talking to someone who really gets you - no pressure, just real support you can count on 24/7.\n\n\n\nREAL-TIME PROGRESS TRACKING\n\nUnlock new levels as you build daily streaks, collect milestone icons, and hit personal bests. Every win earns you progress badges and visual rewards that cheer you on and show just how far you’ve come.\n\n\n\nADVANCED TECHNOLOGY, SEAMLESS EXPERIENCE\n\nPowered by AI technology for realistic conversations, precise transcription, and natural speech synthesis, Sociabl ensures smooth, responsive interactions, maintaining engaging conversational flows under five seconds.\n\n\n\nSUBSCRIPTION INFORMATION\n\nUnlock Sociabl Premium for full feature access. Payment charged to your Apple Account upon confirmation. Subscription auto-renews unless canceled 24 hours prior to renewal. Manage subscriptions via your App Store Account Settings.\n\n\nPrivacy Policy: https://sociabl.app/privacy-policy\nTerms of Use: https://sociabl.app/tos\n\nQuestions or feedback? Contact us at contact@sociabl.app","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/69/2d/f9/692df9c0-5dbb-f033-1465-f197357b9a91/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/sociabl-learn-social-skills/id6746419990?uo=4","developer":"Jake Ackerman","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":3,"2":1,"3":0,"4":2,"5":17}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6443828538","title":"Learna: People Skills.","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":0,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"Master people skills in just 7 minutes a day!\n\n\nWork smarter. Build confidence. Handle workplace challenges with ease.\n\nWant to worker smarter, build confidence, and handle workplace challenges with ease? Learna’s got you covered. \n\nLearna gives you quick, actionable lessons created by over 40 top experts and thought leaders. Designed for busy people who want to grow the work skills that matter most.\n\n200+ lessons. 11 key categories. All practical.\n\nLearna is your go-to for levelling up essential workplace skills such as: \n  -  Communication\n\n  -  Problem solving \n  -  Critical thinking\n  -  Teamwork\n  -  Public speaking \n  -  Leadership\n  -  Adapatibility \n  -  Time Management \n\n  -  Productivity\n\n\nGrow the skills that matter the most for modern work. Download Learna now and start your free trial.\n\nWhy Learna Works\n\n\n*Work has changed - and should the way we learn\nWhether you are at your desk, on your commute, or in between meetings, you can learn something new in just 7 minutes and put it into action straight away.\n\n*Bite-sized learning\nEvery lesson takes 7 minutes or less. Fits into your day, no matter how busy you are.\n\n*Expert content\nLearn from globally recognised futurists, psychologists, leadership coaches and more. No fluff. No theory. Just real-world advice you can use straight away.\n\n*Real-world skills\nEverything's practical, actionable, and designed to solve actual work challenges.\n\n*On-demand flexibility\nLearn at your desk, on a commute, during breaks. Your pace, your schedule.\n\n*Tailored to you\nGet lesson recommendations based on your goals and needs.\n\n*Progress you can track\nSee what you've learned. Build habits. Stay on course.\n\n\nWho Is Learna For?\nWhether you're just starting out or managing a team, Learna provides practical skills training to help you thrive.\n\n*New to managing people? Build strong foundations in leadership, communication and problem solving.\n*Already managing people? Enhance your leadership skills, build stronger relationships, and improve team collaboration.\n*Want to stay relevant? Grow the capabilities that matter for the future of work.\n\n\nDownload Now\n\nSmall steps lead to big results. Work is better when you're better.\n\nWe keep it simple. No jargon. No long lectures. Just quick, research- backed insights to help you work better and be more confident. Because learning should be something that can help you solve real work problems.\n\nUnlock the full experience with a 3-day free trial. No jargon. No long lectures. Just quick, research-backed insights to help you work better and feel more confident.\n\n*Love Learna? \nPlease leave us a quick star rating on the App store. We really appreciate the love.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/98/77/bc/9877bcd8-a00e-2d40-8e67-b310ea47be9b/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007ephone-0-11-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/learna-people-skills/id6443828538?uo=4","developer":"LEARNA APP PTY LTD","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1257834464","title":"Canvas Teacher","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.63405,"ratings":95,"reviewCount":95944,"installs":"N/A","description":"Save time. Teach on the go.\nCanvas Teacher helps educators, instructors, and teachers grade, give feedback, and manage their classes from anywhere.\n\nWhat you can do\n• Grade or mark work: Use mobile friendly SpeedGrader to annotate assignments, apply rubrics and give written, audio, or video feedback\n• Communicate: Post class announcements, reply in discussions, and send messages right from your device\n• Update content: Adjust due dates, publish/unpublish assignments, or fix typos in seconds\n• Stay connected: Manage your Inbox, reply to student questions, and keep class communication flowing on the move\n\nCanvas Teacher is designed for educators—making mobile grading and class management faster and easier.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/7e/02/09/7e02097f-28db-e4fa-297b-12357b35db3c/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-sRGB-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/canvas-teacher/id1257834464?uo=4","developer":"Instructure Inc.","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":3082,"2":1360,"3":3880,"4":10943,"5":76679}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1462735159","title":"DHBW Presentation Coach","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":0,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"The Presentation Coach will give you some tips on how to prepare for your next business presentation. \nThe app is divided into different parts:\n-\tIntroduction\n-\tStandard Presentations\n-\tPersuasive Presentations\n-\tSales Talks\n-\tNon-Verbal Skills\n-\tVisual Aids.\nIn the Introduction, you will receive some important information about how to begin a presentation. This will help to grab your audience’s attention so that they are interested in your topic.\nIn Standard Presentations, you will learn about the most basic form of presenting. You will also be given some helpful tips and phrases that you can immediately use for your next presentation, as well as see and hear a few examples.\nWant to impress your audience? In Persuasive Presentations, you will discover what it takes to convince your audience of your message. There will be some examples of great persuasive speeches and why they are so convincing. Here you will receive some valuable tips to impress your audience about your ideas.\nThe Sales Talk chapter focuses on the essential skills needed to pitch your product or service to your customers or clients. Examples of effective sales pitches will be shown and what made them successful pitches.\nThe Non-Verbal Skills chapter will help you develop your body language tactics to send the correct message to your audience without speaking. These skills are just as important as your speaking skills, so the advice in this chapter will help you to stand confident in front of your audience.\nIn the last chapter, Visual Aids, you will be introduced to some of the most common mistakes made by speakers and how to visually enhance your presentation without overloading people’s senses. You will see examples of how visual aids can effectively complement what you are saying without distracting your audience. \n\nNote: The videos included in this app are not directly embedded in the system but refer to clips on YouTube. Therefore, the authors of the Presentation Coach cannot guarantee the unlimited availability of all visual resources.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/7b/60/e6/7b60e67e-6c7d-102e-1e1b-dcde9bc60345/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/dhbw-presentation-coach/id1462735159?uo=4","developer":"Duale Hochschule Baden-Württemberg Karlsruhe","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6737224695","title":"RiseGuide: Top Expert Insights","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.62281,"ratings":9,"reviewCount":9714,"installs":"N/A","description":"Expert-Powered Self-Improvement. One Daily Lesson at a Time.\n\nRiseGuide gives you structured learning journeys backed by real expert insights, so you can improve your skills, mindset, confidence, intelligence, and personal brand without wasting time on random content.\n\nEvery day, you master one powerful idea. Every week, you feel yourself getting better.\n\nThis isn’t another course you’ll never finish. This is your personalized growth journey.\nThis is your short-cut from people, who’ve done it before.\n\nWHAT YOU GET:\n\n- Daily Bite-Sized Lessons. Communication, confidence & charisma, personal branding & audience growth, intelligence & memory – choose your path or explore them all.\n- Expert-Powered Methods. Learn directly from the insights and strategies of neuroscientists, authors, creators, strategists, leaders, world-class performers and role models.\n- Search Engine for Expert Knowledge, or SEEK. Your bridge to expert knowledge on demand, where you get answers straight from the source. Ask questions, explore topics, and get answers backed by trusted research and expert insights.\n- Interactive Features. Frameworks, cheat sheets, templates, and exercises that turn learning into action. Get real progress with daily to-do’s, reinforcing quizzes, video materials, downloadable workbooks, flashcards. and more.\n- Explore Section. Access a library of expert-powered lessons on a variety of topics, from charisma and communication to cognitive skills and audience growth, and broaden your learning journey.\n\nWHAT OUR USERS ARE SAYING:\n\n- \"I am extremely happy with my first lesson. I feel well understood and very well heard - Riseguide focuses on the exact key things I wish to master. Highly recommend and can't wait my next lesson.\"\n\n- \"My experience with RiseGuide has been solid. The content is real, easy to understand, and it actually makes me think. It's not just motivation - it gives me guidance I can use in my everyday life. I've learned things that helped me stay focused, stay positive, and look at situations differently. RiseGuide has honestly become one of the few pages I check daily because it actually adds value.\"\n\nRiseGuide is your short-cut from people, who’ve done it before. This is your time to to truly upgrade your mind. This is your time to rise!\n\nHOW DOES IT WORK?\n\nAfter you decide to begin your growth with RiseGuide and download the app, you can unlock all features by subscribing to the premium subscription. Free trial option is available.\nPlease note: subscription renews automatically at the end of each period (each week, month, 6 months, or otherwise, depending on the selected option) until you cancel. Canceling your subscription means the automatic renewal will be disabled. Note that deleting the app does not cancel your subscriptions.\n\nRead more about our\n\nTerms and Conditions here - https://legal.riseguide.com/m/terms-of-use\nPrivacy Policy - https://legal.riseguide.com/m/privacy","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/97/27/11/972711ff-f482-e8db-361a-d8fb180ba8b2/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-11-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/riseguide-top-expert-insights/id6737224695?uo=4","developer":"CELEB INNOVATIONS LIMITED","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":263,"2":75,"3":400,"4":1587,"5":7389}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6754809512","title":"Speakr - Charisma & Confidence","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":5,"ratings":9,"reviewCount":9,"installs":"N/A","description":"Improve your confidence, communication, and charisma with Speakr.\n\nSpeakr is a motivating, science-based coach that helps you build confidence, emotional intelligence, and strong speaking habits through interactive voice AI conversations. Whether you want to overcome social anxiety, express yourself more clearly, or feel calm and confident in dating, work, or everyday conversations, Speakr is designed to help you speak like your best self.\n\nBuilt on proven psychology and communication science, Speakr transforms how you express yourself. You’ll learn to sound natural, confident, and engaging while understanding how to manage tone, emotions, and energy in every interaction. \n\nMASTER ESSENTIAL SKILLS:\n\n* Confidence & Charisma\n* Social Skills & Emotional Intelligence (EQ)\n* Public Speaking & Storytelling\n* Dating & Relationship Confidence\n* Professional Communication\n* Active Listening & Empathy\n* Body Language & Eye Contact\n* Vocabulary & Verbal Clarity\n* Handling Awkward Silences & Reducing Filler Words\n\n\nHOW DOES SPEAKR WORK?\n• Choose a Path: Pick from real-life goals and scenarios like small talk, dating, interviews, or presentations. Train with our powerful voice AI or complete interactive daily tasks designed to build real-world confidence.\n\n• Practice in Real Time: Speakr’s lifelike voice AI helps you rehearse conversations, while task-based challenges push you to apply what you learn outside the app—starting convos, improving posture, or maintaining better eye contact.\n\n• Personalized Feedback: Get instant, adaptive insights on tone, pacing, clarity, and emotional delivery, plus practical advice for body language, presence, and expression.\n\n• Habit Building: Confidence becomes a routine with short daily missions that train both your mind and body to stay calm, engaged, and articulate under pressure.\n\n• Science-Based Growth: Each lesson is rooted in behavioral psychology and communication research to strengthen confidence, charisma, and emotional intelligence that last beyond the screen.\n\nWHY USERS LOVE IT?\n– “I finally stopped overthinking before talking to people.”\n– “Helped me sound confident in interviews and meetings.”\n– “Dating anxiety dropped, and I actually enjoy conversations again.”\n– “I became a more confident speaker, and stopped doubting myself during conversations”\n\nSkip awkward workshops and long courses—Speakr is your personal communication coach in your pocket. You’ll strengthen your voice, learn emotional awareness, improve clarity, and naturally become more engaging with every conversation.\n\nSPEAKR IS PERFECT FOR ANYONE WHO:\n• Struggles with social anxiety or shyness\n\n• Wants to improve confidence or dating charisma\n\n• Needs to communicate clearly at work or in interviews\n\n• Wants to break bad speaking habits and filler words\n\n• Aims to grow emotional intelligence and self-awareness\n\n• Wants to be the Speaker you always wanted to be\n\nSpeakr helps you build the confidence to speak effortlessly, make real connections, and express yourself clearly in any setting.\n\nTerms of Use: https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/\nPrivacy Policy: https://getspeakr.com/privacy/","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/fb/63/96/fb6396c1-bfc4-f66b-5f27-0cb081d015ee/AppIcon_1-0-0-1x_U007ephone-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/speakr-charisma-confidence/id6754809512?uo=4","developer":"ByteSand LLC","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":9}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6456224061","title":"Kippy AI Speaking Practice","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.7439,"ratings":328,"reviewCount":328,"installs":"N/A","description":"Do you freeze when speaking a foreign language? Want real speaking practice without nerves or judgment? Meet Kippy, your friendly AI speaking partner and language tutor. \n\nTalk to Kippy like a friend. Practice real conversations for 5 minutes a day. Get instant feedback while you speak and a personalised Speech Report that recommends what to practice next.\n\nPerfect for learners who know the basics and want fluent conversation practice with an AI language tutor.\n\n(◕‿◕) Who is Kippy for?\n\n ▷ Learners who know some sentences and grammar but freeze in real conversations\n\n ▷ People who want speaking practice with useful, everyday phrases instead of textbook lines\n\n ▷ Anyone who wants a judgment‑free AI speaking partner to build confidence and fluency\n\n ▷ Travelers and professionals who need fluent speaking before trips, interviews, or meetings\n\n ▷ Busy people who prefer an on‑demand AI tutor for daily speaking practice\n\n\n(◕‿◕) Speak with a friendly partner\n\n ▷ Talk to Kippy like a friend about anything you care about\n\n ▷ Real‑sounding voices for natural conversation practice\n\n ▷ 30+ real‑life scenarios to rehearse daily situations like ordering food, shopping, or making friends\n\n ▷ New topics every day to keep your speaking practice fresh and fun\n\n\n(◕‿◕) Get help while you talk\n\n ▷ Pronunciation Check with immediate feedback so your speech gets clearer over time\n\n ▷ Grammar Check that fixes mistakes on the spot and helps you sound more fluent\n\n ▷ Instant translations to learn new words as you speak\n\n ▷ Helpful hints when you get stuck so the conversation keeps flowing\n\n\n(◕‿◕) Personalised Speech Report after each session\n\n ▷ Fluency insights and a fluency trend so you can see progress clearly\n\n ▷ Pronunciation and grammar highlights with examples from your conversation\n\n ▷ Recommended phrases and words to practice, chosen from what you actually said\n\n ▷ Smart tips and a short practice plan that guide your next step toward fluency\n\n\n(◕‿◕) See your progress\n\n ▷ Word Reports that show which words you use often and which need more practice\n\n ▷ Track your growth as your vocabulary and fluency increase with every chat\n\n ▷ Save your favorite phrases to review and reuse in future conversations\n\n\nPractice speaking English, Spanish, Japanese, Korean, Chinese, German, Italian, French, Portuguese, or Russian.\n\nJust 5 minutes a day with your AI speaking partner helps you speak more, speak better, and feel more fluent and sure of yourself.\n\nDownload Kippy now and start speaking with confidence.\n\nQuestions? Email us: support@kippy.ai\n\n\nFind out more: www.kippy.ai\n\nTerms of Use: https://www.kippy.ai/terms","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/8f/55/dc/8f55dcd1-b139-7df4-c289-b1c348a42de1/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007ephone-0-1-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/kippy-ai-speaking-practice/id6456224061?uo=4","developer":"DeepSine","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":7,"2":2,"3":12,"4":26,"5":281}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6756185807","title":"Confidently: Confidence AI","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.22222,"ratings":9,"reviewCount":9,"installs":"N/A","description":"Be the most confident speaker in the room.\n\nConfidently helps you practice speaking so real conversations feel easier.\nYou don’t need to be perfect, you just need practice and clear feedback.\n\nSpeak freely, try improv challenges, and learn how you come across when you talk.\n\n1. Practice speaking without pressure\n\nBuild confidence by practicing a little every day.\n\n* Daily improv challenges:\nSpeak for 60 seconds using random prompts.\nGreat for thinking on your feet and real conversations.\n\n* Speech practice:\nRecord longer talks, presentations, or answers.\nPractice at your own pace, up to 30 minutes.\n\n* Upload a video:\nGet feedback on a recording you already have.\n\nPractice often. Get better without stress.\n\n2. Know how you come across\n\nAfter each session, Confidently gives you simple feedback you can understand:\n\n* Confidence score\n\n* Speaking pace and words per minute\n\n* Filler words like “um” and “uh”\n\n* Voice clarity and delivery tips\n\n* Short AI suggestions you can use right away\n\nNo guessing. No vague advice.\n\n3. Build confidence over time\n\n* Review past practice sessions\n\n* See progress from daily practice\n\n* Feel more comfortable speaking in real life\n\nConfidence grows when you practice.\n\n4. Private and focused\n\n* Your recordings stay private\n\n* No ads\n\n* No social sharing\n\nConfidently is a safe space to practice and improve.\n\n\nDownload Confidently and start speaking with confidence today.\n\n\nTerms of Use (EULA): https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/ \nPrivacy Policy: https://www.amberwillo.com/privacy-policy/","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/9c/94/e6/9c94e6f0-49a3-2c19-04a7-89a039925748/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007ephone-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/confidently-confidence-ai/id6756185807?uo=4","developer":"Tyrone Letang","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":1,"2":1,"3":0,"4":0,"5":7}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6745228181","title":"CharmXP: AI Charisma Coach","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.40449,"ratings":623,"reviewCount":623,"installs":"N/A","description":"UNLOCK UNSTOPPABLE CONFIDENCE\n\nCharmXP turns nerve-racking real-life moments into low-stakes practice rounds—powered by cutting-edge AI. Crush first dates, nail job interviews, and close sales calls before you ever set foot in the room.\n\nWHY CHARMXP?\n\n- AI Role-Play Scenarios – Pick a situation (first date, interview, pitch, tough feedback) and chat with a lifelike AI partner that adapts to your tone, questions, and hiccups.\n- Interactive Lessons – Bite-sized modules on charisma, storytelling, active listening, conflict resolution, body language, and public speaking. Learn, then instantly apply.\n- Instant Performance Reports – After every session, get a heat-map of key moments: see where you dazzled and where you stalled on charisma, engagement, clarity, empathy, and more.\n- XP & Level-Ups – The better you perform, the more XP you earn. Level up to unlock harder scenarios and exclusive mastery tips.\n- Progress Tracker – Watch your confidence score climb week by week and celebrate wins that actually matter in the real world.\n\nPERFECT FOR\n* people seeking better relationships and dating life. \n* Job seekers who need interview prep that feels real.\n* Entrepreneurs & sales pros sharpening their pitch.\n* Singles leveling up dating confidence.\n* Anyone battling social anxiety who wants a private practice arena.\n\nHOW IT WORKS\n\n1. Choose a Scenario – Date night? Performance review? You decide.\n2. Talk It Out – Chat, voice-note, or video-role-play with the AI coach.\n3. Get Your Report – Pinpoint strengths, gaps, and exact lines to use next time.\n4. Learn through bite-size lessons, from communication skills to Charisma\n5. Earn XP & Repeat – Advance through tougher missions as your skills skyrocket.\n\nWHY USERS LOVE IT\n\n- “Felt like a real interview. Got the job two weeks later.”\n- “Dating anxiety down, confidence through the roof.”\n- “Every sales objection drilled before the call—closed the deal.”\n\nFREE VS. PREMIUM\n\nGo Premium for the full catalog, lessons, advanced analytics, and challenges. Your future self will thank you.\n\n\nIn-App Purchases: Premium Monthly, Premium Annual\nSupports: iPhone, iPad, iPod touch\nLanguages: English\nPrivacy Policy: https://charmxp-webclient.vercel.app/policies/privacy-policy.pdf\nTerms and Conditions: https://charmxp-webclient.vercel.app/policies/terms-and-conditions.pdf\n\nReady to own every conversation? Download CharmXP now and start leveling up today.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/d6/8b/6d/d68b6dcf-476f-a49b-e1e7-1052165c392c/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007ephone-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/charmxp-ai-charisma-coach/id6745228181?uo=4","developer":"FullBricks LLC","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":62,"2":7,"3":26,"4":50,"5":478}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6751870718","title":"Quota: AI Speaking Coach","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":5,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":3,"installs":"N/A","description":"HOW TO USE QUOTA\n1. Choose what you want to improve such as interviews, meetings, sales, leadership, small talk, or everyday communication\n2. Follow guided Journeys that teach core skills step by step\n3. Practice with Daily Drills designed for quick, realistic reps\n4. Go deeper with Roleplay sessions for full conversations in real-life scenarios\n5. Review instant feedback on clarity, tone, pacing, confidence, and overall delivery\n\nQuota helps you build the communication skills that shape your career, relationships, and daily life.\nIt is not a chatbot, script generator, or entertainment app. It is a structured training system built to help you improve through consistent practice.\n\nIf you are ready to speak with clarity, confidence, and composure, Quota becomes your daily coach.\n\nFor feedback or support, email support@quota.la.\n\nQuota is an educational communication platform and does not provide therapeutic or medical advice.\nProgress depends on practice consistency and individual effort.\n\n*Daily drills are included with an active subscription. Roleplay includes 30 minutes of monthly practice time. If you use all your minutes, you can purchase additional time separately.\n\nTerms: https://quota.la/terms-conditions\nPrivacy: https://quota.la/privacy","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/ad/cc/5f/adcc5fc0-35ee-c74e-d0b1-2b66d906215a/AppIcon-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-11-0-85-220-0.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/quota-ai-speaking-coach/id6751870718?uo=4","developer":"Qu, Inc","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6470384954","title":"Onstage Confidence","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":0,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"Stage fright? Find quick, practical confidence skills that work. Be you. Be heard.\n\n\n\nThe average adult attention span is 8.25 seconds. When you have money or a job on the line, what do you do when the stage fright monster shows up in those precious 8.25 seconds? Do you freeze? Go blank? Does it become hard to breathe? Hard to think? Do you wonder why you said yes in the first place? What happened to that great first impression?\n\n\n\nDo you know anyone who struggles with stage fright? If the #1 adult fear is public speaking, and 77% of adults suffer with it, I’ll bet you do! I sure did!\n\n\n\nNot to worry! You’ve come to the right place! Onstage Confidence is your resource for a more holistic approach to send the stage fright monster packing. There is so much more than “imagine them in their underwear” that you can effectively use when the nerves show up. You can choose!\n\n\n\nWhy does that matter?\n\n\n\nTransforming fear and anxiety depends on your personal fear model. Which are you? When you feel stage fright, do you freeze? Do you get ready to fight? Do you run away far and fast? Your fear response determines what skills work better for you.. You can customize your “Confidence Skills Toolkit '' and simply use the techniques that work best for you. Try them on for size. A wise person once said, “if you don’t know where you are, you can’t get there from here.” We start the road to onstage confidence from where you are.\n\n\n\nThere are videos, articles, exercises, tips & tools to conquer and transform stage fright and create your own brand of authentic confidence. Our more holistic approach includes physical, mental, energetic, emotional and sonic approaches. You’ll find breathing exercises, mindset hacks, theatre games, energy and emotion games and several ways to harness the power of sound. Did you know alchemy crystal singing bowls are powerful instruments to ground and center you in just a moment or two? And Sound Baths are just one of many centering and confidence building techniques.\n\n\n\nWe’ve been helping people conquer stage fright and create stage mastery for over 50 years. The Confidence Skills work! With regular practice your new skills can become so second nature, you are prepared for whatever happens. The skills to create your own authentic confidence that magnetizes your listeners to you are yours for the learning and practicing!\n\nCome on in! You matter. Your voice matters. Your message matters. Let’s help you get out there and send the fear monster packing!","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple126/v4/44/2e/fd/442efde7-bd6f-c7a1-d8b1-a754edba9d74/AppIcon-1x_U007emarketing-0-7-0-sRGB-85-220-0.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/onstage-confidence/id6470384954?uo=4","developer":"Diann Alexander","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6757143128","title":"Minute Hatch","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":0,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"Meet Minute Hatch, the impromptu speaking practice app designed to help you think fast, speak clearly, and build real communication confidence.\n\nPractice impromptu speaking in just one minute a day using guided prompts, timed speaking sessions, and voice recordings. Improve public speaking naturally through daily repetition instead of long courses or theory.\n\n———————\n\nFull access to all features requires a subscription. A free trial may be available for eligible users.\n\nWHAT YOU GET WITH A MINUTE HATCH SUBSCRIPTION\n\n• Daily impromptu speaking prompts\nGet fresh speaking topics every day and practice answering on the spot — just like real conversations, interviews, and presentations.\n\n• Timed speaking exercises\nTrain spontaneous thinking with structured impromptu speaking practice sessions that fit into your daily routine.\n\n• Voice recording + replay\nRecord every speaking session and review how you sound to improve clarity, confidence, and delivery.\n\n• Speaking feedback that matters\nTrack key communication skills:\n- Clarity\n- Confidence\n- Flow\n- Word choice\n- Structure\n\n• Progress tracking:\nBuild a consistent speaking habit and watch your communication skills improve over time.\n\n———————\n\nWHY IMPROMPTU SPEAKING PRACTICE WORKS\n\nShort daily speaking reps help you:\n- Think faster when speaking\n- Reduce hesitation and overthinking\n- Improve public speaking confidence\n- Speak naturally in meetings and conversations\n- Handle interviews and presentations with ease\n\n———————\n\nPERFECT FOR\n\n• Impromptu speaking practice\n• Public speaking training\n• Communication skills improvement\n• Job interviews and presentations\n• Social confidence and conversation skills\n• Anyone who wants to speak clearly without freezing or overthinking\n\n———————\n\nHOW IT WORKS\n\n1. Tap Practice\n2. Get a random impromptu speaking prompt (no choosing)\n3. Speak immediately in a short timed session\n4. Save your recording and review later to improve\n\n———————\n\nSUBSCRIPTION AND FREE TRIAL\n\nMinute Hatch offers a free trial for eligible users.\n\nIf you start a free trial, you will not be charged until the trial ends. Unless you cancel at least 24 hours before the end of the trial, your subscription will automatically renew at the price shown on the payment screen.\n\nSubscriptions renew automatically unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. You can manage or cancel your subscription anytime in your Apple ID settings.\n\nDeleting the app does not cancel your subscription.\n\n———————\n\nPRIVACY\n\nYour recordings stay private and are saved only on your device. You remain in full control of your data.\n\n———————\nEULA\nhttps://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/8f/2c/2a/8f2c2a04-04ca-129e-7daf-8ef93d47f728/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007ephone-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/minute-hatch/id6757143128?uo=4","developer":"Amenallah Hsoumi","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"300028504","title":"PointSolutions","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.45366,"ratings":11,"reviewCount":11555,"installs":"N/A","description":"The PointSolutions polling app (formerly TurningPoint) allows you to use your web-enabled device to respond to questions in real time and self-paced modes. PointSolutions is proven to increase retention and engage learners while allowing instructors to collect data to ensure comprehension.\n\nA variety of subscription options are available.\n\nFEATURES & FUNCTIONS:\n\n• Questions and response options are displayed on your device when polling is opened so that you can answer in real time or at your own pace during self-paced assessments.\n\n• Screen displays group responses, user response and indicates correct answer when polling is closed\n\n• Multiple choice, multiple response, hotspot, numeric response, true/false and short answer, open-ended question types available\n\n• Respond to attendance prompts\n\n• View courses you're enrolled in and track grade data\n\n• Ability to send messages to communicate questions or concerns to the presenter\n\n• Navigate through self-paced assessments in various ways: swiping, navigation carousel, question list view\n \n \nNOTE:\nPointSolutions mobile is compatible with iOS 13 and above. Users participating in sessions with previous OS versions can participate using a web browser by visiting ttpoll.com.\n\nContinued use of GPS running in the background can dramatically decrease battery life.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple126/v4/9b/98/40/9b984049-76f9-5148-e994-0964d2bf08fd/app_icon-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-10-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/pointsolutions/id300028504?uo=4","developer":"Turning Technologies, LLC","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":1013,"2":190,"3":389,"4":913,"5":9050}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6463744184","title":"Knowt: AI Flashcards & Notes","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.73438,"ratings":8,"reviewCount":8866,"installs":"N/A","description":"Discover a new way to study with Knowt, the all-in-one study app trusted by 4 million students. On top of being the #1 Flashcard App with Free Learn mode, Knowt also has unique AI features designed to save you time when studying. With one click, turn your notes into flashcards, or ask our AI to summarize your lecture videos and whip up flashcards on the key info for you. Knowt creates practice tests from any note, pdf, or video to help you prepare for exams. We offer a more efficient way to study, join us and take your learning to the next level with Knowt.\n\nWhat can you do on Knowt?\n\nMake flashcards sets: Use our AI flashcard maker to create your own set or grab some from popular sites like Quizlet.\n\nTurn your notes into flashcards and practice : Upload your notes and let our AI makes flashcards and practice tests to help you learn the material better.\n\nStudy with Free Learn Mode : Master your flashcards with unlimited rounds of learn mode or one of our other study modes (Practice Test, Match, Spaced Repetition)\n\nEfficient note-taking: Use our AI note-taking feature to take notes faster\n\nSpaced Repetition : Nail your tests with our scientifically proven algorithm that helps you remember your flashcards longer\n\nFree AP Study Guides : Check out the Exams Tab for free AP exam study guides, flashcards, and practice tests. (We're adding more exams soon!)\n\nExplore Free Learning Resources: Choose from millions of digital flashcard sets, class notes, study guides, and pdfs on a wide range of subjects, all created by fellow students.\n\nSeamless Sync: All your stuff syncs between the mobile app and website, making it easy to pick up where you left off, regardless of the device you're using.\n\n---------\n\nDownload the new Knowt App today and take your notes & flashcards wherever you go. Improve your grades and unleash the power of AI to learn better & faster.\n\nTerms of Service : https://knowt.com/terms\nPrivacy Policy : https://knowt.com/privacy\n\n---------------------------\n\nJoin the Knowt Community!\n\nDiscord: https://knowt.com/discord\nTikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@getknowt\nInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/getknowt\n\n---------------------------\n\nWe are committed to protecting your personal information and your right to privacy. If you have any questions or concerns about our practices with regard to your personal information, please contact us at contact@knowt.com","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/fd/d0/5b/fdd05b7f-814e-697f-8ded-08b90a2b19be/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-11-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/knowt-ai-flashcards-notes/id6463744184?uo=4","developer":"Knowt Inc.","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":294,"2":101,"3":169,"4":538,"5":7764}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6757496092","title":"ThePodio","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":5,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":2,"installs":"N/A","description":"ThePodio: Your AI-Powered Forensics Coach\n\nDon't practice blind. Get championship-level feedback before you step into the tournament room. ThePodio is designed for high school speech and debate competitors who want to improve their performance faster.\n\nKey Features:\n\nAI-Powered Speech Analysis: Receive instant, objective feedback on your delivery, pacing, and clarity—just like a judge's ballot.\n\nPractice Anytime, Anywhere: No need to wait for a coach or classroom. Record your drills on the go with our mobile-first design.\n\nTrack Your Progress: Visualize your improvement over the season with detailed history tracking.\n\nLeague-Specific Scoring: (Coming Soon) Custom rubrics tailored for NSDA and WACFL formats.\n\nWhether you are competing in Extemp, Oratory, or Debate, ThePodio gives you the competitive edge you need to break to finals.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/2a/0c/65/2a0c65d3-7d0e-a661-cf1c-065a9eb40161/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007ephone-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/thepodio/id6757496092?uo=4","developer":"Saurabh Raisinghani","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1606227567","title":"DebateBase","store":"app_store","genre":"Social Networking","score":5,"ratings":14,"reviewCount":14,"installs":"N/A","description":"Master the art of debate, critical thinking, and persuasive writing with DebateBase —\nyour AI-powered platform for building arguments, refining ideas, and collaborating in\nstructured debates.\nDebateBase transforms disagreement into discovery. Whether you're preparing for academic\ncompetitions, professional projects, or personal growth, our platform empowers you to construct,\norganize, and challenge ideas — all supported by Debato, your personal AI debate assistant.\n\nKey Features:\n● Revamped User Interface: Faster, cleaner, and designed for focused critical writing and\ndebate.\n● 8 AI Agents: Get help generating arguments, organizing citations, summarizing\ndebates, and more.\n● Debato Chatbot: Ask questions, practice building arguments, and get real-time writing\nadvice.\n● Structured Debates: Participate in debates with clear formats — opening, rebuttal, and\nclosing.\n● Personal Libraries: Save and organize your research, articles, and reference materials.\n● Group Reference Sections: Admins can upload shared research hubs for teams and\nclasses.\n● Eonian Debates: Engage in long-term debates that evolve as new evidence and\narguments emerge.\n● Voter Sentiment Scale: Express agreement or disagreement on a 1–10 spectrum, not\njust yes/no.\n● Safe, Respectful Space: Designed to encourage thoughtful critical thinking and\nevidence-based writing.\n\nDebateBase is ideal for:\n● Students practicing academic debate and essay writing\n● Educators enhancing classroom discussions\n● Clubs and teams preparing for tournaments\n● Professionals improving argumentation and analysis skills\n● Anyone seeking to refine critical writing and structured thinking\n\n Why DebateBase?\n● Build confidence in your writing and argumentation\n● Improve critical thinking and decision-making\n● Collaborate with others in public or private debates\n● Leverage cutting-edge AI to accelerate your learning\n\nJoin the future of debate and writing education. Build stronger arguments, refine your thinking,\nand unleash your voice — one debate at a time.\nDownload DebateBase today and start mastering persuasive writing and structured\ndebate!","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/4c/6f/15/4c6f159c-47b2-5ddf-2e09-09a5e7be95d9/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-11-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/debatebase/id1606227567?uo=4","developer":"Debatebase","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":14}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6468587465","title":"Debate Arena","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.69332,"ratings":75,"reviewCount":75,"installs":"N/A","description":"Welcome to the ultimate educational game that transforms you into a rhetoric expert! Dive into the world of persuasive speech, learn the secrets of winning arguments, and become quick-witted with our interactive AI-based learning experience. Whether you're gearing up for a debate, a crucial job conversation, or just want to sharpen your communication skills, Debate Arena is your perfect companion.\n\nKey Features:\n\n- Learn and Master Rhetorical Devices: Uncover an extensive library of rhetorical figures and devices. Understand the power of Straw Man, Ad Hominem Attacks and Red Herring and how to use them effectively.\n- Interactive Learning with AI Opponents: Test your skills in engaging challenges against sophisticated AI. Learn by doing and become adept at employing rhetoric in real-time scenarios.\n- Discuss current real life events and find the common ground, even if you think there is none.\n- Get argument feedback as well as references for your own arguments.\n- Real-World Applications: From asking for a raise to acing debates, our scenarios are crafted to help you apply your rhetorical skills in everyday situations.\n- Recognition Training: Learn to identify when someone else is using rhetorical devices on you. Stay one step ahead in conversations.\n- Quick Wit Development: Enhance your spontaneous speaking abilities. Learn to think on your feet and respond with confidence and flair.\n- Career Advancement: Use your newfound rhetorical skills to communicate more effectively in the workplace. Make your case for that well-deserved raise with persuasive prowess.\n- Engaging and Fun: Who said learning can't be entertaining? Enjoy a gamified approach to learning rhetoric, complete with rewards, achievements, and more.\n\nWhy Debate Arena?\n\n- Win Arguments: Gain the upper hand in debates and discussions.\n- Never Lose an Argument Again: Equip yourself with techniques that make your points unbeatable.\n- Become Quick-Witted: Respond with agility and wit in any conversation.\n- Persuade Effectively: Master the art of persuasion in personal and professional contexts.\n\nReady to elevate your communication skills and become a master of rhetoric? Download Debate Arena now and start your journey to becoming an eloquent and persuasive speaker!","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/92/c4/6b/92c46bf5-9549-39d4-c937-c83ee923c906/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007ephone-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/debate-arena/id6468587465?uo=4","developer":"Krue Software","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":2,"2":2,"3":2,"4":5,"5":64}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1497474446","title":"ArguMap Pro - Map Arguments","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":5,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":3,"installs":"N/A","description":"Develop your critical thinking skills, construct stronger arguments, express your thoughts more effectively, and picture lines of reasoning via ArguMap Pro!  \n\nJust as ordinary maps helps us to figure out where to go geographically, so argument maps help us to shine light on the landscape of reasoning.  ArguMap Pro, an app for mapping out arguments, has been specifically tailored and optimized to help people easily visualize their arguments and lines of reasoning.  It allows people to lay out and explore on screen the essential ingredients of lines of reasoning / arguments: premises, conclusions, objections, counter-objections, and the expressions of the logical relations among all those claims.\n\nArguMap Pro has the following features that make it superior to regular mind-mapping apps when it comes to mapping arguments:\n\n*  ArguMap Pro allows its users easily to group claims together to show how they jointly provide reasons in favor of a conclusion.  ArguMap Pro makes that grouping of claims as easy as dragging them onto each other.\n*  ArguMap Pro users can make use of connecting arrows specifically tailored to depicting how certain claims provide reasons *for* (solid green line) or *against* (dotted red line) other claims.\n*  With simple drags and taps, ArguMap Pro users can easily group or ungroup claims, and connect or disconnect parts of a map.  As a result, trying out different lines of reasoning is as easy as arranging pieces of paper on a table.\n*  With thicker or thinner connecting lines, ArguMap Pro can show how some premises offer stronger or weaker reasons in favor of a conclusion. \n*  Individuals can provide feedback on the various parts of a map using virtual notes. Commented-on maps can then be shared with their creators via email, text, AirDrop, or various other sharing mechanisms. \n\nThe commenting and sharing features of ArguMap Pro make it especially ideal for use by teachers and students who are working on improving the students' critical thinking and reasoning skills.  Students can easily share their maps with their teachers.  Teachers, in turn, can share commented-on maps back to their students.\n\nMaking use of ArguMap Pro's native integration with the Files app, users can save their maps either locally on their own devices or online via cloud storage.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/50/e8/2f/50e82fe9-58c9-0b24-289b-54ba1a8b23ed/ProAppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-0-0-1-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/argumap-pro-map-arguments/id1497474446?uo=4","developer":"AppsolutelyFun LLC","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":8.99,"free":false,"histogram":{}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6749748798","title":"JUNGLE: Live Video Chat Debate","store":"app_store","genre":"Entertainment","score":4.67385,"ratings":325,"reviewCount":325,"installs":"N/A","description":"Engage in meaningful debates and discussions on diverse topics with friends through video chat.\n\nJUNGLE provides a unique platform where each \"forest\" represents a dedicated chat room focused on specific discussion themes.\n\nDiscover which forests are trending and find the perfect conversation to join based on your interests. Whether you want to dive into current events, explore philosophical questions, or discuss everyday topics, there's always an active community ready to engage.\n\nThe app transforms casual conversations into enriching learning experiences. Through structured debates and open discussions, users develop critical thinking skills while exploring different perspectives from people around the world.\n\nVideo calling features enable real-time strategy sessions and deeper conversations, making every discussion more personal and impactful. Connect with like-minded individuals, challenge your viewpoints, and expand your knowledge through interactive dialogue.\n\nJoin JUNGLE to turn every conversation into an opportunity for growth, learning, and meaningful connection with others who share your curiosity about the world.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/91/42/0f/91420f28-95cb-a340-654f-0e7e01be60bf/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007ephone-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/jungle-live-video-chat-debate/id6749748798?uo=4","developer":"NATSUMI MURATA","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":17,"2":1,"3":11,"4":13,"5":283}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6744363860","title":"Hala: Speak English with AI","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.78827,"ratings":307,"reviewCount":307,"installs":"N/A","description":"Are you looking for an effective way to sound more confident in IELTS interviews or real-life conversations? Do you want to build a stronger vocabulary to understand native speakers and give fluent answers during IELTS speaking tasks?\n\nIf yes, then look no further than HalaEnglish – your all-in-one English learning app! Train your speaking and listening skills, build a high-level vocabulary, and master the grammar you need for the IELTS exam.\n\nNote: HalaEnglish is free to download with access to daily lessons. Access to premium features, including the AI Companion and Unlimited Practice, requires a subscription or in-app purchase.\n\nWhy HalaEnglish? HalaEnglish was launched in 2022 with a clear mission: to bridge the gap between English learners and real-world fluency. Many learners spend years memorizing grammar but freeze when it’s time to speak. We created HalaEnglish to provide a safe, judgment-free space to practice with smart AI partners.\n\nWhat You’ll Get: HalaEnglish helps you speak, write, and think more fluently through daily practice:\n\nImprove all four skills: Listening, Speaking, Reading, and Writing.\n\nStructured Lessons: Practice vocabulary, grammar, and pronunciation.\n\nQuizzes: Topic-based exercises designed to help you sound like a native.\n\nAI Companion (Premium): Get real-time feedback to improve your weak points and build confidence.\n\nPrepare for the IELTS Exam Improve your skills to meet B1 to C2 requirements. Write more accurate essays with detailed grammar explanations and quick fixes. Whether you want to achieve a 6.5 or an 8.0 Band, HalaEnglish has you covered.\n\nMain Features:\n\nInteractive Roleplay (Premium): Practice real-life conversations to learn how words are actually used.\n\nFlashcard Guessing Game: Strengthen your memory and recall essential vocabulary quickly.\n\nPronunciation Feedback (Premium): Speak confidently as the app identifies and corrects your pronunciation.\n\nReal-Time Grammar Help: Get immediate corrections to build clearer, better sentences.\n\nMultiple Accents: Familiarize yourself with diverse global accents from around the world.\n\nUnlimited Practice (Premium): Practice conversations as many times as you need to reach your desired fluency.\n\nJoin our growing community and start your journey to becoming a confident English speaker today!\n\nSubscription Information: HalaEnglish offers auto-renewable subscriptions to provide unlimited access to AI tools and premium content. Payment will be charged to your Apple ID account at the confirmation of purchase.\n\nConnect With Us \nEmail: hello.halaenglish@gmail.com \nTerms of Use: https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/30/31/b4/3031b4ac-896b-ebf0-7509-09fde063f5f6/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-11-0-sRGB-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/hala-speak-english-with-ai/id6744363860?uo=4","developer":"Bui Khoi","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":7,"2":2,"3":6,"4":19,"5":273}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6453023919","title":"Study Circle - The Focus App","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.6087,"ratings":23,"reviewCount":23,"installs":"N/A","description":"Searching for a study app? Look no further! Study Circle is the perfect app to boost your motivation and make studying enjoyable. Whether you're prepping for exams, learning new skills, or just need a productivity boost, Study Circle helps you stay focused and connected with your friends on the same journey.\n\nUnlock Your Study Potential:\n\n(1) Power of Community: Connect with your friends in real life and create your own virtual study circle! Share your study progress together, and cheer each other on. Motivation is contagious, and Study Circle makes it easy to stay inspired and accountable.\n\n(2) Intuitive Timer & Focus Mode: Beat procrastination with our easy-to-use study timer. Simply choose your subject, start the timer, and dive into focused study sessions. Break down your study time into manageable chunks for maximum efficiency.\n\n(3) Support & Encouragement: A little encouragement goes a long way. Easily send cheers and messages of support to your friends within the app. Celebrate milestones together and stay positive throughout your learning journey.\n\n(4) Visualize Your Progress: See your hard work pay off! Study Circle tracks your study records and displays them in colorful, easy-to-understand charts. Track your daily, weekly, and monthly progress to stay motivated and on track.\n\nStudy Circle is perfect for:\n* Students preparing for exams.\n* Individuals working towards qualifications or skill development.\n* Anyone believe in the power of shared goals and positive reinforcement.\n\nDownload Study Circle today and transform your study habits! Find your focus, achieve your goals, and enjoy the journey with your friends.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/34/53/59/3453598a-2a36-5ebc-a0d0-d7455d789bf4/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-8-0-P3-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/study-circle-the-focus-app/id6453023919?uo=4","developer":"Hikaru Hanada","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":1,"2":0,"3":2,"4":1,"5":19}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6566170239","title":"Apol: Debate smarter with AI","store":"app_store","genre":"Social Networking","score":5,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":1,"installs":"N/A","description":"Let's face it: online debates are often unproductive shouting matches. People talk past each other, opinions get more entrenched, and nobody really learns anything. Apol is here to change that.\n\nApol uses the power of advanced AI to transform how we discuss online. Simply enter any topic – from climate change to the pineapple-on-pizza debate – and Apol creates a structured discussion space with everything you need to have a productive and engaging conversation.\n\n- Key Questions: Apol automatically generates thought-provoking questions designed to spark insightful discussion and diverse perspectives, helping you understand the full complexity of the issue.\n- Intelligent AI Personas: Interact with unique AI personas, each with their own expertise and opinions, to challenge your assumptions and broaden your understanding.\n- Visualized Discussions: Apol generates a dynamic visual representation of the conversation, highlighting areas of agreement and disagreement to make it easier to follow and understand. Observe how participants' views evolve as the discussion progresses. \n- Summarized Arguments: Compare and contrast participants' views through concise AI-generated summaries of their main points.\n- AI Topic Suggestions: Apol suggests engaging and thought-provoking topics, helping you discover new areas of interest and debate.\n\nApol is here to change how we discuss online, bringing clarity, depth, and even a bit of fun back to important conversations!","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/ac/b8/07/acb80729-c964-0b39-8b23-ca8100219354/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-11-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/apol-debate-smarter-with-ai/id6566170239?uo=4","developer":"Dario Digregorio","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1225114836","title":"Basic English - ESL Course","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.73757,"ratings":5,"reviewCount":5552,"installs":"N/A","description":"EVERYTHING YOU NEED TO SPEAK ENGLISH FLUENTLY\n+ Support iPhone and iPad.\n+ iOS 13.0 above\n+ Can use offline.\n\n● Do you feel nervous or shy when you speak English?\n--> The app can help you learn English and improve your speaking without taking a class.\n--> All the lessons include images, slideshows, audio files, and quizzes to help you learn in an easy way. If you are a beginner or low intermediate English learner, then this app will be perfect for you.\n\n● Do other people sometimes not understand you when you speak English?\n--> The app will improve your English skill speaking, listening and understanding. All the lessons were created in a step-by-step manner teaching simple words and sentences in the beginning and slowly getting harder in later lessons.\n\n● Do you want to practice English speaking even when you have nobody to practice with?\n--> The app have many conversations for you practice speak English naturally and confidently for work, travel, or daily life ...\n\n● Would you like to know how to use English in real world situations?\n--> Become a confident English speaker by seeing, hearing, and participating with interactive lessons\n\n●●● Main features\n- Over 5000 conversations.\n- Support learning offline without internet\n- Expand vocebulary, grammar through videos channel.\n- Practice speaking and record to listen again.\n- Quizzes test will helpful for you test what did you know.\n- Bookmarks: group the lessons to a package.\n- History, Favorite will be better for you learn again.\n- Take note on lesson.\n- Support 3000 words for speaking.\n- Practice listening via English radio.\n\n●●● BEST GOAL: The app can help you after completing \n- You will be able to speak English. \n- Feel confident when you speak English.\n- Speak natural English with clear pronunciation.\n- Improve your English speaking even when you are alone.\n- Learn all the grammar and vocabulary you need to communicate in English.\n- Speak smoothly and fluently without stopping or pausing.\n- Learn English for specific situations like travel or business meeting.\n\n### Purchase to unlock features and ads free on the app ###\n- Privacy policy: https://mobilephl.com/eslcourse/privacy.php\n- Terms of Use: https://mobilephl.com/eslcourse/term_of_use.php\n- And read more USER LICENSE AGREEMENT (about EULA) at here: https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/e2/5a/d3/e25ad359-451c-cb0a-de0f-142290695169/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-10-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/basic-english-esl-course/id1225114836?uo=4","developer":"Nguyen Thi Hoai Thu","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":122,"2":91,"3":152,"4":392,"5":4795}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1069709715","title":"English Speaking for Beginners","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.6946,"ratings":6,"reviewCount":6444,"installs":"N/A","description":"100 Offline English Conversations by Native Speakers.\nDesigned for practicing daily English listening and speaking.\nYou can even practice listening to English while using other applications.\n\nEach English lesson simulates a conversation between the user and a native speaker. Users are put in a variety of real world situations and take part in conversations using the most frequently used english words and english grammar.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple116/v4/89/29/f1/8929f117-31d9-9afd-3106-b2485345ce39/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-0-0-5-0-0-sRGB-0-0-0-GLES2_U002c0-512MB-85-220-0-0.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/english-speaking-for-beginners/id1069709715?uo=4","developer":"Xung Le","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":128,"2":110,"3":269,"4":588,"5":5349}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1460766549","title":"Epop: Learn Real-Life English","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.75535,"ratings":1,"reviewCount":1864,"installs":"N/A","description":"Want to learn English with an app that really works?\nWith Epop, learning English feels like playing a game. You can even compete in leagues against other learners.\n\n1. Step-By-Step English Learning Plan\nJust solve 20 questions, and our AI will provide exercises tailored to your level!\n\n- Learn new phrases and when to use them.\n- Listen to sentences recorded at the speed native speakers actually speak.\n- Practice your listening and pronunciation at the same time.\n\nThere's no need to worry about where to start.\n\n2. Study English like You're Playing a Game.\nFill in the blanks, build sentences, and earn points.\nEpop's exercises are designed so that you'll have fun learning grammar and vocabulary.\nIt doesn't even feel like studying!\n\n3. Practice Speaking English Naturally.\nPractice speaking in scenarios based on real life.\nRepeat sentences, improve your intonation, and get feedback on your pronunciation.\nSpeaking English has never been so easy!\nImprove your pronunciation and listening skills at the same time!\n\n4. Expand Your Vocabulary With Practical, Real-Life Phrases.\nLearn English phrases based on your level and goals.\nYou can create your own vocab list and review it anytime.\nStudy essential words you'll often encounter in exams, while traveling, and at work.\n\n5. No More Forgetting What You've Learned\nOur AI brings back the phrases you need to review at the perfect time to ensure you remember them.\nThanks to our review system, you'll be able to keep vocabulary, expressions, and grammar points fresh in your mind!\nStudy, repeat, and memorize effectively!\n\n6. Optimized for Stress-Free Learning\nOur app is designed so that anyone can learn, speak, and understand English easily and effectively.\nWe're constantly improving our app based on feedback from thousands of learners.\n\n7. Just 10 Minutes a Day Is All It Takes\nWaiting for the bus, during meals, before bed... Turn any spare moment into an opportunity to study English.\n\nEverything You Need for Learning English in One App!\n- [Vocabulary]\nSolve vocab quizzes tailored to your level. You can turn on speaking mode to answer out loud.\n- [Grammar]\nArrange the word cards to build sentences. You'll get detailed grammar explanations if you make a mistake.\n- [Listening & Speaking]\nImprove your pronunciation and intonation through English listening and speaking practice.\n- [Auto-Review]\nPhrases are brought back for you to review at the best time to ensure long-term retention!\n\nOver 8 Million Downloads!\nJoin the millions already learning English with Epop.\nDownload Epop now and master English through AI-powered learning, gamification, and realistic conversation practice!\n\nTerms of Service:\nhttps://epop.ai/legal/termsAndConditions/en\n\nPrivacy Policy:\nhttps://epop.ai/legal/privacy/en","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/3c/86/ff/3c86ffbb-f2a1-528d-b738-3b349b20121b/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-0-0-1-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/epop-learn-real-life-english/id1460766549?uo=4","developer":"EpopSoft Inc.","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":38,"2":25,"3":42,"4":145,"5":1614}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1558659494","title":"10 Minute English","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.69747,"ratings":11,"reviewCount":11976,"installs":"N/A","description":"English is easy! All you need is 10 minutes a day.\nThis is enough to improve your speaking, listening, and even writing skills quickly.\n \nWith the 10-Minute English app, you are going to get better at speaking and understanding the language by expanding your vocabulary—over 500 new words in a month, each month.\n \nSay «Beats me» instead of «I don’t know» and «Can’t complain» instead of «I’m fine», and you will sound perfect to all native English speakers out there.\n \nWhy 10-Minute English?\n \n*It’s scientifically proven*\n \nThe method of spaced repetition enables you to remember words and expressions far better than usual lessons. Even in a year, you will be able to recall 90% of everything you have learned.\n \n10-Minute English employs a learning technique recognized by the best world’s universities. Breaking down big topics into smaller parts allows you to learn the most valuable information in less time, be it common English collocations, idioms, or grammar rules.\n \nOur word-building exercises activate your visual memory and improve your language skills. Get one step ahead of everyone who studies English.\n \n*It gets you speaking right away*\n \nThe first 500 most popular words and phrases will serve as a powerful boost for your English. You will learn to describe your life, socialize and speak in the workplace more confidently.\n\n*Read in English and learn words naturally*\n\nWith 10-Minute English, you also have the opportunity to read popular books in English. The novels have been specially selected and adapted for your learning. Instantly translate words and sentences and learn them in context — this is a natural and engaging way to enrich your vocabulary.\n \n*You learn fast*\n \nIn 3 months, you will cover a language program designed for a one-year college course.\n \nChoose the most compelling ones from 47 up-to-date topics: Travelling and Life in a big city, Business and Job interview, Slang, Hobbies, and many more. Learn top 100 verbs and adverbs to see the improvement immediately.\n \nYour aspiration means everything. It doesn’t matter that you don’t have much time to spend on your English studies. Start off with only 10 minutes a day, and this will work wonders for your skills.\n \nBegin now, and you’re going to be surprised how good at English you really are.\n\nAccess to the 10-Minute English application is offered on a subscription basis. In order to use the app’s services, you will need to subscribe to any of the available plans.\nIf you choose to subscribe, the payment will be charged to your iTunes Account at confirmation of purchase.\nYour account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period at the same price.\nYou can manage your subscription at any time and turn off auto-renewal by going to your iTunes Account Settings.\nAny unused portion of a free trial period will be forfeited when the user purchases a 10-Minute English subscription.\n \nTerms of use: https://www.mobilecleverapps.com/terms\nPrivacy policy: https://www.mobilecleverapps.com/privacy","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/c5/7b/ea/c57bea73-9d2a-47c4-80ba-8b23154ab19a/AppIcon-1x_U007emarketing-0-8-0-sRGB-0-85-220-0.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/10-minute-english/id1558659494?uo=4","developer":"Clever Apps","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":459,"2":124,"3":268,"4":879,"5":10246}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6683289805","title":"Fluently - AI English Tutor","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.83371,"ratings":3,"reviewCount":3903,"installs":"N/A","description":"Fluently: Speak English with AI Tutor\n\nStop memorizing boring rules. With Fluently, you practice speaking English in real conversations and get instant AI corrections — anytime, anywhere.\n\nHOW IT WORKS\n1. Install Fluently\n2. Talk with your AI tutor on any topic you like\n3. Get real-time corrections and a personalized plan to improve faster\n\nWHY FLUENTLY?\n- Practice speaking, not just grammar drills\n- Real-time corrections: grammar, vocabulary, pronunciation\n- Personalized program based on your speech and interests\n- Boost your fluency and confidence in interviews, meetings, or everyday chats\n\nFEATURES\n- Unlimited speaking practice with AI tutor\n- Track your progress and see tangible improvements\n- Vocabulary growth and grammar support\n- Simple and intuitive design — start speaking instantly\n\nFLUENTLY PREMIUM\nGet unlimited access to personalized AI sessions, advanced feedback, and progress tracking.\n\nSubscriptions renew automatically unless canceled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. Manage your subscription in iTunes Account Settings.\nTerms of Service: https://getfluently.app/tos\nPrivacy Policy: https://getfluently.app/privacy\nLicense Agreement: https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/d8/f9/c0/d8f9c0c4-f7fb-3546-9a4f-86fb67914430/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007ephone-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/fluently-ai-english-tutor/id6683289805?uo=4","developer":"Fluently, Inc.","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":77,"2":27,"3":60,"4":140,"5":3599}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"959001619","title":"Tandem: Conversation exchange","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.60078,"ratings":36,"reviewCount":36594,"installs":"N/A","description":"**Tandem language exchange is the process of joining forces with someone who is a native speaker of the language you want to learn**\n\nLanguages are a 'learn by doing' kind of thing. This particular method is at the heart of Tandem, the global language exchange community. Connect with native speakers, start chatting and finally reach fluency in the language you’re learning!\n\nLearn, connect, and share with 1-to-1 chats or try out Parties, the ultimate group learning audio space. There are millions of Tandem members with just as many interests, so find your people – and start speaking their language today!\n\nReach fluency in 300+ languages, including Spanish, English, Japanese, Korean, German, Italian, Portuguese, Russian, Simplified and Traditional Chinese, and 12 different sign languages, including American Sign Language.\n\nWhy Tandem helps you to practice and learn languages:\n\nBOOST YOUR VOCABULARY\nFor the times when you’re struggling to find the correct words, our in-app translation feature helps you compose a message or translate an incoming one. \n\nPERFECT YOUR PRONUNCIATION\nFit in with the locals and improve your speaking skills using voice notes, audio and video calls.\n\nGRASP THE GRAMMAR\nHelp each other grasp the difficult parts of language learning with our message correction and comment features.\n\nTANDEM YOUR WAY\nForget strict schedules and learning by the book. Embrace your personal language learning style—whether that’s messaging, calling, or even meeting in person. \n\nDOWNLOAD TANDEM AND MASTER ANY LANGUAGE NOW!\n\n______________\n\nHow to learn languages on Tandem:\n1. Select the language(s) you want to learn in the app\n2. Tell us about your language learning goals and your ideal Tandem partner\n3. Search for native speakers of your target language in the community \n4. Kick-off your language exchange experience by sending your first message\n5. Share topics with the Tandem community so you can have meaningful conversations about what interests you\n6. Keep up the conversation with your new Tandem “pen pal” and speak like a native in no time!\n\nWhile many features are free, you can choose to subscribe to Tandem Pro to access all the features on the app. Your subscription will automatically renew unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current payment period. Your iTunes account will be automatically charged at the same price for renewal within the 24-hour period prior to the end of the current payment period unless you change your subscription preferences in your Account Settings.\n\n ______________\n\nApp Access Permissions:\n\nOptional permissions:\n\n- Location information: Required to use the Nearby feature to see members near you, the Travel feature to show members around the world and to add an approximate location to your profile.\n- Microphone: Required for sending audio messages, making audio and video calls, and joining Language Parties.\n- Camera: Required for taking photos to upload to your profile or post in a Language Club, take and send a photo in a chat, video calling, and scanning QR codes.\n- Notifications: Used to send you notifications about acceptance into the community, new messages, new followers and their posts, new references and marketing communication.\n- Nearby devices: Bluetooth access is required to connect audio devices during a call or Language Party.\n\nYou can still use Tandem without granting optional permissions, except features where their nature requires the respective permission, like a video call requiring camera permission.\n\nGot a question? Contact us on support@tandem.net \n\nLicenses: Tandem – Language Exchange is licensed by Tandem Fundazioa (http://tandemcity.info) \n\nPrivacy policy: https://tandem.net/privacy\nTerms of Service: www.tandem.net/pages/termsofservice","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/b4/d2/21/b4d2216a-dae5-d541-f7b0-07f888322114/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-0-0-1-0-0-P3-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/tandem-conversation-exchange/id959001619?uo=4","developer":"Tripod Technology GmbH","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":1482,"2":590,"3":1594,"4":3723,"5":29205}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6478287397","title":"Speak & Learn English: Learna","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.6585,"ratings":221,"reviewCount":221405,"installs":"N/A","description":"Ready to Speak English Confidently? \n\nWelcome to Learna AI English Tutor App, your all-in-one solution for mastering the English language! Learn English with grammar, speaking, reading, pronunciation, and vocabulary practices designed to enhance your proficiency in every aspect of the language.\n\nWith Learna AI, you can speak English confidently and effectively through interactive conversations. Our app takes your language learning journey beyond traditional methods. Whether you're a beginner or an advanced learner, Learna AI is here to help you learn & speak English in a fun, engaging, and personalized way.\n\nEnglish practices and lessons are guided by our Learna AI Virtual Chat Character, offering tailored support as you learn. You can speak with the AI character to improve both your speaking and listening skills. The app provides real-time feedback, helping you speak correctly and refine your vocabulary as you go. This makes learning English more dynamic, interactive, and efficient, as you can practice speaking at your own pace.\n\nLearna AI also focuses on improving your grammar skills. You’ll learn essential grammar rules and practice them through a variety of exercises that help reinforce your understanding. The grammar practices are designed to gradually improve your proficiency, allowing you to speak with accuracy and clarity. As you learn grammar, you will build a stronger foundation for your speaking and writing skills.\n\nVocabulary plays a critical role in speaking English fluently. With Learna AI, you can improve your vocabulary by learning new words and phrases that are practical and useful in daily conversations. Each lesson focuses on building your vocabulary, ensuring you have a broad range of words at your disposal. The app features vocabulary practice that adapts to your level, helping you speak more naturally and confidently.\n\nYour pronunciation also gets a boost with Learna AI. As you speak, you’ll receive valuable feedback to improve your pronunciation. The app includes exercises specifically designed to help you master English pronunciation and speak clearly. Pronunciation practices allow you to correct mistakes and sound more authentic when speaking English.\n\nTrack your progress with detailed performance metrics and milestones. Set learning goals to monitor your achievements and celebrate your successes. With continuous practice, you’ll see your speaking skills improve, and your vocabulary will expand. By setting specific goals, you ensure that each practice session is focused and effective.\n\nLearna AI Language Tutor Features:\n\nEnglish Conversation Practice with Learna AI Virtual Chat Character\nGet feedback from Learna AI for your mistakes\nLearn English Grammar with tailored lessons\nImprove your English Reading Skills\nEnrich your English Vocabulary with daily vocabulary practices & Learn new words \nSpelling Check and vocabulary reinforcement\nPerfect your English Pronunciation through interactive exercises\nEnhance your English Speaking Skills through practical speaking practice\nTrack your progress and set goals to continually improve\nSpeak, practice, and learn today with Learna AI, your partner in mastering the English language!\nTerms of Use: https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/a8/6d/78/a86d7853-20ea-480b-5731-3b388939abb8/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-11-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/speak-learn-english-learna/id6478287397?uo=4","developer":"DEEP FLOW SOFTWARE SERVICES","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":7565,"2":4494,"3":8490,"4":14886,"5":185970}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1149631662","title":"Everyday English Speaking","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.68516,"ratings":1,"reviewCount":1442,"installs":"N/A","description":"●●● \u001dDo you want to speak english?\nLet's \"Everyday English Conversation\" help you. The app has many conversation was used everyday for you learn and practice.\nApp has 18 topics such as: Communications, Eating, FASHION ... and over 1000 audios for each topic.\n\n- You can listen audio and speak again. Easy to use and simple. It's really good for beginer.\n\n- Add new conversation for user practice with native speaker\n  + Beginner Conversation\n  + Business Conversation\n  + Conversation Courses\n\n● New features:\n  + Word for English speaking (over 3000 word popular you can learn)\n  + Idioms and Phrases.\n  + Quizzes English test\n  + Record your voice and listen again.\n\n### Purchase to unlock features and ads free on the app ###\n- Privacy policy: https://mobilephl.com/eslcourse/privacy.php\n- Terms of Use: https://mobilephl.com/eslcourse/term_of_use.php\n- And read more USER LICENSE AGREEMENT (about EULA) at here: https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/99/9e/80/999e802b-13d8-7431-afda-6c0c229d7b9e/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-8-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/everyday-english-speaking/id1149631662?uo=4","developer":"Nguyen Thi Hoai Thu","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":42,"2":27,"3":46,"4":113,"5":1214}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1322464061","title":"English Speaking: SpeakFluent","store":"app_store","genre":"Book","score":4.66346,"ratings":312,"reviewCount":312,"installs":"N/A","description":"Speak English confidently with real-life conversations!\n\nEnglish Speaking: SpeakFluent helps you improve your speaking skills with daily English dialogues. Designed for adults, this app is perfect for anyone who wants to practice English speaking every day – anywhere, anytime, even without internet.\n\n● Key Features\n    \n*** Daily English Conversations \n   - Learn useful phrases and expressions through practical dialogues for real-world situations.\n\n*** Offline English Speaking Practice\n   - Cache the lessons and practice anytime without an internet connection.\n\n*** Speak English Fluently    - Improve pronunciation and confidence through repeated speaking practice.\n\n*** Designed for Adults and Beginners\n   - Simple and clear structure, ideal for adult learners at beginner or intermediate level.\n\n*** Learn to Speak English Naturally\n   - Lessons based on everyday topics like shopping, work, travel, greetings, and more.\n\n*** Audio + Text Support \n   - Listen to native speakers and follow along with written transcripts.\n\n*** Track Your Progress \n   - Save your favorite lessons and repeat conversations to build fluency.\n\n\n● Perfect For\n- Adults learning English for work or travel\n- ESL learners who want to improve speaking\n- Self-study English learners\n- Users looking for a simple and effective speaking app\n\nStart speaking English today with SpeakFluent!\nPractice anytime, anywhere – even offline.\n\n\n### Support\n+ Both iPhone and iPad.\n+ iOS 13.0 above.\n+ Can be used offline mode.\n\n### Purchase to unlock features and ads free on the app ###\n- Privacy policy: https://mobilephl.com/eslcourse/privacy.php\n- Terms of Use: https://mobilephl.com/eslcourse/term_of_use.php\n- And read more USER LICENSE AGREEMENT (about EULA) at here: https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/\n\nDownload now and speak English every day!","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/84/c9/1c/84c91c8e-ea12-9148-cc6d-6aeb0030d620/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-8-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/english-speaking-speakfluent/id1322464061?uo=4","developer":"Nguyen Thi Hoai Thu","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":8,"2":3,"3":14,"4":36,"5":251}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"519076558","title":"Blood Pressure Tracker SmartBP","store":"app_store","genre":"Medical","score":4.50823,"ratings":54,"reviewCount":54609,"installs":"N/A","description":"SmartBP® is a blood pressure app that enables you to log, monitor, evaluate, and share BP reports using iOS devices and Apple Watch. In addition, SmartBP connects with Apple Health. With your health information at your fingertips, you can now take a more active role in your own health. For those with prehypertension or hypertension, SmartBP can assist in monitoring progress, identifying trends, and managing all your blood pressure and heart measurements, ultimately aiming to enhance your overall heart health and blood pressure. SmartBP is a smarter way to manage your blood pressure measurements and track your progress.\n\nDisclaimer: \n1) SmartBP al­lows you to record, track and an­a­lyze trends in your blood pres­sure. You can ei­ther man­u­al­ly en­ter your records or use a blood pres­sure mon­i­tor to sync with SmartBP through Apple Health. SmartBP alone does not mea­sure blood pres­sure. You need a sep­a­rate blood pres­sure mon­i­tor to mea­sure blood pres­sure.\n\n2) SmartBP is NOT a substitute for a doctor or professional healthcare or advice. Any health related information provided is for informational purposes only and should not be used to replace the advice of healthcare professionals.\n\n3) SmartBP Cloud Sync is not a replacement for backing up your health data. While we strive for the highest data security, no measures can ensure 100% protection. Regular data backups are the user's responsibility.\n\nFor information on how to use the app, visit our website \n* Video: www.smartbp.app\n* FAQ: www.smartbp.app/faq \n\nFeatures- \n\n- Log your systolic, diastolic blood pressure, pulse rate and weight. Body mass index (BMI), pulse pressure (PP) and mean arterial pressure (MAP) is automatically calculated. You can manually enter measurements or seamlessly sync them with a supported Bluetooth BP monitors such as:\n* A&D \n* Omron \n* Beurer\n* Transtek\n\n- Quickly add notes (e.g. before dinner) and measurement information (e.g. sitting, left arm) using tags. \n\n- Store and access all your blood pressure measurements anywhere and anytime using Apple HealthKit. Avoid manual data entry and reduce errors by automatically uploading blood pressure measurements to HealthKit by auto-syncing with SmartBP. The following Blood Pressure Monitor Apps can connect to HealthKit (check for compatibility with different models): \n* A&D \n* Omron \n* QardioArm\n* iHealth\n* Withings\n\n- Share your blood pressure information with your doctor, healthcare provider or family using email, text message (SMS), Apple HealthKit. Create blood pressure reports in PDF format with blood pressure data, charts and stats and share with your doctor or healthcare provider. \n\n- View 7, 14, 30 day summary grouped by daily AM/PM averages and tags. Create, share and print summary PDF reports and CSV file.\n\n- Print PDF reports or charts directly\n\n- Analyze your progress through clear graphs and statistics (including mean and variability). Filter data using tags to assess lifestyle changes or medication effectiveness. Compare tagged graphs side by side and observe systolic vs. diastolic blood pressure correlations.\n\n- Track your Heart Rate trends\n\n- Sync ECG records\n\n- Back up your health data and access it on all your mobile devices with SmartBP Cloud.  This is an optional service. We do not sell your health data.\n\n- Sync directly between iPhone and iPad through Bluetooth or WiFi without sharing on the cloud.\n\n- Back up blood pressure data by exporting to Dropbox, and Drive, or import from CSV files into the app.\n\n- Protect your data with TouchID, FaceID or Pin keypad protection.\n\n- Set medication reminders & track effectiveness.\n\n- Intuitive color coded data to identify normal, prehypertensive, stage I and II hypertension. These limits can be modified. Categorize your records based on 2017 ACA/AHA, 2023 ESC/ESH or create your own custom categories.\n\n- Create multiple user profiles and manage them from a single app/device.\n\n- US and international height and weight units supported.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/59/32/d7/5932d7a2-f5d8-ce83-40f8-f6d6ea755a68/NewAppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-11-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/blood-pressure-tracker-smartbp/id519076558?uo=4","developer":"Evolve Medical Systems, LLC","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":3186,"2":974,"3":2445,"4":6299,"5":41705}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1296471956","title":"Blood Pressure Tracker •","store":"app_store","genre":"Medical","score":4.6623,"ratings":14,"reviewCount":14821,"installs":"N/A","description":"Blood Pressure Tracker is a blood pressure app that helps you track and monitor your blood pressure at your convenience. You can log your BP, pulse, weight, blood glucose, blood oxygen, and more. There is also a spot for notes, so you can add whatever additional information you need, like how you are feeling that day that may have an effect on your blood pressure, like tired, stressed, anxious, etc.\n\nThe Blood Pressure App also allows you to track your medications. Search from a list of medications, add notes, and include your dosage. This allows you to keep your list of medications with you whether it is for yourself, a loved one or healthcare professional. You can export this list of medications through a report and send to anyone.\n\nThis blood pressure app has an unlimited history and will calculate your average for you as well. Keeping track of your blood pressure over a period of time is the best way to ensure good health. Each log will also display the date and time to ensure you know when exactly you took the measurement. Blood Pressure Tracker also syncs with Apple Health to log your blood pressure and pulse data directly to the Health app!\n\nThe app also allows you to view graphs and generate custom reports. The graphs allow you to spot trends and the PDF reports allow you to share your data with anyone. You can send via text, email and more. \n\nBlood Pressure App is your companion app to help you against hypertension! Using a blood pressure app tracker has been shown to be effective in managing blood pressure. Some features may require a paid subscription. \n\nWe use the Standard EULA which can be found here: https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/93/31/3b/93313bb6-4e19-8dfc-eef4-e241c5dee1ba/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/blood-pressure-tracker/id1296471956?uo=4","developer":"App Sub 1 LLC","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":551,"2":153,"3":451,"4":1440,"5":12226}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6450994700","title":"Blood Pressure App-Health Body","store":"app_store","genre":"Health & Fitness","score":4.47044,"ratings":8,"reviewCount":8747,"installs":"N/A","description":"Introduction to our Blood pressure app - a must-have tool for tracking and analyzing blood pressure records.  Through our user-friendly interface, users can easily record and monitor their blood pressure readings, helping them to keep abreast of their health status.\n\nMain features:\n1.  Record blood pressure readings: Our app allows users to easily record their blood pressure readings, ensuring an accurate and up-to-date record of their health status.\n\n2.  Analyze blood pressure trends: With intuitive charts and graphs, users can easily track blood pressure trends over time.  This feature enables individuals to recognize patterns and make informed decisions about their health.\n\n3.  Health information and tips: Our app not only tracks blood pressure, but also provides a wealth of health information and tips to help users live a healthier lifestyle.  Stay up to date and motivated with our carefully selected content on nutrition, exercise, stress management and more.\n\n4.  Personalized Reminders: Never miss a blood pressure reading with our personalized reminders.  Set reminders to ensure timely measurements throughout the day and promote continuous monitoring of blood pressure.\n\n5.  Secure and private: Protecting user data is our top priority.  Our app ensures the privacy and security of all sensitive information, allowing users to track their blood pressure with confidence.\n\nThe disclaimer states:\n\nAny health advice provided by this app does not constitute professional medical advice.  For any health concerns, we recommend that you consult a professional doctor or medical institution.\n\nGet basic membership to unlock VIP features\nSubscription Plan:\nUnlimited access to all features\n- You can subscribe for unlimited access to all the content offered by the app.\n- Automatically charged at a certain rate based on the selected subscription plan.\n- After confirming the purchase, the payment will be deducted from your iTunes account.\n- After purchase, you can control your subscription and disable automatic renewal in your account Settings.\nYour subscription will be automatically renewed unless you opt out of automatic renewal at least 24 hours before the end of the subscription period.\n\nDisclaimer: https://iserversboost.com/Disclaimer\nPrivacy policy: https://www.iserversboost.com/1/privacy\nUser terms: https://www.iserversboost.com/term\nEULA:https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/\nContact us: ouyangkuan@proton.me\n\nDownload our blood pressure app today and take control of your health.  Easily track, analyze and master your blood pressure readings.  Provide yourself with valuable health information and make informed decisions to achieve a healthier lifestyle.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/61/5c/c4/615cc4a3-b293-1a08-433b-8c2517bed8b0/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007ephone-0-1-0-85-220.jpeg/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/blood-pressure-app-health-body/id6450994700?uo=4","developer":"Vincentius Tech Sdn Bhd","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":752,"2":118,"3":244,"4":782,"5":6851}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1575719736","title":"Blood Pressure Log, Heart Rate","store":"app_store","genre":"Lifestyle","score":4.31841,"ratings":16,"reviewCount":16362,"installs":"N/A","description":"With Heart Rate - Blood Pressure Log App you can effortlessly monitor, analyze, and share your data from your iOS device.\n\nEasily take your heart rate by simply placing your finger on the camera, and keep track of your heart rate trends. Start today to make heart monitoring easier than ever and take charge of your wellbeing!\n\nKEY BENEFITS\n\n • Heart Rate Measurement & Analysis - Gain detailed insights into your heart rate, allowing you to observe how it varies with different activities and emotions.\n • Blood Pressure Log - Record your systolic and diastolic blood pressure, along with your pulse (BPM).\n • Stress & Energy Tracking - Monitor your stress levels and energy throughout the day to support effective stress management and optimize your activities.\n • RMSSD & SDNN - Get a comprehensive view of your heart rate by analyzing the time between heartbeets.\n • Oxygen Level Log - Log your blood oxygen saturation to assess respiratory function and overall oxygen supply.\n • History - Review detailed history and statistics to keep tabs on your progress.\n • Sharing & Export - Quickly share or export your data as needed.\n • Daily Tracking Reminders - Stay consistent and proactive about your wellbeing with gentle daily reminders.\n\nIMPORTANT NOTE\n\nThis app is not intended for medical use, nor to diagnose, cure, treat, or prevent any disease.\nIt is not classified as a medical device and is designed solely for general wellness and lifestyle insights.\nThis app does not directly measure blood pressure and requires an external blood pressure monitor.\nAlways seek professional medical advice for any health-related questions or decisions.\n\nBy using the app, you are agreeing to our Privacy Policy and Terms of Use:\n • Terms of Use: https://tou.bloodpressuremonitor.pro/\n • Privacy Policy: https://pp.bloodpressuremonitor.pro/","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/41/03/56/41035644-72fb-1b96-d232-be85870880fa/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/blood-pressure-log-heart-rate/id1575719736?uo=4","developer":"NarrativeLab OU","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":1713,"2":362,"3":807,"4":1600,"5":11880}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"430133691","title":"Blood Pressure Monitor","store":"app_store","genre":"Medical","score":4.59999,"ratings":2,"reviewCount":2230,"installs":"N/A","description":"The Blood Pressure Monitor app makes it easy for you to manage your blood pressure, weight, temperature, and other health data. It comes with a range of useful features, including lifetime data tracking, chart visualization, statistics reporting, medication correlation, email import/export, optional cloud data synchronization, reminders, and much more.\n\nOne of the standout features of our app is its comprehensive data tracking capabilities. With this app, you can manage all of your health and medical readings in one place, making it easy to manage your health and stay on top of any potential issues. Whether you are trying to maintain a healthy weight, keep your blood pressure under control, or monitor your medication, this app has you covered.\n\n- Comprehensive reading input fields collection\n- Customizable input data form \n- Simplified user interface \n- Optimized keyboard input \n\nMedication correlation - have you ever wanted to find out how your vital signs change according to different medication you take? How your blood pressure differs on two different arms? This app is designed to help you find out.\n\n- Both oral and injection types of medication tracking and correlation \n- Left/right arm tracking and correlation for blood pressure measurement \n- Body position tracking and correlation for blood pressure measurement \n- Meal type tracking and correlation for glucose measurement\n- More to come.\n\nData Visualization – a chart is worth a thousand words. The graphical charts not only give you a visual trend of the vital signs, but also show warning signs (BP only). \n\n- All vital signs are graphically presented \n- No time limitation \n- Swipe to scroll chart to reveal more data history \n- Optimized chart drawing performance \n\nData Sync - seamlessly automatic data synchronization among different iOS devices. \n\n- enter once, view on any devices (iOS only for now) \n- make the cloud work for you \n- an active account is required (free to create) \n\nEmail Import/Export – simple yet versatile email/export feature lets you communicate with your healthcare provider at a breeze. \n\n- Multiple export formats (PDF, CSV, plain message) to choose from \n- Selectable From/To date range \n- Selectable vital sign category to export \n- Charts included in emails and PDF files \n- Flexible format recognition during import \n- Friendly import instructions and feedback messages \n\nLots of other bells and whistles \n- Dual mode history reading views, express for quick browsing and grouped for complete revisiting\n- Built-in reminder, never miss a check up time and seamless integration with iOS reminder app \n- Multiple user accommodation, one app to track the whole family (upgrade might be needed)\n- Adjustable noon time hour, making AM/PM more meaningful, even for “night owls” \n- Adjustable warning threshold values (BP only) \n- Flexible units support with US, metric or mixed system \n\nDisclaimer: this app does not drive any medical device or measure blood pressure directly. All inputs have to be entered manually.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple116/v4/52/ac/3e/52ac3ec8-9338-7519-4494-61d09e241b92/AppIcon-BP-Lite-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-0-0-7-0-0-sRGB-0-0-0-GLES2_U002c0-512MB-85-220-0-0.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/blood-pressure-monitor/id430133691?uo=4","developer":"Taconic System LLC","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":75,"2":35,"3":49,"4":389,"5":1682}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1585198646","title":"Equate Heart Chart","store":"app_store","genre":"Medical","score":4.74451,"ratings":11,"reviewCount":11668,"installs":"N/A","description":"A blood pressure and health metrics tracking app designed by doctors to help you collect and manage your blood pressure readings along with other health metrics. This app has been created to help you measure your blood pressure accurately using your own home monitor, follow your trends over time, and help your healthcare provider best manage your care.\n\n• Ensure your blood pressure measurements are performed accurately by following our \"how-to\" measurement guide.\n\n• Rapidly and efficiently calculate blood pressure averages with our Swipe Averaging™ feature. Bring your phone to your next appointment with your physician or pharmacist, and they can use Swipe Averaging™ to quickly and easily assess your blood pressure for clinical decision making.\n\n• Learn from internationally renowned experts what blood pressure is, about high and low blood pressure, and how blood pressure can best be controlled.\n\n• Easily track your blood pressure using an Equate blood pressure monitor.\n\n\n\nThe following Bluetooth-enabled blood pressure monitors are supported.\n\n• Equate 6000 Series Upper Arm Blood Pressure Monitor\n• Equate 6500 Series Wrist Blood Pressure Monitor\n• Equate 8500 Series Premium Upper Arm Blood Pressure Monitor\n\n\n\nMEDICAL DISCLAIMER: The Heart Chart app is not intended for the diagnosis of or screening for hypertension. Users should be aware that the Heart Chart app is an information management service to enable the analysis of blood pressure data and is not intended to be a substitute for the advice of a health care professional. Individuals should always consult their doctor or other qualified health care professional with any questions they may have regarding a medical condition, including any queries or concerns about blood pressure management. You should never disregard professional medical advice or delay in seeking it because of information transmitted to or contained in your Heart Chart app.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple126/v4/d8/e2/0c/d8e20cdc-7ddc-7132-c49c-943e1eb0abdf/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-0-0-7-0-0-sRGB-0-0-0-GLES2_U002c0-512MB-85-220-0-0.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/equate-heart-chart/id1585198646?uo=4","developer":"A&D Company, Limited","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":137,"2":99,"3":412,"4":1312,"5":9708}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6747271310","title":"Blood Pressure App Free of ad","store":"app_store","genre":"Health & Fitness","score":4.49322,"ratings":738,"reviewCount":738,"installs":"N/A","description":"Track, Manage & Understand Your Blood Pressure – All in One App\n\nTake control of your heart health with our Blood Pressure App – BP Tracker, your personal assistant for monitoring blood pressure, heart rate, and overall cardiovascular wellness. Whether you’re managing hypertension or just staying proactive, our app offers a simple and intuitive way to stay informed and healthy.\n\nEnjoy full access with our yearly subscription—starting with a 3-day free trial. Explore every feature, experience the best of our app, and continue only if you love it.\n- Easy BP Logging: Record your systolic, diastolic, and pulse readings in just seconds.\n- Smart Trends & Charts: Visualize your progress with dynamic charts and historical trends that help you understand changes over time.\n- Personalized Insights: Receive health tips and tailored insights based on your data to better understand your heart health.\n- Multi-User Support: Track readings for yourself and your loved ones all in one place.\n- Reminders & Notifications: Never miss a measurement with custom reminders.\n- Export & Share Reports: Generate detailed health reports to share with your doctor via PDF or CSV.\n\nOur app does not measure blood pressure directly. Instead, it is designed to be used alongside a physical BP monitor to store and analyze your data in a meaningful way.\n\nPerfect for people with hypertension, hypotension, or those just looking to stay on top of their health, this app helps you make informed lifestyle and health decisions.\n\nYour health journey starts here.\nDownload now and take the first step toward smarter, more effective blood pressure management.\n\nPrivacy Policy : https://freeaiutilities.mcanswers.ai/blood-pressure/privacy-policy\nTerms of Use : https://freeaiutilities.mcanswers.ai/blood-pressure/terms-of-use","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/d8/75/02/d87502aa-a398-a548-6b8f-980b91896a07/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-11-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/blood-pressure-app-free-of-ad/id6747271310?uo=4","developer":"FREE AI UTILS COMPANY LIMITED","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":55,"2":16,"3":28,"4":50,"5":589}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"794542324","title":"Blood Pressure Log Feeltracker","store":"app_store","genre":"Medical","score":4.79176,"ratings":2,"reviewCount":2915,"installs":"N/A","description":"Feeltracker: Rated 4.8 with 20,500+ ratings • 60,000+ users • 1M+ downloads • 96% satisfaction\n\nSimply point your camera at your blood pressure monitor and let AI instantly capture and analyze your readings. Feeltracker BP combines cutting-edge scanning technology with AI-powered health insights to make cardiovascular tracking effortless—and help you understand what your numbers really mean. Whether you're managing hypertension or maintaining heart health, get instant clarity you can trust.\n\nCOMPREHENSIVE HEART HEALTH TRACKING:\n• Log systolic, diastolic, and pulse readings with ease\n• Scan blood pressure monitors with your camera for instant, accurate entry\n• AI-powered scanning technology works with Omron and other BP monitor brands\n• Track multiple daily readings for accurate averages\n• Categorize readings by arm, position, and time of day\n• Monitor medication effects on your blood pressure\n• Add notes about activities, stress, or symptoms\n• AI chat, voice feedback, and pattern insights for your heart health\n\nYOUR PRIVACY, PROTECTED:\n• No account required—start tracking immediately\n• Face ID/Touch ID protection for your health data\n• Automatic iCloud sync keeps readings secure across devices\n• Export reports in PDF, CSV, Excel, or JSON formats\n\nDESIGNED FOR DAILY MONITORING:\n• Beautiful Liquid Glass design\n• Eye-friendly Dark Mode for comfortable tracking any time of day\n• Color-coded readings show normal, elevated, or high ranges\n• Quick-entry widgets for logging from home screen\n• Smart reminders for consistent monitoring schedule\n• Full integration with Apple Health\n\nUNDERSTAND YOUR HEART HEALTH:\n• Detailed trends reveal blood pressure patterns\n• Interactive charts—tap any point to view detailed readings instantly\n• Weekly and monthly averages for doctor visits\n• Identify triggers that affect your readings\n• Track improvements from lifestyle changes\n• Generate professional reports for healthcare providers\n\nAI-POWERED FEATURES:\n• Ask a Question: Instant answers about your blood pressure data\n• Chat: Interactive cardiovascular health conversations\n• Voice Summary: Audio summaries of your blood pressure trends\n• Pattern Detective: Discover hidden correlations affecting your readings\n• Goal Assistant: Personalized blood pressure goals\n• Doctor Summary: Professional summaries for doctor visits\n• Tailored Health Report: Comprehensive personal health document\n• Deep Research Report: In-depth cardiovascular pattern analysis\n• Sick Note: Documentation based on your health records\n• Personalized Quiz: Test your knowledge about blood pressure health\n• Make Me Laugh & Calm Me Down: Humor and guided breathing\n\nFREE WITH PREMIUM OPTIONS:\n• All core tracking features completely free\n• Upgrade to Premium for extended AI features and 10x daily AI quota\n• Affordable pricing for lifelong heart health management\n\nIMPORTANT HEALTH DISCLAIMER:\nThis app is for personal tracking and informational purposes only. AI insights and recommendations are powered by OpenAI and do not constitute medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment. Always consult a qualified healthcare provider before making health decisions. In a medical emergency, contact emergency services immediately.\n\nPrivacy Policy: https://feeltracker.com/privacy.html\nTerms of Use: https://feeltracker.com/terms.html","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/c3/a0/1b/c3a01bd8-b561-d8d8-824a-2f7e95747b50/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-0-sRGB-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/blood-pressure-log-feeltracker/id794542324?uo=4","developer":"Custom Arts","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":19,"2":20,"3":74,"4":323,"5":2479}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6462986894","title":"Blood pressure-i Heart tracker","store":"app_store","genre":"Health & Fitness","score":4.58547,"ratings":2,"reviewCount":2866,"installs":"N/A","description":"Heart rate measurement\nIlluminate the subcutaneous capillaries of fingertips with high light (LED flash next to the camera), and when the heart pumps blood, the blood flow causes changes in transmittance. Monitor these changes through the camera and use specific algorithms to detect heart rate.https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/33569935/\n\nPersonalized Alarm Reminders\nSet custom reminders to ensure that you never forget to measure and record important health data.\n\nData Labels and Annotations\nYou can add current status labels to your measurement results for more accurate tracking of your heart health.\n\nExport Health Data with Ease\nThe app provides one-click data export functionality, making it easy to share your heart health data with your family doctor or other professionals.\n\nHealthkit: The app integrates with Apple Health, allowing you to send measurement results to the Health app for comprehensive tracking of your heart and overall health.\n\nMore Heatures\n* Record Blood Pressure＆Check Trends\n* Log Blood Sugar\n* Check Your Stress Level\n* Record Drink Water\n\nDisclaimer:\nPlease note that, as of the current version, all our data is sourced from manual input or Apple Health. For information on the data source and privacy of Apple Health, please refer to https://www.apple.com.cn/ios/health/\nAdditionally, our application is not designed for medical purposes; It is a tool for daily recording and rough measurement. We cannot guarantee the accuracy of the data you record. If you have higher requirements for health assessment or feel unwell, it is recommended to consult a professional doctor or undergo a professional medical equipment examination. Always exercise caution and wisdom when using such applications.\n\nBlood pressure-i Heart tracker provides automatic renewal subscriptions based on in-app purchases. By subscribing, you can unlock all features in the app without advertising or restrictions. The specific details are subject to the display in the app.\n\nWe do not collect or share any of your health data. For details, please review our:\nPrivacy Policy: https://www.clean-booster2023.com/1/privacy\nUser Agreement: https://www.clean-booster2023.com/1/term\nSubscription Notice:https://www.clean-booster2023.com/1/subscription\n\nIf you have any questions, feel free to contact us via email: xilu11feedback@outlook.com","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/dc/c4/82/dcc48267-c531-debc-522d-27d676c6089c/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007ephone-0-1-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/blood-pressure-i-heart-tracker/id6462986894?uo=4","developer":"深圳市喜噜科技有限公司","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":144,"2":43,"3":101,"4":281,"5":2297}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1438082332","title":"My Blood Pressure Journal","store":"app_store","genre":"Medical","score":4.69838,"ratings":4,"reviewCount":4456,"installs":"N/A","description":"A simple and easy to use blood pressure app for keeping a secure  log of all your readings. Also, It works whether you're connected to the internet or not.\n\nStop using pen and paper to track and share details about your heart's health. Use My Blood Pressure Journal to monitor, log and analyze your blood pressure and heart rate. Also keep important notes related to each reading. All readings and information are securely stored locally on your device. So, you can be assured that your data is not vulnerable to potential data breaches on the web.\n\nMy Blood Pressure Journal also integrates with HealthKit, meaning you can automatically push all your readings to Apple Health.\n\nKey Features:\n- Add blood pressure, pulse / heart rate with just a few taps.\n- Keep notes for each reading. \n- Export readings for easy sharing with doctors, family and friends.\n- Share reading via text, email, Facebook and/or Twitter\n- HealthKit Integration: Automatically sync your blood pressure and pulse readings with your Apple Health account\n- Store and access all your readings anywhere and anytime. This app works whether you're connected to the internet or not!\n\nWhether you're battling hypertension, working to prevent it or just monitoring your health per doctor's orders, this app will help you achieve your goals.\n\nSuggestions and feedback welcome at: rwitcher@gmail.com.\n\nNote: Always seek a doctor’s advice in addition to using this app and before making any medical decisions.\n\nTerms of Use: https://pluckshot.webflow.io/terms\nPrivacy Policy: https://pluckshot.webflow.io/privacy","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/24/6a/c7/246ac711-a23a-daef-9dd5-de15987ff4f8/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-8-85-220.jpeg/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/my-blood-pressure-journal/id1438082332?uo=4","developer":"Rodney Witcher, II","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":87,"2":49,"3":165,"4":519,"5":3636}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6462374701","title":"Blood Pressure Level Checker","store":"app_store","genre":"Health & Fitness","score":4.18679,"ratings":4,"reviewCount":4604,"installs":"N/A","description":"Welcome to the Blood Pressure Level Checker!   Stress is an important indicator of health, so paying attention to your blood pressure data is crucial for understanding your body's health status.  This app provides you with functions such as blood pressure data and tracking.   Users can easily record their health data anytime, anywhere, and also synchronize Apple's health data, making it easier for users to better manage their health status.\nThe application interface design is simple and easy to operate!\n\nFunction:\n1.  Blood pressure recording and chart tracking:\nEasily record your blood pressure data, including high and low pressure.\nUnderstand your blood pressure trends through intuitive chart tracking.\nNo paper or pen required, easy to operate\n\n2.  Heart rate measurement and chart tracking:\nUse the built-in heart rate measurement function to detect your heart rate.\nVisualize your heart rate data to help you understand your heart health.\nExplore the trend of heart rate fluctuations and take timely action.\n\n3.  Blood glucose recording and chart tracking:\nFor patients with diabetes, it is easy to record your blood sugar level.\nVisualize blood glucose data to help you manage diet and medication treatment.\nTrack blood sugar fluctuations and improve quality of life.\n\n4.  Personalized alarm reminder:\nDon't worry about missing important health tasks anymore!  Our personalized alarm reminder will be customized according to your health needs.\n\nSet reminders such as medication administration, blood pressure measurement, heart rate measurement, and exercise to fully adapt to your lifestyle.\nReminders can be customized based on your schedule and health goals, ensuring that you maintain a healthy lifestyle at all times.\n\n5.  Exclusive Health Tracking Assistant:\nThe Blood Pressure Level Checker will become your health tracking assistant, providing personalized advice based on your data and needs.\nOver time, the application will learn about your health habits and provide more accurate advice to help you achieve better health outcomes.\n\n6.  Export your health data:\nClick the export button to export your blood pressure, heart rate, and blood glucose data as a CSV file.\nEasily share your health data with doctors or family.\nCustomize the export time range to meet your needs.\n\n7.  More comprehensive data management:\nUse the exported CSV file for further data analysis and tracking on the computer.\nEnsure that your data is permanently saved and keep track of health trends at all times.\n\nApple Health: The APP is integrated with HealthKit to synchronize Apple Health's blood pressure and heart rate data.\n\nDisclaimer\nThe information and estimates in this application are for informational purposes only and are not a substitute for professional medical advice, diagnosis or treatment.  Functions such as heart rate measurement rely on specific algorithms whose accuracy may be affected by factors such as the device, environment, user status, etc., so the displayed data should not be used as a basis for medical decisions.  For health problems, especially those that require medical intervention, always consult a medical professional and follow your doctor's advice.  The app developer is not responsible for health problems arising from the use of its information.  By using this app, you understand and accept these conditions, and please treat the information therein with caution.\n\nBlood Pressure Level Checker Auto Renewal VIP Statement：\n1.   Subscription package：9.99/week\n2.   Subscription package：39.99/year \nFor more details, please refer to the subscription instructions: https://hotspeed-booster.com/1/subscription\n\nPrivacy Policy: https://hotspeed-booster.com/1/privacy\nService Agreement: https://hotspeed-booster.com/1/term\nIf you have any questions about the above content, please contact us: Marksw1989@proton.me","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/c1/fa/4e/c1fa4e6b-e153-aad9-2bf6-5eaa8aaade67/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007ephone-0-1-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/blood-pressure-level-checker/id6462374701?uo=4","developer":"solo mobile","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":649,"2":106,"3":185,"4":460,"5":3204}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1591935741","title":"Blood Pressure App","store":"app_store","genre":"Health & Fitness","score":4.39712,"ratings":4,"reviewCount":4578,"installs":"N/A","description":"Blood Pressure Monitor lets you track, analyze, and share your blood pressure data right from your iOS device. Discover a smarter way to monitor and manage your blood pressure with advanced analytics, comprehensive insights, and AI-powered recommendations.\n\nKEY FEATURES\n• Record & Monitor: Log systolic and diastolic blood pressure readings with timestamps.\n• Detailed Insights & Trends: Analyze BP fluctuations with graphs and historical trends.\n• Multi-Profile Support: Track and manage blood pressure for multiple users in one app.\n• PDF Reports for Doctors: Generate and share detailed health reports via email or text.\n• Apple Health Integration: Sync your BP data for a unified health tracking experience.\n• Glucose & Body Temperature Logging: Maintain a complete health profile.\n• Heart Rate Monitoring: Measure and track your pulse using your iPhone’s camera.\n• Healthcare Assistant & Assessments: Get personalized insights and risk assessments based on your health data.\n• Guided Workouts & Meditations: Improve wellness with 7-minute workouts, mindfulness exercises, and habit tracking.\n\nSUBSCRIPTION & PRICING\nUnlock the full potential of Blood Pressure Monitor with flexible subscription plans. The weekly plan at $6.99 includes a 3-day free trial, allowing you to explore premium features before committing. We also offer an annual plan for $39.99/year, providing full access at a better value. For those looking for a one-time purchase, the lifetime option at $99.99 grants unlimited access to all features forever.\n\nSubscription payments are charged to your iTunes account at purchase confirmation and renewal. Free trials convert to paid plans unless canceled at least 24 hours before the period ends. Unused trial portions are forfeited upon purchasing a subscription.\n\nDISCLAIMER\nBlood Pressure Monitor is a tracking and analysis tool and does not measure blood pressure directly. A clinically approved blood pressure monitor is required for taking measurements. It is not designed for medical use or as a substitute for professional medical advice. Always consult your doctor for any health concerns.\n\nPRIVACY POLICY\nhttps://bpmonitor.top/privacy-policy\n\nTERMS OF USE\nhttps://bpmonitor.top/terms-of-use\n\nSUPPORT DESK\nFor any questions, feedback, or support, our team is here to assist you. Reach out to us at info@bpmonitor.top, and we’ll be happy to help.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/c0/fe/fd/c0fefd95-8572-6925-4dea-aa3a20b80883/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-8-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/blood-pressure-app/id1591935741?uo=4","developer":"Appnap Technologies Limited","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":384,"2":114,"3":227,"4":428,"5":3425}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"458537528","title":"Blood Pressure Companion","store":"app_store","genre":"Medical","score":4.27186,"ratings":1,"reviewCount":1361,"installs":"N/A","description":"Blood Pressure Companion is a blood pressure, heart rate and weight tracker.\n\nKeeping track of blood pressure is a good habit to keep healthy. High blood pressure (HBP) is one of most common and frequently-occurring diseases; heredity, unbalanced diet, fat, lack of exercise, and drink etc may cause high blood pressure.\n\nUsing Blood Pressure Companion to track your blood pressure, you can monitor your blood pressure closely and visual by words, chart and histogram. When you find it abnormal, you can take quick actions to find the reason and keep it from growing high. Also you can share measurements conveniently with your doctors by this app.\n\nMain features:\n\n⁃ Easily add and edit blood pressure, heart rate, weight and test date.\n⁃ Add note to the readings.\n⁃ Track systolic, diastolic, heart rate and weight by chart.\n⁃ Analyze times and percentage of each blood pressure range.\n⁃ Calculate Mean Arterial Pressure (MAP) of each reading.\n⁃ Create a reminder for measuring BP, doctor visiting or anything else.\n⁃ Show MAX, MIN and AVG number of readings by number and histogram.\n⁃ Show statistics of measurement by day, week, month or year.\n⁃ Create a reminder to measure your blood pressure, doctor visit or others.\n⁃ Save snapshots to Photos. \n⁃ Export (Email) readings in format of CSV, HTML or PDF.\n⁃ Custom date range of readings to be exported.\n⁃ Migrate Data to full version.\n⁃ Custom your own color range.\n⁃ Passcode function to protect your info.\n⁃ Supports Touch ID as passcode.\n⁃ Support lbs and kgs.\n⁃ Clean and humanized interface.\n⁃ Supports printing data in app. \n⁃ Supports transferring data to Health app.\n⁃ Support WiFi backup and restore.\n⁃ Supports Dropbox backup and restore.\n⁃ Supports 3D Touch function.\n⁃ Supports Apple Watch version.\n⁃ Supports both iPhone and iPad.\n\nIf you have any questions or suggestion, please kindly mail to maxwellapp@tom.com.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/c2/5b/60/c25b6037-4bb8-da77-e56f-f88e563c936e/AppIcon-free-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-0-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/blood-pressure-companion/id458537528?uo=4","developer":"倩 赵","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":142,"2":27,"3":56,"4":230,"5":906}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"542701020","title":"Withings","store":"app_store","genre":"Health & Fitness","score":4.57897,"ratings":343,"reviewCount":343915,"installs":"N/A","description":"Whatever your goal—weight loss, activity, blood pressure management, or better sleep—the Withings App is your gateway to health management, offering education, insights, and a seamless way to stay connected.\n\nBuilt on clinical expertise, it unifies your health data to drive smarter decisions and lasting results.\n\nYOUR HEALTH ECOSYSTEM, SEAMLESSLY CONNECTED\nEasily install all your Withings devices and sync your data to bring your health universe together.\n\nALL YOUR HEALTH APPS UNIFIED \nConnect your health apps like Apple Health, Strava, MyFitnessPal, and more to centralize your data with ease.\n\nTRUST MEDICAL-GRADE PRECISION, TO DRIVE PROGRESS\nClinical-grade accuracy delivers reliable insights that help you make confident, informed decisions about your health. \n• WEIGHT & BODY COMPOSITION MONITORING\n• ACTIVITY MONITORING \n• SLEEP SCORE\n• HYPERTENSION MANAGEMENT\n• CARDIOVASCULAR DISEASE DETECTION\n• MENSTRUAL CYCLE TRACKING \n• NUTRITION TRACKING \"\n\nSHAPE YOUR HEALTH JOURNEY \nCreate a tailored health profile, monitor symptoms, and set achievable goals to better understand your body, stay motivated, and improve your health over time\n\nMULTIPLE PROFILES TO TRACK FAMILY HEALTH\nTrack the health of your entire household from one app and easily share data between profiles for a more connected approach to care.\n\nINSTANTLY SHARE WITH YOUR DOCTOR\nGenerate secure, shareable reports or send a live link to your health dashboard, giving your healthcare provider immediate access to your most up-to-date metrics.\n\n\nWithings+ \n\nPOWERING YOUR JOURNEY TO LONGEVITY \nPrecision health made personal—AI and in-app cardiologists guiding you forward.\nWith Withings+, our premium subscription service, you decode your health through clinical reviews and AI assessments, delivering precise, tailored care to strengthen long-term habits and help support your journey toward a better, longer life.\n\nYOUR HEALTH SIMPLIFIED\nAll metrics consolidated in one powerful Health Improvement Score to guide your long-term health.\n\nSPECIALIST CARE AT YOUR FINGERTIPS\nGet your ECG reviewed by a cardiologist within 24 hours — with an average wait time of just 4 hours (Observed Jan–Mar 2025). Feel confident knowing your heart health is in expert hands, quickly and reliably.\n\nDECODE YOUR BODY \nWith Withings Intelligence, experience around-the-clock AI-driven insights, smart trend analysis, and personalized coaching to help you take control of your health.\n\nKickstart your day with our brand new Vitalité Indicator.\nThis powerful tool brings together key health metrics—including HRV, temperature, sleep patterns, and more — to evaluate your rest and effort levels. Based on these insights, it offers personalized suggestions to help you boost your energy and optimize recovery for the days ahead. You’ll also receive a detailed breakdown that can highlight early signs of potential illness and signal when it’s time to give yourself extra care.\n\nYOUR WEEKLY HEALTH BREAKDOWN\nTrack your strengths and weaknesses each week to refine and boost your Health Improvement Score.\n\nABOUT WITHINGS\n​​Withings creates clinically validated health devices embedded in beautifully designed, easy-to-use products. A universe of insights all synced to a single source of truth, providing you with the ultimate way to stay connected to your health.\n\nTerms of use:https://www.withings.com/legal/applications-conditions#/legal/services-terms-and-conditions\nPrivacy policy: https://www.withings.com/legal/applications-conditions#/legal/privacy-policy\nMedical compliance: https://www.withings.com/eu/en/compliance?srsltid=AfmBOoovZiYectAmYJC5gs2HhHrMxHAhPdN4NFQQI5RSImnQdrLoxKSc","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/55/09/0d/55090d85-bf42-6fc4-4279-36ca47fe9462/AppIcon-Release-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/withings/id542701020?uo=4","developer":"Withings","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":16842,"2":5592,"3":12034,"4":36585,"5":272862}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"964304010","title":"FNP Exam Mastery | Prep 2026","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.86598,"ratings":11,"reviewCount":11827,"installs":"N/A","description":"Pass the AANPCB/ANCC or Triple Your Money Back! FNP Mastery is the #1 rated FNP exam prep app, developed by U.S.-based nurse practitioners who’ve been where you are.\n\nStart free today and get 10 boards-style questions every single day. No credit card required. \n\n2,500+ Boards-Style Questions Written by U.S. Nurse Practitioners\n• Access 2,500+ AANPCB & ANCC questions written by experienced U.S. Nurse Practitioners\n• Questions categorized for both AANPCB and ANCC exams\n• High-yield content designed to maximize study efficiency\n• Focus on high-yield topics and real-world patient care decisions\n\nAdaptive Learning Engine\n• AI-driven algorithm adjusts question difficulty based on your answers\n• Personalized learning to help you study smarter\n• Focuses on your weak areas to help you study more efficiently\n• Keeps you challenged without feeling overwhelmed\n\nIn-Depth Performance Analysis\n• Instant feedback and detailed progress reports\n• Identify strengths and focus on weak areas\n• Track your readiness with clear insights\n\nDiscussion & Nurse Expert Support\n• Access community discussions after every question\n• Ask questions and get answers from real U.S. nurse practitioners\n• Learn from shared insights and real experiences\n• Never feel stuck, support is just a tap away\n\nRealistic AANPCB & ANCC Simulation Tests\n• Full-length, timed simulations that mimic the real exams\n• Choose between AANPCB and ANCC Simulations\n• Practice pacing, time management, and test-taking strategies\n• Build confidence and reduce anxiety on exam day\n\nOur Unmatched 300% Money-Back Guarantee\n• Pass your boards or get triple your money back — seriously!\n• We’re confident in our product and dedicated to your success\n• Study with confidence, risk free\n• Our Customer Success Team supports you every step of the way\n\nJoin a Vibrant Community\n• Connect with thousands of NP students worldwide\n• Share tips, resources, and motivation\n• Engage on social media for extra support and updates\n\nInterested in AGNP or PMHNP prep? We have apps for those too! Search “AGNP Mastery” or “PMHNP Mastery” in the app store to get the best prep for you!\n\nFNP Mastery offers the following plans:\n1 Month - $49.99\n3 Months - $89.99\n12 Months - $299.99\n\nUpon confirming your purchase, you'll be billed immediately. Your subscription will automatically renew unless you turn off the auto-renewal feature at least 24 hours before the end of the current subscription period. You can manage your subscription and deactivate auto-renewal through your Account Settings after purchase. Note that any unused portion of a free trial, if offered, will be forfeited when you buy a subscription.\n\nPrivacy Policy - http://builtbyhlt.com/privacy\nTerms of Conditions - https://hltmastery.com/eula\n\nAbout Higher Learning Technologies (HLT Mastery):\nWe’re a U.S.-based leader in educational technology, dedicated to helping nursing students pass their exams with confidence and ease. Check out our entire Mastery app suite for continued success.\n\nCustomer Support:\nYour success is our priority. Talk to a real person at support@hltcorp.com or (319) 246-5271.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/96/d8/80/96d8804c-1691-b60a-c0fb-b89388f569be/AppIcon-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-0-85-220-0.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/fnp-exam-mastery-prep-2026/id964304010?uo=4","developer":"Higher Learning Technologies","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":71,"2":38,"3":207,"4":773,"5":10738}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1499948195","title":"A&D Heart Track","store":"app_store","genre":"Health & Fitness","score":4.73174,"ratings":3,"reviewCount":3724,"installs":"N/A","description":"A blood pressure and health metrics tracking app designed by doctors to help you collect and manage your blood pressure readings along with other health metrics. This app has been created to help you measure your blood pressure accurately using your own home monitor, follow your trends over time, and help your healthcare provider best manage your care.\n\n• Ensure your blood pressure measurements are performed accurately by following our \"how-to\" measurement guide.\n\n• Rapidly and efficiently calculate blood pressure averages with our Swipe Averaging™ feature. Bring your phone to your next appointment with your physician or pharmacist, and they can use Swipe Averaging™ to quickly and easily assess your blood pressure for clinical decision making.\n\n• Link your readings directly to your healthcare provider or pharmacist, through the Heart Track BP Telemonitoring System. Find out more at andhearttrack.ca\n\n• Learn from internationally renowned experts what blood pressure is, about high and low blood pressure, and how blood pressure can best be controlled.\n\n• Heart Track is recommended by Hypertension Canada.\n\n• Easily track your blood pressure and weight using an A&D Medical blood pressure monitor and weight scale. Automatically transmit your readings using a compatible Bluetooth-enabled device, or manually enter the value reported by any blood pressure monitor or weight scale.\n\n\n\nThe following Bluetooth-enabled blood pressure monitors are supported.\n\n• A&D Medical Connected Upper Arm Blood Pressure Monitor: UA-651BLE\n• A&D Medical UltraConnect Upper Arm Blood Pressure Monitor: UA-1200CNBLE\n• A&D Medical UltraConnect Wrist Blood Pressure Monitor: UB-1100CNBLE\n• A&D Medical Connected Weight Scale: UC-350CNBLE\n\n\n\nMEDICAL DISCLAIMER: The Heart Track app is not intended for the diagnosis of or screening for hypertension. Users should be aware that the Heart Track app is an information management service to enable the analysis of blood pressure data and is not intended to be a substitute for the advice of a health care professional. Individuals should always consult their doctor or other qualified health care professional with any questions they may have regarding a medical condition, including any queries or concerns about blood pressure management. You should never disregard professional medical advice or delay in seeking it because of information transmitted to or contained in your Heart Track app.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/e6/4d/57/e64d573a-9549-a261-8c97-863e15132252/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-8-0-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/a-d-heart-track/id1499948195?uo=4","developer":"A&D Company, Limited","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":64,"2":28,"3":107,"4":445,"5":3080}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1551799152","title":"BreathNow - blood pressure app","store":"app_store","genre":"Health & Fitness","score":4.73217,"ratings":2,"reviewCount":2748,"installs":"N/A","description":"BreathNow is a powerful blood pressure app, heart rate monitor and stress monitor for Apple Watch which helps to relax and lower blood pressure, pulse and stress with breathing exercises, meditations and more. Includes cardio fitness test from the University of Cambridge. Requires external blood pressure monitor to take blood pressure readings.\n\nKey app features:\nMeasure heart rate, stress and cardio fitness with your phone’s camera or Apple Watch.\nTrack and lower blood pressure and pulse with calming activities, no meds\nGet daily cardio insights and manage heart health risks\nPerform slow breathing and meditate to lower anxiety, BP, heart rate and stress\nFall asleep easily with guided breathing on Apple Watch\nEasily measure which relaxation techniques worked best for you\nThe main advantage of BreathNow blood pressure app is that it is not only a blood pressure & heart rate monitor and stress monitor. It also provides practical tools to lower blood pressure and heart rate with meditation, slow breathing exercises and more. \n\n\nMeasure heart rate, stress and cardio fitness (VO2Max) with your phone’s camera, no external sensors needed. Our cardio fitness (VO2Max) test is developed by scientists from the University of Cambridge. \n\n\nEnter your blood pressure data manually or connect your external blood pressure  monitor to Apple  Health via Bluetooth and analyse what activities helped you  to lower blood pressure. Your data are stored securely in Apple Health  and you may print  them out or share remotely with your doctor. \n\n\nBreathNow alerts you to important cardio signals like elevated heart rate, blood pressure, stress, irregular heart rhythm (also known as Afib) and low blood oxygen level if it is detected  by your Apple Watch.\n\n\nIf BreathNow identifies a risk area from one of the daily indicators,  it will suggest a user to perform  an activity from an extended list to reduce a heart health risk. Choose between: slow breathing, meditation, acupressure, calming music, yoga  and other activities. The list of  breathing exercises includes lower BP breathing, 4-7-8 meditation breathing exercise, IMST breathing exercise, box breathing etc.\n\n\n\n\nBreatheNow blood pressure app features:\n+ Free heart rate and stress monitor for iPhone and Apple Watch\n+ Free blood pressure tracker\n+ Free daily heart risk insights\n+ Free cardio fitness test from the University of  Cambridge\n+ Free breathing exercise to  lower blood  pressure for iPhone and Apple Watch\n+ Free instructional videos  to lower heart health  risks\n+ Plans to lower blood pressure\n+ Broad  selection of meditation  and other activities to lower anxiety, BP, stress and pulse\n+ Reminders\n+ Leaderboard for motivation\n+ Your data stored securely in Apple Health\n\n\nTerms of Use https://www.dmitrikonash.com/terms-of-use\n\n\nPrivacy Policy https://www.dmitrikonash.com/privacy-policy\n\n\nSupports iPhone with iOS15 and above.\n\n\nWe offer auto-renewing in-app subscriptions for a Pro version which includes all heart rate meditation, breathing exercise app, meditation breathing exercise.  Payments will be charged to iTunes Account at confirmation of purchase. Subscription automatically renews at the end of the period unless cancelled by the user.\n\n\nPLEASE NOTE: Heart rate monitor results may differ from heart rate measured by a medical device. BreathNow blood pressure app requires an external blood pressure monitor for taking blood pressure readings.  \n\n\nDISCLAIMER: BreathNow blood pressure app does NOT provide medical diagnosis or treatment advice. Please seek doctor's advice for any medical decisions.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/d4/05/5a/d4055a8f-8089-1c97-842e-8417c71cb113/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-8-0-sRGB-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/breathnow-blood-pressure-app/id1551799152?uo=4","developer":"Cardio Calm Ltd","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":67,"2":23,"3":94,"4":211,"5":2353}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1074367771","title":"Welltory: Health, Heart Rate","store":"app_store","genre":"Health & Fitness","score":4.74576,"ratings":125,"reviewCount":125163,"installs":"N/A","description":"Finally Understand What's Going On With Your Body\n\nTrusted by 16 million users who want to reconnect with their bodies and feel better, featured by the App Store in Apps We Love, and collaborating with 25+ universities worldwide — including Harvard Medical School, Arizona State University, and Johns Hopkins — to advance health science.\n\n— Your heart knows everything about you. Welltory helps you listen and understand —\n\nSometimes your body feels like it’s speaking a foreign language. Welltory translates those signals into science-backed insights — whether you’re facing hormonal changes, heart health concerns, fatigue, burnout, or just want to optimize energy and mood.\n\nWe analyze heart rate variability (HRV) — a proven heart health marker backed by 20,000+ studies — to show what your heart and nervous system reveal about your wellness.\n\n— Your Complete Health Story, One App —\n\nYou don’t have to piece together insights from 5 health apps. When you finally have a moment for yourself, everything you need is right there. \n\nConnect 1,000+ devices and apps — Apple Watch, Oura, meditation apps, lab test results, and more — to create your personal health diary. \n\n— Stop Guessing. Start Understanding —\n\nSleep That Actually Restores You\n\nStruggling with insomnia or waking up exhausted? Our Sleep Analysis goes beyond counting hours. Discover what disrupts your rest and get insights to improve recovery. With Echo — a science-based library of calming content tailored to your heartbeat — you’ll fall asleep faster and wake up truly restored.\n\nHeart Health & Blood Pressure Simplified \n\nYour heart reveals what’s really happening in your body. Welltory helps you track blood pressure, hypertension, and other metrics — plus log symptoms in your personal health diary. Share reports with your doctor, or use Welltory as a tracker helping you navigate health, menopause, and aging with confidence.\n\nCan Apple Watch measure blood pressure? No, but Welltory helps you understand your numbers if you sync a monitor or add data manually.\n\nStress That Makes Sense\n\nTurn your Apple Watch into a stress monitor and catch stress before it takes over. No more wondering “why am I so stressed?” — now you’ll know, and know how to respond. See how work, sleep, workouts, and even Zoom meetings affect your stress levels, and recognize when it’s time to pause and restore balance.\n\nActivity Boost Without Pressure\n\nTrack the 60% of activity most fitness apps ignore — we count every effort: walking the dog, house chores, running for the bus, and more. Every activity grows your Mountain in the app — the taller it gets, the more you’ve moved. We also set a Longevity goal that matches where your body is today and gently guides you toward progress, not perfection.\n\nStart listening to your body — and feel the difference with Welltory.\n\nPRICING & TERMS\n\nApp is free to download and use. You can upgrade to Welltory Premium with an auto-renewing subscription.\n\n–– Subscription renews automatically unless turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the period.\n–– Renewal is charged within 24 hours before the current period ends, the cost will be identified. \n–– Subscriptions may be managed by the user and auto-renewal may be turned off in the user's Account Settings after purchase.\n–– Free trial portions (if offered) are forfeited after purchase.\n–– Please note that the Family Sharing feature is not applicable for our app.\n— Welltory integrates with Apple Health.\n\nTerms of service:\nhttps://welltory.com/terms/ \n\nPrivacy policy:\nhttps://welltory.com/privacy \n\nTerms of Use (EULA):\nhttps://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/\n\nWe store your data in the cloud, honoring your privacy & safety. contact@welltory.com\n\nNOTE\nWelltory measures heart rate variability and detects heartbeats. It cannot measure blood pressure or other vital signs via phone camera or Apple Watch.\n\nWelltory is not a substitute for medical advice. Always consult your doctor if you feel unwell.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/28/f2/09/28f20930-f848-8916-e606-cb4cec816aca/AppIcon_free-0-0-1x_U007ephone-0-1-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/welltory-health-heart-rate/id1074367771?uo=4","developer":"Welltory inc","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":2012,"2":774,"3":2357,"4":16738,"5":103282}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1446163218","title":"Blood pressure app+","store":"app_store","genre":"Medical","score":4.51251,"ratings":2,"reviewCount":2119,"installs":"N/A","description":"Blood Pressure App is a smarter way to manage your blood pressure measurements and track your progress. Our app is a blood pressure management app that allows you to record, track, analyze and share your Blood Pressure information using your iPhone\n\nFEATURES:\n◉ Stylish, easy to use interface\n◉ Save BP and pulse logs\n◉ Logbook. Keep the most comprehensive diary\n◉ Find readings by date\n\nSUBSCRIPTION INFORMATION\n\nWant more from Blood pressure app+? Get PREMIUM and enjoy:\n• BP Analytics\n• MAP Calculation\n• Health Report for Doctor\n• BP Goal Setting\n\nOur standard subscription options are: 1-week subscription for $ 4.99, 1-year subscription for $ 69.99 or equal to the same price tier as Apple App Store Matrix determines as the equivalent of the subscription price in USD.\n\n• Payment will be charged to iTunes Account at confirmation of purchase\n• Subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period\n• Account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period, and identify the cost of the renewal\n• Subscriptions may be managed by the user and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the user's Account Settings after purchase\n• Any unused portion of a free trial period, if offered, will be forfeited when the user purchases a subscription to that publication, where applicable\nTerms: http://7logic.us/termsofuse\nPrivacyPolicy: http://7logic.us/terms","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/f3/ec/eb/f3ecebbc-ed64-c5bb-10ee-5eef55fee68d/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-0-85-220.jpeg/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/blood-pressure-app/id1446163218?uo=4","developer":"Maksim Gudzik","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":tru