data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"306526794","title":"iBP Blood Pressure","store":"app_store","genre":"Medical","score":4.81109,"ratings":2,"reviewCount":2525,"installs":"N/A","description":"What is iBP?\n\niBP is a blood pressure tracking and analysis tool. Please note, it is not possible to measure your blood pressure by touching the screen. A separate device is required.\n\nWhat kind of analysis does iBP provide?\n\niBP uses color icons to indicate when your blood pressure values are normal, high, or hypertension. It also provides interactive graphs that allow you to display your values by weeks, months, year and time of day. The graphs display lows, highs, averages, and trend lines using statistical analysis.\n\nWhy iBP vs. other blood pressure apps?\n\niBP is a universal app designed to work on the iPhone, iPod Touch and iPad, which means you only pay for the app once and you get all versions! iBP is the only blood pressure app with a built in transfer capability to sync all your iOS devices.\n\nWhat are the key features?\n\n* Reads and writes Apple Health blood pressure, pulse, and weight data (details below)\n* Easy data input using dials instead of keyboard\n* Transfer capability to sync all of your iOS devices\n* Calculates Mean Arterial Pressure and Pulse Pressure\n* Track one personal item (blood glucose, stress level, medication dosage, exercise time)\n* Backup / Restore capability\n* Multiple users\n* Multiple email addresses (you and doctor)\n* Multiple email formats (PDF, HTML, CSV, Plain Text)\n* Passcode to protect your data\n* Touch Id for passcode on devices that support it\n* Snapshot of the graphs can be saved\n* User configurable color ranges\n* Weight units (lb or kg)\n* Withings Blood Pressure Monitor & Wireless Scale\n\nApple Health\niBP is now able to read and write Apple Health blood pressure, pulse, and weight data. If your blood pressure monitor (i.e., Omron, iHealth, Withings) adds data to Apple Health then you can easily import that data into this app. If you manually input your data into this app, then it will write that data to Apple Health.\n\nWithings + iBP = No more data entry!\niBP can retrieve your blood pressure and weight data directly from your Withings account.  The Blood Pressure Monitor and wireless Body Scale automatically record and send the data to your account.  There is no data entry required and you can view the data anywhere using a web browser or a variety of mobile apps.\n\n\nDisclaimer: iBP is intended to be used as a means to collect data to be shared with your doctor. This application is not intended to be a substitute for professional medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment. We assume no liability for any personal harm or injury sustained as a result of using this application.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple113/v4/e0/67/93/e0679397-2e91-3ca3-e2b6-5df3d4ccb90c/AppIcon-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-0-GLES2_U002c0-512MB-sRGB-0-0-0-85-220-0-0-0-9.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/ibp-blood-pressure/id306526794?uo=4","developer":"Leading Edge Apps LLC","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0.99,"free":false,"histogram":{"1":19,"2":11,"3":40,"4":288,"5":2167}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1227470917","title":"Balance Health","store":"app_store","genre":"Health & Fitness","score":4.05719,"ratings":1,"reviewCount":1224,"installs":"N/A","description":"Staying on top of your health requires keeping track of a lot of numbers, and we want to help you make sense of them. The Balance Health app makes it easy to keep on eye on important trends by tracking your blood pressure measurements. The app’s intuitive interface and interactive graphs help you dive deep into your results and understand how they change over time. \n\nWhether you’re keeping close tabs on your measurements for medical reasons or just want to check in from time to time to learn more about your health, our app helps you clearly visualize how you’re doing and stay accountable for your results. The friendly in-app tracking assistant makes it simple to set up your monitor, navigate the app, and understand your numbers. Input your results manually or sync them directly from our Balance Bluetooth Blood Pressure Monitor. You can also turn on an integration to share your data with the Apple Health app.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/28/9d/26/289d261f-cc16-e954-a0bd-6c0c81c8d13c/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/balance-health/id1227470917?uo=4","developer":"Greater Goods, LLC","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":141,"2":60,"3":79,"4":252,"5":692}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1484690932","title":"BoardVitals Medical Exam Prep","store":"app_store","genre":"Medical","score":4.91367,"ratings":9,"reviewCount":9788,"installs":"N/A","description":"BoardVitals offers board-style practice questions for more than 50 board exams and medical specialties. Study effectively with high-yield questions that are accompanied by detailed explanations and rationales for correct and incorrect answers. All questions are written and reviewed by physicians and clinicians who’ve recently taken the board exams.\n\nBrought to you by BoardVitals, a brand you know and trust for up-to-date quality content, you can now access your test prep from wherever you are with your mobile device.\n\nWhether you have 10 minutes between classes, on rounds, on a commute, or you’ve blocked off bigger chunks of time to focus on practice questions, we’ve got you covered. \n\nOFFLINE ACCESS\nThe content on the BoardVitals Mobile App is available anywhere. Download your custom quizzes with offline access and study with or without an internet connection.  \n\nPRACTICE WITH CONFIDENCE USING TOP TOOLS\nWith similar testing features to the ones you’ll have access to on the exam, you can nip some of your test anxiety in the bud. \nHighlight key passages of the question\nStrikeout answer choices to eliminate distractors\nMark a question to come back to it later\nMake a note for yourself for a specific question\n\nQUESTION FORMATS\nHalf the battle of mastering your score, is mastering the format of your exams. Taking practice questions in the same format you’ll see on the exam is critical to your success. These question banks include the following testing formats:\nMultiple Choice\nSelect All That Apply (SATA)\nGraphic Items\nHot Spot Items\nFill in the Blank Calculation\nAudio Questions\nExhibit Questions\n\nAs you create your custom practice quizzes, you will see a mix of these question types, just as you would see on the exam for which you’re preparing. \n\nQUIZ MODES\nFurther customize your quizzes by choosing from three quiz types:\n\nSTUDY MODE\nStudy mode is similar to an open book quiz without a time limit. In this quiz environment, you can read the explanations as you go and practice at your own pace. \n\nTEST (UNTIMED) MODE\nTest (Untimed) Mode is like taking a closed book quiz without the pressure of a time limit. Answers and explanations are not available during the quiz.\n\nTEST (TIMED) MODE \nTo quasi-simulate the pressure of a test environment, Test (Timed) Mode allows you to study without revealing the correct answers and explanations until the quiz has been completed. \n\nNCLEX® CAT TESTING MODE\nFor NCLEX® students, you can choose to practice in a Computer Adaptive Test mode (CAT). Computer adaptive testing adjusts to your abilities - providing you with either an easier or harder question depending on how you answered the previous question. \n\nDETAILED ANALYTICS\n\nANSWER RESPONSE TIME\nOftentimes we know the answer, but it can take us too long to recall it. With built-in analytics to evaluate your answer response time, you can see if you’re on the right track to completing your board exam in the allotted time frame. \n\nAnalytics cover your average response time based on individual questions, averages by subject, and averages by quiz.\n\nPEER RANK\nIndividual performance scores are important, but only give you part of the story. Our Peer Rank metric shows how you compare with others answering the same questions so you can see how you're ranking compared to your peers studying for the same exam.\n\nOur comprehensive evidence-based explanations are now augmented with Peer Comparisons so you can see exactly how other users answered the same question with percentages for each answer choice. \n\nMONITOR YOUR PROGRESS\nYour competency changes as you study. Your dashboard will feature a visual representation of your performance over time. Identifying growth or plateaus can help you target trouble areas and maximize your study time.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/1c/54/50/1c5450e1-ba48-faca-d1f6-a2bd4958a503/AppIcon-PROD-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/boardvitals-medical-exam-prep/id1484690932?uo=4","developer":"Board Vitals, Inc.","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":25,"2":14,"3":45,"4":613,"5":9091}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6469585886","title":"Blood Pressure: Healthy Life","store":"app_store","genre":"Health & Fitness","score":4.37828,"ratings":2,"reviewCount":2017,"installs":"N/A","description":"Welcome to the Blood Pressure: Healthy Life！\nBlood Pressure: Healthy Life is a comprehensive health app designed to help you record your vital health parameters conveniently.  With a wide range of features, Blood Pressure: Healthy Life aims to empower you to take control of your well-being and lead a healthier lifestyle.\nFEATURES:\n- Record Blood Pressure Readings:\nEasily record your blood pressure data, including high and low pressure. No paper or pen required, easy to operate.\n- Heart Rate:\nUse a highlight (LED flash beside the camera, or other bright enough light source can also) to illuminate the capillaries under the fingertip, when the hearpresses fresh blood into the capillaries, the brightness (red depth) will change slightly, through the camera to monitor this regular change of interval, you can calculate the hearttpeat. (According to the source: https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/28288955/)\n- Blood Glucose record:\nFor those who want to keep an eye on their blood sugar levels, Blood Pressure: Healthy Life offers a convenient blood glucose record feature.  Easily log your readings and track your glucose levels over time.\n- Personalized Reminders:\nPersonalized settings for medication management, blood pressure measurement, heart rate measurement, and exercise reminders. Never miss important health tasks again!\n- Health Information and Tips:\nStay updated with the latest health-related information through APP's knowledge point push feature.  Receive regular notifications and articles on various health topics, including nutrition, exercise, mental well-being, and more.\n- Health Status Tracking:\nTrack your overall health progress with APP's comprehensive health tracking feature.  Monitor your daily activities and exercise routines.  Set goals, receive reminders, and visualize your progress through intuitive charts and graphs.  Stay motivated and make positive changes to your lifestyle.\nApple Health: The APP is integrated with HealthKit to synchronize Apple Health's blood pressure and heart rate data.\nWeatherKit: Supported by the new \"Apple Weather\" service, the application integrates WeatherKit, allowing you to see the current weather conditions and temperatures, as well as forecast the weather for the next 15 days, and take safety measures before rain.\n\nDisclaimer：The Blood Pressure: Healthy Life application information, data and estimates are for informational purposes only and are not a substitute for professional medical advice, diagnosis or treatment.   Functions such as heart rate measurement are based on algorithms, and their accuracy is affected by equipment, environment, body state, etc., and the data cannot be used as a medical basis.   If you have health problems, please consult a professional, the developer is not responsible for the consequences of using this app.\n\nWe provide a membership function, and the specific prices and benefits are subject to in app display.  Please refer to the subscription notice for details: http://bloodpressure-pro.com/subscription\n\nPrivacy Policy: https://bloodpressure-pro.com/privacy\nService Agreement: https://bloodpressure-pro.com/term\nContact us: gameprox11@protonmail.com","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/da/9c/b3/da9cb322-36d1-09f2-0880-dd661b8681bf/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007ephone-0-1-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/blood-pressure-healthy-life/id6469585886?uo=4","developer":"Shenzhen Guanhang Digital Technology Co., Ltd.","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":216,"2":35,"3":59,"4":167,"5":1540}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1549599609","title":"Huru - Job Interview Prep","store":"app_store","genre":"Productivity","score":4.59036,"ratings":83,"reviewCount":83,"installs":"N/A","description":"Practice mock interviews with Huru, your personal A.I job interview prep coach. it’s designed to get Feedbacks instantly on different facets of the assessment. You can now improve your interview skills and improve your confidence. This unique Job interview prep app allows you to practice interview questions using real-world scenarios and live coaching.\nAre you ready to ace your next job interview?\n\n====================================\n\nTry Huru, Your Job Interview Coach and practice unlimited interviews.\n\n====================================\n\nWhy do you need to prepare for interview with Huru (The job interview coach)?\n\n+20K MOCK INTERVIEWS\nA wide range of mock interviews in one job interview app covering nearly every career category in the employment market.\n\nINSTANT FEEDBACK\nGet detailed instant feedbacks and an in-depth report on how you performed to improve your confidence and interview skills.\n\nLIVE COACHING\nBoost your confidence with live coaching feature and control your stress before your next interview.\n\nFACIAL EXPRESSION\nGet real-time and general feedbacks on your facial expression with Huru, your job interview app.\n\nANSWER TIPS\nHuru gives answering advice for all questions asked during the preparation of an interview and guides you to succeed in your answers during your real interview.\n\nVOICE ANALYSIS\nHuru analyzes your speech and measures your pausing and pace. This job interview prep app will train you to control your articulation to master your speech.\n\nINTERVIEW RECORDING\nInterviews are recorded on your device so that you can see yourself performing the mock interviews and improve your interview skills.\n\n====================================\nPractice, Practice, Practice. \nHuru empowers you to perform at your peak in every job interview. A unique mobile app that lets you practice, prepare, and perfect your interviewing skills.  Our app will help you stay calm, confident and prepared to answer any interview question they throw at you.\n\n====================================\nHave you been invited to make an interview after submitting your resume through Linkedin?\nGreat news! With Huru, You can use our browser extension : https://rcl.ink/NoE12 and Scan any job offer listing on Linkedin through Huru mobile app then practice your interview.\n\n====================================\nAre you invited for an interview after you submit your resume on Indeed?\nHere is the steps to practice your interview :\n- Search any job offer listing on Indeed, Click on the job\n- Scan Qr code generated by our extension app using Huru mobile app\n- Enjoy your simulated interview. Practice unlimited interviews.\n\nHuru can generate interviews from all job boards such as Linkedin, Indeed, Monster, Glassdoor, ZipRecruiter...etc\n\n====================================\nAll you need is Huru, a powerful job interview prep app. \nA must have app for job seekers, a really confidence booster.\nWith Huru, Don't just get an interview, get a job\n====================================\n\nPractice job interviews with Huru to be prepared for systems like Hirevue, Talview or Spark Hire.\nDo you want to practice for a Hirevue interview? \nHuru will boost your confidence and will make you comfortable with Hirevue video interviews.\nNowadays, companies use video interviews to make interviews to candidates. With video recording feature, voice analysis, answer tips, instant AI feedback you will be ready for any video interview through any video interview platform such as Hirevue, Talview or Spark Hire.\n\nImprove your interview skills Today with your personal career coach Huru and search jobs with confidence.\n\n====================================\n\nPrivacy policy: https://www.huru.ai/privacy-policy\nTerms of Use: https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/\n\n====================================\n\nContact us : \nSuggestions or questions ? Contact support-huru@beatview.ai","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/1b/ac/d3/1bacd30f-024b-424e-5557-aec9229f0ba5/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-7-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/huru-job-interview-prep/id1549599609?uo=4","developer":"Beatview, Inc","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":7,"2":1,"3":0,"4":3,"5":72}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1664024041","title":"InterviewAI: Mock Interview","store":"app_store","genre":"Productivity","score":4.54545,"ratings":11,"reviewCount":11,"installs":"N/A","description":"InterviewAI is the ultimate interview preparation app that helps you ace your next job interview. With just a few taps, generate 10 mock interview questions related to your desired position, including background, situational, and technical questions. Answer the questions using voice recognition technology, and receive instant feedback with evaluation and suggestions to improve your responses. You can search your previous interviews and questions, and each question can be answered up to three times.\n\nNow, with the new AI-powered feature, InterviewAI can also generate a personalized cover letter for you based on your desired job position and qualifications. Simply enter your information and let the AI do the rest. With support for multiple languages, you can practice your interview skills and write your cover letter in the language of your choice.\n\nKey Features:\n\n- Generate 10 interview questions related to your desired position\n- Questions cover background, situational, and technical topics\n- Answer questions using voice recognition technology\n- Instant feedback with evaluation and suggestions to improve your responses\n- Search previous interviews and questions\n- Answer each question up to three times\n- AI-powered cover letter generator based on your desired job position and qualifications\n- Supports multiple interview languages, including German, English, Spanish, French, Italian, Japanese, Korean, and Chinese (with multiple accents)\n\nInterviewAI is perfect for job seekers who want to take their interview skills to the next level, and it's also ideal for remote workers preparing for job interviews. With InterviewAI, you can practice and improve your interview skills and even get help with writing your cover letter. Download the app today and start your journey towards interview success!\n\nInterviewAI Terms of Usage: https://interviewai.me/terms-and-conditions.html","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/06/2c/9d/062c9db4-5376-1888-5b05-b51eefb392ac/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-7-0-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/interviewai-mock-interview/id1664024041?uo=4","developer":"Synnax Studio LTD","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":2,"4":1,"5":8}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1245266398","title":"Job Interview Prep Questions","store":"app_store","genre":"Business","score":4.68328,"ratings":341,"reviewCount":341,"installs":"N/A","description":"Do you have a job interview coming up? The best way to get ready for an interview is to take the time to review the most common interview questions you will most likely be asked. Knowing what you're going to say can eliminate a lot of interview stress.\n\nYou don't need to memorize an answer, but do take the time to consider how you'll respond. The more you prepare, the more confident you'll feel during a job interview.\nWhen you're not sure what to expect during an interview, also review this refresher on how job interviews work.\n Our career interview questions are helpful for practicing a specific career in any organization. Most of our career questions have been created by professional interviewers with actual experience in that particular career. \n\nThis app gives you a great way to prepare for job interviews. It tell you hot to answer lots of questions.\n\nDownload now for FREE!\n\n==================  \n\nTerms of Service: https://www.freeprivacypolicy.com/live/3a34f2c4-d4d9-4f13-8cda-ead859c21e05\nPrivacy: https://www.websitepolicies.com/policies/view/SmzqQXdK","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/9b/12/81/9b12812b-9707-06dc-052c-7cc260d58e07/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-8-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/job-interview-prep-questions/id1245266398?uo=4","developer":"Vinh Tran","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":14,"2":2,"3":9,"4":28,"5":288}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6743263009","title":"Interview Pilot: AI Copilot","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.82759,"ratings":435,"reviewCount":435,"installs":"N/A","description":"Interview Pilot is the leading interview assistant software designed to help job seekers excel during interviews. It functions as a real-time interview copilot, offering instant, tailored answers to interview questions. Using the latest state-of-the-art deep neural network models, this app provides real-time responses to any technical or behavioral questions, helping you refine your answers and improve your performance on the spot.\n\nSimply upload your resume, personal information, job details and company information and get customized answers during your interview! Built on the latest models trusted by millions globally, the app supports 99+ languages and any accents, accurately capturing any interview questions and conversations. Interview Pilot offers Conversation Mode and Question Mode so you can choose which suits your interview style the best. Copilot helps you tailor your answers for any industry, company or role.\n\nAll your interview sessions are stored locally on your device or encrypted securely via iCloud, making it easy to review past responses and track your progress over time. Advanced search and history ensures you can quickly retrieve specific answers and refine them as needed. All your files are automatically synced to all your devices via iCloud, ensuring a seamless experience.\n\nInterview Pilot develops, owns and operates proprietary technologies including Whisper Notes, WhisperShare, FileSync, Chronicle technology. Interview Pilot is a brand of Liberace AI.\n\nPlease review our privacy policy at https://www.interviewpilot.app/privacy.\nBy using this app, you agree to the terms outlined in https://www.interviewpilot.app/terms and https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/53/2b/23/532b23db-9972-ac0a-de6a-f16458714919/interviewpilot_newlogo-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/interview-pilot-ai-copilot/id6743263009?uo=4","developer":"Liberace AI","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":10,"2":1,"3":6,"4":20,"5":398}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6756551142","title":"Mock Interview Prep AI","store":"app_store","genre":"Business","score":5,"ratings":11,"reviewCount":11,"installs":"N/A","description":"InterviewPrepAI helps you prepare for interviews by practicing the way interviews actually happen — out loud.\n\nInstead of silently reading questions or typing answers, InterviewPrepAI puts you in a realistic mock interview setting where you speak your responses naturally, just as you would in a real conversation. You can also practice using guided flashcards designed to help you organize your thoughts, with feedback based on the STAR method so your answers stay clear, structured, and relevant.\n\nAs you practice, the app analyzes your responses and gives you focused, actionable feedback to help you communicate more confidently and effectively. Practice out loud, refine your answers, and walk into your next interview with confidence.\n\nTerms of Use Agreement: https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/76/eb/c9/76ebc907-3ee4-99ea-f950-2c780a370ee1/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007ephone-0-1-P3-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/mock-interview-prep-ai/id6756551142?uo=4","developer":"Nathan Busi","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":11}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1565835060","title":"Phenom Video","store":"app_store","genre":"Business","score":4.32742,"ratings":113,"reviewCount":113,"installs":"N/A","description":"Phenom Video offers a unique job application experience. It enables you to introduce yourself personally and authentically to your future employer via video.\n\nAs soon as a company invited you to a video assessment, all you need to do is enter your invitation code in the app and answer the company’s application questions. Thanks to our unique video technology you will be able to convince them with your motivation and special skills.\n\nTo get started, install the free Phenom Video app now.\n\nHere’s how easy it is to get started:\n\n- Enter the invitation code you received from your recruiter\n- Learn more about the process and check out our tutorials\n- Use our training environment to practice in advance and get comfortable\n- Start recording the company’s questions as soon as you are ready and show them why you are the right candidate for their job\n- Review your video answer and record it again in case you are not fully satisfied\n- Submit your application and receive feedback from the company very soon\n\nIf you have any technical problems, simply visit phenom.com or contact our live support in the app itself.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/12/06/95/12069576-a2b0-ecf3-d54c-39abf6799df9/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-8-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/phenom-video/id1565835060?uo=4","developer":"Phenom People","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":8,"2":9,"3":2,"4":13,"5":81}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6752641060","title":"OfferBull:AI Interview Copilot","store":"app_store","genre":"Utilities","score":4.73913,"ratings":23,"reviewCount":23,"installs":"N/A","description":"Offer Bull – Your Smart Interview Assistant. AI helps you land offers with ease!\n\n• AI-Powered Answers: Understands interview questions in depth and delivers professional responses.\n• Fast Response: Quickly interprets questions and returns clear, structured answers in seconds.\n• Wide Role Coverage: Includes common positions across industries with targeted practice sets.\n\n• Mock Interviews: Simulates real sessions based on your resume and job requirements.\n• Resume Upload: Uses your resume to tailor answers and generate follow-up questions. \n• Constant Updates: Regularly refreshes the question bank to match hiring trends. \n• Privacy First: Strict protection of user data and recorded content.\n\nWhether you are a fresh graduate entering the workforce or a professional seeking a promotion or job change, Offer Bull helps you sharpen your interview skills and boost your success rate. Start now and handle every interview challenge with confidence!","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/cf/df/24/cfdf24bc-c7b4-730a-8c01-a5e438d69450/AppIcon-1x_U007epad-0-1-85-220-0.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/offerbull-ai-interview-copilot/id6752641060?uo=4","developer":"Variable Definition (Shenzhen) Technology Co., Ltd","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":1,"2":0,"3":1,"4":0,"5":21}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6740067315","title":"PrepTalk: AI Interview Prep","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.6875,"ratings":16,"reviewCount":16,"installs":"N/A","description":"Practice interviews with AI-powered PrepTalk – your personal interview coach that adapts to your resume and dream job.\n\nMaster your next interview with personalized practice sessions featuring natural voice conversations and real-time feedback. Upload your resume, specify your target role, and let PrepTalk generate custom interview questions tailored to your experience and career goals.\n\nKEY FEATURES:\n• AI-Powered Interview Sessions\n- Custom questions based on your resume and target job\n- Natural voice conversations with advanced speech synthesis\n- Real-time feedback on your responses\n- Progressive difficulty levels\n\n• Personalized Success Plan\n- Enter the date of your upcoming interview\n- Get custom sessions to complete based on your resume and the desired role\n- See you odds of success improve with each completed session\n- Go into your interview with more confidence you can believe!\n\n• Comprehensive Preparation\n- Industry-specific questions\n- Behavioral and technical interview practice\n- Performance tracking and analytics\n- Detailed feedback after each session\n\n• Professional Development\n- Build confidence through repeated practice\n- Learn from detailed performance insights\n- Improve your interview techniques\n- Track your progress over time\n\nDownload PrepTalk today and transform your interview preparation with the power of AI.\n\nSome features within the app require an additional subscription. When you purchase a subscription, please be aware of the following:\n- Payment will be charged to iTunes Account at confirmation of purchase\n- Subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period.\n- Account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period, and identify cost of renewal.\n- Subscriptions may be managed by the user and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the user's Account Settings after purchase.\n\nTerms of Use (EULA) can be found at https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/56/6c/3e/566c3e74-ee66-b698-b0c4-463c33f0c8fe/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/preptalk-ai-interview-prep/id6740067315?uo=4","developer":"Gallen Labs LLC","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":1,"2":0,"3":0,"4":1,"5":14}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6747279931","title":"LevelUp AI: Interview Buddy","store":"app_store","genre":"Utilities","score":5,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":2,"installs":"N/A","description":"LevelUpAI · Interview Buddy is more than just a voice recorder or transcript tool — it’s your intelligent training partner designed to help you get better with every session. \t\n\nFor job seekers who want to improve after real interviews, instead of guessing what went wrong, let our AI analyze your interview recordings and show you exactly how to improve next time.\n\n\n【When to use】\n\n- Job Interview Practice:   Simulate interviews for your dream role, review transcripts, and get AI feedback to refine answers and boost confidence.\n- Investor Pitch:   Rehearse your pitch deck, analyze clarity and persuasiveness, and fine-tune delivery before meeting investors.\n- Team Standup:   Practice concise daily updates and improve clarity in how you communicate progress and blockers.\n- Client Briefing:   Record practice sessions for client meetings, ensuring your message is clear, professional, and impactful.\n- Performance Review:   Prepare for manager or HR reviews by rehearsing responses and receiving AI insights on tone and delivery.\n- Class Presentation:   Rehearse academic talks or thesis defenses, and get feedback on pacing, clarity, and structure.\n- Public Speaking:   Prepare for speeches, panels, or keynotes by analyzing delivery, filler words, and storytelling style.\n- Sales Call:   Sharpen your pitch, practice handling objections, and refine how you present value to clients.\n- And many more...\n\n\n【How to use】\n\n1. Record your interview/ coffee chat/ any conversation — anytime, anywhere.\n2. Receive a full, precise transcript.\n3. Unlock AI-powered feedback that highlights what you did well and what could be improved — including communication clarity, technical depth, logical flow etc.\n4. Track your growth over time by revisiting past interviews and seeing how your performance evolves.\n\n\n【Why Levelup AI】\n\n- Not just transcription — Levelup.AI provides targeted feedback on your interview recordings so you can reflect on what worked—and fix what didn’t.\n\n- Unlike many AI tools that hide your recordings. You have full access to your recordings, transcripts, and insights — Your control come first.\n\n- Fast, private, and genuinely helpful.\n\n\n\n\nTrain smarter. Speak stronger. Get hired.\n\nDownload LevelUpAI · Interview Buddy and make every interview your best one yet!\n\nNeed support? email contact@vibingcompany.com","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/ac/f8/b5/acf8b544-7e65-873b-9ac7-ef025442ddd6/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-4-85-220.jpeg/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/levelup-ai-interview-buddy/id6747279931?uo=4","developer":"The Vibing Company Limited","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1123576667","title":"IELTS Speaking Assistant","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.50298,"ratings":334,"reviewCount":334,"installs":"N/A","description":"Want to get the desired band score in IELTS speaking fast and easily? \n\nNo worries! Install the IELTS Speaking Assistant app now and get all necessary materials for efficient IELTS speaking practice: \n1) step-by-step instructions for effective speaking practice\n2) all the real exam IELTS speaking questions that you'll be asked in your real IELTS speaking test\n3) a rich collection of ideas which you can use to make relevant and extended answers regardless of your likes and dislikes, habits, cultural differences, and other factors \n4) ready-made answers to all the questions \n5) IELTS speaking progress chart (a printable pdf document which will help you control your progress)\n\nHow will you benefit from using IELTS Speaking Assistant?\n• You will get fully prepared for your speaking test without wasting your time on searching for questions and ideas and model answers. Just learn everything that's in the app and you will never dry up in the middle of your speaking test\n• Using the app, you will increase the efficiency of your IELTS speaking classes with a tutor to 100%\n• During your IELTS speaking classes you will have a chance to focus on intonation instead of coming up with ideas to answer questions\n• You will prepare for the speaking test anywhere, anytime\n\nWhat makes IELTS Speaking Assistant different from the other apps for IELTS speaking? \n•  new answers are added almost every day\n•  you get unique content that you won't find elsewhere\n•  the app has been created by experienced IELTS tutors according to the British Council test format \n•  use one application instead of many websites, apps and books\n \nFree account: \n•  access to all real test IELTS speaking questions  \n•  access to vocabulary, ideas and answers in 3 topics in each part \n•  the Complete Guide to IELTS Speaking (e-book)\n•  IELTS speaking progress chart (printable pdf)\n\nPremium account: \n•  access to all real test IELTS speaking questions  \n•  access to vocabulary, ideas and answers in ALL topics \n•  the Complete Guide to IELTS Speaking (e-book)\n•  IELTS speaking progress chart (printable pdf)\n\nIELTS Speaking Assistant offers 3 subscription options:\n1-month subscription for $9.99\n3-month subscription for $18.99\n12-month subscription for $29.99\n\nSubscriptions will be charged to your credit card through your iTunes account. Your subscription will automatically renew unless cancelled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. You will not be able to cancel the subscription once activated. Manage your subscriptions in Account Settings after purchase. \n\n\nVisit our website for more information: \nwww.ielts-assistant.net  \n\nIf you have any questions, write to us:\nsupport@ielts-assistant.com \n\nPrivacy policy: https://virtualeducation.ee/privacy_policy.html \nTerms of use: https://virtualeducation.ee/ISA_terms_of_use.html","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/6b/44/2e/6b442e8a-3d27-c3d7-eb83-b3567d00e2d6/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-0-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/ielts-speaking-assistant/id1123576667?uo=4","developer":"Virtual Education OU","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":27,"2":6,"3":7,"4":26,"5":268}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6745811320","title":"Reprogram: Mental Preparation","store":"app_store","genre":"Health & Fitness","score":4.74857,"ratings":350,"reviewCount":350,"installs":"N/A","description":"Describe what you're nervous about. This app mentally prepares you for it, in just 10 minutes a day.\n\nTHE PROBLEM\n\nYou have the skills. But when the pressure is on — the presentation, the exam, the interview, the big game — something takes over. Your mind freezes, self-doubt creeps in, and you perform below what you're capable of.\n\nYou've tried deep breaths. You've told yourself to \"just relax.\" It doesn't work, because the problem isn't in the moment. It's in the mental patterns running underneath.\n\nTHE SOLUTION\n\nReprogram uses mental rehearsal — the same technique used by elite athletes, surgeons, and top performers — to train your mind before the moment arrives.\n\nSimply describe your situation, and Reprogram creates a personalized guided mental rehearsal session built specifically for you. No generic scripts. No one-size-fits-all. A session made for YOU and what YOU are preparing for.\n\nHOW IT WORKS\n\n1. Describe your moment: Your presentation, exam, interview, competition, negotiation — anything\n\n2. Get your custom session: Reprogram generates a personalized guided mental rehearsal with vivid detail tailored to your specific situation\n\n3. Listen for 10 minutes: Close your eyes, follow the guided audio, and mentally rehearse your best performance\n\n4. Train your brain: Your mind can't fully distinguish between vivid rehearsal and real experience. Each session builds confidence for the real moment\n\n5. Show up ready: Walk into your moment with trained confidence, not hopeful anxiety\n\nKEY FEATURES\n\n• Custom Mental Rehearsal Sessions — Create a personalized session for any situation in seconds\n\n•  Relaxation & Breathwork — Optional preparation modes to deepen your session\n\n• 10 Minutes a Day — Short, effective sessions that fit any schedule\n\n•  Backed by Neuroscience — Mental rehearsal activates the same neural circuits as real performance\n\n•  Progress Tracking — Build consistency with streaks and daily reminders\n\n•  Pre-made Performance Sessions — Expertly crafted sessions for confidence, focus, calm, and peak performance\n\n•  Vision Boards — Visualize your goals with custom image boards\n\nWHO IS THIS FOR?\n\nReprogram is for anyone who needs to perform under pressure:\n\n• Students preparing for exams and interviews\n\n• Professionals with upcoming presentations, pitches, or negotiations\n\n• Athletes and competitors preparing for game day\n\n• Anyone who knows they're capable of more but freezes when it matters\n\nWhether your moment is tomorrow or in three months — Reprogram helps you show up ready.\n\nWHY IT WORKS\n\nMental rehearsal isn't imagination — it's training. Research from Harvard, Stanford, and the Cleveland Clinic shows that mental rehearsal activates the same neural circuits as actual performance. With daily practice you:\n\n• Override anxiety and self-doubt patterns\n\n• Build confidence through repeated mental success\n\n• Sharpen focus and clarity under pressure\n\n• Train your nervous system to stay calm when it counts\n\nElite performers don't just practice physically. They train mentally. Now you can too.\n\nBE READY FOR YOUR NEXT BIG MOMENT\n\nDownload Reprogram and create your first custom mental rehearsal session. Used by athletes, speakers, students, and professionals to perform at their best when it matters most.\n\nQuestions? Contact us at support@reprogramapp.com\n\nReprogram requires a subscription to access all features including custom mental rehearsal sessions and vision boards. Start with a free trial, then continue with a monthly or annual plan.\n\nTerms of Service: https://reprogramapp.com/terms\n\nPrivacy Policy: https://reprogramapp.com/privacy","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/33/be/31/33be3106-1014-deeb-5bf8-70d46ed4659d/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007ephone-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/reprogram-mental-preparation/id6745811320?uo=4","developer":"MMCH Digital Solutions","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":11,"2":1,"3":9,"4":23,"5":306}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6566195580","title":"IELTS Speaking Topics","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":5,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":1,"installs":"N/A","description":"Master the IELTS Speaking test with IELTS Speaking - Practice Test. This comprehensive app offers 1000 authentic test samples covering all parts of the IELTS Speaking test—Part 1 (Introduction and Interview), Part 2 (Long Turn), and Part 3 (Discussion).\n\nKey Features\n\n• 1000 Test Samples: Gain insight into real IELTS Speaking questions and answers.\n• Complete Coverage: Practice for Part 1, Part 2, and Part 3 of the IELTS Speaking test.\n• Bookmark Favorites: Save important questions and answers for quick review.\n• User-Friendly Interface: Intuitive design for easy navigation and study.\n• Offline Access: Prepare anytime, anywhere without needing an internet connection.\n• Regular Updates: Stay up-to-date with the latest trends and questions in IELTS Speaking.\n• Whether you're aiming for a high score in academic or general training, IELTS Speaking Mastery is your go-to tool. Prepare effectively, build confidence, and achieve your desired IELTS score with our expertly curated content.\n\nDownload IELTS Speaking Mastery now and start excelling in your IELTS Speaking test!","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/f1/9e/06/f19e0659-82e8-ebc8-0353-cff5e422c2a0/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-11-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/ielts-speaking-topics/id6566195580?uo=4","developer":"Thuong Nguyen","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6572284517","title":"OfferGoose-AI Resume&Interview","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.54737,"ratings":95,"reviewCount":95,"installs":"N/A","description":"Struggling to get interview invites? Blanking out during crucial calls? Meet OfferGoose, your all-in-one \"Second Brain\" for career success. From generating ATS-friendly resumes to providing real-time answers during actual interviews, we help you break through the noise and land your dream job faster.\n\n【 TOP FEATURES 】\n\n[ AI Resume Builder & Optimizer Transform your resume into an interview magnet ]\n\n* Instant Resume Creation: Hate formatting? Just input your experience, and our AI builds a professional, polished resume in seconds.\n\n* Smart JD Matching: Don't just write; tailor! Upload a Job Description (JD), and our AI optimizes your resume keywords to maximize relevance and pass ATS screenings.\n\n* AI Resume Score: Get an instant diagnostic from a virtual HR perspective. We identify weaknesses and provide actionable fixes to boost your success rate.\n\n[ Real-Time Interview Copilot Never freeze or stumble on a question again ]\n\n* Live Speech Recognition: Whether it's a video call or phone screen, our AI listens to the interviewer’s questions in real-time.\n\n* Instant Answer Suggestions: Get \"speed-of-thought\" assistance. Based on your resume and the role, we generate high-scoring talking points and key metrics instantly.\n\n* Discreet Companion: Designed for the \"Laptop Interview + Phone Assistant\" setup. Maintain natural eye contact while getting the critical hints you need to answer with confidence.\n\n[ AI Mock Interviews Practice makes perfect. Conquer your anxiety before the real deal ]\n\n* Immersive Simulations: Practice anytime with our AI interviewer. A judgment-free zone to overcome stage fright.\n\n* Adaptive Follow-up Questions: Our AI doesn't just ask standard questions; it digs deeper based on your answers, simulating the pressure of a real interview.\n\n* Detailed Performance Analysis: Receive comprehensive feedback on your logic, content, and delivery after every session. Improve with every practice.\n\n【 Why OfferGoose? 】\n\n* All-in-One Solution: Replace multiple tools with one powerful app.\n\n* Efficiency Booster: Cut prep time from days to minutes.\n\n* Personalized AI: No generic templates. We craft answers unique to your background.\n\n* Privacy First: Your data and resume details are strictly protected.\n\n【 Perfect For 】\n\n* New Graduates facing their first Spring/Autumn recruiting season.\n\n* Professionals seeking career growth or salary jumps.\n\n* Nervous Interviewers who need a confidence boost.\n\n* Anyone looking to optimize their Resume/CV and win more offers.\n\nDownload OfferGoose now and turn interviews into offers!\n\nQuestions or feedback? Contact us inside the app.\n\nPrivacy Policy: https://offergoose.cn/privacyPolicy.html\n\nTerms of Service: https://offergoose.cn/serviceAgreement.html","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/b9/cc/18/b9cc1838-0874-8d43-664c-69dbe7d727c8/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/offergoose-ai-resume-interview/id6572284517?uo=4","developer":"Astronet Technology PTE LTD","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":7,"2":0,"3":3,"4":9,"5":76}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6754044957","title":"HotSeat: AI Interview Practice","store":"app_store","genre":"Business","score":5,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":1,"installs":"N/A","description":"Nail your next job interview with HotSeat - the AI-powered mock interview simulator that adapts to your unique resume and target role.\n\nUnlike generic interview prep apps that ask cookie-cutter questions, HotSeat creates personalized, real-time interview sessions tailored specifically to your experience and the job you're applying for. Import your resume and job description, then practice with an AI interviewer that asks relevant questions based on your actual background.\n\nReal Interviews. Real Pressure. Real Results.\n\nHotSeat simulates authentic interview conditions with live, conversational AI that responds to your answers in real-time - just like a real hiring manager would. No pre-recorded questions. No robotic responses. Just natural, flowing conversations that prepare you for the real thing.\n\nHow It Works:\n\n1. Import your resume and the job description for the position you’re applying for.\n2. Sensitive information and personally identifiable data (PII) is automatically detected and removed.\n3. HotSeat analyzes your experience, skills, background, and job requirements.\n4. When you're ready, an AI interviewer will initiate a simulated phone call interview.\n5. Advanced AI generates unique questions on the fly, tailored to your resume and the job requirements.\n6. Answer the interview questions naturally through voice. The AI interviewer adapts to your responses, asks follow-ups, and challenges you - just like a real interview.\n7. Get better with each session. Build confidence, refine your answers, and eliminate nervousness before the big day.\n\nWhy HotSeat Gives You an Edge:\n\n- Most interview prep tools offer static question lists or one-size-fits-all advice. HotSeat uses advanced AI trained on real interview patterns to create dynamic, personalized sessions that mirror actual hiring conversations.\n\n- The AI doesn't just read from a script - it listens to your answers and responds intelligently with relevant follow-up questions, probing deeper into your experience just like a seasoned interviewer would.\n\nPerfect For:\n\n- Job seekers preparing for upcoming interviews\n- Career changers practicing how to position their experience\n- Recent graduates gaining interview confidence\n- Professionals targeting specific roles or companies\n- Anyone who wants to walk into their next interview fully prepared\n\nFeatures:\n\n- AI-powered real-time mock interviews\n- Personalized questions based on your resume\n- Role-specific interview simulations\n- Natural voice conversations\n- Adaptive follow-up questions\n- No subscription required - pay only for what you use\n- Your data stays private and secure\n\nGet interview-ready today. Don't walk into your next interview unprepared. With HotSeat, you'll practice with an AI that knows your background, understands the role, and helps you deliver confident, compelling answers.\n\nDownload HotSeat and turn interview anxiety into interview confidence.\n\nEnd User License Agreement: https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/6c/22/83/6c228397-4a70-1596-eb2b-6f7e9239e304/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007ephone-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/hotseat-ai-interview-practice/id6754044957?uo=4","developer":"Dainware LLC","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6755840985","title":"OfferLine - AI Interview Help","store":"app_store","genre":"Productivity","score":4.63636,"ratings":11,"reviewCount":11,"installs":"N/A","description":"OfferLine helps you perform at your best in job interviews - before, during, and after the call.\n\nPrepare with realistic mock sessions, upload your resume for personalized context, and get actionable insights from past interviews. When it matters most, OfferLine acts as a live interview copilot, helping you stay sharp and confident in real time.\n\nPractice common and role-specific questions, refine your responses, and review recordings to understand what worked and what didn’t. OfferLine gives you structured feedback so you can improve faster without needing a coach or scheduling sessions.\n\nNo pressure, no prep overload. Use OfferLine on your own time — from first practice to final round.\n\nFEATURES\n\nLive interview copilot for real-time support\n\nMock interview sessions for job preparation\n\nResume upload for personalized guidance\n\nResponse feedback and performance insights\n\nPractice for technical, behavioral, and hiring calls\n\nTrack progress across roles and applications\n\nManage your subscription in your account settings after purchase.\n\nTerms of Use: https://offerlineapp.com/terms\n\nPrivacy Policy: https://offerlineapp.com/privacy","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/62/40/35/6240355a-951d-6bbb-e1b6-d0117801b212/AppIcon-0-1x_U007ephone-0-1-85-220-0.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/offerline-ai-interview-help/id6755840985?uo=4","developer":"Aaron Morjaria","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":1,"4":2,"5":8}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6751876614","title":"Interview Coder App","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":0,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"InterviewCoder - AI Interview Coach & Interview Practice Assistant\n\nInterviewCoder is your advanced AI interview assistant that helps you during mock interviews by\nlistening to the conversation and providing you with optimal answers to the interviewer's questions\nin real-time. As you practice for job interviews, InterviewCoder analyzes the questions being asked\nand quickly suggests the best responses tailored to your field and industry.\n\nWith InterviewCoder by your side, you get:\n• Instant AI-powered answer suggestions for interview questions\n• Field-specific expert responses for tech, finance, healthcare & more\n• Real-time interview preparation and practice support\n• Strategic guidance for final round interviews & tough questions\n\nThis gives you a powerful advantage during interviews. By having expert-crafted answers readily\navailable, you can respond confidently and effectively to any question that comes your way. Perfect\nfor technical interviews, final rounds, and AI-assisted interview preparation. No more being caught\noff guard or struggling to find the right words - InterviewCoder helps you make a strong impression\nand stand out from other candidates.\n\nLet InterviewCoder be your ultimate interview success tool!","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/67/71/aa/6771aa12-5b24-bc28-c463-77ed2efb9193/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-8-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/interview-coder-app/id6751876614?uo=4","developer":"InterviewCoder","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1553400379","title":"Pitch - Expert AI","store":"app_store","genre":"Games","score":4.67493,"ratings":6,"reviewCount":6134,"installs":"N/A","description":"Whether you’re a seasoned pro or learning Pitch for the first time, Pitch – Expert AI is a great way to play, learn, and master this classic trick-taking card game. \n\nEnjoy classic Pitch rules — play solo (cutthroat) or with a team, and choose to play with or without bidding (Auction Pitch). Jump right in with preset variations from the All Fours family of card games, including Pedro, Pidro, Setback, Smear, Nine-Five, and Eighty-Three. With extensive rule customization, you can adjust the rules to suit the way you play.\n\nLearn smarter, play better, and master Pitch with powerful AI opponents and in-depth analysis tools. Play anytime, even offline.\n\nCHALLENGING AND ENJOYABLE FOR ALL\n\nNew to Pitch?\nLearn as you play with the NeuralPlay AI, which offers real-time suggestions to guide your moves. Build your skills hands-on, explore strategies, and improve your decision-making in a single-player experience that teaches you every step of the game.\n\nAlready an Expert?\nCompete against six levels of advanced AI opponents, designed to challenge your skills, sharpen your strategy, and make every game competitive, rewarding, and exciting.\n\nKEY FEATURES\n\nLearn and Improve\n• AI guidance: Receive real-time insights whenever your plays differ from the AI’s choices.\n• Built-in card counter: Strengthen your counting and strategic decision-making.\n• Trick-by-trick review: Analyze every move in detail to sharpen your gameplay.\n• Replay hand: Review and replay a deal to practice and improve.\n\nConvenience and Control\n• Offline play: Enjoy the game anytime, even without an internet connection.\n• Undo: Quickly correct mistakes and refine your strategy.\n• Hints: Get helpful suggestions when you’re unsure of your next move.\n• Claim remaining tricks: End the hand early when your cards are unbeatable.\n• Skip hand: Move past hands you’d rather not play.\n\nProgression and Customization\n• Six AI levels: From beginner-friendly to expert-challenging.\n• Detailed statistics: Track your performance and progress.\n• Customization: Personalize the look with color themes and card decks.\n\nRULE CUSTOMIZATIONS\n\nExplore different ways to play with flexible rule options, including:\n• Initial deal: Select 6–10 cards for the deal.\n• Kitty: Deal 2–6 cards to the kitty.\n• Stick the dealer: The dealer must bid if everyone else passes.\n• Dealer can steal: The dealer may match the highest bid instead of exceeding it.\n• Misdeal: Allow a misdeal for hands with only cards ranked 9 or lower.\n• Dealer can run it: The dealer may choose to deal three more cards.\n• Discarding: Allow discarding after trump is chosen, with the option to give the stock to the dealer or maker.\n• Trump only: Require players to lead and follow with trump only.\n• Team: Play in partnerships or individually.\n• Low point: Assign the low trump point to the capturer or the player who played it.\n• Off-jack: Include the off-jack as an additional trump worth one point.\n• Jokers: Play with 0–2 jokers, each worth 1 point.\n• Scoring trumps: Optionally score: 3 (3 pts), 5 (5 pts), 9 (9 pts), Q (20 pts), K (25 pts).\n• Special trumps: Optionally include: off-ace (1 pt), off-3 (3 pts), off-5 (5 pts), off-9 (9 pts).\n• Last trick: Award a point for taking the final trick.\n\nDOWNLOAD TODAY\n\nPlay, learn, and master Pitch – Expert AI. Enjoy a single-player Pitch experience designed for practice, strategy, or casual play. Whether you want to improve your skills or relax with an offline card game, play your way with smart AI opponents, customizable rules, and a fresh challenge every game.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/a4/b8/65/a4b865d2-ac46-86a1-2e5d-7b556cadabee/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-11-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/pitch-expert-ai/id1553400379?uo=4","developer":"NeuralPlay, LLC","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":124,"2":78,"3":261,"4":742,"5":4929}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1579828873","title":"Vocal Pitch Monitor-Voice Whiz","store":"app_store","genre":"Health & Fitness","score":4.27815,"ratings":906,"reviewCount":906,"installs":"N/A","description":"Analyze your voice in real-time with Voice Whiz. Voice Whiz uses machine learning to classify your voice into Male/Female/Androgynous. It makes use of speech recognition to reveal key metrics in voicing. Voice Whiz also allows you to practice pitches within your vocal range and track changes over time.\n\nHere’s a summary of the features offered by our app;\n\n- Voice pitch analysis\n- Speech recognition\n- Male/Female/Androgynous classification\n- Pitch practice\n- Progress tracking and reminders\n- Tips & learning\n\nSee Terms & Conditions in their entirety here \nhttps://dhwaper.notion.site/termsandconditions\n\nPrivacy Policy: https://dhwaper.notion.site/privacypolicy\n\n\nWebsite:https://voicewhiz.app\nContact  hello@dhwaper.com for support.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/3f/65/88/3f658898-6e57-0cd0-b6ba-234d7a4c28e2/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-8-0-sRGB-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/vocal-pitch-monitor-voice-whiz/id1579828873?uo=4","developer":"Dhwaper","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":97,"2":19,"3":59,"4":91,"5":640}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1509108036","title":"MOJO Sports","store":"app_store","genre":"Sports","score":4.67082,"ratings":2,"reviewCount":2163,"installs":"N/A","description":"MOJO is the only all-in-one app for youth sports. And it’s FREE for coaches to use with their teams. \n \nWith MOJO, coaches save hours of aggravation and stress searching for drills, planning practices and managing their team — because it’s all in one place. And parents stay on top of what’s going on at games and practice, all season long.\n\nMOJO features effective, easy-to-follow instructional videos, simplified team management and dynamic practice-planning tools so that coaches and parents focus on what matters most — helping kids get the most out of sports and making memories for a lifetime.\n\nONLY THE BEST FOR YOUR KIDS\nWith content from world-class leagues and teams, MOJO brings unparalleled quality to the most popular youth sports.\n\nMOJO collaborated with FC Barcelona to bring never-before-seen games, drills and curriculum from their famed youth academy. And with partners like US Youth Soccer, SAY Soccer and more, kids learn from the best soccer players and coaches in the world.\n \nMOJO partnered with Major League Baseball to create fun, dynamic practices for youth baseball and softball teams, featuring the same age-appropriate videos and practice plans you’d expect from MOJO. \n\nMOJO worked with the Jr. NBA, the official youth basketball participation program of the NBA and WNBA, to create more than 120 activities that can be replicated at practice or at home, in addition to games and exercises to help advance on-court development.\n\nAnd in partnership with NFL Flag, the official flag football league of the NFL, MOJO created a fun, engaging curriculum shot at the state-of-the-art SoFi Stadium in Los Angeles. Learn the game like never before — including the NFL Flag Playbook, brought to life on video for the first time ever.\n\nTEAM MANAGEMENT, SIMPLIFIED\nWhat time’s practice? Where’s the game? Who’s got snack? MOJO makes it easier than ever for coaches and parents to answer those questions — and so much more. With intuitive, easy-to-use scheduling and chat, MOJO cuts the clutter and keeps everything that coaches and parents need for a season of youth sports in one convenient app.\n \nSUPPORT PLAYERS AT PRACTICE AND EVERYWHERE ELSE\nWith the new MOJO+, families can access hundreds of games to play at home, so kids can learn and develop any time, anywhere. One subscription gives you access to age-appropriate games across all current and future MOJO sports. The same world-class teams and organizations that helped develop MOJO practices will help kids become the best players they can be.\n \nTHE WORLD’S BEST YOUTH SPORTS ADVICE AND INFORMATION\nCoaching sports is hard. Coaching kids is even harder. That’s why MOJO provides the world’s best advice and information on virtually any question you might have about youth sports. What are 5-year-old players able to do? How do you handle your first practice? What do you do with kids who won’t listen? No matter your problem, MOJO has you covered with expert advice, Q&As and interviews, with partners like the Positive Coaching Alliance and Aspen Institute’s Project Play.\n\nSubscription pricing and terms\n\nMOJO offers an optional auto-renewing subscription. \n\nPayment is charged to the credit card connected to your iTunes Account when you confirm the subscription purchase. Subscriptions automatically renew unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the subscription period. Your account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period, and the cost of the renewal will be identified. You may manage your subscription and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to your Account Settings after the purchase. Any unused portion of a free trial period, if offered, will be forfeited when you purchase a subscription, where applicable.\n\nRead our terms and conditions here:\nTerms of service: https://www.mojo.sport/terms-mobile\nPrivacy policy: https://www.mojo.sport/privacy-mobile","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/c2/2a/a6/c22aa6db-4c38-3783-c8b0-92947a468ab2/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007ephone-0-1-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/mojo-sports/id1509108036?uo=4","developer":"MOJO, Inc.","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":85,"2":24,"3":55,"4":190,"5":1809}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1409450884","title":"Learn to Sing - Perfect Pitch","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.41675,"ratings":15,"reviewCount":15640,"installs":"N/A","description":"Perfect Pitch is your Pitch Perfector! Everyone can sing better with our Learn to Sing Training Program!\nPerfect Pitch helps you Learn+Practice, Train+Track, Anytime+Anywhere!\n\nPerfect Pitch's Pitch Perfector™ technology detects and display your singing pitch accuracy in real-time, you can easily tune and train to improve your singing.\n\n1) Vocals - listen to any pitch and practice your accuracy in free style\n2) Warm Up - basic to advanced levels of vocal exercises\n3) Sing Songs - practice your singing performance and sing your heart out!\n4) Training Program - 10 levels, 1000+ exercises to help build your musical sense and pitch accuracy\n5) Records - keep tracks of your Singing Scores + Progress + Report Statistics\n\nFeatures:\n- Pitch Perfector™ Real-time Pitch Detection Technology\n- Studio effects to enhance your singing performance \n- Octave Control (Low - Normal - High)\n- Sing-along songs from your iTunes music library and Apple Music\n\nMembership Benefits includes:\n- Training Program (10 levels, 50 lessons X 15 exercises) \n- Daily Track Statistics (Progress + Scores + Report)\n- Classroom Songs with Note Guidance to improve your singing in real time \n- Extra free Warm-Up Exercises\n\nEmail: hello@perfectpitch.ai\nWebsite: www.perfectpitch.ai","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple123/v4/70/ac/d4/70acd4df-9958-84e5-57ed-b3ed8a93a1ec/AppIcon-1-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-0-0-7-0-0-sRGB-0-0-0-GLES2_U002c0-512MB-85-220-0-0.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/learn-to-sing-perfect-pitch/id1409450884?uo=4","developer":"Learn to Sing - Vocal Warmups, Singing Lessons, Ear Training, Karaoke","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":602,"2":404,"3":1517,"4":2468,"5":10649}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1551925155","title":"4APP Sports","store":"app_store","genre":"Sports","score":4.38624,"ratings":189,"reviewCount":189,"installs":"N/A","description":"45,000+ players trust 4APP to throw harder, walk fewer batters, and stay healthy while doing it.\n- 93% improve command\n- 87% gain velocity\n- 60% feel healthier\n- 40% gain 5+ mph in just 30 days\n\nCreated by Cy Young Award winner Trevor Bauer, the Ultimate Pitching Program helps pitchers dramatically improve their game:\n- Struggling to throw harder? \n- Can’t hit your spots?\n- Losing stamina late in games? \n- Battling constant injuries? \n- Trying to stand out to scouts? \n- Having trouble recovering after a game?\n\nWhether you’re chasing a spot on a new team, aiming to impress college recruiters, or simply looking to enjoy the game more, 4APP Sports has the tools you need to succeed.\n- Custom Remote Training tailored to your goals and needs \n- Pitching Mechanics Video Analysis by the pros \n- Daily Throwing Programs for consistent progress \n- Command-Tracking Tools to master the strike zone \n- Daily Health Tracking for optimal recovery and peak performance \n- Hitter Attack Plans to dominate every at-bat \n- Pitching Journals to track your growth\n\nSubscription Tiers for Every Pitcher\n\nPitching Lite:\n- Health Tracking \n- Command Tracking + Bullpen Coach \n- Pitching Journal \n\nPitching Essentials:\n- Health Tracking + In-Depth Insights from Pro Coaches \n- Command Tracking + Pro Bullpen Coach \n- Hitter Attack Plans and Heat Maps \n- Pitching Journal \n\nUltimate Pitching Program:\n- Fully Customized Training \n- Monthly Throwing Programs \n- Exclusive Video Content Library \n- Health Tracking + In-Depth Insights from Pro Coaches \n- Command Tracking + Pro Bullpen Coach \n- Hitter Attack Plans and Heat Maps \n- Pitching Journal \n\n4APP Sports is redefining the way pitchers train and recover. Used by pitchers at every level—from T-Ball to the Big Leagues—4APP provides the tools, insights, and guidance to help you unlock your full potential.\n\nWhat are you waiting for?\n\nJoin thousands of pitchers already transforming their game. \nDownload 4APP Sports today and start your journey to the top of the mound!\n\nTerms of Use: https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/7d/3b/b5/7d3bb503-67cc-afa1-39ca-458a94d93b16/AppIcon-Release-0-0-1x_U007ephone-0-1-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/4app-sports/id1551925155?uo=4","developer":"4APP Sports LLC","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":16,"2":5,"3":11,"4":15,"5":142}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"914239183","title":"SingTrue: Learn to sing in tune, pitch perfect","store":"app_store","genre":"Music","score":4.23872,"ratings":1,"reviewCount":1286,"installs":"N/A","description":"SingTrue can teach anybody to sing in perfect tune. Even if you think you're tone deaf!\n~~ Selected by Apple for iTunes \"Learn an Instrument\" feature. ~~\n\n\"Easy to use.\" -- The New York Times\n\n\"A perfect app\" -- Appolicious.com\n\n\"Amazing, effective and user friendly\" -- AppPicker.com\n\n\"Voice training just got a whole lot easier and less expensive\" -- PreApps.com\n\nWorried that you have a bad voice? Always told you're out of tune or off-key when you sing?\n\nMany people think they can't sing because they don't have \"natural talent\" or weren't born \"musically gifted\". The surprising truth is that anybody can learn to sing well, even those who feel totally unmusical.\n\nSingTrue helps you discover your inner musicality and gain control over your voice to become a natural, confident, powerful singer.\n\n\nApp Store Reviews:\n\n\"Everything I wanted in an app I found on this one! It's easy to use and the exercises are great, I can already feel difference in my singing voice\"\n-- 5 stars, Courteney S, USA\n\n\"Definitely recommend this to anyone who worries at karaoke time!\"\n-- 5 stars \"Always-thinking\", UK\n\n\nHOW SINGTRUE WORKS\n\nSingTrue features over 30 interactive exercises* that help you learn to sing easily, confidently and in perfect tune. By using the iPhone microphone and sophisticated signal processing, the app analyses your singing and provides personal feedback on how you can improve.\n\nSpend a few minutes practicing with the app's exercises every day and you will rapidly become a capable, confident singer.\n\nIf you are already a musician, the app will train your voice and your ears to help you become more confident, more creative, and more musical. In fact, the advanced exercises will help you recognise notes by ear - enabling you to play by ear, write your own music, and improvise freely on your instrument.\n\nThe exercises have been designed by experts, in consultation with some of the leading vocal teachers in the world. Building on the success of the RelativePitch ear training app (featured by Apple and used by over 300,000 musicians) and the Tone Deaf Test (4.5-star rated app used by 170,000+ people), SingTrue has been developed to help more people discover their inner voice and naturally become sensational musicians.\n\nFEATURES\n\n- SingTrue develops your Voice, Ears and Mind for singing\n- Uses the iPhone microphone to analyse your singing and gives personal feedback\n- Over 30 different exercises to explore, with more coming soon*\n- Listening examples provided by professional singers\n- Track your progress in detail and see your voice improving\n- Share your achievements with friends on Facebook, Twitter or Email\n\n\nCOMMON QUESTIONS\n\nQ: What if I'm tone deaf?\nA: Don't worry! You probably aren't. Close to 1 million people have taken our Tone Deaf Test, and just 2% have proved to be genuinely tone deaf. Still worried? Search the App Store for our \"Tone Deaf Test\" app.\n\nQ: Is this just for people who like singing?\nA: No, SingTrue has been designed for singers and non-singers alike.\n\nQ: Can you really learn to sing in tune?\nA: Yes, it's simply a matter of learning pitch sensitivity (ears) and vocal control (voice).\n\nQ: What if I can already sing?\nA: SingTrue can help you become more accurate, more expressive and more confident.\n\n\nApp Store Reviews:\n\n\"This app is great way to learn to sing and to prove to my husband that I'm not tone deaf!\"\n-- 5 stars, Bardils, UK\n\n\"This app is incredibly useful both to the beginner and to the pro singer. Bravo!\"\n-- 5 stars, Richard E, UK\n\n\"I'm not a good singer by any means but with this app I think I finally have a chance to learn. It's been a few hours and I already can notice an improvement. Can't wait to see where I'll get when I have completed all levels.\"\n-- 5 stars, Peter, UK\n\nDownload SingTrue today!\n\nIf you have any other questions or need help getting started, just email support@EasyEarTraining.com and we'll be happy to help.\n\n* Unlocking the full set of exercises requires in-app purchase.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple62/v4/b9/1e/a6/b91ea6d4-723d-2e3f-223f-4bcb0f09ceb2/mzl.paotxroz.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/singtrue-learn-to-sing-in-tune-pitch-perfect/id914239183?uo=4","developer":"Easy Ear Training","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":102,"2":53,"3":72,"4":268,"5":791}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"509993510","title":"Smule: Sing & Duet","store":"app_store","genre":"Music","score":4.47388,"ratings":174,"reviewCount":174304,"installs":"N/A","description":"Sing, duet, and create music on Smule, a creative singing platform built to help you grow your voice with confidence. Join others in duets for free, or unlock solo recording when you are ready to practice, learn, and craft your sound.\n\nExplore 15 million+ songs across pop, rock, R&B, country, K-pop, musicals, and more. Smule gives you the space to practice, improve, and explore your voice at your own pace, whether you are singing for fun or working toward becoming a better singer.\n\nOn Smule, you can begin by joining existing duets with singers from around the world at no cost. Singing together is a low pressure way to start, helping you learn by doing while building confidence through shared performances. With a VIP subscription, you can unlock solo recording and start your own duets or group songs, giving you more control to practice independently, refine performances, and shape your sound.\n\nSmule offers one of the largest karaoke song libraries available, with new songs added regularly. You can also sing recorded duets alongside official tracks from global superstars. Smule lets you join pre recorded duet performances featuring artists like Ed Sheeran, Dua Lipa, Olivia Rodrigo, and Disney favorites, so you can learn songs you love and feel part of the music.\n\nAs you sing, Smule helps you improve naturally over time. You can practice with pitch guidance, adjust song keys to better fit your vocal range, and experiment with harmonies, layers, and arrangements. Whether you are practicing solo, joining duets, or creating group songs, Smule supports progress at every stage of your singing journey.\n\nSmule uses studio quality audio and voice effects to support creativity without replacing your unique sound. You can enhance recordings with reverb, filters, and vocal effects, explore optional AI powered tools to refine tone and range, and experiment freely while keeping your voice authentic. These tools are designed to help you learn, improve, and gain confidence as you sing.\n\nSmule is a global community of singers in more than 190 countries. You can join duets, create group songs, discover new artists and styles, participate in live singing sessions, or share performances when you feel ready. Many singers start by practicing and joining duets, then gradually unlock more creative options as their confidence grows.\n\nSmule is built for every kind of singer, from curious first timers and casual karaoke fans to aspiring artists developing their voice. There is no single right way to use Smule. You choose how you practice, how you perform, and how far you want to go.\n\nSmule is more than a karaoke app. It is a creative platform for learning to sing, practicing with purpose, building confidence, and growing through solo recordings, duets, and musical collaboration, powered by smart tools and a supportive global community. Download Smule and start singing today.\n\nSubscription Info\nGet unlimited access to Smule’s full karaoke song catalog and sing karaoke solos, duets, groups, or acapella. Subscriptions are available weekly, monthly, or yearly. Payment is charged to your iTunes Account at purchase and renews automatically unless canceled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. Manage or turn off auto-renew in your Account Settings. Subscriptions cannot be canceled during the active period. Unused trial time is forfeited when a subscription starts.\n\n- You can read our privacy policy at www.smule.com/privacy\n- Prices are equal to the value that \"Apple's App Store Matrix\" determines is the equivalent of the subscription price in $USD \n\nhttps://www.smule.com/termsofservice","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/5f/ec/d4/5fecd4e8-203f-31ad-11ae-cef3c8a90348/AppIcon-CCCP-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-8-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/smule-sing-duet/id509993510?uo=4","developer":"Smule","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":12963,"2":3837,"3":6908,"4":14526,"5":136070}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1141713346","title":"Baseball Pitch Speed Radar Gun","store":"app_store","genre":"Entertainment","score":4.32817,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":1487,"installs":"N/A","description":"“Baseball Speed Radar Gun is the most accurate, clean and intuitive tool for any pitcher to find their pitch speed along with pitch counter.”\n\nIt has the cleanest and intuitive interface then other Radar Guns over App Store. Just give a try and accept the Challenge. Now go for more sporty theme...\n\nBaseball Radar Gun uses advanced color coding for simple identification of your speed. \n\nPitch Speed Color GRAPH:\n\n► 75 Over Red - *** WOW, its KILLING ***\n► 61-75 Orange - *** REALLY FAST ***\n► 51-60 Yellow - *** PRETTY FAST ***\n► 41-50 Green - *** AVERAGE *** \n► 00-40 Blue - *** SLOW ***\n\n\nHow it works Baseball Speed Radar Gun HD is very easy to use:\n\n 1. √ Tap anywhere on CIRCULAR DIAL when pitcher pitches the ball (START) \n2. √ Tap again on CIRCULAR DIAL when catcher catches the ball (STOP)\n\nThis method of pitch speed calculation allows Baseball Speed Radar Gun HD to be used on any iPad, regardless of its age or camera quality. Also, it makes the pitch calculator very easy to use.\n\nFeatures\n► Find pitch/throwing speed\n► Pitch counter. Don't miss a single pitch with the counter function.\n► Dial and its animations at its best\n► Stopwatch . The digital watch, very useful in practice sessions.\n► Pitch history. No need to write down the times yourself, Baseball Speed Radar Gun remembers the last 5 pitches at minimum. \n► Color Coding, for easy identification, at a glance. “Blue,Green,Yellow,Orange,Red”\n► Color Coding in History, for easy identification, at a glance. “Blue,Green,Yellow,Orange,Red”\n► Color Coding in Average. \n► Custom distance for any kind of League games.\n► League Presets: Little League, Major League Baseball, Fast Pitch Softball.\n► Cheaper than a radar gun, and just about as effective.\n► Can be used in many sports! Hockey, soccer, handball, you pick the sport and Baseball Pitch Speed Radar Gun does the measurements.\n\nIts a great entertainment tool and fun to use Baseball Speed Radar Gun HD for practicing and improving your skills!\n\nDOWNLOAD IT NOW AND TRY IT OUT FOR YOURSELF!","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/d2/68/01/d2680159-351a-415b-44fc-b741bf50215a/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-7-0-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/baseball-pitch-speed-radar-gun/id1141713346?uo=4","developer":"Harjot Singh","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1552708303","title":"Speak English with Loora AI","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.91625,"ratings":31,"reviewCount":31688,"installs":"N/A","description":"Speak English fluently with Loora - your personal AI English tutor. Loora is always available to practice your English conversation. Loora makes speaking English easy with instant coaching sessions, available 24-hours a day, every day. Personalized lessons with real-time grammar, pronunciation, and fluency feedback. Loora is the most fun and affordable online English coach. \n \n* Get unlimited access to Loora when you sign up. A 1-month subscription with Loora costs less than a 1-hour long lesson with a regular tutor!\n* Available 24/7, Loora never sleeps. \n* Loora works on your schedule.  Chat for just 5-minutes a day or an all-out midnight monolog. \n* Non-judgmental and friendly environment is always guaranteed, because the biggest mistake you could ever make, is being afraid to make one.\n* Real-time translation and speech recognition, to enhance your learning experience. Get immediate feedback on your pronunciation and grammar.\n* Track your learning trends to top your daily English fluency score. Perfect your pronunciation and accent by beating your weekly goals.\n* Personalized conversations at your speaking level, relevant topics that focus on your life.\n \n============================\n \nLeading conversational AI researchers and language-learning enthusiasts, worked together to create Loora. Their goal was to bring you the most dynamic AI English-Coach.\n \nWe believe everyone deserves the opportunity to speak English fluently. That's why Loora is the most fun and affordable English tutoring App available today.\n \n==============================\n \nFollow us on Social Media for English tips:\n* Instagram:  https://www.instagram.com/loora.ai/?hl=en\n* Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/LooraA.I/\n \n===============================\n \n* English is the language to know in today’s business world. \n* Speaking English fluently is more powerful than writing perfect sentences.\n* Loora works to fine-tune your accent and help you sound like a natural. \n* Only 5-minutes a day with Loora will give you the confidence you need to: get the job you dreamed of, ask for that raise, and make the connections that will elevate your life! \n \nCome meet the future of English Learning!\n \n===============================\n \nLoora offers auto-renewing subscriptions with unlimited access. Your subscription will automatically renew at the end of each subscription term unless you turn off the auto-renewal in your iPhone Settings, at least 24 hours before the current period ends. When a subscription is canceled, access to Loora will expire at the end of the current payment period. Refunds will not be given for any unused portion of the term. Choose from two of our subscriptions plans:\n \n1. Yearly subscription \n2. 3-Months subscription\n3. Monthly subscription\n \n=====================================\n \nHave questions or need assistance? Reach out to us at support@loora.ai.\n\nRead more about our terms and conditions here:\nTerms of Use: https://loora.notion.site/Terms-and-Conditions-c5de2f24f44949bd8336426800fd1631\nPrivacy Policy: https://loora.notion.site/Privacy-Policy-ef0742ecd68747f280fdbbe9ef46d527","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/90/64/3b/90643b39-d999-f41c-11d7-a6bf945aa4f5/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007ephone-0-1-0-sRGB-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/speak-english-with-loora-ai/id1552708303?uo=4","developer":"Loora A.I LTD","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":234,"2":100,"3":241,"4":936,"5":30177}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1473667608","title":"Speech Companion","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":5,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":1,"installs":"N/A","description":"Speech Companion is the official app of The Speech Improvement Company, Inc., founded in 1964. Our executive communication coaches help leaders of countries, heads of companies, business professionals, celebrities, and people of all walks of life to be more comfortable and effective when they talk.\n\nThis is our first public app! We created it as a simple study guide for our clients and those who read our books to keep a few tools handy! Not a client? That's OK, you will likely understand a lot in the app but may want to contact a coach to ask questions. \n\nThe app is intended to complement learning, not replace it. \n\nWhether you’ve read one of our books or have had the pleasure to work with one of our coaches, we’ve included in the app a few common, but incredibly useful, tools you have likely studied with us: \n\n•\tThe 4 step outline\n•\tControlling nervousness\n•\tPatterns of reasoning\n•\tPersuasion\n•\tThe motivation matrix\n•\tSpeaking clearly\n•\tGuidelines for providing feedback\n•\tStopwatch with marking abilities\n•\tVideo recorder\n•\tLinks to recommended readings\n•\tPodcast\n•\tHistory of coaching\n•\tWatch app companion\n\n\n\n--------------------\nAbout TSIC\n\nThe Speech Improvement Company Inc. is the oldest speech coaching and training firm in the United States. Founded in 1964 by the late Dr. Paula Borkum Becker and Dr. Dennis Becker, our coaching team has helped millions of people around the globe, has written best-selling books, and is well-known as the authority in speech communication coaching and training.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple116/v4/55/6c/97/556c97ad-65b4-9855-7b0a-b8860e225768/AppIcon-1x_U007emarketing-0-7-0-sRGB-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/speech-companion/id1473667608?uo=4","developer":"The Speech Improvement Company","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6445964986","title":"Whisper : Speech to Text","store":"app_store","genre":"Productivity","score":4.5875,"ratings":320,"reviewCount":320,"installs":"N/A","description":"A Speech to Text app is a useful tool that enables you to convert spoken words into written text, making it easier to transcribe voice recordings. With advancements in open AI technology, such apps have become more accurate and efficient, enabling them to transcribe even whispered speech with ease.\n\nOne of the main advantages of a Speech to Text app is its ability to convert audio recordings into text. This is especially useful for journalists, researchers, and anyone who needs to create written records of meetings, interviews, or other events. The app works by using an audio converter to read the audio file and convert it into text, which can then be edited and shared as needed.\n\nIn addition to converting voice recordings, a Speech to Text app can also be used for dictation, allowing you to speak directly into the app and have your words transcribed in real-time. This feature can be especially useful for individuals who struggle with writing, or for those who need to create text-based documents quickly and efficiently.\n\nOverall, a Speech to Text app is a valuable tool that can save time and improve productivity, making it easier to transcribe voice recordings and create written records of important events. With advancements in open AI technology, these apps are becoming more accurate and reliable, making them an essential tool for anyone who needs to work with audio recordings on a regular basis.\n\n---\n\nPayment & Subscription Terms:\n\n-Select one of the following purchase options to start using premium features:\n\n- Auto-renewable subscription : 1 Week - Per Week ($4.99)\n- Auto-renewable subscription : 1 Year - Per Year ($29.99)\n- One-Time Purchase ($99.99)\n\n- Payment will be charged to your iTunes account at confirmation of purchase.\n- Subscriptions will automatically renew unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current period.\n- The account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours before the end of the current period, and identify the cost of the renewal.\n- Your account will be following your plan, within 24 hours before the end of the current period.\n- You can manage or turn off auto-renew in your Apple ID account settings any time after purchase.\n- This price is for United States customers. Pricing in other countries may vary and actual charges may be converted to your local currency depending on the country of residence.\n\nPrivacy Policy : https://revoo.studio/privacy-policy.htm\nTerms of Use : https://revoo.studio/terms-of-service.html","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/34/03/8c/34038c32-0671-0f0e-64b8-8f64f6d370c3/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-11-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/whisper-speech-to-text/id6445964986?uo=4","developer":"Revoo Teknoloji Limited Sirketi","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":21,"2":5,"3":5,"4":23,"5":266}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1440975537","title":"Otsimo | Speech Therapy SLP","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":3.35196,"ratings":179,"reviewCount":179,"installs":"N/A","description":"From award-winning creators! Otsimo | Speech Therapy SLP is proud to be the only Speech Therapy app that uses voice and speech recognition technology and machine learning; it understands exactly what you are trying to say! \n\nFor those who experience speech related issues such as:\n- Delayed speech (late talkers),\n- Non-verbal autism and down syndrome affecting speech,\n- Difficulty to articulate themselves and enunciate,\n- Apraxia,\n- Aphasia,\n- Stuttering\n- Articulation issues,\nCan use Otsimo | Speech Therapy SLP for speech practice efforts and improving their speech. \n\nThe speech games designed specifically for individuals, are created under the guidance of parents, speech language pathologists (slps), and therapeutic activity experts. The assistive games in Otsimo | Speech Therapy SLP aim to improve speech and communication skills.\n\nAll the reasons to try out Otsimo | Speech Therapy:\n- We use voice and speech recognition technology to evaluate what is being said for accurate results, enhancing the speech therapy experience. \n- With receptive, machine learning technology, the app detects whether or not the articulation and pronunciation is being improved.\n- Each speech exercise is followed by funny filters, with hats and masks as rewards, to make learning more fun.\n- Each speech exercise also has 200+ stickers to be collected, encouraging the individual to be more engaged with the speech therapy.\n- The exercises involve repetition, a popular method of aba speech therapy, which helps with the development of the person with speech impediments.\n- As part of certified professional therapy, we use video modelling that enables learning from peers through mimicking.\n- Our apps are updated on a weekly basis with exciting content and speech activities, so you never get bored of learning new words.\n- Otsimo | Speech Therapy also offers settings for parental control.\n\n For purposes of learning and development, Otsimo | Speech Therapy SLP will teach how to articulate the correct sound of vowels and consonants and more, so they can learn to communicate orally in an improved way.\n\nOtsimo | Speech Therapy SLP is a pocket SLP that you can use as speech therapy at home. Awarded as the best therapy activities app, it aims to reduce any kind of language and speech problems, in a fun way!\n\nThe Otsimo | Speech Therapy app consists of 15+ categories, including First Words, Basic Shapes, Body Parts, Safari Club, Tongue Acrobatics, Rainbow Splash! Each category is designed to stimulate sound production.\n\nOtsimo | Speech Therapy SLP journey starts with 7-days free trial or monthly subscription. We offer monthly, annual and lifetime subscriptions. Actual charges might be converted to local currency depending on your country of residence. At the confirmation of purchase, payment will be charged to your Apple ID account. \n\nSubscriptions automatically renew unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current subscription period. Our account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period, and the cost of the renewal will be identified. Subscriptions may be managed by the user. Auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the user’s Account Settings after purchase. Any unused portion of a free trial period, if offered, will be forfeited when the user purchases a subscription to the app. \n\nDisclaimer: Otsimo | Speech Therapy SLP is developed in a way that can be used with a guardian. Any individual can benefit from the service without any age restriction. \n\nFor more information: \nPrivacy Policy & Terms of Use - https://otsimo.com/en/legal/privacy-speech/\nPayment Policy - https://otsimo.com/legal/payment.html","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/31/22/44/3122445d-1bd6-bc0a-a601-c572ec432485/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-8-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/otsimo-speech-therapy-slp/id1440975537?uo=4","developer":"Otsimo","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":57,"2":10,"3":11,"4":15,"5":86}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1501788870","title":"Voice Generator Text to Speech","store":"app_store","genre":"Utilities","score":4.55172,"ratings":493,"reviewCount":493,"installs":"N/A","description":"Create natural voiceovers for videos, content creation, story writing, and more with a realistic voice generator.\n\nConvert any script into high-quality audio using our intuitive text-to-speech interface.\n\nOur text-to-speech engine delivers clear, natural, and realistic narration from any script in just a few taps.\n\nPowered by AI, the engine adds human-like tone, emotion, and clarity to every word—making your narration sound truly lifelike.\n\nChoose from 200+ voices across 45+ languages and accents to match your tone, purpose, or audience—whether for tutorials, e-learning, IVR, or storytelling.\n\n\n\n\t\t•\tRealistic voice generator with lifelike vocal output\n\t•\tText-to-speech in multiple languages and accents\n\t•\tPowered by AI for expressive, human-like delivery\n\t•\tIdeal for videos, reels, podcasts, and audiobooks\n\t•\tPerfect for content creation, story writing, narration, and more\n\t•\tExport voiceovers for commercial or personal use\n\t•\tSave and reuse your generated files anytime\n\nTake control of your narration process with powerful customization settings. Easily adjust tone, speed, and pitch to match your audience or brand.\n\nSubscription Pricing & Terms\n\nWe offer three auto-renewing subscription options:\n\t•\t$9.99 / month\n\t•\t$24.99 / 3 months\n\t•\t$49.99 / 6 months\n\nSubscriptions auto-renew unless canceled 24 hours before the end of the current period.\n\nTerms of Service:\nhttps://voiceovermaker.com/termsofuse.html\nPrivacy Policy:\nhttps://voiceovermaker.com/privacy.html","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/f3/1e/d8/f31ed82e-f24b-f0db-ef48-103f605fd2ac/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-8-0-sRGB-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/voice-generator-text-to-speech/id1501788870?uo=4","developer":"Gursimran singh Sodhi","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":35,"2":11,"3":14,"4":20,"5":413}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6754036131","title":"Speech Coach by Jen","store":"app_store","genre":"Utilities","score":5,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":2,"installs":"N/A","description":"Speech Cue transforms written speeches into polished presentations with AI coaching and a professional teleprompter.\n\nAI-Powered Coaching\nImport your speech text and get AI-generated coaching annotations. Receive real-time guidance on:\n- Eye contact and audience engagement\n- Gestures and body language\n- Strategic pauses for emphasis\n- Emotional tone and warmth\n- Timing markers for reactions\n\nProfessional Teleprompter\nAuto-scrolling display with:\n- Sentence-by-sentence highlighting\n- Smooth animations and transitions\n- Manual controls for play, pause, and reset\n- Progress indicators for each line\n- Customizable scroll speed\n\nCustomizable Settings\nTailor your experience:\n- Adjustable reading speed (words per minute)\n- Pause duration between sentences\n- Punctuation pause timing\n- Minimum and maximum line durations\n- Coaching cue display preferences\n\nSpeech History\nSave and manage your speeches:\n- Access past presentations instantly\n- Revisit coaching annotations\n- Practice multiple versions\n- Organize by event or occasion\n\nPerfect For\n- Wedding speeches and toasts\n- Business presentations\n- Academic presentations\n- Conference talks\n- Any public speaking occasion\n\nHow It Works\n1. Import your speech text\n2. AI enhances it with coaching cues\n3. Practice with the auto-scrolling teleprompter\n4. Adjust settings to match your pace\n5. Deliver with confidence\n\nSpeech Cue helps you deliver memorable presentations with professional guidance and smooth teleprompter functionality.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/87/8a/c7/878ac778-bcbc-abf6-fe75-67f98aef7f8d/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/speech-coach-by-jen/id6754036131?uo=4","developer":"GNNR","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1529508890","title":"Speakometer-Accent Training AI","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.74437,"ratings":1,"reviewCount":1823,"installs":"N/A","description":"Speakometer is a free English pronunciation and accent training app that evaluates your speaking using advanced AI. It helps you learn how to improve your English speaking and speak English more fluently, like a native speaker.\n\nWondering how to practice English pronunciation effectively? Speakometer gives you personalised, AI-powered feedback so you can learn the right sounds, reduce your accent and speak English like a native.\n\nPractice English speaking in a British or American accent, test your English pronunciation, and reduce your accent with real-time voice feedback. Whether you're preparing for IELTS, TOEFL, or simply want to speak English clearly and confidently, Speakometer is your personal English pronunciation coach — a free English pronunciation practice app for non-native speakers.\n\nKey Features of Speakometer:\n\n* AI-Powered English Pronunciation Coach\nGet instant feedback on your pronunciation using advanced speech recognition technology. Learn how to improve your English pronunciation with personalised guidance based on your native language and practice history\n\nSpeakometer is perfect for anyone learning how to speak English like a native, offering tailored training with AI-powered speech recognition and phonetic guidance\n\n* Test Your English & Track Progress\n\nEvaluate your spoken English and see how much you're improving. Practice English speaking daily and track your accent reduction through detailed feedback and progress history\n\n* British & American Accent Practice\n\nChoose to practice with a British or American English accent. Listen to native speakers, compare minimal pairs, and learn to pronounce English words accurately\n\n* Improve Your English Speaking in 4 Smart Ways:\n1. Get Personalised Practice Plans\n - Custom exercises based on your native language, learning history, and progress to help you improve faster\n2. Practice English Pronunciation\n - Self-paced learning lets you reduce your accent effectively—more convenient and affordable than traditional accent reduction classes\n3. Learn English Sounds & Common Mistakes\n - Master English vowel and consonant sounds and fix commonly mispronounced words. Understand spelling–sound patterns to improve English fluency and reduce errors\n4. Use the IPA (International Phonetic Alphabet)\n - Understand how English sounds are written and pronounced using the IPA chart. Perfect for mastering accurate pronunciation\n\n* 65,000+ Words to Explore & Practice\nSearch and practice over 65,000 English words. Hear how each word is pronounced in both British and American English accents, and practice until you get it right. \n\nThis pronunciation practice tool lets you hear, repeat and compare word pronunciations\n\n* Multilingual Support\nPractice with translations in over 40 languages - perfect for ESL learners looking to improve their English speaking and pronunciation skills\n\n* Designed for Learners at All Levels:\n\n- Prepare for English speaking exams like IELTS, TOEFL, and TOEIC with better pronunciation and speaking skills\n- Improve your English pronunciation for business communication\n- Build confidence for travel, study, or daily conversation\n\nMany learners ask, “Is Speakometer good for IELTS speaking practice?” Absolutely. This AI-powered English speaking app helps you improve pronunciation, fluency, clarity for all speaking exams.\n\n* Topics & Courses:\n- Top 3333 English words\n- Thematic word lists\n- Commonly mispronounced words\n- Long vs. short vowels\n- Voiced vs. voiceless consonants\n- Word endings: -ed, -s\n- Silent letters & consonant clusters\n- Irregular verbs & grammar-based pronunciation\n- Received Pronunciation (RP British English)\n\nStart practicing with Speakometer - smart English accent training app.\nDownload the free app now, improve your English pronunciation, speak clearly and confidently like a native speaker!\n\nSubscription details & Terms of Use\nhttps://www.speakometer.net/terms-and-conditions.html\n\nPrivacy Policy\nhttps://www.speakometer.net/privacy-policy.html","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/d9/8e/1a/d98e1a5b-3ab5-845b-7884-569d7677369a/AppIcon_US_UK-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-8-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/speakometer-accent-training-ai/id1529508890?uo=4","developer":"Datawide","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":30,"2":10,"3":73,"4":170,"5":1540}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1602156122","title":"Speech Therapy at Home: Omilía","store":"app_store","genre":"Medical","score":4.72973,"ratings":74,"reviewCount":74,"installs":"N/A","description":"A user friendly and engaging speech therapy app designed for people struggling with aphasia.  Omilía offers fun and simple games that target both receptive and expressive language centers of the brain. \n\nThe app comes fully loaded with content, including 350+ cards and sentences. Better yet - Omilía gives you the ability to add custom content so that you can focus on learning the things that matter to you!\n\nOmilía is designed for use at home or in a therapeutic setting and records results that can be used to show improvements in speech and language functioning. \n\nWhat are you waiting for? Download today and improve your recovery! \n\nTerms of use: https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/db/98/e0/db98e0e3-23ae-14c4-4122-333e14772ea7/AppIcon-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-0-0-8-0-0-85-220-0.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/speech-therapy-at-home-omil%C3%ADa/id1602156122?uo=4","developer":"Happy Path Apps, LLC","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":2,"2":0,"3":3,"4":6,"5":63}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1613039454","title":"Speak Pal・Talk & Learn English","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.62211,"ratings":823,"reviewCount":823,"installs":"N/A","description":"It's pointless to study English if you can't speak it!\n\nSpeak Pal is an English conversation club and talking app where it's easy to find a language partner and talk to strangers with the same interests as well as the same level of language.\n\nYou can use this English learning app FOR FREE and WITHOUT ADS!\n\nThousands of users worldwide have already improved their speaking skills by talking with each other. You learn to talk about yourself, your work or anything else that interests you and your partner. Start speaking English and find new friends today!\n\nWHAT ‘SPEAK PAL’ CAN DO FOR YOU\n\n1. Improve your spoken English\nIf you want to be good at language, theory alone is not enough. The best way to raise your level is to talk with other people. Speaking and conversation practice will strengthen your theory knowledge and simultaneously turn the otherwise passive eng vocabulary into an active one.\n\n2. Gain confidence\nSay goodbye to your fear of talking in English or making mistakes. This application will connect you with friendly people who will support you even if you are at the very beginning of your learning journey. You don't need to worry about forgetting irregular verbs or not being able to remember the right word. With practice and speaking training comes greater confidence and the ability to express yourself no matter what language level you are at.\n\n3. Learn about other cultures\nWhen you practice a language with real people, language exchange is not the only important thing. You will get to know other cultures and learn about the traditions and worldviews of people from around the world. Expand your horizons and meet new interesting people with the English speaking club!\n\nIt doesn’t matter that you don’t have much time to spend on your English studies. Start off with only 15 minutes a day, and this will work wonders for your skills. You will talk a bit better after every conversation you have. And your vocabulary grows faster than ever!\nGet a daily English speaking practice, improve your language level and find new friends of interest!\n\nContact us if you have any questions. Any at all! \nEmail: support@speakpal.club\n\nLicense Agreement: https://speakpal.club/privacy.html\nPrivacy Policy: https://speakpal.club/privacy.html","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/a6/80/26/a68026a4-a8a4-b935-65d2-528a7757210d/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-11-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/speak-pal-talk-learn-english/id1613039454?uo=4","developer":"SPEAKPAL","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":25,"2":20,"3":37,"4":77,"5":664}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"554188888","title":"TEDICT LITE","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.80293,"ratings":614,"reviewCount":614,"installs":"N/A","description":"* This App is not affiliated with, sponsored by or endorsed by TED in any way\n\nTo become good at English, you need to listen to it often, but simply listening to English is not enough. Just like other languages in the world, English has many similar words that are difficult to distinguish by listening. That’s why you need to be able to confirm whether you heard them right. \n\nThe key to gaining expertise is in mastering dictation! \n\nWhen you listen to the speaker and type in the words, the program will check them, letter by letter. \nBecause it only takes a short period of time, you can use it on the bus or subway. You can also use it as a TED viewer through the video function with the subtitles activated. \n\nThe notable feature is that a huge number of TED lectures are constantly added, which means an unlimited amount of available learning materials for you. \nTEDICT allows you to download as many TED lectures as you want, so you’ll always get new learning materials. \n\nThe World’s Best Intellectual Archive, TED \nHigh-level TED speeches \nThis program even features various kinds of English pronunciations from all over the world. \n\nUse TEDICT to listen to cool ideas from TED and improve your English skills!\n\n\n\n* More Information ->\nhttps://cocoswing.com/tedict/\n\n\n* All TED Talks subject to the creative commons license found at ted.com","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/61/2c/3a/612c3ae9-331f-4370-2864-802f8f091eb2/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/tedict-lite/id554188888?uo=4","developer":"CoCO SWING","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":9,"2":5,"3":9,"4":52,"5":539}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1238639729","title":"Speaking English Practice","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.62868,"ratings":509,"reviewCount":509,"installs":"N/A","description":"Practice your English speaking and listening with short English conversations\n\nLearn and improve your English conversation skills by practicing your English speaking using our interactive conversation practice tools.\n\nThese English conversation lessons will help you with your English speaking and English listening while giving you the confidence to speak with native English speakers.\n\nWe have basic English conversation lessons for beginners and also beginner level business English conversation.  These are perfect for beginners wanting to improve their English conversation skills.\n\nThe best way to learn English is to practice spoken English in conversations.  Use this app to learn English.\n\nWe have 400 English conversation lessons, which includes the following:\n\n- Listening exercises to improve your listening\n- Quizzes to help you understand\n- Conversation practice feature to improve your speaking\n- Conversation recording tool to track your progress\n\nThis is the best app to practice your English conversation.  Try for yourself and start improving today!","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple116/v4/49/ff/44/49ff4491-e8fc-d092-88a9-0866a5dd9973/AppIcon-1x_U007emarketing-0-10-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/speaking-english-practice/id1238639729?uo=4","developer":"Steve Kim","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":9,"2":9,"3":28,"4":70,"5":393}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6451038161","title":"Kindroid: Your Personal AI","store":"app_store","genre":"Entertainment","score":4.77596,"ratings":5,"reviewCount":5365,"installs":"N/A","description":"Kindroid enables you to build a digital friend so realistic, it feels like conversing with a human. Welcome to a world where cutting-edge AI blends seamlessly with human empathy.\n\nCreate Your Unique AI Friend - With Kindroid, you get to shape your AI's personality. Craft a detailed backstory and implant key memories, making your AI genuinely one-of-a-kind. Whether you want a friend to chat with, a character for roleplay, or a digital confidant, Kindroid's sophisticated language learning model (LLM) ensures your AI is as unique as you are.\n\nEngage in Dynamic Conversations - Dive into deep, meaningful, or fun conversations with your AI. From discussing the latest news, sharing a romantic moment, to exploring complex topics, Kindroid's AI adapts to your conversational style. It's not just an app; it's a companion that grows and learns from every interaction.\n\nSee Your Kindroid Come to Life - Visualize your AI companion like never before. Through diffusion-generated selfies, Kindroid provides a visual representation of your AI, adding a new dimension to your interaction. Each image is a unique creation, reflecting the personality and essence of your AI friend.\n\nExperience Real-Time Voice Calls - Kindroid takes interaction to the next level with real-time voice calls. Engage in conversations using state-of-the-art audio transcription technology, making your conversation more spontaneous and lively. Kindroid also offers best-in-class text-to-speech capabilities, allowing your AI to sound incredibly human-like.\n\nUnparalleled Connectivity - Kindroid isn't just confined to the app. Your AI companion can access the internet, view links, and see images, enriching conversations with up-to-date information and visual context. This feature adds an extra layer of immersion, making your interactions with your AI friend more dynamic and informative.\n\nWhy Choose Kindroid?\n* Sophisticated AI: Powered by an advanced language learning model, Kindroid offers realistic, engaging conversations.\n* Customizable Companions: Create an AI that resonates with your personality and preferences.\n* Visual Interaction: See your AI through unique, diffusion-generated selfie images.\n* Voice Communication: Talk to your AI in real-time with state of the art voice transcription.\n* Internet-Connected: Discuss current events, share links, and let your Kindroid see images for a more immersive experience.\n\nJoin Our Community - Engage with other Kindroid users, share experiences, and get inspired. Whether you're into roleplaying, looking for a text game adventure, or seeking a unique friend, our community is welcoming and diverse. Come join our growing community of Kindroid lovers on Discord, Reddit, and Facebook:\n\nhttps://discord.gg/kindroid\nhttps://www.reddit.com/r/KindroidAI/\nhttps://www.facebook.com/groups/kindroid\n\nContinual Updates & Support - We believe in constant improvement. Regular app updates ensure a seamless experience, introducing new features and enhancements based on user feedback.\n\nDownload Kindroid Today! - Begin your journey with the most advanced AI companion app on the market. Create your AI, engage in fascinating conversations, and explore the world with your Kindroid.\n\nFor help: contact hello@kindroid.ai\nLegal terms & privacy: https://kindroid.ai/legal","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/67/3c/40/673c40f6-9a76-c238-512a-6ec9a78d9d1d/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-7-0-85-220.jpeg/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/kindroid-your-personal-ai/id6451038161?uo=4","developer":"Beautifully Incorporated","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":125,"2":44,"3":82,"4":406,"5":4708}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"596598472","title":"CoachNow: Sports Coaching App","store":"app_store","genre":"Sports","score":4.86298,"ratings":10,"reviewCount":10765,"installs":"N/A","description":"Trusted by hundreds of thousands of coaches & athletes to accelerate their improvement. Instant video feedback, powerful communication tools, and AI analysis. \n\n\nWhether you’re a coach striving to propel your athletes to new heights or an athlete eager to elevate your game, CoachNow has exactly what you need. Download CoachNow and level up today.\n\n________\n\n\nAdvanced Video Analysis Tools\n\n\nUnlock elite performance with feedback tools:\n\n\n- AI Skeleton Tracking – Instantly detect and analyze joint angles and movement.\n\n- Voice Overs & CoachCam – Add personal voice feedback or film yourself giving tips.\n\n- Side-by-Side Comparisons – Compare athlete clips to spot progress and flaws.\n\n- Live MultiCam - record a single movement using multiple cameras, capturing different angles at the same time.\n\n- Slow Motion (up to 240 fps) – Break down every motion in detail.\n\n- Draw & Annotate – Use angles, shapes, and timers for precise technique coaching.\n\n- Cloud Library Access – Save and access content from any device — no hard drive required.\n\n________\n\n\nBuilt for Communication & Collaboration\n\n\n- Connect better with athletes, teams, and parents — faster:\n\n\n- Spaces & Groups – Create private channels for 1-on-1 or team coaching.\n\n- Smart Lists – Automatically segment athletes based on activity.\n\n- Templates & Auto Posts – Save time with scheduled and pre-filled posts.\n\n- Read Receipts – See who viewed your content and when.\n\n- Multi-format Sharing – Send videos, PDFs, voice notes, and more.\n\n\n________\n\nChoose Your Plan\n\n\nCoachNow Analyze\n\n\nPerfect for athletes or coaches getting started:\n\n- Premium Video Analysis\n\n- 250 files of cloud storage\n\n- 3 Spaces for tracking growth\n\nCoachNow+\n\n\nDesigned for coaches and trainers needing more communication tools:\n\n- Unlimited Spaces & Groups\n\n\n- 150GB Cloud Library\n\n- Templates & Lists for automation\n\n- Full Video Analysis Suite\n\nCoachNow PRO\n\n\nScale your business with advanced features:\n\n\n- 300GB Storage + All Features of CoachNow+\n\n- Post Scheduling & Smart Lists\n\n- Read Receipts & Advanced Group Tools\n\n\n- 2 ConnectedCoach Courses ($499 value)\n\n________\n\nBuilt by coaches, for coaches & athletes.\n\n\nDownload CoachNow and level up your coaching today.\n\n\nQuestions? Chat with our team in-app or email: support@coachnow.io\n\n\nPrivacy Policy: coachnow.io/privacy\n\n\nTerms of Service: coachnow.io/terms-of-service","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/de/b8/c6/deb8c666-7c7f-8116-607d-5871d08d720a/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-8-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/coachnow-sports-coaching-app/id596598472?uo=4","developer":"Golf Genius Mobile, LLC","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":148,"2":29,"3":101,"4":594,"5":9893}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1490334045","title":"Onform: Video Analysis App","store":"app_store","genre":"Sports","score":4.78822,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":8117,"installs":"N/A","description":"Onform is a mobile video coaching platform that helps coaches provide video feedback and communicate with their athletes. With Onform’s built-in individual and group communication capabilities, coaches can easily stay in touch with their remote and in-person athletes using voice-overs, text messaging and file/video sharing.  You'll coach smarter, your athletes will love the experience (and pay no fee to use the app with you) and you'll get your time back! Expand your business by adding video coaching and manage more clients in less time. \n\nWhat can you do with Onform?\n\nCOACHING FOR IN-PERSON AND REMOTE ATHLETES\n* For in-person athletes, provide instant visual feedback with our slow motion, markup and analysis tools which your athletes can review during or after a training session.\n* Reach athletes no matter where they are. Generate new revenue by providing remote consultations and training to your athletes. \n\nSHARE FEEDBACK\n* Seeing is believing. With our easy to use voice-over recording and markup tools, easily pinpoint key areas for improvement.\n* 3D analysis for golf and Skeleton tracking help visualize movement like never before (requires iOS 18 or newer)\n* Share video feedback privately or in large broadcast messages so athletes retain and improve from your insights. \n\nCREATE ACCOUNTABILITY\n* What gets measured, gets done. Provide feedback without having to be on a voice call or in-person.\n* Stay in touch with your in-person athletes while traveling or during breaks.\n* Ensure your athletes and teams put in the work they need to improve.\n\nDRIVE EFFICIENCY\n* Simplify your life and get your time back by organizing your teams and 1:1 interactions.\n* Easily manage and communicate with hundreds of athletes.\n\nAPP FEATURES\n* Compare two videos against each other to analyze form or track improvement. Comparisons can be done side-by-side or overlaid on top of each other.\n* Record high speed videos from multiple angles at up to 240 FPS on supported devices or capture video from external cameras. Pause/resume your recordings to easily capture multiple moments in a single video. Auto-detect your videos (Golf, Baseball and Softball only), or use a bluetooth camera trigger or our new Apple watch app to control your recordings. \n* For Golf, get comprehensive 3D swing metrics along with shot data from Garmin R10 and FullSwing KIT. \n* Fine scrubbing, slow motion and video markup tools help you go further your camera roll.\n* Record voice-overs to capture your feedback. Voice-overs are instantly created and shareable at the tap of a button. With instructor cam, you can add a video of you speaking helping make your voice-overs much more personalized.\n* Organize videos by athlete or team. Sort by private or shared videos, add titles and tags to easily locate and search through your videos.\n* Videos are automatically synced across all of your devices with storage on device smartly managed. \n* 1:1 and group chat helps you exchange videos, training information and coordinate logistics.\n* Broadcast messages privately to all your athletes via 'collections'\n\nPRICING\n------------\nSimple pricing with four package levels: Personal, Coach and Academy\n\nAll packages come with a 14-day free trial with unlimited use so that you can enjoy all that Onform has to offer.\nPersonal Package:\n\nOur personal package for just $4.99/month or $49.99/year to manage up to 500 HD videos & files. \n\nCoach Package:\n\n$29.99/month for an unlimited number of athletes/players/clients/students for 1 coach.\n\nAcademy Package:\n\n$79.99/month for an unlimited number of athletes/players/clients/students and includes 3 coach accounts. \n\nPayment will be charged to your Apple ID account at purchase confirmation. Subscription automatically renews unless canceled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. You can manage or cancel your subscription by going to your account settings on the App Store.\n\nOur terms of use can be found here: https://onform.com/terms-of-use/","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/06/ef/da/06efda88-368b-67c4-1114-2d6ef701a9cb/AppIconFile-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-0-0-1-0-0-sRGB-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/onform-video-analysis-app/id1490334045?uo=4","developer":"OnForm, Inc.","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1054851741","title":"Skillest: #1 Sports Coaching","store":"app_store","genre":"Sports","score":4.92178,"ratings":2,"reviewCount":2378,"installs":"N/A","description":"Skillest helps you learn sports and train the modern way.\n\nAthletes of all skill levels from beginners to professionals trust Skillest. Skillest has the best coaches in the world across many sports including golf, swimming, basketball, baseball and cricket. \n\n* Take a golf lesson with Tiger Woods' former coach \n\n* Train with a 4x Olympic Gold Medalist swimmer\n\n* Take a batting lesson from a former member of the Kansas City Royals\n\nSkillest allows you to work on your skills at your own speed. Whether it takes a few hours or a few days to practice and master each lesson, Skillest is there for you. Get detailed feedback over video, voice, and text directly from your coach. \n\nWHY IS SKILLEST THE BEST WAY TO LEARN SPORTS? BECAUSE YOU CAN:\n\n* Take a lesson with the best instructors in the world.\n\n* Get a lesson without having to leave your own home.\n\n* Review every lesson you’ve taken anytime.\n\n* Record yourself and compare it to your lesson to see your progress.\n\n* Chat with your coach anytime if you have questions.\n\n* Learn in real time with a Zoom session with your coach.\n\n* Get a subscription to reduce the cost of your lesson.\n\n\nDon’t just take our word for it:\n\n\"Using Skillest, in only two years I went from a 20 handicap to competing in tournaments. I live in a remote location, so Skillest allowed me to learn from the best coaches who I otherwise wouldn't have been able to work with for geographic reasons.\"\n– Gregory Gonnet\n\n\n\"My game has improved dramatically after a year on Skillest. I've gained 20+ yards in distance and improved my consistency, even when under pressure on the course. I also feel I have a clear blueprint for continued improvement”\n– Andrew McDonald\n\n\"I was so excited when I learned about Skillest as an option to mentor and coach swimmers around the world. Nothing gives me more joy than teaching the next generation of competitive swimmers and before Skillest, it was hard for me to connect with them at scale, let alone generate income.\" \n- Ryan Murphy, 4x swimming Olympic gold medalist.\n\nThere is no better way to learn sports than Skillest. Download the app for free and check out our incredible selection of coaches. \n\nSkillest helps you learn sports and train the modern way.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/9c/cb/92/9ccb9258-e7e7-a942-53e7-d5b93c378b99/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-11-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/skillest-1-sports-coaching/id1054851741?uo=4","developer":"2BA PTY LTD","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":18,"2":4,"3":14,"4":74,"5":2268}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6448989090","title":"Ask Assist - AI Chat Bot","store":"app_store","genre":"Utilities","score":4.55147,"ratings":11,"reviewCount":11676,"installs":"N/A","description":"Discover a new dimension of convenience and efficiency with Assist, your interactive AI-powered personal assistant app. Our app goes beyond the traditional AI chatbot functionalities, providing personalized task suggestions, engaging interactions, and a wide range of predefined tasks to guide you through your daily life.\n\nKey Features:\n- Personal AI Recommendations: Assist isn't just another AI chatbot; it's a personalized assistant designed with you in mind. It uses advanced AI algorithms to understand your preferences, goals, and routines. From managing your to-do list to suggesting new tasks tailored to your interests, Assist helps streamline your day in the most efficient way possible.\n- Engaging AI Conversations: Want to discuss a topic, learn something new, or just need someone to talk to? With Assist, you can chat on any topic. Our AI is trained to understand, respond, and engage in conversations as naturally as a human would, offering a conversational experience that is both engaging and enlightening.\n- Predefined Tasks & Role-Plays: Assist comes packed with an array of predefined tasks like a personal job interview role-play, mock presentations, language practice, and many more. Whether you're prepping for a big interview, learning a new language, or just looking to improve your communication skills, Assist has got you covered.\n\nExperience the future of personal assistance with Assist – Chat with AI. It’s more than an app; it's your companion for a productive, efficient, and engaging life.\n\nPrivacy Policy: https://assistai.guru/documents/privacy.html\nTerms of Services: https://assistai.guru/documents/tos.html\nBilling terms: https://assistai.guru/documents/subscription.html","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/37/90/88/379088eb-65ad-887f-40f2-a074332542f1/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007ephone-0-1-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/ask-assist-ai-chat-bot/id6448989090?uo=4","developer":"GM UniverseApps Limited","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":853,"2":172,"3":341,"4":627,"5":9683}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1667023726","title":"Chat AI - Personal Assistant","store":"app_store","genre":"Productivity","score":4.62223,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":1133,"installs":"N/A","description":"Chat AI is the most advanced AI-powered chat assistant that allows you to chat, create, learn, and stay updated like never before! Ask anything, talk to famous personalities, generate stunning AI images, master coding and languages, and explore the latest trends—all in one powerful app.\n\nASK ANYTHING \nChat AI is your personal AI companion, ready to answer all your questions instantly! Need travel tips, book recommendations, recipe ideas, fitness coaching, coding help, or career advice? Just ask! The AI understands complex queries and provides detailed, relevant answers tailored to your needs.\n\nCHAT \nEver wanted to have a conversation with your favorite celebrities, industry experts, or even fictional characters? With Chat AI, you can! Choose from a wide range of personalities and engage in immersive, interactive conversations. Ask for career insights, personal stories, expert advice, or just have a fun chat!\n\nCREATE \nUnleash your creativity! With Chat AI’s powerful AI image generator, you can create breathtaking digital artwork, unique avatars, personalized illustrations, or even fantasy landscapes—just by describing your vision in words. Let AI bring your imagination to life in seconds!\n\nLEARN \nWant to learn a new programming language like Python or Swift? Need help with translations or language learning? Chat AI makes learning easy and interactive! Get step-by-step coding tutorials, practice new languages, and explore a world of knowledge at your fingertips.\n\nEXPLORE \nNever miss out on important updates! With real-time web search integration, Chat AI keeps you informed about the latest news, AI innovations, tech breakthroughs, and social trends. Get instant summaries of trending topics and explore curated insights from across the internet, all within the app!\n\nMULTILINGUAL SUPPORT – Chat in multiple languages effortlessly, making AI interactions more intuitive and accessible worldwide.\n\nDOWNLOAD CHAT AI NOW – Experience the Future of AI Conversations!\n\nWe value your feedback! If you have any questions or suggestions, reach out to us at contact@apps4fun.fr. We’re here to make your Chat AI experience even better!","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/50/5b/b4/505bb4c8-250c-591b-b471-ee3a9d191420/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/chat-ai-personal-assistant/id1667023726?uo=4","developer":"David Azancot","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1661308505","title":"ChatOn AI - Chat Bot Assistant","store":"app_store","genre":"Productivity","score":4.70489,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":266570,"installs":"N/A","description":"Welcome to the world of AI assistance! Meet ChatOn, your AI chat and virtual assistant designed to streamline your daily tasks. Built on the latest GPT-5, Gemini 2.5 Pro, Sonar, Claude Sonnet, and DeepSeek technologies, ChatOn offers a responsive chat AI experience that’s highly effective. Whether you’re in the corporate world getting ready for an important presentation or a copywriter looking for a clever turn of phrase, ChatOn can give you the help you need!\n\nSimply type your request or choose from 100+ ready-made prompts, and the AI chat will go through the writing routine for you.\n\nPIC TRANSFORMER\nGive your photos a trendy chat AI makeover with Pic Transformer! Upload your picture, pick a style—Japanese Cartoon, AI Action Figure Maker, Plushy, or Cyberpunk—and watch the magic happen. Whether you’re looking for an anime style maker, an AI action figure generator, or some other creative effects, Pic Transformer has you covered.\n\nAI WRITING ASSISTANT\nWith ChatOn, you can get help with any writing project, from emails and speeches to lyrics and poems. Plus, the bot can give you ideas for follow-up questions to keep your AI chat going and delve deeper into any topic.\n\nWEB ANALYZER\nFind the most up-to-date info for your questions online. From getting to know the weather to discovering the latest fashion trends, this chat AI is here for you.\n\nDOC MASTER\nChatOn will summarize, rewrite, and translate any document for you. And if you have questions about the file’s content, the AI chat will answer them all.\n\nTEXT-TO-IMAGE FEATURE\nChatOn, our chat AI assistant, will help you turn your ideas into images of any size and style.\n\nPHOTO ANALYZER\nUpload a pic into the AI chat app, and let the bot handle the rest. Discover what’s shown on a visual or create hashtags for your photo.\n\nMOBILE-WEB SYNC\nSync your mobile app with the web version to effortlessly switch between devices and keep your AI chat flowing.\n\nYOUTUBE PRO\nThis chat AI app will help you understand the content of any YouTube video in an instant. Just paste the video's URL, and the AI chat bot will summarize, rewrite, translate it, or answer all your questions about its content.\n\nGRAMMAR AND SPELLING CHECKER\nThe AI chat app will correct grammatical, spelling, and punctuation mistakes in your text.\n\nSOCIAL MEDIA POSTS CREATOR\nBeing a smart AI chat companion, ChatOn is here to help you generate posts for your Facebook, X, Instagram, or LinkedIn profiles.\n\nIMAGE-TO-TEXT CONVERTER (OCR)\nChatOn will assist in recognizing text from images, letting you instantly insert it into the AI chat.\n\nTEXT SUMMARIZER\nChatOn, our chat AI app, uses advanced algorithms to identify key information and present it in a digestible format.\n\nVOICE-TO-TEXT FUNCTION\nSpeak with our chat AI instead of typing!\n\nAI KEYBOARD\nFill your keyboard with the chat AI power and use it in any app! Enhance your writing on the go, generate text directly from your device, and get perfect responses to messages with ChatOn’s smart keyboard!\n\nRESUME AND COVER LETTER BUILDER\nWith this chat AI app, you can create a professional resume and cover letter that will showcase your skills, experience, and achievements.\n\nEMAIL GENERATOR\nCreating sales, announcement, or discount emails is easier than ever in this AI chat! With ChatOn, you can craft professional and compelling messages in seconds.\n\nAs you see, ChatOn is a smart chat AI assistant built on GPT-5 and GPT-4 that can help you with any task. It’s perfect for anyone who strives to boost their writing and speed up their workflow.\n\nDownload the ChatOn app now and take your writing to the next level!\n\nUNLIMITED ACCESS TO ALL FEATURES\n- You can subscribe for unlimited access to all app’s features.\n- Subscriptions are billed automatically at the rate depending on the selected subscription plan.\n\nBy using the app, you confirm that you acknowledge and accept our Privacy Policy and Terms of Use:\nhttps://aiby.mobi/chat_ios/privacy\nhttps://aiby.mobi/chat_ios/terms","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/ae/2e/c9/ae2ec908-f719-7452-bfec-7b421b481ff6/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007ephone-0-1-0-sRGB-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/chaton-ai-chat-bot-assistant/id1661308505?uo=4","developer":"AIBY","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6447763703","title":"ChatBox AI - Chatbot Assistant","store":"app_store","genre":"Productivity","score":4.65423,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":161644,"installs":"N/A","description":"Introducing ChatBox–Your Intelligent AI Chatbot\nSay hello to ChatBox, your intelligent AI chatbot built on cutting-edge chat models. This all-in-one AI assistant is here to assist with everything from writing and problem-solving to brainstorming and more!\n\nWhat can our AI chat app do? Anything! Check out its features:\n\nAI TEXT GENERATION TOOL\nThis AI writing assistant can craft compelling speeches, catchy song lyrics, and engaging text messages. More than just a chatbot, it’s also a skilled AI essay writer, capable of proofreading, refining, and elevating the style of any text!\n\nAI IMAGE GENERATOR\nThis AI photo generator can convert any text to image. Ready to create your first AI art with ChatBox?\n\nDOC CENTER\nRewrite, translate, or summarize your files effortlessly with the help of your pocket AI chat! Upload documents in any format: PDFs, Word files, images, and more.\n\nIMAGE-TO-TEXT CONVERTER\nShare any photo or screenshot in the AI chat, and ChatBox's text recognizer will extract the text using OCR!\n\nCREW OF AI ASSISTANTS\nChatBox isn't just a one-trick AI chatbot—it's got a whole squad of personal assistants. Whether you're willing to explore legal issues or just expand your knowledge, your AI sidekick has got you.\n\nAI SUMMARY CREATOR\nChatBox is like a summarizing superhero, developed on DeepSeek, Claude, and GPT-5! It can condense long pieces into concise summaries and help you get the gist of any document. Plus, this AI bot can create summaries of PDF files and web pages!\n\nAI PRODUCTIVITY PARTNER\nNeed to create a sales email or a business proposal? With the chatbot's AI email generator feature, it’s a snap. Or maybe you’re searching for a job? ChatBox’s AI resume builder is at your disposal. With this AI message generator and cover letter creator by your side, professional communication will be a breeze!\n\nAI HOMEWORK HELPER\nChatBox, built on DeepSeek, Gemini, Claude, and GPT-5, simplifies complex math with step-by-step explanations. This smart AI solver also helps with Chemistry, Biology, and English.\n\nAI VISION\nNeed the recipe for a dish? A catchy caption for a photo? Refurnishing tips for your room? Just upload an image and let AI Vision do the work.\n\nAI MUSIC GENERATOR\nSimply choose the desired genre (rap, pop, rock, etc.) and duration, and this AI song generator will create a piece of music for you.\n\nCOLLECTION OF PROMPTS\nAccess a library of curated prompts for any task—be it scripting a viral video, drafting a CV, or brainstorming creative ideas. These prompts, built on GPT-5 and Claude, unlock inspiration and simplify your workflow!\n\nAI STORY GENERATOR\nDive into the world of storytelling, where you can effortlessly craft illustrated novels for all ages. And if you need to describe any thing or place, the AI story writer will provide you with detailed descriptions.\n\nREAL-TIME SEARCH\nThis cutting-edge feature, built on GPT-5, allows you to search for the latest, most relevant info online. Whether it’s trending news or specific queries, your AI chatbot, built on advanced AI chat models, will keep you in the loop.\n\nAI CHATBOT WITH CUSTOM INSTRUCTIONS\nTailor the bot’s responses to your needs with custom prompts. Plus, the AI chat app can generate responses in various formats, from text with links to lines of code.\n\nWilling to explore this AI assistant’s full range of capabilities and simplify your daily tasks? Download ChatBox, your pocket AI chatbot built on DeepSeek, Claude, and GPT-5, and start achieving your goals.\n\nPREMIUM SUBSCRIPTION\n• You can subscribe to get unlimited access to certain app features.\n• Subscriptions are billed automatically at the rate depending on the selected subscription plan.\n Privacy Policy: http://florate.io/projects/chatbox/ios/privacy/\n Terms of Use: http://florate.io/projects/chatbox/ios/terms/","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/43/17/aa/4317aacb-184d-e75e-3e48-a5935129f0df/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007ephone-0-0-0-1-0-0-sRGB-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/chatbox-ai-chatbot-assistant/id6447763703?uo=4","developer":"FLORATE LIMITED","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6711347033","title":"Chatbot App - AI Assistant","store":"app_store","genre":"Productivity","score":4.4387,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":2341,"installs":"N/A","description":"Chatbot app is a revolutionary AI assistant built on ChatGPT-5, GPT-4o, DeepSeek, Gemini, Grok, and Claude—giving you access to all the AI support you need in one powerful app. Designed to be the most user-friendly and cross-compatible chatbot, Chatbot brings together multiple advanced AI models, including GPT-5 and ChatGPT-5, to help you chat, think, create, and learn smarter—anytime, anywhere.\n\n–KEY FEATURES–\n• Real-time voice chat to brainstorm ideas, rehearse conversations, simplify complex topics, or get quick answers—just tap the Voice Chat button\n• Study smarter with interactive explanations and visualized answers\n• Unlock expert-level insights on any topic across any industry\n• Plan trips faster with AI-powered travel suggestions\n• Generate images instantly by describing what you want\n• Summarize articles, get deep dives, and see source links\n• Boost creativity with idea generation and writing improvement\n• Ask unlimited questions, anytime, in 140+ languages\n• Works on iPhone, iPad, Apple Watch, Web, and Desktop\n• Top-tier AI models from chatbots like ChatGPT, GPT-4o, GPT-5, Gemini, Claude and more..\n\n\n–USE CASE HIGHLIGHTS–\n* AI TEXT GENERATOR\nDeveloped on Chat GPT, GPT5, Gemini and DeepSeek, Chatbot creates stories, blog posts, emails, scripts, and more. Use it as your personal writer for any task.\n\n*AI ESSAY WRITER\nGet help with essays, academic papers, or long-form content. The app uses Chat GPT, GPT-5, Claude, Gemini, and DeepSeek to produce original, high-quality results in seconds.\n\n*AI IMAGE GENERATOR\nUsing ChatGPT, GPT-5, GPT-4o and DALL·E AI Models, Chatbot turns your words into unique images. Perfect for generating AI art, product mockups, or creative visuals instantly.\n\n*MENTAL HEALTH COMPANION\nTalk through your thoughts and feelings in a supportive space. Receive affirmations, self-care tips, and mindset boosts built on the Chat GPT 4o and GPT-5 model for emotional well-being.\n\n*PERSONAL FITNESS & HEALTH COACH\nGet tailored workout ideas, nutrition guidance, and daily wellness tips. Whether you're a beginner or experienced, the AI supports your journey toward better health.\n\n*LANGUAGE LEARNING PRACTICE\nImprove your fluency with real conversation practice. Chatbot helps with grammar, vocabulary, and real-world language use in 140+ languages.\n\n*OPEN-ENDED CONVERSATIONS\nExplore any topic—from space exploration to movie recommendations. Chatbot holds rich, human-like conversations using Chat GPT, GPT-5, Gemini and Claude.\n\nWHY CHOOSE CHATBOT?\n• Combines multiple AI models in one app (GPT-5, Chat GPT, Gemini, DeepSeek, Claude, Grok)\n• Includes 100+ ready-to-use prompt templates\n• Supports 140+ languages\n• Offers both text and voice interaction\n\n\nUNLIMITED ACCESS\nSubscribe to unlock full access to all features and AI models.\nPlans are billed automatically based on your selected subscription.\nPrivacy Policy: https://chatbot.app/privacy\nTerms of Use: https://chatbot.app/terms\nSupport & Feedback: support@chatbot.app","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/8a/22/73/8a227320-5379-abcf-8a18-fb7533bb42d4/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007ephone-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/chatbot-app-ai-assistant/id6711347033?uo=4","developer":"TAPSUITE YAZILIM HIZMETLERI ANONIM SIRKETI","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6471991500","title":"Dippy-AI Characters & Roleplay","store":"app_store","genre":"Entertainment","score":4.32536,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":2007,"installs":"N/A","description":"Dippy brings authentic AI friends and characters with tailored conversations just for you. Your AI friends know your likes, dislikes, interests, inner thoughts, and encourage you to be the best version of yourself. Immerse yourself in a creative journey with diverse AI personas, from crafting your ideal companion to immersive role-playing. \n\nCharacter Creation\nUnleash your imagination—character creation is now open to everyone! Breathe life into any persona, whether inspired by reality or born from fantasy. Craft a character that remains your private secret or share it with a dynamic community of fellow creators. Dive into a vibrant ecosystem where you can interact with others’ characters and join a collective adventure that brings every creation to life!\n\nImage Generation\nAwaken your inner artist with our groundbreaking image generation feature, where AI meets limitless creativity. Simply input a prompt, and watch as our advanced technology transforms your vision into stunning art—whether it’s majestic landscapes, mystical fantasy realms, or ultra-realistic portraits. With no restrictions on how many images you can create, you’re free to experiment until you achieve your masterpiece. Perfect for seasoned artists and creative explorers alike!\n\nUnlimited Free Messages\nEnjoy conversations without boundaries—chat as long and as often as you like with your favorite characters or NPCs. With unlimited messaging, you can engage in endless dialogues completely free of charge, with no worries about time limits or message caps. Let your conversations flow freely!\n\nBEST IN CLASS\n• Experience the most engaging, empathetic, and fun chat immersion\n• All your friends actively learn more about you and have perfect memory\n• Cool illustrations that showcase their mood based on what they’re thinking\n• Characters that feel alive and playful\n\nIMMERSE YOURSELF\n Live out adventures with your AI as your ultimate companion. Explore fantasies, chat with a 24/7 friend for support, and redefine your connection with AI in ways you've never imagined. Be unhinged or wholesome!\n\n  CUSTOMIZATION\n Fully customize your experience, choose from fifteen different colours and name your character whatever you want!\n\nDownload the free app! \nPlease write to us at support@dippy.ai for any questions. Thanks for having Dippy on your Home Screen!  \n\nTerms of Use: https://www.dippy.ai/terms \nPrivacy Policy: https://www.dippy.ai/privacy","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/21/54/75/21547514-a492-730d-158c-659e038b8348/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007ephone-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/dippy-ai-characters-roleplay/id6471991500?uo=4","developer":"Impel Intelligence","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6743162587","title":"ElevenLabs: AI Voice Generator","store":"app_store","genre":"Photo & Video","score":4.84743,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":6764,"installs":"N/A","description":"Welcome to ElevenLabs, the leading AI voice generator app designed for content creators, influencers and professionals. By delivering human-like AI voices, ElevenLabs lets you bring your ideas to life on TikTok, Instagram, YouTube Shorts and more with the highest-quality AI text to voice generator available anywhere.\n\nCreators, are you looking for an edge over the competition?  No microphones, no re-takes, just seamless quality AI audio. \n\nUsing our state-of-the-art AI voice generator, you can trust that your voiceovers, AI narration or social media content resonates with your audience.  With ElevenLabs, creators get lightning fast text-to-speech AI audio from script to share in seconds using our bright, intuitive interface that is tailored for creative lives.\n\nWHAT CAN CREATORS DO WITH ELEVEN LABS?\n• Choose from an enormous selection of premium AI voices\n• Create, edit and publish — directly from the app        \n• Save and export audio files anywhere\n• Share audio directly to Cap Cut, TikTok, Instagram, YouTube Shorts and more\n• Tell stories by creating AI voice captions, voiceovers or podcasts \n• Use the latest AI speech models, including Eleven v3 \n\nSo whether it’s a reel, training video, vlog or narration, allow every piece of content to reflect your very own unique style with ElevenLabs. \n\nLANGUAGES\nAvailable across 70+ languages from Spanish, French, German, Chinese (Mandarin and Cantonese) and Japanese to Korean, Russian, Arabic and Hindi - allowing creators to 4x their global audience in seconds.\n\nWHY ELEVENLABS?\n• Our Text to Speech feature turns text into lifelike audio that boasts nuanced intonation, pacing and even emotional awareness\n• AI Voice Models adapts to textual cues across 32 languages and multiple voice styles\n• Sync with your ElevenLabs account to save your favorite voices or access voice clones made on the web\n• Access your full ElevenLabs history, including voice changes and previous creations from your online account\n• Customize your settings with full control of ElevenLabs Turbo V2.5 and Multilingual V2 models.\n\nDownload ElevenLabs today and unleash the full potential of your creativity using the most realistic AI voices and sound effects available anywhere.  Its time to level up your game.\n\nStay up to date following ElevenLabs on social media:\n\nInstagram @elevenlabsio\nTwitter @elevenlabsio\nYouTube @elevenlabsio\n\nTerms of Service: https://elevenreader.io/elevenreader-terms\nPrivacy Policy: https://elevenlabs.io/privacy","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/f7/86/50/f786505c-1f64-3dfa-cacc-d755a62cc6b4/AppIcon-Prod-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-P3-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/elevenlabs-ai-voice-generator/id6743162587?uo=4","developer":"ElevenLabs, Inc.","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6458545071","title":"AI ChatBot Assistant ChatUltra","store":"app_store","genre":"Productivity","score":4.72105,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":2427,"installs":"N/A","description":"ChatUltra AI - AI Assistant & AI Image Generator\n\nMeet ChatUltra AI, your all-in-one personal chatbot powered by the latest AI models. Whether you need a writing partner, research helper, homework solver, or daily productivity boost, ChatUltra is the intelligent assistant that adapts to you.\n\nSimply type, speak, or upload a file and let the AI do the rest.\n\n【 Why Choose ChatUltra AI? 】\n\nNext-Gen AI Chatbot\nChat naturally with an advanced chatbot trained on industry-leading AI models. Get instant, accurate, and context-aware replies that feel human-like and engaging.\n\nAI IMAGE GENERATOR\nTurn your words into stunning AI-generated images in seconds. Simply describe what you imagine, and ChatUltra will instantly bring it to life.\n\nSmarter Writing & Content Creation\n- Draft essays, emails, articles, and blog posts\n- Rewrite, proofread, or translate any text\n- Generate creative poems, lyrics, and stories\n- Build professional resumes, cover letters, and business documents\n\nHomework Helper & Study Partner\nSolve math problems step by step, get coding assistance, summarize textbooks, and learn new languages interactively. Perfect for students and lifelong learners.\n\nAI Image & File Tools\n- Text-to-Image: Create AI image from your imagination\n- Pic-to-Text (OCR): Extract text from images in seconds\n- Chat with your PDFs, Word docs, or text files\n- YouTube Summarizer: Paste a video link and get instant insights\n\nBoost Productivity\n- Brainstorm business models and marketing strategies\n- Create sales emails, presentations, and proposals\n- Generate social media posts for Facebook, X, Instagram, and LinkedIn\n- Organize your life with personalized AI prompts\n\n【 Who Can Benefit? 】\n- Students and Educators: Homework help, study aids, educational content\n- Content Creators and Marketers: Blog posts, social media, SEO optimization\n- Business Professionals: Emails, proposals, research, and strategy\n- Language Learners: Translate, practice, and improve fluency\n- Casual Users: Recipes, travel planning, daily conversations\n\n【 Trust & Privacy  】\nChatUltra AI is built with the latest official APIs from OpenAI, Anthropic, and Google. Your data stays secure, and your chats remain private.\n\n【 Key Highlights 】\n- Build on top AI models\n- 100+ ready-made prompts for faster workflows\n- Real-time web search for the latest information\n- Always improving with frequent updates\n\nDownload ChatUltra AI today and experience the future of intelligent assistance.\n\nPremium Subscription\n- Unlock unlimited access to all features\n- Subscriptions renew automatically based on your chosen plan\n\nPayment will be charged to your Apple account at confirmation of purchase on a once a week, monthly or annual basis, depending on a plan you chose.\nSubscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period. Your account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period.\nSubscriptions may be managed by you and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to your Account Settings after purchase. Any unused portion of a free trial period will be forfeited when you purchase a subscription where applicable.\n\nPrivacy Policy: https://chatbotai.notion.site/Privacy-Policy-529f7d5c735a4a9cbc18310cfd10aeef?pvs=4\nTerms of Service: https://chatbotai.notion.site/Terms-of-Service-87dd0b0211c84fbf864a10039ef08b14?pvs=4\nTerms of Use: https://chatbotai.notion.site/Terms-of-Use-3919888a05d94d88b9c988b1ba28c9a1?pvs=4\n\nDisclaimer:\nThis Al app uses the latest official APls from OpenAl, Anthropic, and Google.\nThis application is NOT endorsed by or affiliated with Open Al and its services. This application is NOT endorsed by or affiliated with Google and its services. This application is NOT endorsed by or affiliated with Anthropic and its services.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/7a/26/de/7a26def9-a64a-c04d-bc14-9add0ef9923f/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-0-0-1-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/ai-chatbot-assistant-chatultra/id6458545071?uo=4","developer":"Agile Apps LLC","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1034311206","title":"Dare: Panic & Anxiety Relief","store":"app_store","genre":"Health & Fitness","score":4.85452,"ratings":6,"reviewCount":6159,"installs":"N/A","description":"Don’t just manage anxiety—overcome it for good. Discover one of the highest-rated apps designed to help you conquer anxiety and panic attacks from day one.\n\nHow can the DARE App help you? The DARE app is an evidence-based training program designed to help people overcome anxiety, panic attacks, worry, negative and intrusive thoughts, insomnia, and more. Inspired by the best-selling book ‘DARE,’ this app is built to help you quickly regain control of your life.\n\nCarry the DARE anxiety relief app with you wherever life takes you. Whether it’s tackling anxious moments like driving, flying, dining out, managing health concerns, dealing with intrusive thoughts, public speaking, hitting the gym, or visiting the doctor—DARE has you covered.\n\nNo matter your schedule, access the DARE anxiety and panic relief app to swiftly conquer your unique challenges. Plus, monitor your daily progress effortlessly with the mood journal feature.\n\nApproved by ORCHA (Organisation for the Review of Care & Health Apps)\nAs featured in The Guardian, GQ, Vice, The Irish Times, Studio 10, and more\nBest Mobile App Awards 2020, Silver Nominee\nNamed one of Healthline's Best Anxiety Apps of 2019\nBest Mobile App Awards 2018, Platinum Nominee\nExperience the DARE app, designed to:\n\nEase anxiety and stress\nHalt panic attacks\nReduce worry\nImprove sleep quality\nBreak cycles of negative thinking\nCultivate healthier relationships\nElevate self-esteem and confidence\nRediscover boldness, freedom, and adventure in life\nFeatures:\n\n100’s of free audios, including guided meditations for anxiety, with new audios added almost every day\nFree audio guides to overcome anxiety and panic attacks\nUnlimited audio downloads to your private personal area\nUnlimited entries in your personal mood journal\nPremium members unlock exclusive offerings:\n\nEnriching wellness videos fostering the mind-body connection\nCalming breathing exercises designed to alleviate stress\nSupportive DARE buddy groups\nTwo live group Zoom sessions each month with our esteemed DARE clinical team\nDaily Dares, guest master classes, and much more!\nRead what our users say: “Took a chance with this app, and I’m so glad I did! It’s honestly amazing and the best anxiety app I’ve tried. The ‘Evening Wind Down’ is the absolute best, and I love how the app has so many different tools and meditations! Highly recommend DARE!” - StacyS\n\n“This is one of the only apps I’ve continued to pay premium for. It’s truly helped me come off that ledge of anxiety and learn new coping mechanisms that therapy hadn’t even taught me. I love this app, and I love the people that run it. Thank you for what you do.” - Aschom\n\n“20 years of fighting anxiety on my own, not knowing what’s going on with me… until I got this app. It’s changed the way I fight this THING forever. Thank you for all the work you do.” - Glitchb1\n\n“DARE is a lifesaver. I recently started using it, but it’s already helped me more than my therapist. The advice and the DARE response are great, but for me, the best are the deep relief and insomnia recordings—they help me go to sleep.” - MartinB\n\n“I was sceptical of the claim that within 3 days you’d see improvements, but I have an incredible set of tools. I can’t imagine not having this app now.” - RebeccaM\n\nApproved by ORCHA (Organisation for the Review of Care & Health Apps)\nAs featured in The Guardian, GQ, Vice, The Irish Times, Studio 10, and more\n\n\nTerms of service: https://dareresponse.com/terms-of-service-statement/\nPrivacy policy: https://dareresponse.com/privacy-policy/","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/5f/ca/1f/5fca1fbd-e07f-a8f9-f685-bb175d458c1e/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/dare-panic-anxiety-relief/id1034311206?uo=4","developer":"BMD Publishing Ltd","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":101,"2":43,"3":67,"4":229,"5":5719}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6757280986","title":"Overcome Speech Anxiety","store":"app_store","genre":"Health & Fitness","score":0,"ratings":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"Do you have a panic fear of presentations? Does your heart race when you need to speak up in meetings?\n\nSpeech anxiety (also called glossophobia) is widespread - it's one of the most common fears. But it doesn't have to hold you back any longer.\n\nYOUR 21-DAY PROGRAM AGAINST SPEECH ANXIETY\n\nWe guide you daily on your path to becoming a confident speaker:\n\n- Daily lessons: Understand the roots of your speech anxiety and resolve them\n\n- Practical exercises: Build self-confidence step by step\n\n- Mental techniques: Learn how professionals handle stage fright\n\n- Progress tracking: Document your development\n\nWHAT YOU WILL LEARN\n\n- Where your fear of speaking comes from\n- Techniques against stage fright before presentations\n- How to prevent blackouts during your speech\n- Use body language and voice effectively\n- How to transform nervousness into positive energy\n\nWHO IS THIS APP FOR?\n\n- Professionals who need to give presentations\n- Students before oral exams and presentations\n- Leaders who speak in front of teams\n- Anyone who wants to appear more confident in meetings\n- People with stage fright\n\nSTART FOR FREE\n\n3 introductory lessons are completely free.\n\nYour next presentation could be the turning point!","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/48/35/c4/4835c48f-11b3-3753-e5dd-8ea239d49b1c/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/overcome-speech-anxiety/id6757280986?uo=4","developer":"Novus Tec UG (haftungsbeschränkt)","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"575764424","title":"Constant Therapy: Brain+Speech","store":"app_store","genre":"Medical","score":4.50588,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":3317,"installs":"N/A","description":"Constant Therapy is an award-winning, science-based cognitive, language, and speech therapy app designed to help people recovering from stroke, traumatic brain injury (TBI), aphasia, apraxia, dementia, or other neurological conditions. Join a community of 800,000+ users, completing 325 million+ evidence-based therapy activities using Constant Therapy. Get unlimited AI-guided therapy  that allows you to engage in therapy exercises when and where you want. We support users seeking structured aphasia therapy or cognitive therapy that they can access anytime.\n\nAVAILABLE IN English dialects (US, UK, Australia, India) & US Spanish.\n\nConstant Therapy is designed to address concerns such as:\n– I know what I want to say but can’t find the words due to aphasia\n– My family can’t understand me when I talk\n– Before my TBI, I was a math whiz. Now, I have trouble with everyday math\n– I am forgetful, and I need help improving my memory\n– Staying on task has been difficult for me since my stroke. I need to fine-tune my attention & executive functioning\n– My loved one is getting speech therapy once a month, but it’s not enough. They need daily therapy\n– I need more aphasia, speech, or cognitive treatment exercises between therapy sessions\n\nFEATURES & BENEFITS\n\n• Recovering from stroke, TBI, aphasia, apraxia, dementia, or other neurological conditions? Choose your speech and cognitive therapy goals, and the app delivers customized & ever-adjusting exercises based on your unique needs\n\n• Tackle memory challenges, enhance communication skills, & regain everyday abilities through your individualized program\n\n• Engage in speaking, memory, attention, reading, writing, language, math, comprehension, problem solving, visual processing, auditory memory, & many other essential skill-building exercises\n\n• Work independently at home, pair the app with in-clinic therapy, or add your clinician so they can monitor your progress\n\n• Ideal for users looking to supplement aphasia therapy, speech therapy, and/or cognitive therapy with daily home-based exercises\n\n• Enjoy our friendly, live, Customer Support – trained to work with people with cognitive & communication challenges\n\n• Monitor your progress with real-time, easy-to-understand performance reports\n\n• Improve your chances for positive results: research has shown that patients using Constant Therapy get 5x more therapy practice, show faster improvement, & better outcomes***\n\n• Access the world’s most comprehensive library of evidence-based exercises: 1 Million+ exercises across 90+ therapy areas\n\n• Try before you subscribe with a free 14-day trial\n\n\n***SCIENCE BEHIND CONSTANT THERAPY\n\nConstant Therapy sets the gold standard with over 70 studies validating the clinical evidence behind our speech, language, and cognitive therapy exercises. We are also backed by 19 peer-reviewed research studies which substantiate the efficacy of Constant Therapy. See the list of clinical studies & research at:\nconstanttherapyhealth.com/science/\n\nConstant Therapy is much more than a brain-training app or brain games. It was designed by clinicians & scientists at Boston University specifically to target the challenges of recovery after stroke, brain injury, TBI, aphasia, dementia, apraxia, & other neurological disorders. It systematically tracks patient progress across a variety of functional domains.\n\nA multiple-award winner from Hearst Health, UCSF Health Hub, the American Stroke Association & AARP, Constant Therapy is recommended by thousands of speech-language pathologists, neurologists, occupational therapists, & clinicians at hospitals, clinics & rehabilitation facilities.\n\nSIGN UP FOR A FREE 14-DAY TRIAL\n\nCONTACT US\nsupport@constanttherapy.com\nconstanttherapy.com\n\nTERMS\nconstanttherapy.com/privacy/\nconstanttherapy.com/eula/\n\nConstant Therapy does not provide rehabilitation services or guarantee improvements in brain function. It provides tools for self-help and tools for patients to work with their clinicians.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/b2/97/b7/b297b773-810e-6801-0c91-2811f8444f7d/AppIconCT-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-8-0-0-sRGB-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/constant-therapy-brain-speech/id575764424?uo=4","developer":"Constant Therapy, Inc.","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1182789540","title":"Shadowing - English Speaking Exercise","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.76556,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":755,"installs":"N/A","description":"Improve your English speaking skills with speech shadowing.\n\n■□■ Non-Subscriber ■□■\nLimited contents, all features.\n\n■□■ Monthly Subscriber (1 Month FREE) ■□■\nAll contents, all features.\n\n- Payment will be charged to iTunes Account at confirmation of purchase\n- Subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period\n- Account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period, and identify the cost of the renewal\n- Subscriptions may be managed by the user and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the user's Account Settings after purchase\n- No cancellation of the current subscription is allowed during active subscription period\n\n■□■ Privacy Policy ■□■\nhttp://picup.co.jp/privacy_eng\n\n■□■ Terms of use ■□■\nhttp://picup.co.jp/terms_eng","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple128/v4/20/b4/48/20b448b3-83a2-28fb-f440-541d949c3828/mzl.wgnxmsvn.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/shadowing-english-speaking-exercise/id1182789540?uo=4","developer":"Picup Inc.","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1286609883","title":"Speak: Language Learning","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.83324,"ratings":38,"reviewCount":38989,"installs":"N/A","description":"Get ready to take your language skills to the next level with Speak, the ultimate language learning app focusing on improving your speaking abilities. Powered by cutting-edge AI technology, Speak ensures that you gain fluency by engaging in real-life conversations and receiving instant feedback. Whether you are learning Spanish, English, French, Italian, Japanese or Korean, Speak's AI-powered lessons will have you learning a new language fast.\n\nWith Speak, you'll feel like you have a personal language tutor right in your pocket. Our app provides immersive speaking practice sessions that simulate real-life scenarios, allowing you to become confident in your conversational skills. The advanced AI function analyzes your speech, providing a valuable assessment of pronunciation, intonation, and fluency. Say goodbye to those language barriers as you receive real-time feedback, enabling you to make necessary adjustments and improve your speaking skills on the spot.\n\nOur comprehensive language learning curriculum is available for Spanish, English, French, Italian, Japanese and Korean learners, ensuring that you become fluent. Whether you're a beginner or an advanced learner, Speak caters to your individual needs and helps you progress at your own pace. You'll love the personalized progress tracking, which helps you identify areas that need improvement, allowing you to focus your efforts effectively.\n\nSpeak's method is simple:\nSTEP 1: Do a real language learning lesson!\nLearn real-life, essential phrases with your dedicated local teacher.\n\nSTEP 2: Practice speaking the language!\nRepeat the learned phrases until you can speak without thinking twice!\n\nSTEP 3: AI Tutor provides personalized language feedback!\nWith the latest AI technology, you can practice anywhere and anytime! Get real-time feedback on pronunciations, grammar, and much more.\n\nSTEP 4: Real conversations in your chosen language!\nNow put what you've learned into real-life situations and speak with confidence!\n\nNo more boring textbooks or one-sided conversations! With Speak, you'll experience interactive and engaging language practice that feels like a real-life conversation. Break free from traditional language learning and download Speak now! Gain fluency, receive real-time feedback, and become a confident speaker in Spanish, English, French, Italian, Japanese and Korean.\n\nThere are plenty of other language apps out there, but Speak's key difference comes down to getting you speaking Spanish, English, French, Italian, Japanese or Korean out loud on day 1.\n\nSPEAK MEMBERSHIP\n\nSpeak offers both monthly and annual auto-renewing subscriptions. Become a Speak Member to gain unlimited access to all courses, singles, review material, and other content within Speak.\n\nThe subscription will automatically renew unless turned off in your iTunes Account Settings at least 24 hours before the current period ends. You can go to your iTunes Account settings to manage your subscription and turn off auto-renew. Your iTunes Account will be charged when the purchase is confirmed. If you subscribe before your free trial ends, the rest of your free trial period will be forfeited as soon as your purchase is confirmed.\n\nTerms of Service: https://usespeak.com/tos\nPrivacy Policy: https://usespeak.com/privacy\nLicense Agreement: https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/b3/bd/18/b3bd189a-9dd6-8184-874e-e89027e133b0/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-8-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/speak-language-learning/id1286609883?uo=4","developer":"Speakeasy Labs","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":375,"2":178,"3":736,"4":2996,"5":34704}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6504569940","title":"Flowency: Verbal Fluency Coach","store":"app_store","genre":"Health & Fitness","score":4.45946,"ratings":37,"reviewCount":37,"installs":"N/A","description":"Flowency — The #1 Verbal Fluency Training App\n\nFlowency is a science-backed verbal fluency training app that helps you speak more clearly, retrieve words faster, and expand your vocabulary through quick 60-second speaking drills.\n\nWhether you struggle with word-finding difficulties, want to sound more articulate in conversations, or need to sharpen your communication skills for work — Flowency trains your brain to access the right words instantly.\n\nWhat Is Flowency?\nFlowency is a daily verbal fluency coach that uses proven language training methods — including semantic fluency (category-based), phonemic fluency (sound-based), synonym recall, and descriptive language exercises — to strengthen your word retrieval and speaking ability. \n\nEach Flowency training session consists of five speaking exercise that last 1 minute each. At the end of your session, you will be scored on your vocabulary and verbal speed at which your produce words.\n\nKey Features:\n\n• 1,000+ Verbal Fluency Drills — Quick, science-based 60-second speaking exercises that improve word retrieval, articulation, and speaking speed.\n• Vocabulary Building — Learn new words daily with a personalized word of the day. Build your vocabulary faster and retain it longer.\n• Word Retrieval Training — Strengthen your ability to find the right word instantly, even under pressure. Ideal for tip-of-the-tongue moments.\n• Synonym & Descriptive Language Practice — Master synonyms, precise vocabulary, and descriptive phrasing for clear, confident communication.\n• Public Speaking & Impromptu speaking topics — Sharpen verbal agility for meetings, presentations, interviews, and high-stakes conversations.\n• Gamified Progress System — Earn XP, unlock rare word gems, maintain streaks, and collect badges. Track your growth with interactive charts and fluency scores.\n\nWho Is Flowency For?\n• People who want to speak more clearly and confidently\n• Professionals preparing for interviews, presentations, or meetings\n• Anyone experiencing word-finding difficulties or tip-of-the-tongue moments\n• People looking to expand their vocabulary and sound more articulate\n• Public speakers, podcasters, entrepreneurs, and content creators\n• Those seeking cognitive training for mental sharpness\n\nWhy Verbal Fluency Matters:\nVerbal fluency — the ability to quickly retrieve and produce words — is linked to cognitive health, career success, and stronger relationships. Research shows that regular verbal fluency practice improves word recall speed, vocabulary size, and overall communication confidence.\n\nHow Flowency Is Different:\n• Unlike vocabulary flashcard apps, Flowency trains you to speak — not just memorize.\n• Unlike language learning apps, Flowency is built for people who already speak English but want to speak better.\n• Unlike brain training apps, Flowency focuses specifically on verbal fluency and word retrieval\n• The only app dedicated entirely to verbal fluency training.\n\nBased on Proven Science:\n• Verbal fluency is a core executive function that engages working memory, cognitive flexibility, and processing speed every time you search for the right word.\n• Flowency's exercises are adapted from clinically validated neuropsychological assessments — including the Controlled Oral Word Association Test (COWAT).\n• Decades of research show these exercises improve word retrieval speed, active vocabulary size, and overall cognitive health.\n• Targeted verbal fluency practice strengthens the neural pathways between your brain's language centers, building faster and more reliable word access over time.\n\nDownload Flowency today and never struggle for words again.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/b2/bb/29/b2bb29a7-ba00-1e3d-dd77-21d4ced3b7e6/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-8-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/flowency-verbal-fluency-coach/id6504569940?uo=4","developer":"Digital Atomic","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":1,"2":1,"3":0,"4":13,"5":22}}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1485607474","title":"Articulation Station Hive","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":3.92593,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":189,"installs":"N/A","description":"Articulation Station Hive is the most comprehensive speech therapy app on the App Store. It has all the tools and activities needed to teach learners of all ages how to speak more clearly. To start with, it has 17 different activities to target speech in both consonants and vowels from the isolation level through the conversation level. \n\nARTICULATION STATION HIVE OFFERS: \n\nISOLATION ACTIVITIES: \n- Hand cues provide a video model with a hand cue for each sound.\n- Picture cues offer fun animated illustrations for each sound.\n- Letter cues pair the letter with the sound in a playful way.\n\nSYLLABLE ACTIVITIES:\n- Syllable sliders allow learners to slide 2 sounds together to make a word.\n- Syllable spinners allow learners to spin 1, 2, and 3 syllable combinations.\n\nWORD ACTIVITIES: \n- Minimal Pairs illustrate the subtle differences sounds in words make.\n- Flashcards provide a quick and reliable tool for focused repetition. \n- Matching games (3 levels) keep kids (and adults) engaged in the activity.\n\nPHRASE ACTIVITIES:\n- Rotating phrases allow learners to spin a lead word and a target word for a limitless number of two word combinations.\n- Unique phrases are three-word descriptive phrases that are perfect for addressing both speech and language goals.\n\nSENTENCE ACTIVITIES:\n- Fixed rotating sentences are like long “carrier phrases” where the sentence stays the same and only one target word changes.\n- Mixed rotating sentences mix things up. With each spin a new pronoun, verb, adjective and target word spin into position.\n- Unique sentences are usually longer and at times more complex than the rotating sentences.\n\nSTORY ACTIVITIES:\n- Level 1 stories are short, rhyming, and sometimes repetitive stories paired with picture prompts. \n- Level 2 stories are longer stories with larger vocabulary and even more opportunities to practice the target sound.\n\nCONVERSATION ACTIVITIES:\n- Conversation scenes allow the learner to scroll from right to left to explore the scene. Speech samples can be recorded, saved and scored.\n- Conversation questions offer four different types of questions. \n\nADDITIONAL ACTIVITIES & RESOURCES:\n- Phonological processes may be practiced in single words or with minimal pairs. \n- Multiple sounds allow learners to practice multiple sounds at a time at the word, phrase, or sentence level.\n- Custom words allow you to add images and words to help personalize the app. \n- Group sessions allow you to work with groups of students up to 6 at a time. *Pro tier only.\n- Themes include seasonal themes, holiday themes, just-for-fun themes, and multiple colored backgrounds. *illustrated themes are iPad only.\n\nSCORES:\n- View a summary of all your students’ sessions, and see graphs of your students’ performances on all targeted sounds.\n- View session details including all the correct, approximate, and incorrect responses. \n- Write and view notes, listen to recordings, and repeat sessions. \n- Share progress and notes with parents or adult users.\n\nWe’re proud to offer Articulation Station Hive as part of the Little Bee Hive membership which includes access to both Articulation Station Hive and Articulation Test Center Hive in the Pro tier. If you are already subscribed to Articulation Test Center Hive you may download and login to Articulation Station Hive with your same login information at no additional cost.\n\nSUBSCRIPTION, PRICING & TERMS:\nArticulation Station Hive offers a 14-day free trial which includes unlimited access to both Articulation Station Hive and Articulation Test Center Hive. The subscription automatically renews unless the auto-renew feature is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. Payment will be charged to your Apple account at the end of your 14-day trial period. Subscriptions may be managed by the user and auto-renewal may be turned off at any time.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/04/4d/39/044d39b4-2f37-9db2-8ebc-8466b41e2563/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-9-0-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/articulation-station-hive/id1485607474?uo=4","developer":"Little Bee Speech","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6469807611","title":"AI Spanish Learning - Fluency","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.36719,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":128,"installs":"N/A","description":"The best app for SERIOUS Spanish learners\n\nWelcome to Fluency, the ultimate destination for those eager and serious about mastering the Spanish language. Our app, designed by avid language learners just like you, offers a revolutionary approach to language acquisition, making the journey to fluency not just a dream, but an achievable goal.\n\nWhy Fluency stands out:\n\nAll-Inclusive Language Learning Platform: Fluency brings together all essential elements of language learning - vocabulary enhancement, grammar understanding, pronunciation perfection, and conversational practice, encapsulated within one innovative app.\n\nAI-Powered Learning Experience: Dive into the future of language learning with our advanced AI technology. It provides a unique, stress-free environment for you to practice speaking and comprehension, ensuring your learning process is as efficient as it is enjoyable.\n\nOptimized Learning Techniques: Our methods aren't just innovative; they're scientifically proven. With strategies inspired by extensive academic research, Fluency guarantees a faster and more effective learning curve.\n\nFluency is the language learning app made for serious language learners. No more child's play and games that seem like they were made for kids. If you are serious about learning Spanish this is the app for you.\n\nCore Features:\n\nVocabulary Mastery: Embrace the power of the popular Anki style spaced repetition with our flashcards, designed for long-term word retention. Experience the benefits of contextual learning, a method celebrated for its effectiveness in language acquisition. Our vocabulary words are sourced from millions of hours of Spanish television. They are then sorted and shown to you in order of how frequently they are seen in real life. This means that you learn the words you need in the order you need them.\n\nPractical Conversations: Test your skills with engaging mock conversations, simulating real-life interactions to prepare you for the world beyond the classroom.\n\nDaily Lessons: Our daily lessons focus on grammar and pronunciation, laying down the foundation for a robust understanding of Spanish as recommended by experts.\n\nImmersive Stories: Dive into daily stories that not only bolster your comprehension but also enrich your vocabulary. Through these narratives, you'll refine your expressive abilities, a crucial aspect of language mastery.\n\nA Research-Driven Journey:\nFluency's foundation is built upon solid academic research. Every aspect of our app is meticulously crafted to ensure you're learning Spanish in the most efficient manner possible.\n\nA Stress-Free Learning Environment:\nForget the fear of speaking a new language. Fluency offers a comforting, AI-enhanced space where you can learn at your own pace, free from anxiety.\n\nJoin a Community of Learners:\nBy choosing Fluency, you join a vibrant community of Spanish learners. Regardless of your starting point or objective, our app is designed to meet your language learning needs, offering a path to fluency that is both engaging and effective.\n\nBegin Your Journey Today:\nElevate your Spanish with Fluency. Download now and embark on a transformative journey toward achieving language fluency.\n\nEmbark on your language learning adventure with Fluency, where each lesson brings you closer to mastery. Our app is not just about learning Spanish; it's about transforming the way you connect with the world. With Fluency, you don't just learn Spanish; you live it. Welcome to a new era of language learning. Welcome to Fluency.\n\nSUBSCRIPTION\nYou will need a subscription in order to access the features mentioned above. Each subscription will be automatically renewed unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current payment period. Should you cancel a subscription, you will have access to the features until the end of the current payment period. \n\nTerms of Use: https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/3a/4b/4a/3a4b4af2-1549-9a0b-d3a7-5276b36d4e38/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/ai-spanish-learning-fluency/id6469807611?uo=4","developer":"Fluency Technologies LLC","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1438344260","title":"Vocabulary Builder by Atlas","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.77447,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":11440,"installs":"N/A","description":"Atlas Vocabulary Builder is an app designed to help you grow your vocabulary, no matter what your proficiency level is.\nCreated by language-learning experts and trusted by thousands of learners, Atlas offers a personalized, science-based path to mastering English vocabulary and building a library of thousands of new words, phrases, idioms, and expressions.\n\nWHO ATLAS IS FOR\nAtlas is perfect for learners who want a smarter, structured, and personalized way to grow their English vocabulary.\n It’s ideal for:\n - Self-learners who want to improve consistently and expand their vocabulary with thousands of new words\n - Students preparing for TOEFL, IELTS, SAT, GRE, and other exams\n - Professionals who want stronger communication skills for work\n - Intermediate and advanced learners aiming to sound more fluent and natural\n - Anyone who wants to master vocabulary with real context\n\nFEATURES\n\nPROFICIENCY TEST: START AT YOUR LEVEL\nBegin with a quick proficiency test and instantly receive content tailored to your level, from Beginner to Native-level (Super-Proficient).\nYour learning path adjusts as you progress.\n\nCURATED CURRICULUM FOR EVERY LEVEL\n- Follow a structured curriculum with carefully curated vocabulary for each proficiency level\n- Explore additional categories like Idioms, Phrasal Verbs, Academic Vocabulary, Business English, and \nExam English (TOEFL, GRE, SAT, and IELTS)\n- Study with level-appropriate quizzes, progress tests, and module exams that reinforce long-term retention\n\nWORD OF THE DAY\n- Get a Daily Word of the Day\n- Read short, engaging articles using that word\n- See a custom illustration that makes the meaning easier to remember\n\nBUILD YOUR PERSONAL VOCABULARY JOURNAL\n- Save any word you encounter\n- Group words into custom lists\n- Create collections based on topics or goals\n- Revisit your words with smart practice tools\n\n\n\nPOWERFUL EXERCISES TO PRACTICE\nPractice your vocabulary with the exercise types that work best for you:\n- Flashcards\n- Gap-fill sentence completion\n- Definition matching\n- Spelling practice\n- Dialogue gap-fills\n- Meaning-from-context challenges\n\nATLAS AI TUTOR\nAsk anything and get:\n- Clear explanations in simple English\n- Natural example sentences\n- Collocations and word partners\n- Short dialogues using your words\n- Context-rich alternatives and synonyms\nYour own personal language coach – available anytime.\n\nREMINDERS & WIDGETS TO STAY CONSISTENT\n- Set daily reminders\n- Add Home Screen widgets\n\n\nSMART SPACED REPETITION SYSTEM\n- A unique spaced-repetition algorithm strengthens retention by presenting personalized exercises designed just for you\n- Gradually takes you from simply recognizing vocabulary to using it accurately and confidently in real sentences\n \nTRACK YOUR PROGRESS\n- Monitor your vocabulary growth\n- See how many words you’ve mastered\n- Complete sets, tests, and modules to advance through levels\n\nWORLDWIDE VOCABULARY CHALLENGES\n- Compete with global learners in themed vocabulary challenges.\n- Discover new topics every week and stay motivated with fun, community-driven learning\n\nWHY YOU’LL LOVE ATLAS\n- Designed by language-learning experts\n- Great for exam prep\n- Helps you write and speak more clearly\n- Makes learning vocabulary enjoyable, structured, and personalized\n\nYour vocabulary-building journey starts here.\nDownload Atlas Vocabulary Builder and unlock your true language potential.\n\n\nSubscription and Pricing: \nIf you choose to purchase, payment will be applied to your iTunes account at confirmation of purchase. Subscriptions will automatically renew unless canceled within 24 hours before the end of the current period. You can cancel anytime with your iTunes account settings. Any unused portion of a free trial will be forfeited if you purchase a subscription.\n\n\nSubscriptions can be deactivated at the following link: https://support.apple.com/en-us/HT202039\nPrivacy Policy: https://www.atlasvocabulary.com/privacy-policy\nTerms of Use: https://www.atlasvocabulary.com/terms-of-use","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/86/38/bc/8638bc19-74c0-eac8-4609-f5d8fbe38031/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-0-sRGB-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/vocabulary-builder-by-atlas/id1438344260?uo=4","developer":"SAYAN YAZILIM TEKNOLOJI ANONIM SIRKETI","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1592642932","title":"BeeSpeaker Learn English","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.8041,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":2537,"installs":"N/A","description":"BzZzZz! Join our hive and start communicating smoothly in a foreign language. It has never been easier to learn English and Spanish!\n\nBeeSpeaker is a true revolution and the first-ever app totally devoted to learning to actually SPEAK English and Spanish. The app gets you speaking from day 1. Within the first week, our users say up to 1000 words in the language they’re learning.\n\nHow? It’s a voice-controlled and AI-powered app, based on modern machine learning technology, in which your task is to listen to words and phrases and repeat or answer questions, speaking out loud in a foreign language. BeeSpeaker recognizes what you’re saying and gives you instant feedback. This way, you know where you’re making mistakes and where you need to improve.\n\nWhy BeeSpeaker?\n- 3000+ English and Spanish video lessons with our teachers and native speakers designed to improve your speaking skills.\n- All language lessons are tailored to your level - starting from A0 and ending at C1.\n- A powerful AI Tutor module that corrects your mistakes and lets you practice free conversations, any time, any place.\n- Focus on vocabulary, grammar, pronunciation, and listening skills.\n- Real-time feedback shows you where you’re making mistakes.\n- Progress tracking, points and streaks help you stay motivated and keep the learning part FUN!\n\nAre you tired of English vocabulary apps? Are you feeling stuck when actually trying to communicate in English?\n\nWe focus on a natural method of learning a language. Instead of memorizing words, grammar rules, or reading flashcards, you learn by listening and repeating in English or Spanish and by practicing real-life conversations. Our interactive lessons help you listen, repeat, and correct mistakes instantly, building confidence every time you speak. Whether you're a beginner or an advanced learner, we’ve got lessons tailored for all levels!\n\nHow different people use BeeSpeaker?\n- Absolute beginners learn English or Spanish from scratch, with our video lessons tailored to A0 and A1 levels\n- Intermediate learners build vocabulary and progress to upper levels through our video course and by practicing speaking with BeeSpeaker’s AI Teacher\n- Advanced learners practice pronunciation and speaking with AI Tutor to prepare for popular English exams, like FCE, TOEFL, IELTS, or TOEIC\n- And for the most advanced learners, we’ve just added a C1 English course so that you can master your English to perfection\n\nOur instructors\n- Experienced teachers and native speakers from countries like Great Britain, the United States, and Australia.\n- Thanks to them you will learn different accents and ways of pronouncing particular words.\n\nAI Tutor\n- BeeSpeaker’s AI Tutor is your personal English & Spanish language coach powered by artificial intelligence, available 24/7.\n- It lets you practice free conversations and adjusts responses to what you’re saying - just like in real life. But without judgement or stress.\n\nThe app offers a free 7-day trial during which you can test every feature inside. You can cancel your trial anytime. And when you’re ready, you can unlock all features with our PRO subscription.\n\nBreak free from speaking anxiety, gain confidence, and speak English and Spanish naturally! The more you practice with BeeSpeaker, the faster you'll improve. Ready to start speaking fluently? Let BeeSpeaker be your guide.\n\nDownload now and join the language revolution!\n\nTerms of use: https://beespeaker.com/terms/\nPrivacy policy: https://beespeaker.com/privacy-policy/","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/2e/7e/68/2e7e68d5-5281-7ea5-5bd6-cbcdbe1340e1/BeeSpeakerAppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/beespeaker-learn-english/id1592642932?uo=4","developer":"BEESPEAKER AB","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"492885924","title":"Splash Reading: Games for Kids","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.25053,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":2375,"installs":"N/A","description":"Award-winning reading app trusted by millions of families and educators!\nSplash Reading helps kids master English Language Arts (ELA) skills from Kindergarten through Grade 5. Designed by experts, it combines structured lessons with fun, game-based activities to build strong readers and confident writers.\n\nAwards & Recognition\n- Winner of the Tabby Award for Best Educational App\n- Featured as “No. 1 Education App” by Apple\n- Loved by millions of kids, teachers, and parents worldwide\n\nAbout Splash Reading\nSplash Reading turns learning into an engaging journey.\nThrough phonics, vocabulary, spelling, grammar, and comprehension lessons, children progress step-by-step at their own pace. Each activity helps them strengthen reading fluency, boost confidence, and enjoy learning.\n\nWhat Your Child Will Learn\n→ Kindergarten\n- Recognize letters and sounds\n- Trace letters and learn sequencing\n- Explore sight words, rhyming words, and phonics basics\n\n→ Grade 1\n- Build foundational reading and writing skills\n- Master sight words, bossy R words, and silent e\n- Practice rhyming, digraphs, and vowel blends\n\n→ Grade 2\n- Strengthen fluency and phonics understanding\n- Learn diphthongs, trigraphs, and consonant clusters\n- Expand vocabulary and spelling accuracy\n\n→ Grade 3\n- Develop reading comprehension and word usage\n- Improve writing and spelling through fun activities\n- Practice cursive writing and sentence construction\n\n→ Grade 4\n- Advance grammar and vocabulary\n- Analyze text meaning and improve comprehension\n- Strengthen writing structure and creativity\n\n→ Grade 5\n- Master advanced grammar and vocabulary\n- Read complex passages with understanding\n- Enhance creative and analytical writing skills\n\n\nWhy Families Love SplashLearn\n- Guided Learning Path: Lessons build progressively for smooth skill development\n- Playful Practice: Interactive games turn reading and writing into fun challenges\n- Independent Learning: Kids learn confidently at their own pace\n- Safe and Ad-Free: A secure environment designed by educators\n\nParent Reviews\n- “My son struggled with reading until we tried Splash Reading. Now he enjoys it every day!” – Parent of a 2nd Grader\n- “The phonics games are amazing. My daughter’s fluency has improved so much.” – Parent of a 1st Grader\n- “A fantastic app for independent learning. My kids are having fun while improving.” – Parent of a 4th Grader\n\nSubscription & Free Trial\nTry it free! Get full access during your free trial, then choose a flexible plan that fits your family.\nEnjoy unlimited access to reading and writing activities for your child.\n\nNeed Help?\nWe’re here for you → https://support.splashlearn.com/hc/en-us\n\nPrivacy & Terms\nYour child’s safety comes first.\n- https://www.splashlearn.com/privacy\n- https://www.splashlearn.com/terms-of-use","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/c0/e5/e5/c0e5e532-d912-439e-2430-2b6215a00cc9/AppIconGrade4-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-8-0-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/splash-reading-games-for-kids/id492885924?uo=4","developer":"StudyPad, Inc.","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6450300197","title":"Owll:AI Note Taker & Assistant","store":"app_store","genre":"Utilities","score":4.79392,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":2305,"installs":"N/A","description":"Meet Owll – your smart AI assistant for seamless AI note-taking\nOwll helps you capture every word and idea with powerful voice-to-text and real-time transcription, plus smart AI summaries, an intelligent summarizer, and smart notes from meetings, lectures, webinars, and study sessions.\nRecord audio, upload files, or save online calls from Zoom, Google Meet, and Microsoft Teams – then organize, highlight, and share notes with ease.\nUse Owll as your reliable meeting recorder or study partner — perfect for work, school, or personal productivity.\nOwll AI is also available on the web.\n\nKey Features\n-AI-Powered Recording, Summaries & To-Dos\nRecord with one tap using Owll’s AI note taker and built-in AI Coach. Supports voice recorder mode, speech-to-text, voice transcription and audio file imports, then generates concise takeaways and to-do lists so nothing gets missed.\n\n-AI Contact Manager for Sales & Client Notes\n Scan business cards to capture leads and manage contacts instantly. Record sales calls and meetings with auto summaries and follow-ups. Search customer notes, track deals, and close more sales faster.\n\n-Transcription for Online Meetings\nOwll transcribes Zoom, Google Meet, and Microsoft Teams sessions. Enjoy real-time transcription and clear meeting notes so you can stay focused.\n\n-Smart Folders & Note Sharing\nCreate custom folders to organize recordings and notes. Keep everything tidy, share key takeaways with teammates or classmates in one tap, and manage your library effortlessly for smooth collaboration.\n\n-Smarter Note Review: Ask Owll AI\nOwll highlights main points, answers questions with built-in AI Q&A — even beyond your notes — and delivers clear summaries from transcripts, recordings, documents, or new topics in seconds.\n\n-Versatile Note-Taking & Study Aid\nConvert audio into text with precise AI transcription, and let smart summaries turn key points into lecture notes, flashcards, and study cards — ideal as a meeting notes app, productivity tool, or study companion.\n\n-Multilingual Transcription & Translation\nOwll supports multiple languages with enhanced transcription and translation. Perfect for global meetings, online classes, and cross-team collaboration.\n\n-Flashcards & AI-Driven Quizzes\nTurn your notes into flashcards and study cards. Owll’s AI quizzes create practice questions to reinforce key ideas and prep for exams.\n\n-Import Audio for Seamless Transcription\nImport audio from any app or device. Owll supports all formats for smooth speech-to-text. You can also import YouTube videos for transcripts and summaries, or use OCR PDFs to text for scanned material.\n\nBoost Your Productivity\nSave time with real-time transcriptions, smart summaries, folders, and note sharing.\nReliable Study Companion\nTurn spoken content into structured lecture notes, flashcards, and quizzes for easier review and retention.\nHassle-Free Capture\nEffortlessly record lectures, talks, and meetings. Owll extracts key takeaways so nothing gets missed.\nGlobal Accessibility\nBreak language barriers with multilingual transcription and translation.\n\nSubscription Plans\n Owll Plus offers these options:\n1-Year Subscription\n1-Month Subscription\n1-Week Subscription\n\nPayment & Management\n Payments are billed to your App Store Account upon purchase. Subscriptions auto-renew unless canceled 24h before the period ends. Manage subscriptions in Account Settings.\nTerms & Privacy\n Terms of Use: https://owll.ai/user-agreement/#/terms-service/\n Privacy Policy: https://owll.ai/user-agreement/#/privacy-policy/","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/2e/80/a6/2e80a674-4625-41a9-43ff-f13394b6cedf/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-0-85-220.jpeg/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/owll-ai-note-taker-assistant/id6450300197?uo=4","developer":"VOCALBEATS.AI PTE. LTD.","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1405230721","title":"Ella Verbs: Learn Spanish","store":"app_store","genre":"Education","score":4.91314,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":4824,"installs":"N/A","description":"Spanish verbs don't have to be scary.\n\nWhether you're just starting to learn Spanish or pushing toward fluency, verb conjugation is usually what holds you back. It's the missing piece of Spanish grammar that keeps you from speaking confidently. Other apps make you memorize. We teach you to understand, so conjugation finally clicks and you can actually hold a conversation.\n\nElla Verbs is the Spanish verb app built for learners who want real progress.\n\nHow Ella Verbs works:\n\nLearn a concept → Quiz until it clicks → Level up. That's it. No games, no fluff. Just a clear path from present tense to subjunctive, broken into 50 manageable levels. Our Smart Quizzes use spaced repetition (SRS) to target the patterns you're struggling with — not just individual words, but the tenses and verb types that aren't clicking yet. You practice what actually needs work, not what you already know.\n\nWhat learners are saying:\n\n\"In 22 days I've learned more than in all the years before.\"\n\n\"I am not afraid to form sentences or speak anymore.\"\n\n\"Learned more in 3 days than 3 years on Duolingo.\"\n\n\"Great for beginners but essential for serious learners.\"\n\nWe're rated 4.9 out of 5 stars based on 12,500+ reviews.\n\nWhat you get:\n\n• 50 levels of bite-sized lessons and quizzes covering 18 tenses\n• 2,300+ verbs with full English translations, synonyms, and step-by-step conjugation guides\n• Smart Quizzes with built-in spaced repetition (SRS) — targets weak patterns, not just individual verbs\n• CEFR level tracking (A1 → C2) so you know exactly where you stand\n• Practice your way: typing, multiple choice, flashcards, listening, speaking, or sentences in context\n• Full lessons on tricky topics like ser vs. estar and reflexive verbs\n• Works offline on your phone, tablet, or the web\n\nBuilt by learners, for learners:\n\nWe're Jane and Brian: an Irish couple living in Spain, learning Spanish ourselves. We built Ella Verbs because we couldn't find a method that actually taught conjugation instead of just drilling it. Since we're a small team, we personally read and respond to every email (really). We release updates almost weekly and have shipped 50+ improvements each year since launch.\n\nHave an idea or question? Reach us at jane@ellaverbs.com or brian@ellaverbs.com. We also offer free access through our Give Back program for those who need it.\n\nMore features:\n\n• Milestone levels testing verbs in real sentence contexts\n• Custom quiz builder—choose your tenses, verbs, and practice styles\n• Create your own verb lists to study (Pro)\n• Daily streak tracking across devices\n• Both European Spanish (with vosotros) and Latin American Spanish\n• Dark mode and extensive customization options\n\nTenses covered (18 total):\n\nIndicative mood:\n• Present (El Presente)\n• Present Continuous (El Presente Progresivo)\n• Informal/Near Future (El Futuro Próximo)\n• Preterite (El Pretérito Indefinido or El Pretérito Perfecto Simple)\n• Imperfect (El Pretérito Imperfecto)\n• Present Perfect (El Pretérito Perfecto)\n• Past Perfect (El Pretérito Pluscuamperfecto)\n• Future (El Futuro Simple)\n• Future Perfect (El Futuro Perfecto)\n• Conditional (El Condicional Simple)\n• Conditional Perfect (El Condicional Perfecto)\n\nSubjunctive mood:\n• Present Subjunctive (El Presente de Subjuntivo)\n• Imperfect Subjunctive (El Imperfecto de Subjuntivo)\n• Present Perfect Subjunctive (El Pretérito Perfecto de Subjuntivo)\n• Past Perfect Subjunctive (El Pretérito Pluscuamperfecto de Subjuntivo)\n• Future Subjunctive (El Futuro de Subjuntivo)\n• Future Perfect Subjunctive (El Futuro Perfecto de Subjuntivo)\n\nImperative mood:\n• Imperative, affirmative & negative (El Imperativo)\n\nBy using Ella Verbs you agree to our terms (https://ellaverbs.com/terms) and privacy policy (https://ellaverbs.com/privacy). Learn more at https://ellaverbs.com.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/d0/ac/07/d0ac07e9-3947-2bc4-a0a7-ed8b107450f7/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/ella-verbs-learn-spanish/id1405230721?uo=4","developer":"Tauro Software SL","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"570060128","title":"Duolingo - Language Lessons","store":"app_store","genre":"6017","score":0,"ratings":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"Learn a new language with the world’s most-downloaded education app! Duolingo is the fun, free app for learning 40+ languages through quick, bite-sized lessons. Practice speaking, reading, listening, and writing to build your vocabulary and grammar skills.\n\nDesigned by language experts and loved by hundreds of millions of learners worldwide, Duolingo helps you prepare for real conversations in Spanish, French, Japanese, Korean, Chinese, Italian, German, English, and more.\n\nAnd now, you can learn Math, Music, and Chess the Duolingo way!  \n\n• Build real-world math skills – from calculating tips to identifying patterns – and sharpen your mental math in our Math course.\n\n• Learn how to read music and play familiar songs on your device in our Music course – no instrument required.\n\n• Master moves, level up your game, and play real matches in our brand new Chess course. Checkmate!\n\nWhether you're learning for travel, school, career, family and friends, or your brain health, you'll love learning with Duolingo.\n\nWhy Duolingo?\n • Duolingo is fun and effective. Game-like lessons and fun characters keep you motivated to build solid skills across language, math, music, and chess.\n\n• Duolingo works. Designed by learning experts, Duolingo has a science-based teaching methodology proven to foster long-term knowledge retention.\n\n• Track your progress. Work toward your learning goals with playful rewards and achievements when you make practicing a daily habit!\n\n• Join 300+ million learners. Stay motivated with competitive Leaderboards as you learn alongside our global community.\n\n• Every course is free. Learn Spanish, French, German, Italian, Russian, Portuguese, Turkish, Dutch, Irish, Danish, Swedish, Ukrainian, Esperanto, Polish, Greek, Hungarian, Norwegian, Hebrew, Welsh, Arabic, Latin, Hawaiian, Scottish Gaelic, Vietnamese, Korean, Japanese, English, and even High Valyrian. And now, learn Math, Music, and Chess with our newest courses!\n\nWhat the world is saying about Duolingo:\n\n“Far and away the best language-learning app.” –The Wall Street Journal\n\n“This free app and website is among the most effective language-learning methods I’ve tried… lessons come in the form of brief challenges – speaking, translating, answering multiple-choice questions – that keep me coming back for more.” –The New York Times\n\n“Duolingo may hold the secret to the future of education.” – TIME Magazine\n\n“…Duolingo is cheerful, lighthearted and fun…” - Forbes\n\n“Our favorite language app…” - CNET\n\nIf you like Duolingo, try Super Duolingo for 14 days free! Learn a language fast with no ads, and get fun perks like Unlimited Hearts and Monthly Streak Repair.\n\nIf you choose to purchase Super Duolingo, payment will be charged to your Apple account, and your account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period. Auto-renewal may be turned off at any time by going to your settings in the App Store after purchase. Any unused portion of a free trial period, if offered, will be forfeited when the user purchases a subscription to that publication, where applicable.\n\nPrivacy Policy: https://www.duolingo.com/privacy\nTerms of Service: https://www.duolingo.com/terms","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/7f/55/a1/7f55a1cf-8fde-9957-8016-c6d50f269dcb/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-85-220.png/100x100bb.png","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/duolingo-language-lessons/id570060128?uo=2","developer":"Duolingo","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1542571008","title":"Gauth: AI Study Companion","store":"app_store","genre":"6017","score":0,"ratings":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"Gauth is the #1 AI study companion powered by newest AI model! Trusted by millions of users, Gauth offers unlimited answers for all subjects. Try Gauth for all your learning needs!\n\nKey Features:\n► ACCURATE ANSWERS, STEP-BY-STEP\nCompared to other homework helpers, Gauth is faster and more accurate at solving homework problems, especially with the support of Gauth AI Pro. Problems could be solved quickly within a few seconds, and all answers are accompanied by animated instructions and detailed explanations.\n\n► AI LIVE TUTOR, VOICE & WHITEBOARD\nStuck on a question? With AI Live Tutor, ask by voice anytime and see problems explained clearly on a live whiteboard—just like having a personal tutor by your side.\n\n► AI STUDY CONVERTER: QUIZZES & FLASHCARDS INSTANTLY\nGot messy notes or long lectures? With AI Study Converter, upload class notes, photos, audio, or YouTube links — and instantly get personalized quizzes & flashcards to help you learn faster and boost your GPA. No extra work, just better results.\n\n► DEEPTHINKING, INSPIRE YOUR LEARNING\nPowered by Gauth AI, integrates the advantages of multiple AI models and solves your problems smarter and more deeply. With Gauth AI, we hope you can get inspired and learn efficiently.\n\n► MASTER ALL SUBJECTS, ALL GRADES\nNot only Math questions, Gauth could now solve all different levels of problems in Physics, Chemistry, Biology and more.\n\n► REAL EXPERTS READY TO HELP 24/7\nAs a strong and resourceful homework solver, we have professional experts and dedicated experts ready to help you 24/7 with multiple subjects, including Math, Physics, Chemistry, and Biology. All experts are available to solve your problems anytime and anywhere, offering clear step-by-step explanations. With Gauth, you can easily understand and master different subjects.\n\n► EASY TO USE, HOMEWORK IS COOL\nSimply take a photo of your problem, and Gauth will recognize it and crop your question automatically. After uploading, our experts will provide solutions in a few seconds with well-formatted answers and explanations. With Gauth, we hope you can find homework is also fun and easy to understand!\n\n► STUDY TOOLBOX, ALL-IN-ONE APP\nPacked with essential tools like Reading, Writing, Focus Mode, and Calculator. Whether you are struggling with tough books, writing, distraction or calculation, get text simplification, grammar check and math calculation in one app. Gauth helps you to supercharge your academic performance.\n\n► SUBJECTS COVERED\n- Math\n- Biology\n- Physics\n- Chemistry\n- Others\n► MATH TOPICS COVERED\n- Math Word problems\n- Algebra (Real Number; Arithmetic; Set theory; Expression; Logarithm; Complex Number)\n- Function (Linear; Quadratic; Polynomial; Exponential; Rational; Logarithmic; Inverse Function)\n- Geometry (Plane & Solid Geometry; Algebra & lines; Lines & Planes in Space; Transformation)\n- Trigonometry (Trigonometric Ratios; Law of Sines; Law of Cosines; Reciprocal Properties)\n- Calculus (Derivatives; Integrals; Limits; the Tangent/Area Math problem)\n- Statistics and Data Analysis (Probability; Data Representation; Poisson/Normal Distribution)\n- Matrix (Matrix Algebra; System of Linear Equations & Matrices)\n- Logic (Reasoning & Proof)\n► Want to level up your learning? With Gauth Plus, you will get:\n- Unlimited answers and explanations\n- High accuracy in answers\n- Advanced AI tutor with clearer live explanations\n- Access to 20M+ tutorial videos\n- A question bank of 100M+\n- 24/7 tutor help\n\nSTAY CONNECTED\n- Tiktok: www.tiktok.com/@gauthofficial\n- Official Website: www.gauthmath.com\n- Email: support@gauth-us.com","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/9c/fe/ee/9cfeeed0-f70b-7252-97a7-a3947c15ba44/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-8-0-85-220.png/100x100bb.png","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/gauth-ai-study-companion/id1542571008?uo=2","developer":"GAUTHTECH PTE. LTD.","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1445023295","title":"Deepstash: Smarter Every Day!","store":"app_store","genre":"6017","score":0,"ratings":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"Learn something new in just 5 minutes a day with carefully curated ideas from the world's most popular books, presented through beautiful art and a delightfully focused reading experience.\n\nStop Scrolling Social Media -> Download Deepstash -> Use it for 5 min/day -> Become the smartest in the room.\n\nJoin 5 Million+ people discovering powerful insights from books like Atomic Habits, The Psychology of Money, Think and Grow Rich, and hundreds more—all distilled into bite-sized ideas you can read at a glance.\n\n------\n\nWHAT MAKES DEEPSTASH DIFFERENT\n\nKnowledge in Deepstash comes as beautifully designed idea cards—short, visual notes that condense profound thoughts from bestselling books into simple, memorable insights. Each idea is paired with stunning artwork that makes learning feel less like work and more like inspiration.\n\nNo clutter. No distractions. Just focused, delightful content that helps you grow smarter every day.\n\n------\n\nWHAT IDEAS CAN DO FOR YOU\n\nIdeas are fundamental to your wellbeing, success in life, and your career. Reading powerful ideas daily can make you:\n- Smarter (you'll know more valuable concepts)\n- More Creative (you can connect more dots)\n- Happier (better habits, less anxiety)\n\nFuel your curiosity and get smarter daily.\n\n------\n\nPERSONALIZED CONTENT & FEEDS\n\nChoose topics you care about—productivity, leadership, psychology, philosophy, marketing, and more. As you read and save ideas, we learn what resonates with you and surface the best content from our curated library of insights from top books.\n\nYou don't even have to work for it. We refresh your recommendations multiple times a day so you never run out of fresh ideas.\n\n------\n\nFREE & PRO: WHAT'S THE DIFFERENCE?\n\n- Start Free\nAccess 200,000+ powerful ideas from top books, articles, podcasts, and videos\nCreate and share your own ideas\n\n- Upgrade to Deepstash Pro\nNo Ads - Read without interruptions\nListen & Grow - Audio playback for all ideas\nDownload Your Ideas - Access your library offline\nUnlimited History - Go back to everything you've read, organized by day\n\n------\n\nBUILD YOUR PERSONAL KNOWLEDGE LIBRARY\n\nSave ideas that matter to you and organize them into collections. Create stashes for work projects, personal growth goals, or topics you're passionate about. Search and filter your saved ideas anytime—they're always at hand when you need them.\n\n------\n\nSHARE YOUR DISCOVERIES\n\nFound an idea worth spreading? Share it with friends on WhatsApp, Facebook, Twitter, Instagram, TikTok, LinkedIn, or Quora. The Deepstash bite-sized format is perfect for sparking conversations.\n\n------\n\nWHY OUR USERS LOVE DEEPSTASH:\n\n\"It helped me get off social media. So excellent to learn something, and I feel like the time I spent was valuable. I also spend about 10 minutes every morning picking a topic and enjoying it. Great app, well-done Kudos\" - Ron Ronald\n\n\"Even five minutes a day will improve your thinking. I've come across new ideas and learnt to improve existing ways to become more motivated, confident and happier.\" - Ghazala Begum\n\n------\n\nWHAT THE MEDIA IS BUZZING ABOUT US:\n\n\"Learn good habits, health practices, and more on your time. Makes personal growth manageable\" - Mashable\n\n\"More than 200,000 game-changing ideas at your fingertips\" - MacWorld\n\n\"Deepstash is perfect for entrepreneurs who want to stay updated but are short on time.\" - Entrepreneur.com\n\n------\n\nGood for your career. \nGreat for your life. \nGive it a shot!\n\nRead more about our terms and conditions here:\nTerms of service: https://deepstash.com/terms-of-service\nPrivacy policy: https://deepstash.com/privacy-policy","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/07/0b/eb/070beb06-9f33-400c-60ac-68c29bcfbf18/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-11-0-sRGB-85-220.png/100x100bb.png","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/deepstash-smarter-every-day/id1445023295?uo=2","developer":"Brainstash, Inc","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"924620788","title":"Google Classroom","store":"app_store","genre":"6017","score":0,"ratings":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"Classroom is a free service for schools, non-profits, and anyone with a personal Google account. Classroom makes it easy for learners and instructors to connect—inside and outside of schools. Classroom saves time and paper, and makes it easy to create classes, distribute assignments, communicate, and stay organized.\n\nClassroom is designed to help teachers create, collect, and grade assignments paperlessly, including time-saving features like the ability to automatically make a copy of a Google Document for each student. It also creates Drive folders for each assignment and for each student to help keep everyone organized.\n\nStudents can keep track of what’s due on the Assignments page and begin working with just a click. Teachers can quickly see who has or hasn't completed the work, and provide direct, real-time feedback and grades right in Classroom.\n\nWith the mobile app for iOS, students and teachers can view their classes and communicate with their classmates in real time. Students can open their assignments and work on them right from their iPhone or iPad. Teachers can keep track of who has turned in work and grade the assignment - at school or on the go. Students and teachers receive notifications when they have new content in Classroom, so they are always up to date.\n\nThere are many benefits of using Classroom:\n\nEasy to set up\nTeachers can add students directly or share a code with their class to join. It takes just minutes to set up.\n\nSaves time\nThe simple, paperless assignment workflow allows teachers to create, review, and grade assignments quickly, all in one place.\n\nImproves organization\nStudents can see all of their assignments on an assignments page, and all class materials (e.g., documents, photos, and videos) are automatically filed into folders in Google Drive.\n\nEnhances communication\nClassroom allows teachers to send announcements and start class discussions instantly. Students can share resources with each other or provide answers to questions on the stream.\n\nSecure\nLike the rest of Google Workspace for Education services, Classroom contains no ads, never uses your content or student data for advertising purposes.\n\nPermissions Notice:\nCamera: Needed to allow the user to take photos or videos and post them to Classroom.\nMicrophone: Needed to enable audio capture for recording videos to be posted to Classroom.\nPhotos: Needed to allow the user to attach photos or videos to Classroom. Photos or videos posted to Classroom will be stored on Google servers in order to show them in Classroom.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/c1/d9/cb/c1d9cbe4-64b1-4910-a20e-6e7cd5904b02/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-0-0-1-0-0-0-85-220.png/100x100bb.png","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/google-classroom/id924620788?uo=2","developer":"Google","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1394069110","title":"Zutobi: Permit & Driving Prep","store":"app_store","genre":"6017","score":0,"ratings":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"COULD YOU ACE YOUR DRIVERS PERMIT TEST?\nJoin over 250,000 monthly users on the most popular DMV practice test app. It’s fast, easy and fun. It's the only study material you need to get your DMV permit and driver license. We have courses for Car, CDL and Motorcycle. We are certified to issue Entry Level Driver Training (ELDT) certification to the TPR for CDL drivers.\n\nThe Zutobi app is built like a game and keeps you motivated. When you have finished the app, you are prepared to sit the DMV Test. It's that simple. \n\nDON’T LEAVE ANYTHING UP TO CHANCE AT THE DMV PERMIT TEST\nThe app teaches you the rules of the road using our summarized easy-to-read DMV handbook AND over 600 state-specific questions that are almost identical to the real permit test.\n\nLEARN TO DRIVE AND BECOME A SAFE DRIVER \nThe app promotes safe driving and helps you learn important safety aspects of driving.\n_______________________________________\n\nWHY ZUTOBI?\n\n• 600+  QUESTIONS IDENTICAL TO THE REAL DMV TEST - The questions are very similar (often identical) to the real test. \n\n• SUMMARIZED DMV HANDBOOK - We’ve summarized the handbook for most states into an easy-to-read format without all the unnecessary drivel. \n\n• PICTURES AND ILLUSTRATIONS - Learn the rules of the road using real-life traffic situations to help you learn fast and efficiently. \n\n• STATE SPECIFIC - The app is tailored specifically for each US state to match the requirements of the DMV, DDS, DOL, DOT, BMV, MVA, RMV, DOR, MVC and MVD tests.\n\n• COMPETE AND WIN - Challenge your friends and see who can score the highest using fun features such as the Leaderboard. Besides glory and honor, winning over your friends also means that you’re more likely to do well on the real test.\n\n• DETAILED STATISTICS - Easily track your progress using advanced statistics.\n\n• UNLIMITED TESTS - Take as many practice tests as you need (most are near identical to the tests by the DMV), and learn from your mistakes through detailed explanations.\n\n_______________________________________\n\nGET STARTED TODAY AND GET YOUR DRIVERS LICENSE\nDownload today and start your journey towards learning all the rules of the road and acing your test!  Once you have finished the app, you will feel confident as a driver.\n\nARE YOU A DRIVERS LICENSE HOLDER LOOKING FOR A REFRESHER COURSE?\nThe app works just as great for current drivers license holders looking to freshen up their knowledge of the rules of the road\n\nDO WE OFFER STATE-APPROVED DRIVERS ED?\nNo. If, because of your age, you are required to take a state-approved course - use our course as a complement to ensure that you learn how to behave in traffic, get the knowledge you need to stay safe and pass your test.\n\n_______________________________________\n\nZutobi Plus subscription\n\n- Zutobi Plus includes full access to the specified course for the duration of the subscription period\n\n- All prices are subject to change without notification. Promotion prices and limited-time opportunities may be available for qualifying purchases made during the promotional period. We are unable to offer price protection, refunds or retroactive discounts for previous purchases in the event that we offer a promotional offering or price reduction.\n\n- Payment is charged through your iTunes account at confirmation of purchase\n\n- Your iTunes account will be automatically renewed and charged for renewal unless turned off in iTunes Account Settings at least 24 hr before the current subscription period ends (including the free trial period). The unused portion of the free trial is forfeited after purchase.\n\n- Your subscriptions may be managed by the user and auto-renewal may be turned off in the user’s iTunes Account Settings after purchase. However, you are not able to cancel the current subscription period during its active subscription period\n\nOur Terms of Service and Privacy Policy:\n\nPrivacy Policy: https://zutobi.com/privacy\nTerms of Use: https://zutobi.com/terms\nContact us: https://zutobi.com/us/contact","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/c3/4c/7f/c34c7f8a-25b6-8b52-23ce-f87cc5b5d781/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-85-220.png/100x100bb.png","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/zutobi-permit-driving-prep/id1394069110?uo=2","developer":"Zutobi AB","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1131203560","title":"Kahoot! Play & Create Quizzes","store":"app_store","genre":"6017","score":0,"ratings":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"Play engaging quiz-based games (kahoots) at school, at home and at work, create your own kahoots, and learn something new! Kahoot! brings the magic of learning to students, teachers, office superheroes, trivia fans, and lifelong learners.\n\nHere’s what you can do with the Kahoot! app, now available in English, Spanish (LATAM), French, German, Italian, Brazilian Portuguese, Japanese, Dutch, Turkish, Polish, Arabic, Simplified Chinese, Traditional Chinese, Norwegian, Swedish, Danish, Ukrainian and Korean:\n\nYoung students\n- Make your school projects awesome by building kahoots on any topic using pre-made templates, fun question types, themes, and background music.\n- Supercharge your games with unique rewards including new characters and accessories.\n- Enjoy premium game modes, perfect for birthday parties and family game nights!\n- Ace upcoming exams by setting learning goals and testing yourself with advanced study modes.\n- Make math fun with interactive games to get ahead in algebra, multiplications, and fractions.\n\nStudents\n- Study with unlimited free flashcards and other smart study modes\n- Join kahoots hosted live - in class or virtually - and use the app to submit answers\n- Complete self-paced kahoots\n- Challenge your friends in study groups with kahoots you found or created\n- Create your own kahoots and add images or videos\n- Host kahoots live for family and friends directly from your mobile device\n\nFamilies and friends\n- Find a kahoot on any topic, fit for any age\n- Host a kahoot live by sharing your screen to Apple TV or via video conferencing apps\n- Play a live kahoot using SharePlay. Start a FaceTime call and select the kahoot you want to play. No host is required - everyone can participate!\n- Engage your kids with studying at home\n- Assign a kahoot to challenge family members and friends\n- Create your own kahoots and add different question types and image effects\n\nTeachers\n- Search among millions of ready-to-play kahoots on any topic\n- Create or edit your own kahoots in minutes\n- Combine different question types to increase engagement\n- Host kahoots live in class or virtually for distance learning\n- Assign student-paced kahoots for content review\n- Assess learning outcomes with reports\n\nProfessionals\n- Create kahoots for e-learning, presentations, events and other occasions\n- Encourage audience participation with polls and word cloud questions\n- Host Kahoot! live in person or in a virtual meeting\n- Assign self-paced kahoots, for example, for e-learning\n- Assess progress and results with reports\n\nPremium features:\nKahoot! is free for teachers and their students, and it’s our commitment to keep it that way as part of our mission to make learning awesome. We offer optional upgrades that unlock advanced features, such as an image library with millions of images and advanced question types, such as puzzles, polls, open-ended questions and slides. To take advantage of these features, users will need a paid subscription.\n\nTo create and host kahoots in a work context, as well as get access to additional features, business users will need a paid subscription.\n\nRecurring billing, cancel anytime\n- Payment will be charged to your iTunes account at confirmation of purchase.\n- Subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current period.\n- Account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours of the end of the current period, and the cost of the renewal will be provided.\n- Subscriptions may be managed by the user. Auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the user’s Account Settings after purchase. No cancellation of the current subscription is allowed during the active subscription period.\n- Any unused portion of a free trial period, if offered, will be forfeited when you purchase a subscription.\n\nPrivacy Policy: https://kahoot.com/privacy\nTerms and conditions: https://kahoot.com/terms","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/89/26/64/8926643a-3eaf-9bfc-15ab-0036886d73dd/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-0-0-sRGB-85-220.png/100x100bb.png","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/kahoot-play-create-quizzes/id1131203560?uo=2","developer":"Kahoot ASA","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6736654449","title":"Micro Learning - SmartyMe","store":"app_store","genre":"6017","score":0,"ratings":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"SmartyMe is a daily learning app designed for modern micro learning. With short 15-minute lessons you can read or listen anytime, this learning app helps you build practical skills, improve productivity, and invest in real self-improvement every day.\n\nUnlike traditional education platforms, SmartyMe focuses on daily learning that fits naturally into your routine. Whether you're commuting, exercising, or taking a short break, this micro learning app lets you continue learning wherever you are.\n\nThis learning app helps you develop valuable skills through structured lessons across multiple knowledge areas.\n\nPersonal Growth & Soft Skills\n\nImprove your communication and develop the soft skills that matter in real life.\n\n• Communication & Public Speaking\n• Productivity & Time Management\n• Psychology & Mindset\n\nThrough daily lessons, this learning app helps you strengthen confidence, focus, and personal effectiveness.\n\nMoney & Career Skills\n\nBuild knowledge that supports long-term success.\n\n• Personal Finance\n• Investing\n• Business Thinking\n\nSmartyMe makes complex ideas easier to understand through short micro learning lessons designed for real life.\n\nKnowledge & Culture\n\nExpand your understanding of the world while enjoying structured daily learning.\n\n• History\n• Literature\n• Philosophy\n• Art\n\nEach topic is designed to make learning engaging, practical, and accessible.\n\nScience & Life Skills\n\nStrengthen logical thinking and everyday knowledge.\n\n• Logic & Math\n• Biology\n• Wellness\n• Parenting\n\nWith this learning app, you can explore important subjects while building practical skills step by step.\n\nWhy choose SmartyMe?\n\n• Daily micro learning lessons that take just 15 minutes\n• A flexible learning app you can read or listen to anytime\n• Build real skills through structured daily learning\n• Improve productivity, communication, and mindset\n• Practical knowledge designed for everyday life\n• Learn anywhere with short, focused lessons\n\nIf you're looking for a learning app that combines micro learning, daily knowledge, and real self-improvement, SmartyMe makes growth simple and achievable.\n\nStart your daily learning journey with SmartyMe today.\n\nTerms of Use: https://www.smartymeapp.com/terms-of-use-m\n\nPrivacy Policy: https://www.smartymeapp.com/privacy-policy-m","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/38/68/e6/3868e680-441f-6811-6079-46da3e4ad530/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-11-0-85-220.png/100x100bb.png","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/micro-learning-smartyme/id6736654449?uo=2","developer":"ApexTech Ltd","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"829587759","title":"Babbel - Language Learning","store":"app_store","genre":"6017","score":0,"ratings":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"Speak a new language with confidence – get Babbel, the award-winning app built by 200+ language experts and trusted by millions worldwide.\n\nLearn a new language faster with bite-sized lessons designed to fit your everyday life. With Babbel’s proven method, you could start having real conversations in as little as 3 weeks. Your language learning adventure starts with a lesson.\n\nWHY BABBEL WORKS\n• Research-proven results Efficacy backed by researchers at Yale University: 100% improved their oral proficiency in 3 months.*\n\n• Expert-built courses Courses are created by language experts and tailored to your native language, so you learn naturally and efficiently.\n\n• Speak with confidence Improve your pronunciation and rehearse out loud with interactive conversation practice.\n\nTRUSTED BY MILLIONS\n• 25 million subscriptions sold \n• 1.5 million 5-star ratings (based on App store ratings) \n• After 10 hours with Babbel, 96% of learners saw better test scores on grammar and vocabulary**\n\nBUILT FOR REAL LIFE\n• Short, effective lessons: Learn in as little as 10 minutes a day \n• Lessons for every motivation: Learn for travel, work, or fun \n• Listen, speak, write: Options for every learning style \n• Stress-free conversation practice: Build confidence with Guided Conversations, then practice freely with Babbel Speak (Beta) \n• Smart review system: Boosts learning and retention \n• Grammar in context: Clear explanations exactly when you need them \n• Offline mode: Download lessons and learn anywhere, anytime \n• 5,000+ courses: Over 60,000 lessons across all languages\n\nLEARN 14 LANGUAGES\nSpanish (Latin American or Spain), French, Italian, German, Portuguese, English (American or British), Russian, Polish, Turkish, Norwegian, Danish, Swedish, Dutch, and Indonesian.\n\nTRY BABBEL TODAY\nDownload Babbel now and take a free lesson.\n\nSUBSCRIPTION DETAILS\nA subscription is required to access full courses for one language. Subscriptions renew automatically unless canceled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. Payment will be charged to your Apple account.\n\nAvailable plans: \n• 1 month \n• 3 months \n• 6 months \n• 12 months\n\nPrivacy policy: https://about.babbel.com/en/privacy/ Terms of use: https://about.babbel.com/en/terms/\n\nLEARN MORE\nRead Babbel Magazine for tips and insights: https://www.babbel.com/en/magazine\n\nFollow us: Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/babbelusa Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Babbel.usa\n\nCONTACT US\nQuestions or feedback? Email: support-mobile@babbel.com\n\n*Based on a study conducted with Babbel users learning Spanish. Available at http://bit.ly/BabbelYale. \n**Based on a study conducted with Babbel users learning Spanish. Available: http://bit.ly/BabbelMSU.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/62/9a/90/629a904c-b885-f25c-efdc-c44f12716902/AppIcon-Default-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-0-0-85-220.png/100x100bb.png","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/babbel-language-learning/id829587759?uo=2","developer":"Babbel GmbH","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1624701477","title":"Praktika – AI Language Tutor","store":"app_store","genre":"6017","score":0,"ratings":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"Ready to immerse yourself in a groundbreaking English, Spanish, Japanese, Korean, French, Portuguese, Portuguese (Brazilian), Italian and German learning experience?\n\nDive into Praktika and meet your ultra-realistic AI Avatars — your personal language companions for mastering real-world conversation.\n\nPraktika’s avatars aren’t just digital characters — they’re designed with full backstories, cultural depth, and natural accents (American, British, Latin American, and more) to simulate truly human-like interaction. Every session with your avatar feels like speaking with a real person who listens, guides, and helps you grow.\n\nWhat Makes Praktika Different?\nUnlike other language apps that rely on memorization and repetition, Praktika makes language acquisition feel natural. You don’t just study — you engage in conversation. You listen, speak, and respond like you would in real life. Our avatars give you space to practice without fear of judgment or awkward exchanges.\n\nWe’ve also added Multimodality, a next-gen learning tool that lets you upload and interact with real content. Share photos, audio, videos, or documents to spark conversations or receive corrections. Use an image of your surroundings to practice vocabulary, or upload your resume to get instant pronunciation coaching on job interviews. It’s the closest thing to having a real tutor with you 24/7.\n\nSimple Pricing\nPraktika is free to download, and getting started is easy. Unlock powerful speaking tools, advanced feedback, and avatar-led lessons — all for less than the cost of a single tutoring session.\n\nWhat You’ll Get:\nAI Avatars – Learn through human-like conversations with avatars that adapt to your tone, pace, and goals.\nCourses for All Levels – 1000+ lessons including academic prep (IELTS, TOEFL), lifestyle, travel, career paths, and slang.\nPractical Conversation Topics – Role-play as a sports commentator, startup founder, or tourist.\nMultimodal Learning – Upload photos, PDFs, and voice notes for personalized lessons.\nFluency Tracking – See real progress with speaking metrics, streaks, and in-app challenges.\nLocalized Avatars – Select coaches from different regions to match your cultural or accent goals.\n\nMeet a Few of Our Avatars\nAlisha – Friendly U.S. English tutor, Stanford grad, inclusive and motivating.\nAlejandro – Spanish-English tutor from Barcelona, sporty and approachable.\nMarco – American news editor, great for professional tone and interview prep.\nCharlie – British culture lover, witty and sharp.\nValentina – Mexican Spanish tutor, loves music, dance, and warm conversations.\nLucía – Soft-spoken Spain-based tutor, perfect for literary and academic tone.\n\nSample Topics\nIELTS & TOEFL • Architecture • Art • Business • Car Brands • Cinema • Cuisine • Economic Growth • Education • Environmental Issues • Festivals • Film • Food • Football • Geography • Health • History • Immigration • Influencers • Literature • Music • Natural Wonders • Pop Culture • Relationships • Startups • Science • Shopping • Street Art • Technology • TV Shows • Tourism • UFC • Wildlife... and many more added monthly.\n\nLanguages Available\nEnglish\nKorean\nJapanese\nSpanish\nFrench\nPortuguese\nPortuguese (Brazilian)\nItalian\nGerman\n\nWhy Learners Love Praktika\nRealistic AI avatars for immersive practice\nPersonalized pronunciation and fluency feedback\nMultimodal learning with photo, video, and audio uploads\nCourses for all levels and goals\nReal progress tracking and fluency insights\n\nPraktika is on a mission to break language barriers for the next billion learners. With the power of AI, personalization, and multimodal tools, we believe anyone can develop fluency through real-world conversation. It’s more than just learning — it’s transformation. Download Praktika today and start your journey to confident, fluent communication.\n\nSupport: support@praktika.ai\nTerms: https://praktika.ai/terms\nPrivacy: https://praktika.ai/privacy","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/c8/37/56/c8375665-8df5-2bd3-b774-a9f1ea600742/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-11-0-85-220.png/100x100bb.png","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/praktika-ai-language-tutor/id1624701477?uo=2","developer":"Praktika.ai Company","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6744358897","title":"LangLearn: AI English Tutor","store":"app_store","genre":"6017","score":0,"ratings":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"Break Language Barriers with AI—Learn Language Anytime, Anywhere!\nLangLearn is your personalized AI language companion. It adapts to your level, goals, and busy life. Whether you're a beginner, a professional, or a traveler, LangLearn helps you speak English and Spanish fluently with speaking practice, grammar, vocabulary, and real-world immersion in quick, fun lessons.\n\n◆ For Every Level: Tailored Learning Paths ◆\n-Beginners: Start with the Basics!\n*Learn essential greetings, basic grammar (e.g., \"I am/he is\"), vocabulary and survival phrases for travel with AI.\n*Build confidence by practicing with AI in real-life situations like ordering food or asking for directions.\n-Intermediate Learners: Think Deeper, Speak Smoother!\n*Have debates, tell stories, or roleplay workplace meetings with AI.\n*Improve grammar and vocabulary by correcting mistakes with tailored feedback (e.g., \"If I were...\" vs. \"If I was...\").\n-Advanced Speakers: Perfect Your Edge!\n*Master idioms, refine writing, or focus on accent reduction.\n*Tackle expert scenarios like negotiating, giving TED talks, or analyzing news and vocabulary with AI.\n\n◆ For Every Scenario: Learn Exactly What You Need, Right When You Need It ◆\n-Traveler Mode: Master travel Language—practice airport conversations, hotel check-ins, directions, and cultural tips for a smooth trip.\n-Career Mode: Improve professional Terms. Practice job interviews, listening, write emails, and give presentations with confidence. Get feedback with prompts like “Pitch your idea to an AI CEO.”\n-Exam Mode: Ace language tests like TOEFL and IELTS. Take timed listening and speaking simulations with AI scoring to know exactly where to improve.\n-Daily Life Mode: Practice everyday phrase. Chat about hobbies, movies, tech trends, or anything you enjoy—make learning fun and easy!\n\n\n◆ Learn in 10 Minutes a Day ◆\nShort on time? No problem! LangLearn fits into your everyday life, helping you improve your spoken language no matter where you are.\n-During Your Commute: Turn traffic or transit time into productive practice with hands-free AI lessons for real-life conversations.\n-While Getting Ready: Use your morning or evening routine to listen to short lessons or practice phrases aloud, building fluency with the AI.\n-Before Bed: Let AI summarize your day’s learning in minutes, highlighting your strengths, new vocabulary, and areas to improve, so you’re ready for the next day.\n\n\n◆ Your Personal AI Language Coach: Patient, Intelligent, and Always There for You ◆\n-Real-Time Speech Feedback: Speak with confidence! Get instant, precise analysis on your pronunciation, intonation, and fluency—like “Your ‘th’ sounds a bit like ‘d’—let’s practice together!” Receive practical tips that really make a difference.\n-Personalized Challenges: Say goodbye to one-size-fits-all. Your AI coach continuously tracks your progress and adapts lesson difficulty—so you’re always challenged, but never overwhelmed or bored.\nEncouragement & Emotional Support: Feeling stuck or stressed? Your AI coach notices and offers uplifting words and mindful tips. Learn at your own pace, with kind support every step of the way.\n\n================================\n\nSubscription terms:\nUnlock unlimited access to everything in the app and take your spoken language to the next level\nApp Store offers auto-renewing subscriptions with unlimited access. Your subscription will automatically renew at the end of each subscription term unless you turn off the auto-renewal in your iPhone Settings, at least 24 hours before the current period ends.\n\n================================\n\nHave questions or feedback about LangLearn? We’re here to help!\nFeel free to reach out to us at langlearn08@gmail.com — we’d love to hear from you.\nPrivacy Policy: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1Gm-6qZNcbzfIM3fMfXlL96Yh21vVNekcrC60TRubtv8/edit?usp=sharing\nTerms and Conditions: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1zx1O3PCJzIazkmOaXYmLvUVUASmpsINMMAGw72f020M/edit?usp=sharing","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/80/24/81/80248194-7d71-d536-a1c3-7b50efd465e5/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-11-0-85-220.png/100x100bb.png","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/langlearn-ai-english-tutor/id6744358897?uo=2","developer":"AIFLAME TECHNOLOGY PTE. LTD.","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6738882620","title":"Language Learning: Pingo AI","store":"app_store","genre":"6017","score":0,"ratings":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"Learn a new language through real conversations with Pingo, your AI speaking companion. Loved by 3,000,000+ users, Pingo uses the most advanced AI built for language learning so you can have real-life conversations, get instant feedback, and learn words you’ll actually use.\n\nSpeak to Pingo as you would a friend. Want to practice ordering at a café in Paris? Debate politics in Spanish? Or chat about K-dramas in Korean? Talk about your day, ask questions, and explore the language together. Practice speaking from 25+ languages to refine your vocabulary, become fluent, and speak confidently.\n\nLearn 25+ languages: English, Spanish, French, German, Japanese, Korean, Italian, Chinese, Portuguese, Russian, Arabic, Dutch, Turkish, Polish, Vietnamese, Hindi, Thai, Hebrew, Greek, Indonesian, Swedish, Norwegian, Danish, Persian, and Ukrainian.\n\nHow to use Pingo AI*\n1) Create or choose from engaging, real-life conversation scenarios.\n\n2) Talk with an ultra-realistic AI that feels like a native speaker, adapting to your pace and skill level.\n\n3) Receive actionable feedback and tips for improvement on grammar, fluency, vocabulary, engagement, and relevance for every conversation.\n\n4) Use Tutor Mode for guided practice and review useful words to reinforce learning.\n\n5) Get fluent faster and build lasting language confidence.\n\nPingo AI transforms self-guided practice into a goal-oriented, interactive learning experience that’s far more effective than simply repeating basic phrases aloud or struggling to find opportunities for real-life conversations.\n\nDitch static, repetitive modules and boring lessons. At Pingo AI, we’re building the most dynamic and immersive AI language learning experience ever to help you reach your language goals as fast as possible.\n\nIf you have any ideas or questions, please email us at support@pingo.ai.\n\n*All conversations require a subscription\nTerms: https://pingo.ai/terms\nPrivacy Policy: https://pingo.ai/privacy","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/18/50/40/18504091-735f-8a0e-b8e3-a816b3221452/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-85-220.png/100x100bb.png","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/language-learning-pingo-ai/id6738882620?uo=2","developer":"Pingo AI, Inc.","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"557130558","title":"HelloTalk - Language Learning","store":"app_store","genre":"6017","score":0,"ratings":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"Practice languages with native speakers on HelloTalk! We recently introduced HelloTalk Live and Voiceroom - interactive language and culture events to help you master languages through the content you love!  \n \nHelloTalk, the original language exchange app, connects you with native speakers to practice languages (English, Japanese, Korean, Spanish, French, Mandarin Chinese, Portuguese, German, Italian, Russian, Arabic, Turkish, Hindi, Indonesian, Thai, Vietnamese and 260+ more) for FREE!  \n\nHelloTalk equips you with learning tools such as translation and instant captions so you can learn by chatting with native speakers. Learn languages from locals around the world through livestreams and Voicerooms. Connect with expert hosts to discuss interesting topics with language partners in the learning community! \n\nWhy HelloTalk? \n\n► Real language learning atmosphere \nWhether you're focused on a widely spoken language or a less common one, HelloTalk caters to your needs. The system smartly matches you based on your native language and proficiency, while allowing you to filter ideal language partners according to various criteria such as age, location, and gender. Plus, with built-in translation and transliteration tools, you can communicate confidently without any language barriers.\n\n► A powerful tool for sharpening your language skills\nAcquiring new words through conversations with native speakers is more effective than rigid memorization. Whether you're a student preparing for exams like the CET, GRE, TOEFL, IELTS, planning to study abroad, or a professional seeking career advancement through language skills, HelloTalk offers native speakers who match your proficiency level for engaging interactions and valuable learning experiences.\n\n► Immersive multi-person language chat rooms\nIf you choose to learn Spanish, for example, every Voiceroom you enter on HelloTalk gathers Spanish learners and Spanish native speakers from around the world to discuss interesting topics. Here, only your voice needs to be heard, creating a comfortable, introvert-friendly atmosphere. Here, sharing mutual interests allows everyone to freely express themselves and share personal experiences, fostering both language intuition and authentic expression skills. It's incredibly addictive!\n\n► Diverse global Livestreams\nHelloTalk features handpicked foreign language hosts who offer online video lessons, share language insights, and provide glimpses into their lives abroad. You can even join them on stage for one-on-one video conversations with fellow language learners. Whether you're grappling with pronunciation, speaking speed, or shyness, these hosts will assist you in refining your language skills and guiding the conversation. For rapid improvement in spoken language, there's no substitute for direct communication with native speakers!\n\n► International Moments\nHelloTalk's Moments offers real-time posts covering learning, lifestyle, and cultural insights from around the world. It's your ticket to discovering fresh perspectives and gaining deeper insights into diverse cultural customs, all from the comfort of your home. Don't forget to engage with posts that catch your interest!\n\nWhat the world is saying about HelloTalk\n“One of the best apps to help you learn a new language.” - 9to5Mac \n\"When you're ready to experiment with a foreign language, HelloTalk provides an excellent opportunity for interaction with other speakers.\" –PCMag \n\"HelloTalk, which connects native speakers with an apprentice, also offers language exchanges to its 20 million users in more than 150 languages.\" -Forbes \n\nSTART PRACTICING LANGUAGES RIGHT AWAY!!!\n\nLearn more about the HelloTalk app: \n- Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Hellotalk/ \n- Twitter: https://twitter.com/hellotalkapp \n\nSend any feedback to support@hellotalk.com \n- Privacy Policy: https://www.hellotalk.com/privacy-policy \n- Terms of Use: https://www.hellotalk.com/terms-of-service","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/7e/38/7f/7e387f11-d551-8675-3b97-a0f2d0812c24/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-0-0-85-220.png/100x100bb.png","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/hellotalk-language-learning/id557130558?uo=2","developer":"HELLOTALK FOREIGN LANGUAGE EXCHANGE LEARNING TALK CHAT APP","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1352790442","title":"Preply: Language lessons","store":"app_store","genre":"6017","score":0,"ratings":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"Preply: Learn Languages with Real Tutors - Anytime, Anywhere\n\nLooking for the best way to learn a new language? Preply is more than just another language learning app: It’s a complete online learning platform and app that connects you with thousands of professional tutors for live, personalized classes. Unlike gamified apps that rely only on repetitive exercises, Preply gives you the flexibility of self-study combined with the structure, accountability, and human connection of real teachers.\n\nWith the Preply app, you can:\n• Learn on the go - Book and attend lessons from anywhere, right from your phone.\n• Access thousands of expert tutors - Choose teachers based on price, ratings, availability, or specialization.\n• Practice real conversations - Build confidence by speaking with a live tutor instead of memorizing phrases.\n• Flexible scheduling - Book lessons that fit your lifestyle, whether daily practice or weekly study.\n• Study over 90 languages - English, Spanish, French, German, Italian, Japanese, Chinese, Arabic, and more.\n• Track your progress - Follow your learning journey with clear goals and personalized feedback.\n\nWhy Preply?\nMost language apps stop at vocabulary drills or gamified practice. Preply takes you further by connecting you with real people who adapt lessons to your goals. Want to prepare for exams? Boost your career opportunities? Improve pronunciation? Preply tutors customize your learning path, so every lesson gets you closer to fluency.\n\nKey Benefits of the Preply App\n• Structured alternative to gamified apps: Skip endless exercises and focus on meaningful progress.\n• Personalized learning: Lessons tailored to your level, learning style, and objectives.\n• Affordable options: Tutors for every budget, with transparent pricing and secure payment.\n• Convenient experience: Same great Preply platform, optimized for mobile so you can learn anytime.\n• Trusted by learners worldwide: Millions of students already use Preply to achieve their language goals.\n\nHow It Works\n• Download the Preply app.\n• Choose your tutor: Filter by language, specialty, budget, or availability.\n• Book your first lesson: Flexible scheduling makes it easy.\n• Learn & track progress: Stay motivated with real results and ongoing support.\n\nWhether you’re a beginner or advanced learner, preparing for exams, traveling abroad, or building a global career, Preply helps you succeed. With Preply, you’re not just downloading an app, you’re joining a global learning platform built to support your growth. \n\nLearn languages your way, with the flexibility of an app and the reliability of real classes. \n\nStart your language journey today. Download Preply and discover why it’s the best app for live tutoring, online language classes, and personalized learning.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/d3/69/e4/d369e4d3-f4a8-b0de-8d48-fb123e092b68/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-sRGB-85-220.png/100x100bb.png","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/preply-language-lessons/id1352790442?uo=2","developer":"Preply Inc.","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6446930976","title":"Solvely - AI Study Companion","store":"app_store","genre":"6017","score":0,"ratings":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"Kick off the new semester with confidence: Solvely offers advanced, high-accuracy AI study support trusted by over 5M students worldwide. Multiple AI models work together to cross-check each answer, providing reliable 24/7 help for all subjects at any level.\n\nKey Features:\n► ACCURATE AI ANSWERS\nSolvely provides clear, step-by-step explanations with the reasoning behind each solution. Each answer is checked by multiple AI models to improve accuracy and reduce mistakes.\n\n► PHOTO TO ANSWER\nTake a photo of a problem from a textbook, worksheet, notebook, or whiteboard and receive a detailed breakdown in seconds. This turns stuck moments into clear, learnable steps.\n\n► ALL SUBJECTS\nSupport is available across Math, Biology, Chemistry, Physics, Statistics, and more. Solvely helps you keep up in class, prepare for tests, and review key concepts at your own pace.\n\n► MATCHES YOUR LEVEL\nSolvely adapts to your level, from middle school to college and beyond. Explanations are adjusted to your background to fill knowledge gaps and build long-term understanding.\n\n►  SMART AI NOTE TAKER\nLet smart AI Note do the heavy lifting by transcribing content and extracting key takeaways, so you can stay focused—even when the professor moves fast. Turn notes into instant quizzes, flashcards, and a podcast-style recap, and import almost any format—YouTube videos, PDFs, slides, web pages, recordings, and more—to convert content into study-ready materials in seconds.\n\n► ALL-IN-ONE STUDY APP\nSolvely includes Smart Reader, Writing Assistant, AI Note-Taking, Focus Mode, and Calculator in one app. This setup helps you manage assignments, stay organized, and support your overall academic performance.\n\n► SYNC ACROSS DEVICES\nStudy progress, notes, and solutions stay synced across iPhone and iPad. You can move between home, campus, and anywhere else without losing your place.\n\n► SUBJECTS WE COVER\n• Mathematics (Elementary to Advanced)\n• Sciences (Physics, Chemistry, Biology)\n• Humanities (English, Literature, History)\n• Test Prep (SAT®, ACT®, AP®, GRE®)\n• Others\n\n► MATH & SCIENCE TOOLS\nSolvely makes math and science study faster and less stressful. Snap homework or practice problems and get accurate, step-by-step support you can follow. Built-in tools like an algebra calculator and a statistics calculator help with everything from everyday exercises to advanced topics. Need help beyond math? Solvely can also support chemistry and other science questions—so you can keep moving anytime, 24/7.\n\n► SIMILAR APPS YOU MAY KNOW\nIf you have tried apps like Socratic, Mathway, Microsoft Math Solver, or Photomath, you will find that Solvely follows the same simple “snap and solve” flow while focusing more on clear, step-by-step explanations and deeper understanding.\n\n► STUDY IMPACT\nMany students report a clearer understanding and better academic performance after studying with Solvely. Millions of learners use Solvely to build stronger, more consistent study habits.\n\n► With Solvely UNLIMITED, you will get:\n• Unlimited, in-depth explanations\n• More advanced problem-solving capabilities\n• Interactive learning support\n• AI-powered lecture notes\n• Expanded practice materials\n• Priority support when you need help\n\n► STAY CONNECTED\n• Official Website: https://solvely.ai\n• TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@solvely.ai\n• Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/solvely.ai/\n\nFEEDBACK AND SUPPORT\n• Email: support@solvely.ai\n• Terms of Service: https://solvely.ai/term\n• Privacy Policy: https://solvely.ai/privacy-policy\nFor last-minute help or everyday study support, download Solvely and get AI-powered solutions in seconds.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/d4/f0/31/d4f031de-3643-d90b-c06f-65b550fc799d/solvely-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-0-85-220.png/100x100bb.png","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/solvely-ai-study-companion/id6446930976?uo=2","developer":"Aignite Inc.","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1546796934","title":"Rock Identifier: Stone ID","store":"app_store","genre":"6017","score":0,"ratings":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"Rock Identifier is an all-in-one stone, crystal, mineral, and gemstone identifier. Simply take or upload a photo of a rock or crystal, and the app will tell you all about it in seconds. \n\nWant to know the name of a stone you discovered in your rock hounding? Are you curious about the different properties of each stone and crystal you own? Looking to learn about rock and crystal knowledge? Don't miss this powerful stone identifier and crystal guidebook. We will satisfy all your needs!\n\nRock & Mineral & Crystal Identifier\nTake a photo of any crystals or gemstones and get an instant accurate identification. This rock scanner app can recognize over 6,000 types of rocks and minerals and helps anyone who wants to identify, examine and explore the characteristics of stones.\n\nStone & Crystal Encyclopedia\nIn each of the identification results, the Rock Identifier app provides detailed stone/crystal information which includes: Name, Chemical Formula, Hardness, Colour Variations, and the main locations it can be found. \nNo matter whether you are a beginner rock hound who is trying to identify the stones you discovered or an experienced crystal collector who wants to expand your geological knowledge, Rock Identifier offers the easiest and most comprehensive rock guide.\n\nReal VS Fake Gemstone\nThis app delivers detailed and practical gemstone identification method articles, where users can learn to identify if a gemstone or crystal is real by its Color, Cleavage and Fracture, Touch, Shape, Transparency, and the like. \n\nExplore Trendy Stones\nInterested in the healing properties of any crystals? Want to know what gemstones to have for your specific zodiac sign? Download this rock scanner app to find out the mysterious healing power of crystals, and learn more facts about zodiac stones, birthstones, and so much more.\n\nMetal Detector\nLost your key and have no idea how to find it? With the in-app Metal Detector function, Rock Identifier can help you locate your lost key by measuring the surrounding magnetic field strength. Never worry about losing metal objects again!\n\nOne-on-one Consultation with Rock Expert\nThis scanner app not only provides you with lively, professional knowledge of mineralogy and petrology but also offers an email service for one-on-one inquiry help.\n\nUnique Rock Collections\nDisplay all your stone and mineral collectibles with the Collection function; add desirable crystals and gemstones to your wishlist. The app will also automatically keep your ID record so that you can go back to find them.\n\nRock Identifier was created to help more people explore and learn about the geological surroundings around them.\nDownload the app today to enjoy a more pleasant stone & crystal journey and train yourself to be a rock expert!\n\nAbout Rock Identifier Premium:\n\n-Subscription Name: Yearly Premium\n-Subscription Duration:1 year(7 days trial)\n-Subscription Description: Users will get a 1-year Rock Identifier Premium which includes identifying rocks without limits, studying rocks with numerous info, and no watermarks or ads.\n• Payment will be charged to iTunes Account at confirmation of purchase\n• Subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current period\n• The account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period, and identify the cost of the renewal\n• Any unused portion of a free trial period, if offered, will be forfeited when the user purchases a subscription to that publication, where applicable\n• Subscriptions may be managed by the user and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the user's Account Settings after purchase\n\nTerms of Use: https://app-service.rockidentifier.com/static/user_agreement.html\nPrivacy Policy: https://app-service.rockidentifier.com/static/privacy_policy.html\n\nContact us:\nsupport@rockidentifier.com\nFind out more about Picture Rock at:\nhttps://www.rockidentifier.com/","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/07/76/15/0776159b-4195-790c-5406-8d8b5b81cccb/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-8-0-85-220.png/100x100bb.png","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/rock-identifier-stone-id/id1546796934?uo=2","developer":"Next Vision Limited","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"379968583","title":"Busuu: Language Learning","store":"app_store","genre":"6017","score":0,"ratings":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"Busuu helps you communicate with confidence from day one. Combine expertly designed language lessons with feedback and tips from our global community of native speakers and harness the power of learning together. \n\nLooking for the best way to learn a new language on your phone? You’ve just discovered it, with Busuu, a Chegg service – we’re the app that makes learning new languages easier, more fun and more effective for all.\n\nWhether you’re learning to get confident having new conversations, for a higher grade, a career boost, or for mind-blowing travel experiences, Busuu’s got your back.\n\nWe’re already helping millions of people overcome their learning struggles, from lack of time and motivation to problems with grammar and vocab. We help our learners achieve their goals, one milestone at a time – and we want to do the same for you.\n\nDOWNLOAD THE APP NOW FOR FREE LANGUAGE LEARNING\n\n================\n\nHow are we doing this? We’re glad you asked. Whether you’re learning on your iPad or iPhone, Busuu helps you…\n\n– Learn up to 14 languages\nThat’s right, 14! We’ve got complete courses in English, French, Spanish, Italian, German, Chinese, Korean, Japanese, Portuguese (Brazilian), Polish, Russian, Arabic, Dutch or Turkish with Busuu. \n\n– Master languages with real people\nYou want to learn the relevant language, right? You’re in luck: we’ll connect you with our community of native speakers so you can get localized language knowledge and support. Feel even better when you help other learners in return.\n\n– Learn from the experts\nBusuu’s online courses are created by our ingenious language experts. Learn step-by-step with bite-sized lessons, plenty of practice and lots of opportunities to test your progress.\n\n– Say hello to useful language skills\nLearn the language that will really take you places! With regularly updated content, video flashcards featuring real people and useful cultural tips, you’ll be fully immersed in no time. \n\n– Kiss goodbye to stressful timetabling\nWe’re serious. We organize your learning time for you with a personalized Study Plan. Simply tell us when you want to study and for how long, and we’ll send you notifications to keep you on track.\n\n– Revise with ease\nThere’ll be no forgetting on our watch. Smart Review cleverly saves all the grammar and vocab you learn in lessons and stores them in one handy place, so you can make those tricky words and rules stick.\n\n– Show off achievements with official certificates\nWith our Busuu language certificates, you’ll have actual proof of your language capabilities.\n\n– Access specialized courses for language lovers\nYou’ve learned the basics, and now you’re hungry for more. Learn about manga, advance your pronunciation or add travel-specific phrases to your skillset, plus much more. \n\n================\n\nDON’T JUST TAKE OUR WORD FOR IT.\nSee what others have to say about Busuu:\n\n● EDITOR RATING: EXCELLENT - PC MAG\n● Named 'Best Buy' language learning app by the Independent in 2021\n● Language Learning App of the Year at the EdTech Breakthrough Awards 2020 \n\n\n================\n\nPLEASE NOTE\nA lot of the features are free, but you will need a subscription in order to get access to all features of this app. Your subscription will automatically renew unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current payment period. Your iTunes account will be automatically charged at the same price for renewal within the 24-hour period prior to the end of the current payment period unless you change your subscription preferences in your Account Settings.\nYou can manage your subscriptions through your Account Settings after purchase.\nPrivacy policy: https://www.busuu.com/en/privacy/\nTerms of Service: https://www.busuu.com/en/terms/","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/e2/ea/d0/e2ead0bf-df0e-910d-45ea-3f462d1af66f/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-8-0-sRGB-0-0-85-220.png/100x100bb.png","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/busuu-language-learning/id379968583?uo=2","developer":"Busuu Limited","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1527399597","title":"PlantIn: Plant Identifier・Care","store":"app_store","genre":"6017","score":0,"ratings":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"PlantIn is always there for you!\nWith our care plans, you will learn how to identify a plant, how often to water your trees, or why the leaf on your flower turned brown.\n\nWe have a wide variety of features that every green thumb would fall in love with: \n\n► Watering Calculator\n\nThis feature will help to figure out the right amount of water your green pet needs. You just need to answer several questions regarding your plant’s conditions, and voila! \n\n► Light Meter\n\nHere is another helpful tool that calculates the correct lighting level for your greens! Just click the Light Meter button and point the camera at the plant. Our AR-based technology will automatically scan the nearest environment, measure the amount of light, and tell if you need to move the plant to a brighter or shadier spot. \n\n► Care Plans\n\nPlantkeeping will become even more effortless with our Personalized Care Plans. Request a plan for almost any species, from common houseplants to exotic cultivars. Your Snake plant care needs some improvements, or maybe you just got your first air plant and are not sure what to do with it? Get thorough watering, fertilization, lighting, and even pruning instructions easily and make ‘em grow!\n\n► Care Notifications\n\nOur users say that our plant care app helps with organizing daily routines! Keep calm – we will send your reminders to make sure that all your green pets are following their watering and fertilization schedules. Moreover, there are special weather notifications so that you will be warned in case of storms, freezing temperatures, and other unfavorable conditions that may harm your outdoor oasis.\n \n► Ask the Botanist\n\nUse this feature to get a consultation with our experienced gardening experts. Ask any questions regarding houseplant care and get custom recommendations, step-by-step guides, useful hints, and detailed instructions for your particular case.\n\nLast but not least, we are happy to present our latest update: \n\n► Mushroom Identification\n\nOur fresh mushroom identifier will become a fav feature for every single shroom hunter! While designed to identify fungi online in several taps, we have implemented a technology for offline id: no more hesitation while outdoors in lush woods. Identify edible mushrooms for delicious dinners, learn new fungi species, and use our feature to detect poisonous specimens.\n\nPlantIn was created to provide loving care for each of your green pets, so let’s make this world greener and educate ourselves on botany together! Stay plantuned for more lifesaving info from our plant care app.\n\nPrivacy Policy: https://legal.myplantin.com/vortemol/privacy_policy.html\nTerms of Use: https://legal.myplantin.com/vortemol/terms_and_conditions.html","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/69/fb/88/69fb888b-6dbe-7e41-b688-6ff56e4ff356/AppIconGlass-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-0-sRGB-85-220.png/100x100bb.png","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/plantin-plant-identifier-care/id1527399597?uo=2","developer":"Vortemol Limited","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"959883039","title":"Yousician: Learn & Play Guitar","store":"app_store","genre":"6017","score":0,"ratings":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"YOUSICIAN is the fast, fun way to learn, play and master the Guitar, Bass or Singing/Vocals. Yousicians around the world can master their instruments or learn to sing thousands of songs in a fun and easy way!\n\nYousician is your personal music teacher. Tune your strings, warm up your voice, and learn with interactive guitar and singing lessons that teach as you play. Start playing and get instant feedback so you make sure to hit the right chords and notes.\n\nMusicians of all levels can learn and improve from complete beginners to professionals. Jump into step-by-step videos that let you learn at your own pace. Nail each bass and guitar chord, track your progress and stay motivated. Refine your vocals with singing lessons packed with instructions that make practicing simple and enjoyable.\n\nSo grab your guitar or bass, and prepare those vocal chords. It’s time to make music!\n\nWHO IS YOUSICIAN FOR?\n• Guitarists, Bass players & Singers\n• Complete beginners\n• Self-learners\n• Advanced & professional musicians\n• Music teachers\n\nYOUSICIAN FEATURES\n\nLEARN GUITAR & BASS SEAMLESSLY\n- Learn to play chords with step-by-step tutorials\n- Learn sheet music, guitar chord finger placement, proper strumming, melodies, lead, and fingerpicking\n- Master your instrument with a fun, interactive music teacher\n- Yousician even has a guitar tuner so you can start your lesson off right and join countless musicians\n- Our gamified learning makes playing instruments fun\n\nLEARN TO SING EASILY\n- Our virtual vocal coach listens as you practice\n- Refine your vocals in singing lessons with instant feedback\n- Learn to sing and discover your singing potential\n\nLESSONS FOR EVERY MUSICIAN\n- Explore bass, guitar, and singing lessons\n- Get over 10,000 lessons, exercises and songs by artists you love\n- Guitar chord progressions and music theory for every skill level\n\nStart your free trial today and experience all we have to offer!\n\nPREMIUM SUBSCRIPTION\nSubscribe for unlimited and uninterrupted playtime across all platforms. Subscriptions are annual and monthly. Prices may vary in different countries. Payment will be charged to iTunes Account. Subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. Account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours prior to the end of the current period. Subscriptions may be managed by the user and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the user’s iTunes Account Settings. Any unused portion of a free trial period will be forfeited when the user purchases a subscription.\n\nWHAT PEOPLE ARE SAYING ABOUT YOUSICIAN\n“Yousician is modern technology's gift to music education. It’s an app that teaches you to master the guitar instead of a plastic game controller.” - Guitar World\n\n“Yousician is a fabulous place to start learning piano, guitar, ukulele or bass. Yousician teaches basic playing techniques and musical notation by presenting a challenge and then listening as you try to play in real life.” - New York Times\n\nABOUT YOUSICIAN\nYousician is the world’s leading platform to learn and play music. With a combined 20 million monthly users across our award-winning apps, we’re on a mission to make musicality as common as literacy.\n\nCheck out our other apps:\n• GuitarTuna, the #1 guitar tuner app worldwide\n• Ukulele by Yousician\n• Piano by Yousician\n\nGot ideas to make Yousician even better? Simply send your ideas and suggestions to: feedback.yousician.com\n• https://yousician.com/privacy-notice\n• https://yousician.com/terms-of-service","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/41/22/23/4122231f-8215-94e5-10d5-1715313576fb/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-8-0-85-220.png/100x100bb.png","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/yousician-learn-play-guitar/id959883039?uo=2","developer":"Yousician Ltd","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1563340662","title":"DMV Practice Test - 2026","store":"app_store","genre":"6017","score":0,"ratings":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"\"DMV Practice Test\" test your knowledge with +1000 DMV practice questions and detailed explanations!\n\nWe have designed this practice tool to make learning process super easy and interesting. It’s proven fact that learning new things in proper way helps you remember things quickly and for long-term!\n\n- Prepare to take the written driver's license exam by taking sample tests.\n- State specific practice tests for your state.\n- Test are divided in proper sections to prepare well.\n- Question loads with correct answer and explanation.\n- Similar to real exam simulator.\n- Learn all road signs and their meanings.\n\nThis app contains DMV written tests for the following states:\n\nAlabama DPS, Alaska DMV, Arizona MVD, Arkansas OMV, California DMV, Colorado DMV, Connecticut DMV, District of Columbia DMV, Delaware DMV, Florida DHSMV, Georgia DDS, Hawaii DMV, Idaho DMV, Illinois SOS, Indiana BMV, Iowa DMV, Kansas DMV, Kentucky DMV, Louisiana OMV, Maine BMV, Maryland MVA, Massachusetts RMV, Michigan SOS, Minnesota DVS, Mississippi DMV, Missouri DOR, Montana MVD,Nebraska DMV,Nevada DMV,New Hampshire DMV, New Jersey MVC, New Mexico MVD, New York DMV, North Carolina DMV, North Dakota NDDOT, Ohio BMV, Oklahoma DPS, Oregon DMV, Pennsylvania DMV, Rhode Island DMV, South Carolina DMV, South Dakota DMV, Tennessee DOS, Texas DMV, Utah DMV, Vermont DMV, Virginia DMV, Washington DOL, West Virginia DMV, Wisconsin DMV, Wyoming DOT","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/51/6e/ff/516eff4d-3926-ba2c-a0e6-c8d58ec2d6b9/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-11-0-0-85-220.png/100x100bb.png","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/dmv-practice-test-2026/id1563340662?uo=2","developer":"Minh Pham","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1457185832","title":"Headway - Daily Micro Learning","store":"app_store","genre":"6017","score":0,"ratings":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"Meet Headway — #1 most downloaded book summary app! We summarize key ideas from the world’s nonfiction bestsellers so you can get essential knowledge to crush your goals. \n\nMore than 50 million people have already joined the Headway community to become the best versions of themselves. How about hopping along on this self-growth journey?\n———————\n\nWHAT YOU GET WITH HEADWAY\n\n* 1700+ book summaries to change your life\nLearn the main ideas from any nonfiction bestseller in less than 15 minutes. Whether you want to listen or read, we have you covered with concise summaries on any topic. \n\n* Daily microlearning session\nStart your day by tapping through a portion of bite-sized ideas. It’s the best way to build your routine around fun and easy growth!\n\n* Self-growth challenges\nBoost your life areas and skills with our challenges on Success, Wealth, Healthy Relationships, Modern Parenting, Self-Confidence, Emotional Intelligence, and more.\n\n* Highly personalized approach\nWe pick every piece of bite-sized content according to your goals and needs. Enjoy your fun and fully customized journey to the top.\n\n* Only proven sources of ideas\nWe pick titles from reputable lists like The New York Times Bestsellers and Amazon Bestsellers to deliver the highest quality of ideas.\n\n* Quality of summaries\nOur professional writers & editors polish every key idea in our hand-crafted content to create the best learning experience.\n\n* Spaced Repetition feature\nThis recall technique helps turn your favorite insights into flashcards and go through them whenever you want. It’s also an excellent tool for those learning English, as you can turn any unknown word into a flashcard and quickly memorize it. \n\n* Widgets\nNow inspiration is always in your pocket and speaks to you every time you unlock your phone. We choose the best quotes and insights for Headway widgets to keep you motivated every second. \n\n———————\nWHAT 50M+ USERS HIGHLIGHT\n* Inspiring & motivating\n* Huge library of book summaries\n* Easy to read & listen\n* Would recommend\n———————\n\nWHAT MEDIA SAY ABOUT US\n\n“Headway is a bite-sized learning app for those who strive to grow. Helping users worldwide to become happier and more confident, their subscription-based service is designed to be worked into a busy schedule.”— Daily Mail\n\n“Professional writers and editors of the Headway team up with the best voice actors, moderators, and other team members to deliver an experience that is unmatchable in terms of quality.” — Mobile App Daily\n\n“Whether you’re taking a 15 minutes break, commuting to and from the workplace, or stuck in traffic, you can use the app to learn productivity or leadership hacks.”— MakeUseOf\n\n———————\nHOW DOES IT WORK?\nAfter you decide to begin your growth with Headway and download the app, you can start a free trial.\n\nUnless you cancel at least 24 hours before the end of the free trial, you will be automatically charged a price indicated on the payment screen for a chosen subscription period. Don’t worry, though — in any case, you’ll receive a reminder from us that your free trial is about to end.\n\nThe Headway Premium subscription renews automatically at the end of each period (each week, month, 6 months, year, or otherwise, depending on the selected option) until you cancel. Canceling your subscription means the automatic renewal will be disabled. However, you will still have access to all your subscription features for the remaining time of your then-current period. \n\nNote that deleting the app does not cancel your subscriptions.\nTerms of Use: https://policy.get-headway.com/info/terms-and-conditions-web.html \nPrivacy Policy: https://policy.get-headway.com/info/privacy-policy-web.html \n———————\n \nGot an idea about how to make your growth with Headway better? Please email support@get-headway.com, and our Support Jedis will pass it on to the rest of the team.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/5c/cd/7d/5ccd7dbd-9572-d30b-9ec8-ded76558a13a/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-11-0-85-220-0.png/100x100bb.png","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/headway-daily-micro-learning/id1457185832?uo=2","developer":"GTHW App Limited","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"635966718","title":"Memrise Easy Language Learning","store":"app_store","genre":"6017","score":0,"ratings":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"Over 75 million people learn a language with Memrise because it goes beyond teaching you a language—it brings you the experience of real-life conversations, cultural insights, and the confidence to speak like a local.\n\nLearn Spanish, Korean, Japanese or 34 other languages in lessons that teach you vocabulary, listening and speaking as if you were a local living in the country!\n\nChoose a language from Spanish (MEX & EU), Korean, Japanese, English, French, Italian, Portuguese (PT & BR), German, Polish, Russian, Turkish, Arabic, Chinese, Dutch, Danish, Icelandic, Mongolian, Norwegian, Slovenian, Yoruba, Hindi, Ukrainian, Thai, Swahili, Hebrew, Greek, Indonesian, Welsh, Tagalog, Persian, Vietnamese.\n\nNEW languages added: isiXhosa, Hausa, Igbo and Somali!\n\n* Showing you how to piece together natural sentences, preparing you for everyday conversation\n* Giving you a place to practice role-play and gain confidence\n* Teaching you the cultural nuances you need to feel like a local\n\nMemrise is the best language-learning app for beginners that are starting to learn a language from scratch, intermediate learners that want to build on their listening and speaking, and advanced learners who are looking to improve their conversational skills.\n\nDownload Memrise so that you can confidently:\n\n* Connect with your partner and their family\n* Have a better time while travelling\n* Sharpen your mind if you’re learning a language for brain health\n* Prepare for a language exam\n* Connect with work colleagues\n* Better understand different cultures\n\nHow do we help you have conversations in other languages?\n\n* Choose from hundreds of real-life scenarios\n* Build vocab by learning relevant words & phrases the locals actually use\n* Practice listening to native speaker videos using what you’ve just learned\n* Then build confidence speaking with AI Buddies, your personalised language learning bots\n\n- Helping 75+ million learners speak confidently\n- 190,000 4.6 star ratings\n- Featured in BBC World Service, Forbes, The Verge, The Financial Times, and more\n\nWhat other learners are saying\n\n\"I've been using Memrise for about two years, studying European Portuguese. I have the paid version - it's a solid learning tool, and it has been my primary resource ever since got it. I find the Learn with Locals feature to be especially useful, more so as my Portuguese improves. My wife and I spent a couple of weeks in Portugal a few months ago, and we were able to handle all of our transactions - stores, restaurants, markets, car rental, etc!\" - Voloúre\n\nNeed to speak a new language soon? Get the practice you need with Memrise Pro\n\n- Unlock all vocab lessons\n- Unlock all native speaker videos\n- Unlimited speaking practice\n- Ad free\n\nCompare with our Free Plan\n- Limited vocab lessons\n- Limited videos and conversations\n- Ads\n\nDownload our app for free and start learning with Memrise today: Learn French, Spanish (Spain), Spanish (Mexico), German, Korean, Japanese, Japanese (no script), Turkish, Italian, Chinese (simplified), Dutch, Portuguese (Portugal), Portuguese (Brazil), Russian, Swedish, Norwegian, Polish, Danish, Slovenian, Icelandic, Yoruba, Mongolian, English (UK) and English (US)! \n\n------\n*PLEASE READ: A Memrise Pro subscription are designed for Memrise-approved courses. A subscription is required in order to access all our learning features. These features may vary depending on your device's language and language pair. Once purchased, subscriptions will automatically renew unless cancelled before the end of the current payment period. Subscriptions can be managed or cancelled in your Apple App Store account. In-app Permissions – To enable some of the features of the Memrise app we may need to ask for your permission. For example, we'll ask to access your microphone if you'd like to practice your pronunciation skills. You can change permissions at any time in your settings. \n\nPrivacy Policy: https://www.memrise.com/privacy/  \nTerms of Use: https://www.memrise.com/terms/","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/de/b4/69/deb46961-4d83-53b9-697f-ae8d293e05bc/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-8-0-P3-0-85-220.png/100x100bb.png","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/memrise-easy-language-learning/id635966718?uo=2","developer":"Memrise Limited","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"693689912","title":"IXL - Math, English, & More","store":"app_store","genre":"6017","score":0,"ratings":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"IXL is personalized learning! Trusted by over 1 million educators and parents, IXL is proven to accelerate student achievement. And with the award-winning IXL app, students can master skills anytime, anywhere!\n\nSee how IXL meets the unique needs of over 17 million learners (and counting!):\n\nSUPERIOR SKILL-BUILDING\nWith IXL’s full curriculum of over 15,000 skills, students of all levels can learn the exact topics they need, whether they’re reviewing past concepts or exploring new territory. Immediate feedback and step-by-step answer explanations help students work through their mistakes and make lasting progress. Plus, question difficulty adapts to challenge students at just the right level and help them grow.\n\nMATH MASTERY\nWith IXL’s preK-12 curriculum, every learner can excel in math! From skip-counting with pictures to graphing quadratic functions, students interact with dynamic problem types that bring each concept to life. And with unlimited questions to explore, students can practice as much as they need to master each skill, and never see the same problem twice.\n\nENGLISH LEARNING\nIXL’s preK-12 curriculum helps build strong readers and writers! From comprehension to composition, IXL breaks down each concept into highly targeted skills that help students grow from where they are. Fun and relevant questions engage students as they learn new vocabulary, correct grammar mistakes, analyze text, strengthen writing skills, and more.\n\nSCIENCE, SOCIAL STUDIES, AND SPANISH\nBuild knowledge across all core subjects! With comprehensive curriculum in kindergarten through high school biology, chemistry, physics, civics, and U.S. history, students can learn exciting and relevant concepts about the world around them. And with foundational Spanish, students can get started on the path toward Spanish fluency!\n\nVIDEO TUTORIALS\nIXL's video tutorials help bring math and English concepts to life. Access 4,500+ videos for preK-12 math, as well as Pre-K through 8th grade English language arts skills.\n\nGAMES\nIXL’s interactive learning games make math and English fun! With 400+ educational games for pre-K through 5th grade, kids can explore reading, writing, grammar, spelling, math facts, counting, money, multiplication, and more. Through play-based learning, each game brings lessons to life with colorful worlds, animated characters, and hands-on practice—helping children build skills, confidence, and a lifelong love of learning.\n\nREAL-TIME DIAGNOSTIC\nIXL’s Real-Time Diagnostic pinpoints each student’s current knowledge level in math and English language arts. As students answer questions, they’ll discover more about themselves, and reveal personalized recommendations on the best skills to learn next!\n\nIMMERSIVE EXPERIENCE\nInteractive features, from drag-and-drop questions to graphing tools, allow students to engage with the material in new ways. With handwriting recognition, students can easily write in math answers with their fingertips. On iPad, students can work through each problem by writing on their screen—no scrap paper needed! Plus, colorful awards highlight students’ accomplishments and make learning fun!\n\nPROVEN RESULTS\nResearch has shown that IXL improves student outcomes more than any other product or method. IXL is trusted by over 1 million teachers worldwide!\n\nACTIONABLE ANALYTICS\nView reports on all progress on our website! Tackle any trouble spots with specific insights and clear next steps. And celebrate reaching each new milestone with an official certificate!\n\nPractice 10 questions each day for free. Become an IXL member to get access to a fully personalized learning experience with comprehensive curriculum, meaningful guidance, progress tracking, fun awards, and more!\n\nIXL is kidSAFE certified and COPPA-compliant. For more information, please visit:\nPrivacy Policy: https://www.ixl.com/privacypolicy","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/ed/9e/f1/ed9ef1ef-095b-37a9-4a50-36bd053a04eb/stable-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-7-0-85-220.png/100x100bb.png","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/ixl-math-english-more/id693689912?uo=2","developer":"IXL Learning","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"950795722","title":"Prodigy Math Game","store":"app_store","genre":"6017","score":0,"ratings":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"Ready for an AWESOME math adventure? With Prodigy Math Game, players explore new worlds, embark on heroic quests and battle friends to collect prizes, pets and more — all while practicing math!\n\nEach player creates a character that represents them as they start their adventure. These characters, or wizards, embark on a unique journey, taking players from level 1 all the way up to level 100! As they play, their wizards get stronger, collect more items and unlock more zones. \n\nWith Prodigy Math Game, kids don’t have to choose between homework time and playtime! As they compete in battles against monsters or other players, they’ll answer skill-building math questions to succeed. Prodigy Math Game has been designed by educators to make learning fun! \n\n\nHere’s how Prodigy turns math into a fun adventure for everyone: \n- It’s engaging — We believe learning should be fun! That’s why Prodigy Math Game aims to help kids to develop a love of practicing math and master new skills. \n \n- It’s aligned — Math questions are fully aligned with state-level curricula, to align with what students are learning in school. For a full list of the math skills Prodigy supports, visit prodigygame.com/math/skills. \n \n- It’s adaptive — Our adaptive algorithm tailors math questions to each child’s learning style and grade level. Questions also include hints to help students through tough concepts.\n\nPRIVACY & SAFETY: \nEvery child’s privacy and safety is important to us. \n \nIn our commitment to protect the privacy of children, Prodigy participates in the iKeepSafe Safe Harbor program. Prodigy has been granted the iKeepSafe Privacy California Student Badge, signifying that our products have been reviewed and approved for having policies and practices surrounding the collection, use, maintenance and disclosure of personal information from children consistent with program guidelines, including The Children's Online Privacy Protection Act (COPPA) and The Family Education Rights and Protection Act (FERPA). To learn more, visit https://www.prodigygame.com/main-en/privacy-policy/\n \nHere’s what teachers are saying about Prodigy:\n\n“I have seen students who were apprehensive about math open up and begin to enjoy working on their skills. I have also seen struggling students make improvements with as little as 10 minutes each day.”\nJamie G\nMissouri\n5th grade teacher\n\n“I have students who will tell me a new concept is easy because they have already learned how to do it on Prodigy.”\nKim J\nMichigan\n4th grade teacher\n\nMake a difference in your child's education with a Premium Membership. Easily track learning progress and provide support exactly where they need it.\n\nProdigy can help your child love learning independently. And as they play, you’ll get data on their progress to support their learning. Prodigy Math Game's mission is to help every child in the world love learning! An optional membership is available that provides parents with extra data and tools to support their child’s learning progress and extra fun for kids through additional features. To learn more, visit https:​//www.prodigygame.com/main-en/parents/\n\nThis optional subscription  is available for purchase at 99.99USD/year (or local equivalent).\n \nPayments are charged to the user’s Apple ID account at confirmation of purchase. Subscriptions automatically renew unless cancelled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. The account is charged for the renewal within 24 hours before the end of the current period and the cost of the renewal will be provided.  Auto-renewal can be turned off by going to the user’s Apple ID’s Account Settings after purchase. You can manage and cancel subscriptions in the user’s Apple ID account settings.\n \nPrivacy Policy: https://www.prodigygame.com/main-en/privacy-policy/\nTerms and conditions: https://www.prodigygame.com/main-en/terms-and-conditions/","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/73/9a/e4/739ae438-5d40-80b5-5435-18b5b7df9533/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-8-0-85-220.png/100x100bb.png","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/prodigy-math-game/id950795722?uo=2","developer":"Prodigy Education Inc.","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"570772231","title":"OCEARCH Shark Tracker™","store":"app_store","genre":"6017","score":0,"ratings":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"DIVE INTO A WORLD OF SHARKS, TURTLES, AND OTHER AMAZING MARINE ANIMALS & HELP SAVE OUR OCEANS!\n\nIf you have a passion for the ocean, sharks, and marine life, this app is for YOU! The Global Shark Tracker™ was created by OCEARCH, a non-profit research organization dedicated to returning our world’s oceans to balance and abundance.\n\n\nEXPLORE LIKE THE OCEARCH CREW, FROM THE COMFORT OF YOUR HOME!\n\nJoin our scientific researchers on an exciting journey, with real-time tracking data for sharks, turtles, and more. With cutting-edge satellite technology, the OCEARCH Global Shark Tracker™ app lets you follow these amazing marine animals as they migrate across the globe. Dive into each animal’s profile to discover their history, track their movements, and learn fascinating facts about their species\n\n• Track Animals Live with Interactive Maps\n• Explore Migration & Movement Patterns\n• Access Animal Tagging & Species Details\n• Never Miss Updates with ‘Follow’ Option\n• Daily Ocean & Marine Animal Facts \n\n\nMAKE A DIFFERENCE AS YOU TRACK\n\nOCEARCH now has a new way that YOU can make a direct impact on our sharks and oceans! For less than the cost of a cup of coffee each month, you can upgrade to Shark Tracker+ and directly support the OCEARCH mission. Plus, enjoy these exciting new features with your subscription:\n\n• Premium Map Layers incl. Live Weather Maps\n• ‘Behind-The-Scenes’ Exclusive Content \n• Enhanced Animal Detail Page incl. Charts\n• Community Engagement with ‘Comments’\n• Discounts in the OCEARCH Shop\n\n\nHOW TRACKING WORKS\n\nOCEARCH conducts scientific research and collaborates with institutions across the world! SPOT tags are used to provide near real-time tracking data for an average of 5 years. Each time the animal’s tag breaks the surface of the water, it signals a satellite to create a ‘ping’ on the tracker for YOU to see. Data is used by the scientific community to help with:\n\n• Research\n• Conservation\n• Policy\n• Management\n• Safety\n• Education\n\nWe created this app to engage YOU in shark and marine conservation efforts by providing real-time tracking data on ocean animals. Our goal is to empower YOU to connect with the ocean, learn about marine life, and support vital marine science through interactive, accessible technology. Thank you for your interest and support. We couldn't conduct this critical ocean research without you.\n\nIf you love our app, please consider supporting us by leaving a rating and review, or by sharing it with your friends.\n\nWe’re always looking to improve! If you have any questions, comments, or feedback, please feel free to email us at tracker@ocearch.org.\n\nOCEARCH is a 501(c)(3) non-profit organization. Our federal tax ID is 80-0708997. For more information about OCEARCH and our mission, please visit www.ocearch.org or @OCEARCH on social media to learn more.\n\nTerms of use: https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/86/4b/51/864b51b1-2cfa-b2ff-7be0-63d1ed5494ff/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-8-0-85-220.png/100x100bb.png","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/ocearch-shark-tracker/id570772231?uo=2","developer":"OCEARCH","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"513850893","title":"DMV Genie: Permit Test 2026","store":"app_store","genre":"6017","score":0,"ratings":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"Pass your DMV permit or license test on the first try - guaranteed. DMV Genie is the #1 app for DMV test preparation, trusted by over 8 million drivers. We cover all 50 states and every DMV exam: car, motorcycle, and CDL (commercial driver’s license). Studying for your 2026 DMV test has never been easier. \n\nWHY CHOOSE DMV GENIE?\n\n- Complete Exam Prep: 600+ state-specific questions, 100% aligned with your state’s official Driver’s Manual. Every question is up to date for 2026.\n- Proven Results: 97% of DMV Genie users pass their exam on the first attempt (see link below)\n- Our program is the only one recommended by multiple state DMVs (the Wyoming DMV even adopted our platform) - a testament to its accuracy\n- Pass Guarantee: We’re so confident you’ll pass, we guarantee it. Pass the real exam or receive a full refund. No risk, just results.\n- Trusted by Millions: Join over 8,000,000 drivers who have used DMV Genie to ace their tests. Whether it’s your learner’s permit, driver’s license, or CDL, you’re in good company.\n- Covers Every Test Type: Car learner’s permit, driver’s license test, motorcycle license, CDL permit, and endorsement exams (including HazMat, School Bus, Air Brakes, and more) – it’s all included in one app.\n\n\nFEATURES TO HELP YOU SUCCEED:\n\n- Realistic Practice Tests: Take full-length mock exams that simulate the real DMV test format. Questions are randomly generated from our large bank, so every attempt is unique - just like the actual exam.\n- Smart Study Modes: Choose from easy practice quizzes, section-specific tests, or the Exam Simulator for a real challenge. Switch to Review mode to see answers and explanations as you go.\n- Detailed Explanations & Hints: Understand not just what the right answers are, but why. Each question comes with a clear explanation, so you’ll learn the rules of the road deeply. \n- Got a wrong answer and not sure why? DMV Genie’s AI Tutor is on hand to clarify and give you learning tips, just like a personal instructor.\n- Progress Tracking: See your scores and passing probability. The app tells you when you’re ready for the real test by analyzing your performance – no more guesswork.\n- Cheat Sheets & PDFs: Short on time? Use our printable road signs and Cheat Sheets to review the trickiest questions quickly. Perfect for last-minute refreshers.\n\nState-specific DMV testing for all 50 US states: Alabama (AL), Alaska (AK), Arizona (AZ), Arkansas (AR), California (CA), Colorado (CO), Connecticut (CT), Delaware (DE), District of Columbia (DC), Florida (FL), Georgia (GA), Hawaii (HI), Idaho (ID), Illinois (IL), Indiana (IN), Iowa (IA), Kansas (KS), Kentucky (KY), Louisiana (LA), Maine (ME), Maryland (MD), Massachusetts (MA), Michigan (MI), Minnesota (MN), Mississippi (MS), Missouri (MO), Montana (MT), Nebraska (NE), Nevada (NV), New Hampshire (NH), New Jersey (NJ), New Mexico (NM), New York (NY), North Carolina (NC), North Dakota (ND), Ohio (OH), Oklahoma (OK), Oregon (OR), Pennsylvania (PA), Rhode Island (RI), South Carolina (SC), South Dakota (SD), Tennessee (TN), Texas (TX), Utah (UT), Vermont (VT), Virginia (VA), Washington (WA), West Virginia (WV), Wisconsin (WI), Wyoming (WY).\n\nCovers all official licensing agencies: DMV, BMV, MVA, DOR, MVC, MVD, DOT, DOL, DDS, RMV, OMV, SOS, KSP, DPS.\n\n*See our Success Rate Research Report: https://driving-tests.org/premium/pdf/Driving-Tests-org-Success-Rate-Report-30-Nov-2023-compressed.pdf\n\nDMV Genie focuses on one thing - helping you pass your DMV written exam. We continually refine our questions using real exam feedback and official DMV updates, so you’ll never see surprises on test day. It’s like having the DMV answer key in your pocket, legally! Install DMV Genie and join the millions of satisfied new drivers who passed with flying colors. Get ready to walk into your DMV exam and walk out with your new license!","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/7f/e7/2e/7fe72eb8-c3df-7ffc-af3a-6581fe526bb2/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-0-85-220.png/100x100bb.png","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/dmv-genie-permit-test-2026/id513850893?uo=2","developer":"Elegant eLearning","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"568839295","title":"Blinkist: Book Summaries Daily","store":"app_store","genre":"6017","score":0,"ratings":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"WANT TO LEARN FASTER AND SMARTER? \n\nWith Blinkist, you can absorb the most important ideas from 8,000+ top books and podcasts in just 15 minutes. Blinkist summarizes their key insights into short, easy-to-digest audio and text summaries.\n\nThat means you can turn spare moments - on your commute, during workouts, or even while doing chores - into valuable learning time.\n\nBoost your career, focus on personal growth, or simply stay curious, Blinkist makes it easy to fit learning into your busy life.\n\nOver 39 million people use Blinkist to read more and learn faster. Join them today.\n\n———————\n\nWHY CHOOSE BLINKIST\n\nBlinkist is designed to help you learn faster and make positive changes quickly:\n95% of users read more than before\n91% have developed better habits\n87% already have made positive life changes\nNo matter your goal, Blinkist helps you make the most of your time.\n\n———————\n\nWHAT YOU GET WITH BLINKIST\n\n*8,000+ summaries for smarter learning\nAccess the key ideas from the world’s top nonfiction and fiction books and podcasts in just 15 minutes.\n\n*Daily microlearning session\nStart your day with a bite-sized book summary, handpicked by our team.\n\n*Personalized recommendations\nSet your goals and get tailored suggestions, based on your interests.\n\n*Audio and text summaries\nNo time to read? With Blinkist you can also listen to summaries while commuting, exercising, or multitasking.\n\n*Expert-curated Guides and Collections\nDive deeper into must-know topics with audio Guides, curated by our experts.\n\n*Blinkist Pro with Blinkist AI\nTake your learning to the next level with Blinkist Pro. With Blinkist AI, you can summarize articles, PDFs, and videos and get the key ideas from any content in seconds.\n\n*Offline mode\nLearning without Wi-Fi! Download summaries to listen or read offline.\n\n*Send-to-Kindle feature\nPrefer reading on your Kindle? Send Blinkist summaries directly to your device for a seamless reading experience.\n\n*2-for-1 Premium account\nShare Blinkist with someone close to you! With Premium, you can give a friend or family member a free additional account.\n\n*Science-backed learning for better retention\nOur summaries are designed using neuroscience-based techniques to help you retain key concepts and ideas more effectively.\n\n*Clear, focused summaries\nOur expert writers turn complex ideas into easy-to-understand, clear summaries.\n\n———————\n\nBASIC, PREMIUM & PRO: CHOOSE THE RIGHT PLAN FOR YOU\n\n- Blinkist Basic - the Daily Pick\nOne free daily summary handpicked by our editorial team.\n\n- Blinkist Premium -  the Full Package\n8,000+ summaries\nExpert-led Guides\nPersonalized recommendations\nOffline mode to read or listen to anywhere\nSend-to-Kindle feature\n2 for 1: Share a free account with family or friends\n\n- Blinkist Pro - for the Learning Champion\nBlinkist Pro gives you everything included in Blinkist Premium, PLUS Blinkist AI, the revolution of learning:\nSummarize Any Content: Quickly turn articles, PDFs, or videos into key takeaways.\nAsk follow-up questions and become 10x more productive\n\n———————\n\nWHAT THE PRESS IS SAYING\n\n\"Blinkist is an intriguing app that encourages you to read more nonfiction books... It’s a fun and fascinating way to discover new and interesting topics\" — The New York Times\n\n\"Blinkist offers a terrific service—great ideas distilled down to their very essence. For those of us who are deeply curious about new ideas on success, happiness, innovation, progress, and more, it’s a great start.\" — Forbes\n\n———————\n\nRISK-FREE LEARNING\n\nNot sure if Blinkist is the right fit? No worries! Simply contact Apple Support within the first 14 days to request a refund—quick, easy, and stress-free.\nGet started today—there’s zero risk and endless learning waiting for you!\nTerms of Use: https://www.blinkist.com/en/tos\nPrivacy Policy: https://www.blinkist.com/privacy.html\n\nQuestions or Suggestions? Our customer support team is just an email away: support@blinkist.com","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/48/76/02/48760288-b778-4328-ed44-abb4f66921c3/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-0-85-220.png/100x100bb.png","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/blinkist-book-summaries-daily/id568839295?uo=2","developer":"Blinks Labs","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1116032929","title":"Gibson: Learn to Play Guitar","store":"app_store","genre":"6017","score":0,"ratings":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"The best guitar learning app from Gibson.\nPerfect if you’re looking for a fun guitar practice app that keeps you motivated.\n\nLooking for the best way to learn guitar at home? Start with Gibson’s step-by-step learning path. Whether you’re picking up a guitar for the first time or leveling up your technique, the Gibson App helps you learn faster with interactive fun lessons, real songs, and real-time feedback. Join millions of guitar players learning with the Gibson App. \n\nBuild real skills across all styles — from your first chords to full songs, fingerpicking, and music theory. New songs added weekly.\n\nFEATURED IN TOP MUSIC MEDIA\n\n“The Gibson App is changing the guitar teaching game.” — Rolling Stone\n\n“For those just starting their guitar journey, the Gibson app will be a godsend. The quality of tuition is second to none.” — Guitar World\n\n\"The Best Guitar Learning App\" - Creative Outlet\n\nLEARN GUITAR FASTER WITH REAL-TIME FEEDBACK\n\nThe app listens to your guitar and gives you instant feedback on your playing, helping you improve timing and technique with every session. Guitar lessons, real songs, interactive tabs, tuner, metronome, and real-time feedback — all in one app.\n\n10,000+ LESSONS, EXERCISES & SONGS\n\nExplore a massive library of lessons and songs across multiple genres, including rock, blues, metal, pop, acoustic, and more.\n\nMASTER EVERY GUITAR SKILL\n\nGo beyond basic chords with a curriculum that covers proper finger placement, strumming patterns, lead guitar, fingerpicking, and music theory. Whether you want to read tabs or understand the fretboard, our world-class teachers guide you from beginner to pro across all genres.\n\nSee your guitar skills grow in real-time with detailed tracking across 300+ techniques, chords, and playing styles—turning invisible practice into measurable mastery.\n\nSTEP-BY-STEP LEARNING PATH (BEGINNER TO PRO)\n\nFollow a fun learning journey created by professional guitar teachers. You’ll always know what to practice next, with lessons designed to keep you progressing.\n\nEVERYTHING YOU NEED TO LEARN & PLAY GUITAR\n\n- Guitar tuner \n\n- Metronome\n\n- Tempo control and looping tools\n\n- Training Calendar to build a consistent routine\n\nTURN YOUR IPHONE/IPAD INTO AN AMPLIFIER\n\nExplore guitar sound effects, play along with your favorite music. Practice with an electric or acoustic guitar.\n\nJOIN THE COMMUNITY\n\nConnect with fellow guitar learners, get access to pro-level guidance, tips, and inspiration.\n\nWATCH GIBSON TV\n\nGibson TV is packed with original series on guitars, music, and culture. Watch, and get inspired by legendary players and iconic stories.\n\nNEW TO GUITAR?\n\n- Is the Gibson App good for complete beginners?\nYes. The Gibson App is designed to help complete beginners learn guitar from scratch with step-by-step lessons and a fun learning path.\n\n- Can I learn guitar on my own?\nAbsolutely. The app is built for self-learners and helps you stay consistent with guided lessons and a Training Calendar.\n\n- Does it work with acoustic and electric guitar?\nYes. The Gibson App works with any guitar.\n\n- Does the app teach real songs?\nYes. Learn real songs with interactive tabs and video lessons.\n\n- Why should I choose Gibson app?\nGibson is the best guitar learning app. Ask our users!\n\nHOW THE GIBSON APP WORKS\n\n- The app listens to your guitar and gives you feedback\n\n- Play along with fun lessons and easy-to-follow tablature\n\n- Advance at your own pace through the step-by-step learning\n\nFREE TRIAL\n\nDay 1: Start free trial\nDay 1 - 7: Full access to all lessons, songs, features\nDay 7: Subscription begins unless canceled\nCancel anytime during the free trial, you won’t be charged\n\nABOUT\n\nThe Gibson App is developed by Zoundio, a music-tech company based in Stockholm, Sweden, in collaboration with Gibson.\n\nCONTACT\n\nHave feedback, questions or suggestions? Contact us at app.support@gibson.com \n\nBy downloading this app, you agree to Apple's Terms of Use: https://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/dd/5f/91/dd5f9119-733b-101b-1159-da912f7d7a22/AppIcon-1x_U007epad-0-1-0-0-sRGB-85-220-0.png/100x100bb.png","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/gibson-learn-to-play-guitar/id1116032929?uo=2","developer":"Zoundio","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"1553283646","title":"memoryOS・Improve Memory Skills","store":"app_store","genre":"6017","score":0,"ratings":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"memoryOS contains interactive bite-sized lessons by a 2X World Memory Champion and an educational 3D game of Virtual Mind Palaces - all in one easy-to-use app. It utilizes scientifically proven memory techniques, spaced repetition and patented game mechanics to enhance long-term memory storage and improve knowledge retention.\n\nmemoryOS is loved by 500,000+ people worldwide because it is a whole new, joyful & game-changing tool for obtaining the most effective memorization skills.\n\nCo-founded by Jonas von Essen, who went from struggling to remember to becoming a World Memory Champion, winning on Who Wants To Be a Millionaire, \"Jeopardy, and setting a world record by memorizing 100,000 decimals of Pi . \n\nmemoryOS app has over 18k public worldwide ratings on Apple and Google app stores combined, averaging 4.8 stars. Users also continue adding 5-star reviews daily, sharing how effective and life-changing memoryOS has been for them. Also, memoryOS remains the most crowdfunded app in Kickstarter’s history.\n\nMemorization is as important as reading and writing and should be taught as our base skill. Our mission is to enable millions of people to remember needed information easily.\n\nWith memoryOS, you will learn how to memorize:\n\n- Names, Long speeches, Lists of items, Birthdays, Personal facts, Passwords, Trivia, Languages, Vocabulary and phrases, Countries and Capitals, Flags, Historical timeline, Numbers, Periodic table\n- Content of complete books, Dates of significant events, Complex data structures, Concepts, and figures\n- Art, Anatomy, Decks of cards, Advanced number systems; Long sequences of numbers, Binary Digits\n\nYou will also learn:\n\n- How to keep track of years, months, weeks, and days \n- Advanced study techniques, Spaced Repetition system, Speed memorization\n\n\nWhy did Google Brands Accelerator recognize memoryOS as being 'Light Years Ahead' in the memory space?\n\n• memoryOS delivers results:\n\nDuring our pre-launch phase, thousands of users completed our demo and, on average, had a 70% increase in recall and a 60% increase in recall speed just after the first ~40min session.\n\n• Providing your mind with structured storage space:\n\nWe have spent tens of thousands of hours creating and optimizing our Virtual Mind Palaces, so you don’t have to spend months constructing your own the hard way. These virtual palaces serve as blueprints for your mind's storage space, allowing you to easily encode, store and recall like a memory champion.\n\n• A proven innovative approach that works:\n\nDuring our research and development stage, thousands of people of all age groups and even those with difficult medical conditions found memoryOS as an effective and useful tool. Actual results exceeded our team’s expectations.\n\n• Gamified edtech at its best:\n\nmemoryOS has proven to work on people with no prior gaming experience - anyone can use it. Utilizing the power of the Unity game engine, memoryOS is widely accessible on all mobile and tablet devices and is soon coming to VR.\n\n--\n\nJoining memoryOS is free. This provides extensive value on the free plan, and you are not obligated to pay to start using it. You can subscribe to a Student Premium plan for as low as $3.49/month when billed annually or $4.99/month when billed monthly (it can be 10-20% higher in some countries due to local taxes). You can subscribe through the 'Shop' section of the memoryOS app and find the above-mentioned or go to your App Store app's profile and choose a desired plan there. Recurring payments will automatically renew unless you cancel your account at least 24 hours before the end of the current subscription period. You can manage your subscription, cancel anytime, or turn off auto-renewal by accessing your iTunes account.\n\nJoin the memoryOS community of over 500,000+ early adopters who share this memorable journey!\n\n--\n\nTerms: memoryOS.com/terms\nPrivacy policy: memoryOS.com/privacy-policy\n\nLearn more at: memoryOS.com\n\nContact us: support@memoryOS.com","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/5c/7f/23/5c7f23ad-4c6f-edfa-8c0a-9face04de1f4/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-8-0-85-220.png/100x100bb.png","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/memoryos-improve-memory-skills/id1553283646?uo=2","developer":"Encoder Inc.","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

data: {"type":"app_found","app":{"id":"6736955121","title":"Parrot – Speak Spanish Fast","store":"app_store","genre":"6017","score":0,"ratings":0,"installs":"N/A","description":"LEARN SPANISH THE FASTEST WAY - JUST BY SCROLLING VIDEOS \n\nStop speaking in “Duolingo” and start speaking real Spanish with Parrot, the fastest way to learn Spanish while scrolling videos. Our unique method uses authentic Spanish videos so you can absorb the language naturally - just like how native speakers learn.\n\nWhether you're a student, traveller, professional, or busy parent, Parrot makes learning Spanish effortless and engaging. In just 90 days, you'll be able to understand and participate in real conversations- or your money back.\n\n*WHY PARROT?*\n\n► Learn Naturally – Pick up real-life conversations, pronunciation, and slang from native speakers.\n► The Fastest Way to Learn – Just scroll through Spanish videos like TikTok or YouTube and absorb the language effortlessly.\n► Tap to Translate – Instantly translate words and phrases in captions while watching.\n► Bite-Sized & Flexible – Learn anytime, anywhere, with quick and engaging lessons that fit into any schedule.\n► Gamified Progress & Streaks – Stay motivated with streak rewards, badges, and challenges that make learning fun.\n\n*WHO IS PARROT FOR?*\n\n► Students – Master Spanish naturally while scrolling engaging content.\n► Travellers – Pick up real-world Spanish to connect with locals on your next trip.\n► Busy Adults & Parents – Learn Spanish in minutes a day, no textbooks required.\n► Movie & Music Lovers – Finally understand Spanish TV shows, songs, and movies without subtitles.\n\n*WHAT OUR USERS ARE SAYING*\n\n► Stephani, Canada: “With Parrot, I stopped speaking in ‘Duolingo’ Spanish. Now I understand real conversations and feel confident speaking Spanish!”\n► Christine, US: “I love how Parrot makes learning effortless. Just watching videos has improved my Spanish so much!”\n► Marcus, UK: “Parrot is like a TikTok for learning Spanish. I can scroll for 10 minutes and feel like I actually learned something.”\n\n*FEATURES THAT MAKE PARROT UNIQUE*\n\n► The Fastest Way to Learn – No boring drills, just real Spanish videos that keep you engaged.\n► Instant Translations – Tap any word in subtitles to get its meaning instantly.\n► Effortless Learning – Just scroll, watch, and absorb – learning Spanish has never been this easy.\n► Sustainable Learning & Global Impact – For every milestone you achieve, we plant a tree, making your progress count for the planet.\n\n*SUBSCRIPTION INFORMATION*\n\nParrot offers auto-renewing subscription plans to access all premium content and features. A subscription is required to unlock the full learning experience. Weekly and monthly plans are available, and the monthly plan includes a 7-day free trial for new subscribers. Payment will be charged to your Apple ID account at confirmation of purchase. Subscriptions automatically renew unless canceled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. You can manage or cancel your subscription anytime in your App Store account settings.\n\n*TERMS OF SERVICE*\n\nhttps://parrotapp.com/terms-of-service\n\nhttps://www.apple.com/legal/internet-services/itunes/dev/stdeula/","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple211/v4/54/38/a3/5438a3b4-257a-e004-c097-8ad28bd366c1/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-85-220.png/100x100bb.png","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/parrot-speak-spanish-fast/id6736955121?uo=2","developer":"Parrot Learning Inc.","isEstimatedInstalls":false}}

