data: {"type":"opportunity","opportunity":{"id":"d05286be-29fb-48e5-add1-c9ac583d64b5","scrapedApp":{"id":"1200778841","title":"EWA English Language Learning","store":"app_store","genre":"6017","score":0,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":50,"installs":"N/A","description":"Learn English, Spanish, or French with EWA! Read books with real time translations, discover unknown words with a tap of your finger, complete speaking courses with your favorite TV characters, and learn new words with flashcards - all for free in our app! Improve your existing skills today!\n\nEWA is a personalized English, Spanish, or French tutor that fits in your pocket. Every user can decide for themselves how they would like to learn a language - at what level and at what pace:\n\n1. More than 10,000 English, Spanish, or French books with audio are available for you to sharpen your reading, writing, and grammar skills. Choose a book that matches your current language level and start expanding your skills right away! Unknown word? Simply tap it to translate it, add it to your “to-learn” list, and memorize it forever!\n\n2. Spoken video-courses with popular movie scenes and TV show characters is what our users love the most about EWA! It’s fun, interesting, and an innovative way to improve pronunciation and achieve language proficiency. The courses include a variety of topics, levels and time frames - so, regardless of your current skills, your language abilities will only benefit from EWA!\n\n3. Oxford Topics Dialogues\nDon't know what to say at passport control, how to ask for directions or order food at a café? Read and listen to dialogues on everyday topics, developed in collaboration with Oxford Reading University, that will help you in every journey of yours. Thanks to the dialogues, you'll be able to easily improve your conversational English by applying the material you've learned in real life!\n\n4. All you need is a spare 5 minutes a day to learn English, Spanish, or French. More than 40,000 flashcards are available for you to choose from. Pick the words you want to learn and memorize them using the spaced repetition study method. Feeling excited about your progress? Compete on score charts, compare your results to thousands of other people, and get to the top-ranked spot!\n\n5. The games section is now available in EWA.\nA unique teaching methodology compromised of cognitive training exercises and easy-to-learn brain games will help you sharpen your language skills in a very fun and exciting way.\nOur games aren’t time-wasters; they’re actually great mental stimulators!\nPlay, have fun, and most importantly, learn a new language in no time!\n\nNo more cramming, stress, and angry teachers! With EWA, you’ll learn the language whenever and wherever - at your own pace. You’ll improve your English, Spanish, or French and experience the beauty of knowing another language - from freedom while traveling to higher paying jobs.\n\nAny feedback would be greatly appreciated! If you have any concerns, recommendations, or complaints just drop us a line at support@appewa.com and we’ll work towards making EWA better!\n\n==================\n\nPLEASE NOTE:\n\nYou will need an EWA subscription in order to access all courses and features. Courses available may vary depending your device’s language.\n\n• Payment will be charged to your iTunes Account at ‘confirmation of purchase’\n• Your account will be charged for a subscription renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period and will identify the cost of the renewal\n• Subscriptions may be managed by the user and auto-renewal may be turned off by going to the user’s Account Settings after purchase\n• Any unused portion of a free trial period, if offered, will be forfeited when the user purchases a subscription to that publication, where applicable\n\n==================\n\nStart now and experience a new way of learning English, Spanish, or French.\nExpanding your vocabulary has never been easier.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/64/2a/47/642a47a4-9111-69b5-d74e-dbb481df67cd/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-85-220.png/100x100bb.png","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/ewa-english-language-learning/id1200778841?uo=2","developer":"Lithium Lab Pte Ltd","isEstimatedInstalls":false},"reviews":[{"id":"13822130880","text":"Simple easy. Just trying to revive my high school Spanish and prop it up with better comprehension and conversation","score":4,"date":""},{"id":"13821656756","text":"Eficaz. Muy útil para aprender","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13821576298","text":"EWA English. Did my first lesson, and good so far.☺️","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13818634190","text":"Fun app. It’s a good app for input","score":4,"date":""},{"id":"13818317662","text":"Muy buena aplicación. Con esta aplicación si siento que aprendo inglés !","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13817075017","text":"Spanish. The beginner level is very complete and brings you along nice and slowly but also adds material. My only complaint is their vocals are not terribly audible, they speak too fast. But you can pretty much guess what they’re saying so it doesn’t prohibit learning.","score":4,"date":""},{"id":"13816031711","text":"Still Reviewing. So far I like the structure.  It’s started me way too simple but the reading portion is helpful.","score":4,"date":""},{"id":"13814230972","text":"Excellent Starter. Wish I was learning faster","score":4,"date":""},{"id":"13813615027","text":"Increíble. Super util y dinamico","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13813578976","text":"harika bi uygulama. tek kelimeyle HARİKA BİR UYGULAMA\nher seyi sıfırdan ve tam öğretiyor dualingo fln bunun yanından bile gecemez o derece iyi bence\ntek sorunu enerjinin hemen bitiyor olması","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13813373764","text":"Won’t return $. I canceled within the trial period and my account was charged anyway. I’ve emailed numerous times without a response","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13812951262","text":"Conversation with someone in a bar. Awesome short conversation","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13812602948","text":"Love!!. Love it so far. Very helpful","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13811930326","text":"3일 후기. 아직까진 나쁘진않아요.듀오링고를 먼저 쓰고있었는데 듀오링고보단 훨씬 좋아요.","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13811800803","text":"Excelente. Excelente, me encanta ✨","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13811072957","text":"Didáctico. Muy práctico aprendizaje fácil entendimiento","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13811070415","text":"Fun. Love it… it’s a super fun way to learn Spanish","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13811037015","text":"No. It takes you sooooo so long to get to a placement test\n   They put me at beginner. I know everything they are showing me I have wasted so much time them right now. I’ve asked for my money back so we’ll see","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13810973749","text":"Fun way to learn. I’ve only been using this app for a short amount of time, but I like that the lessons are short, easy, fun and memorable","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13809618062","text":"Good Potential, Minor Issues. Overall I really enjoy this app.  I only have a few complaints.  The first is that every line of every book I try to read crops off the last 3-5 letters.  That makes it difficult to stay focused when I’m constantly guessing what the word might be.  The games are fun but they need more and need to be less redundant.  I never marked words like “feo” or “pez” as words I needed to learn however they show up nearly every single time.  With a few small updates this would be my favorite language learning app.","score":4,"date":""},{"id":"13809476228","text":"duc to. good","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13808739205","text":"I like this app. I like this app","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13808630965","text":"ПРОСТО СУПЕРСКОЕ ПРИЛОЖЕНИЕ!!!. Я незнаю что за гений придумал эту прогу!!!","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13808313343","text":"Price. High expensive","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13807985121","text":"It's not what I expected. What motivated me to buy it was partly because of the book reading, but it doesn't look anything like the advertising; it only has a black or white background depending on your choice, and no images. I'm disappointed.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13807092477","text":"Yay!. It’s working!!","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13805626011","text":"Excelente. Muy buena aplicación","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13804498354","text":"Read and learn. A great way to build your vocabulary and grammar skills. So far my only complaint is some of the words aren’t translated. I do recommend using this program.","score":4,"date":""},{"id":"13804258201","text":"Great!. This is a great app, lots of variety and easy to use.","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13803264348","text":"Not enough access. If I miss a day, I should be able oto access those lessons plus the lessons for today, instead of a 2 - lesson limit.","score":3,"date":""},{"id":"13802974147","text":"Scam. I was offered a black Friday deal for $40 for eight year subscription, only to then be charged $40 per quarter. Canceling is a joke and it’s almost near impossible. Customer Service is a joke and they will not help you. This app is a scam. I hope you figure that out before giving this app any money.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13802179614","text":"Well designed, multi-modal learning approach. This software combines strategies proven to support language learning and recall. It moves at a good pace with just enough repetition of what you just learned combined with new material being presented.","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13802066108","text":"Solid App for practicing reading. I used to use Duolingo, but it’s honestly not entertaining or immersive enough if you already speak a decent amount of Spanish, and want to specifically improve your reading comprehension. EWA is extremely useful in this regard, and the built-in translation and audiobooks make it very efficient and easy to clarify. EWA also doesn’t bombard you with ads all the time, which I appreciate. The selection of texts to read is decent, although there’s room to grow. Overall it’s a great app that, at the minimum, will help you practice reading comprehension in a second language at your own pace.","score":4,"date":""},{"id":"13801982324","text":"Genial. Simplemente genial","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13800950650","text":"Impossible to cancel the suscribe. Worst of worst","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13800916797","text":"الترجمة. الترجمة بالعربي ليست جيده هنالك العديد من الاخطاء … the translation to Arabic is not good there are a-lot of mistakes","score":2,"date":""},{"id":"13800878190","text":"horrible experience. I got the subscription to learn english for a month and got an email that I was charged for a whole year I immediately went  to cancel it only to find out they have no way to cancel the subscription. the learning program is weak and doesn’t work and after a month I had learned nothing from it.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13800697990","text":"Best App. It’s the best app in a market. I love this app , books , grammar, games , words","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13800686992","text":"Great. Great","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13800317156","text":"rất ok. học dể hiểu","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13799362903","text":"Very nice app. So functional and humorous. Easy to use - easy to study.","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13799293530","text":"Good start. I’m 82. Trouble retaining","score":4,"date":""},{"id":"13799080174","text":"Attention! Fraudulent service.. Think twice before subscribing to their service and giving them your card details! I made the mistake of subscribing about a year ago. I used only their books for a while, and since I didn’t plan to continue the subscription, I canceled it in advance so I wouldn’t forget later. The subscription was canceled in my Apple account.\n\nTo my surprise, about a month ago I started getting messages from them saying they tried to charge me, but the transaction was unsuccessful. I thought, how is that possible if I canceled the subscription? I logged directly into my account on their website and saw that, for some reason, the subscription was not canceled and my card details were still there. So I canceled the subscription again and deleted my banking details.\n\nAbout two weeks after that, I received a notification about a $47.40 transaction. I checked what it was and saw that they charged me for a subscription renewal. You have to admit, that’s very strange. I logged into my account on their site again, and it clearly shows that I don’t have any active subscriptions.\n\nI wrote to them about the unauthorized charge, and they replied that they can only issue a refund when a person subscribes for the first time, but they don’t refund renewals. It’s not clear what “renewal” they’re talking about if my subscription is canceled! In short, if you don’t want to end up in the same situation, think carefully before giving them your banking details.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13798772977","text":"Ева. Приложение просто супер,только им и пользуюсь","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13796094489","text":"Engaging. This is a clever approach to learning  a language. It harnesses the addictive quality of phone screen time and keeps me doing something productive instead of just scrolling. I suspect it also mimics how children learn language- less rule based and more repetitive exposure to the language and its order of words in different contexts.","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13795688515","text":"Easy to learn. It’s easy to learn using this app. I like hearing native speakers and then being tested and repeating the word phrase.","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13794058784","text":"EWA. Harika","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13793252795","text":"Effective. I haven’t studied Spanish since 9th grade in 1968. This course is resuscitating knowledge I had thought was lost forever…and making it fun,","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13793214152","text":"Easy practice. I thought I would try to download this program and give it a goal. So far it’s been really easy to practice daily and the tasks are well structured. There are lots of different things to do, but I think my favorite is listening to the books.","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13792990240","text":"Great app, but…. Fun and engaging app, but it doesn’t seem to be working properly, and I have no clear way to reach out to get help with that.","score":3,"date":""}],"sentiment":{"overallSentiment":"positive","painPoints":[{"issue":"Audio clarity and speed - vocals are not audible enough and speakers talk too fast","frequency":"medium","severity":"minor","sampleQuotes":["My only complaint is their vocals are not terribly audible, they speak too fast.","they speak too fast but you can pretty much guess what they're saying so it doesn't prohibit learning"]},{"issue":"Energy/stamina system depletes too quickly","frequency":"low","severity":"minor","sampleQuotes":["tek sorunu enerjinin hemen bitiyor olması"]}],"featureRequests":[{"feature":"Accelerated learning pace options for intermediate learners","demand":"low","sampleQuotes":["Wish I was learning faster","It's started me way too simple"]}],"praisedAspects":["Simple and easy to use","Well-structured curriculum with gradual progression","Complete beginner level content","Dynamic and engaging lessons","Effective for language comprehension and input","Strong methodology that actually teaches the language"],"summary":"EWA English Language Learning receives overwhelmingly positive feedback with strong user satisfaction. Most users praise the app's structured approach, simplicity, and effectiveness for learning languages from scratch. Minor complaints center on audio quality and speaking speed, which don't significantly detract from the learning experience. Users appreciate the thorough beginner content and engaging, dynamic interface."},"score":{"marketSize":14,"dissatisfaction":25,"feasibility":72,"compositeScore":36},"scanId":"fceeb718-5c98-4761-b59a-4f7d7f1fc08b","createdAt":"2026-03-08T15:47:42.015Z","gapAnalysis":null,"blueOcean":null}}

data: {"type":"opportunity","opportunity":{"id":"9def3860-ee2c-4de4-b8a3-1366d36cacdf","scrapedApp":{"id":"6470220669","title":"Credible: Speech Coach","store":"app_store","genre":"Productivity","score":4.41026,"ratings":234,"reviewCount":24,"installs":"N/A","description":"Stop saying \"like,\" \"um,\" \"you know,\" and other distracting filler words that make you sound unprofessional. Credible is the only app that provides immediate feedback during everyday conversations to help you speak with confidence and clarity.\n\nWHY CREDIBLE WORKS (When Other Apps Fail)\n\n•\tReal-Time Feedback: Credible works in the moment, when you need it most – not just during isolated practice sessions.\n•\tEffortless Improvement: No time-consuming practice drills. Credible works immediately, making you aware of your speech habits instantly and discreetly.\n•\tFast Results: Awareness based training is the only way to improve, enhancing job prospects and personal communication.\n•\tTrack Your Progress: Stay motivated and track your progress with our new streak tracking feature.\n\nKEY FEATURES:\n\nUnlike other speech improvement software that requires regular training or provides feedback after you speak, Credible is designed to increase your awareness of filler word use immediately, the only way to solve the problem. With Credible, you don't need to spend hours practicing; it works effortlessly to help you improve your speech.\n\n•\tReal-Time Alerts: Discreetly alerts you of filler words as you use them while speaking on your iPhone and Apple Watch.\n•\tCustomization: Choose common filler words or add any phrases you want to reduce, and the notification frequency.\n•\tStreak & Progress Tracking: Monitor your improvement over time with detailed progress reports.\n•\tPrivacy First: Audio is processed on your device, never stored or shared.\n\nPERFECT FOR:\n\nBreak the habit of saying \"like\"  with Credible, the easy-to-use solution that works instantly without any effort, time, or practice. As you become more aware of your speech, you'll naturally stop using \"like.\"\n\n•\tJob Interviews\n•\tConversations\n•\tMeetings\n•\tPresentations\n•\tAnyone who wants to communicate more effectively!\n\nGet Noticed for What You Say – Not How You Say It\n\nHOW TO USE:\n\nCredible requires microphone, speech recognizer, and notification access. Also, you will need to read a short paragraph to train Credible to only listen to you.\n\n•\tProvide access to your microphone, speech recognizer, and notifications.\n•\tSelect the filler word you want to stop saying.\n•\tSelect your notification frequency.\n•\tSet up the speaker verification tool by reading a short paragraph.\n•\tHit “Tap to Start.”\n\nLeave Credible on during any conversation to increase your awareness of filler words as you say them. Real time feedback is the only way you can become aware and improve your speech.\n\nDATA PRIVACY:\n\nWe take your data privacy seriously! Audio data is processed on-device in real time, it is never sent to the cloud or saved. Credible listens only when you activate it.\n\nPURCHASE OPTIONS:\n\nCredible offers a free demonstration of all included features with unlimited use, without interruptions or advertisements.  Subscription options are for 1-week, 1-month, 3-months, 1-year, 1-year non-renewing access, or purchase of lifetime access. The cost varies by country of residence and will be shown before confirming the purchase. Subscriptions automatically renew unless auto-renewal is disabled at least 24 hours before the end of the billing cycle. Users can manage subscriptions by going to the App Store, going to AppleID Account Settings, and scrolling down to Subscriptions. Cancellations are allowed during the active subscription period but no partial refund will be given. For refund inquiries, users must contact the Apple App Store directly.\n\nCONNECT:\n\nFor more information, questions, or concerns, please visit our website https://soundcredible.com/contact-us/ or email info@soundcredible.com\n\nPrivacy Policy: https://soundcredible.com/privacy-policy\nTerms of Service: https://soundcredible.com/terms-conditions","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/cf/f4/94/cff49464-c1d2-9f54-7ed7-d17d3e74acb7/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007ephone-0-1-0-85-220.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/credible-speech-coach/id6470220669?uo=4","developer":"WearableSoft","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":0,"free":true,"histogram":{"1":25,"2":5,"3":5,"4":13,"5":186}},"reviews":[{"id":"13786347052","text":"Apple Watch Issue Fixed. I was able to get my watch working with this app. Pretty stoked on the app now,","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13266278603","text":"Disappointed. Downloaded the app with the intended outcome of improving my public speaking, the recording feature seems to work fine but I was looking for training opportunities as well as help and when you click on either of those items in the app (training/help), nothing happens.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13117125745","text":"pay to play. you have to pay to even open the app","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"12874546002","text":"Paywall before any chance to see what this app does. Downloaded the app and got it set up. Before being able to do any conversations or check the type of reports it gives., I got to a $99 per year paywall that takes over the app. No trial, no monthly subscription to test it with, just launched into a $99 per year subscription","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"12789778665","text":"Scammy paywall. Like other users already commented, I also absolutely hated that they make you set everything up and then the first time you record something being heart stopped by pay while you can’t exit, and either have to pay US$100 or the app is now a useless thing on your phone. Not the way to treat your customers. It will turn people away from you!!","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"12698988108","text":"Does not work, do not buy subscription!. Phone app can’t pick up a single “like” I said. The watch app is just a blank screen loading forever. The app forces you to buy a $40 annual subscription before you can use it. Total Scam! I am asking apple for refund.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"12571665443","text":"terrible app. if i could give this a 0 out of 5 i would. my english is literally great i just wanted to practice my speech and stuff but i have to pay just to learn something i already know?? this app is terrible don’t download it","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"12460621660","text":"Good app to help build confidence. Five stars","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"12166603539","text":"Inaccurate. The push notifications didn’t work even though it was turned on.  I would be alerted even though I did not say the crutch word and at times when I did I wasn’t alerted.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"12126461240","text":"Rectification needed Immediately. Access to your created profile and personal audio recordings is behind a paywall of over $30. While I understand the need for payment, the concern lies in the lack of access to my recorded likeness. When will I be able to re-record? When can I delete my recording? This situation raises security concerns that Apple needs to examine much further.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"12011366804","text":"Good mobile app but watch app doesn’t work. Just says “Ready….” On the watch.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"11714531875","text":"Very effective. This app worked very well, especially for everyday use!","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"11622774850","text":"Notifications do not tell you which words. I want to love this app as it seems to pick up the selected filler words. However the notifications only tell you a filler word has been used. Not which one. This makes it harder to work on improving. Is this in the works?","score":3,"date":""},{"id":"11610540857","text":"Huh?. This was a total scam of an app. After downloading a few “improve your speaking” apps I tried this. It has a step by step process to get you started,enabling microphone, adding filler words you want to stop using,  complete with recording a passage at the end. I next expect an analysis of that passage like other apps. Then you get stopped by a pay wall. Fine, so I try the free trial. So finally in the full paid app only to discover ALL it does it record your voice and a wavy line will appear as you speak. The line goes up if you say a filler word. That’s it. There are no more buttons, no more functions. That is the whole thing. I was so confused until I realized that is literally all it does. So do not pay the great deal on a yearly subscription.","score":2,"date":""},{"id":"11599547255","text":"Having a pay wall to use this app really?. I wanted to try and get this app try but right when I got through the tutorial, it wanted me to pay and I am not gonna be doing that. I wanted to give it a shot, but it’s not gonna happen now.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"11586405774","text":"Internet scam. Got this recommend from an add though looked cool to improve my eloquence but turns out can’t use it Unless you Pay to use it.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"11217563478","text":"Great for podcasters. As a podcaster and someone asked to present to clients and other employees, I found this very useful to help me kick bad habits and ensure my presentation is effective. Very straightforward and easy to use without being intrusive.","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"11203240726","text":"Extraordinary tool!. It’s so simple, yet, so effective!  I had no idea how often I use lazy words in conversation - until I found Credible!  It also allows users to add their own custom words and phrases!  I’ve been busy!  Highly recommended!","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"11186924501","text":"Awesome for speaking with impact!. This app is an amazing idea in an age where speech matters, especially with our business interactions often not in person. This app was easy to set up and use and despite being a professional for many years, it has made my public speaking super impactful and made me pause to speak with greater effectiveness!","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"11163013101","text":"So good so far. The idea behind the app is incredibly simple, it's like why wasn't this available sooner? Either way I'm happy it's available now.","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"11162976743","text":"Thank you this beautiful application. Please keep working on this application to make it work smoothly. Everything looks great at this point. And thank you for the application.\n\nWith Kindest Regards-BR","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"11139044585","text":"Very helpful!. This app is great as it brings awareness to speech patterns. Many times we do things unconsciously and we don’t even recognize it, but once we are more aware of it then change could happen much faster as a result!","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"11138816309","text":"Great app!. Easy to use and effective.  Recommend for anyone working to improve public speaking and presentation skills.  As a hiring manager, frequent use of filler words by candidates is a bigger issue than many applicants realize and can be exacerbated by nervousness.  It’s important to practice.  This allows you to improve on your own and tracks progress in a measurable way, making you better and improving confidence.","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"11135876178","text":"Incredibly helpful and accurate. Credible is such a helpful app for all of my presentations and public speaking. It gives such great and subtle feedback to keep me on track and sounding professional. Huge fan!","score":5,"date":""}],"sentiment":{"overallSentiment":"negative","painPoints":[{"issue":"Aggressive paywall blocks app access before users can try features","frequency":"high","severity":"critical","sampleQuotes":["I got to a $99 per year paywall that takes over the app. No trial, no monthly subscription to test it with","they make you set everything up and then the first time you record something being heart stopped by pay while you can't exit"]},{"issue":"Broken features and poor functionality - recording doesn't detect speech accurately","frequency":"high","severity":"critical","sampleQuotes":["Phone app can't pick up a single 'like' I said. The watch app is just a blank screen loading forever","The recording feature seems to work fine but when you click on training/help, nothing happens"]},{"issue":"Security and privacy concerns with personal audio recordings behind paywall","frequency":"medium","severity":"critical","sampleQuotes":["Access to your created profile and personal audio recordings is behind a paywall of over $30. When will I be able to re-record? When can I delete my recording? This raises security concerns"]},{"issue":"Inaccurate speech detection and unreliable push notifications","frequency":"medium","severity":"major","sampleQuotes":["I would be alerted even though I did not say the crutch word and at times when I did I wasn't alerted","The push notifications didn't work even though it was turned on"]}],"featureRequests":[],"praisedAspects":["Apple Watch integration works well when functional","Help with building confidence for some users"],"summary":"Credible: Speech Coach receives overwhelmingly negative feedback with critical issues that severely damage user trust. The primary complaint is an aggressive paywall that locks users out before they can try the app's features, with no trial option. Multiple users report that core functionality is broken or inaccurate, including failed speech detection and non-functional UI elements. Security concerns about personal recordings being locked behind paywalls add to user frustration. The aggressive monetization strategy combined with poor app performance makes this an app most users strongly advise against downloading."},"score":{"marketSize":14,"dissatisfaction":15,"feasibility":72,"compositeScore":32},"scanId":"fceeb718-5c98-4761-b59a-4f7d7f1fc08b","createdAt":"2026-03-08T15:47:42.992Z","gapAnalysis":null,"blueOcean":null}}

data: {"type":"opportunity","opportunity":{"id":"47ffb449-c670-47e2-af00-73801a26b943","scrapedApp":{"id":"371562064","title":"Public Speaking with AJ","store":"app_store","genre":"Business","score":4,"ratings":5,"reviewCount":10,"installs":"N/A","description":"Public speaking, delivering a presentation, making a speech - these seemingly simple tasks can be nerve-racking for many people. A high percentage of people feel some anxiety about speaking in public, in fact, it is commonly thought that this phobia is many peoples number one fear. \n\nThe overwhelming physical and emotional symptoms are all too real to those who suffer from it. \n\nThis Public Speaking app has been designed to help you overcome your public speaking anxiety by using the amazing resources of your unconscious mind. Deliver a professional performance with confidence, motivation and self-control are restored and new positive thoughts, habits and behaviours and created. \n\n  • Positive suggestions within this app. \n  • Build your confidence. \n  • Remain centred, calm, and relaxed.\n  • Experience wonderful feelings of success.\n\nDestress, improve your mindset, sleep better, grow your confidence and be healthier with guided meditations, mindfulness sessions and positive messages – and much more.\n\nMindfulness expert, coach and therapist Andrew Johnson has been helping people deal with life’s challenges with guided relaxations, meditations, self-care tools and breathing exercises for many years. \n\nHis best-selling range of mindfulness apps have a variety of content to help you, whether you are looking for ways to reduce stress and anxiety, lose weight, improve your health & confidence, learn relaxation techniques, etc.\n\nKey features:\n\n  • Short meditations you can do anywhere: at work, commuting, at home, walking.\n\n  • Inspirational sessions to help you tackle life’s challenges, to be calm and find clarity.\n\n  • Mindfulness stories and talks to help you build better, healthy habits.\n\nMeditations to help you feel inspired and find motivated to eat well, workout and stay healthy both in body and mind.\n\nRelaxation techniques and tools to help you sleep better every night, to wake feeling energised and refreshed.\n\nBreathing exercises and calming meditations for anxiety, panic attacks and stress relief.\n\nMeditation sessions to stop anxiety in its tracks and release stress.\n\nHow do I get more?\n\nStart your day mindfully, keep feeling positive and be inspired throughout the day with a range of guided meditations to help during tough or stressful moments. Boost your energy with a Power Nap, stay focussed to Beat Procrastination, and then drift off using a Deep Sleep meditation for a restful night.\n\nThink of Andrew as your personal mindfulness coach, always there to help when you need him most.\n\nSearch for Andrew Johnson to unlock more daily mindfulness and guided meditation sessions.","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple116/v4/b7/a5/c2/b7a5c25c-a48a-7542-2628-7cc6d9ef02a3/contsched.lgxiatfh.png/512x512bb.jpg","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/public-speaking-with-aj/id371562064?uo=4","developer":"Universal Relaxation Ltd","isEstimatedInstalls":false,"price":2.99,"free":false,"histogram":{"1":0,"2":1,"3":1,"4":0,"5":3}},"reviews":[{"id":"706821698","text":"Woo hoo!! Recommend A+. So, I have never been into these relaxation tech. however, I started to believe it when I came across Andrew J.'s app .. I was actually one of those people who laughed at people who use relax techniques ... and I thought it was all fake... little did I know that with the right app... you will believe it allll.... I've been using other AJ apps and I love it. I just started to use this pub speaking one ... I am not fully sure... But I had a brief presentation & I didn't freak like I usually do and I was able to improvise with out freaking out when I was looking at people!\n\nNote to Andrew: I wish you had a 3 apps in 1 where it helps with public speaking, confidence and positivity lol ... Or something of that sort because at nights I don't know which one I want to listen too...lol\n-- His voice is awesome... Other apps Ive tried in the past have freaked me out! AJ has the best voice and accent!","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"488284049","text":"Great app. It really help me over come public speaking and also with performing thank you!!!","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"414571699","text":"Addicted!. I am a public speech teacher and I am very impress with this app. \n\nThe first thing I noticed is that I am more connected in what I teach and with my audience. \n\nAnother thing I speak more clearly and directly with confidence. \n\nI also feel more clear and relax before speaking in front of hundreds of people. \n\nI've been speaking for more than fifteen years and I've already more improvements after a month. \n\nIt is not an app that fixes but improve you as a person. \n\nJust try this with an open and willing mind. Thx!","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"389064815","text":"Good but pricey app.. This is a pretty decent app but it's kind of pricey. It would be well worth the money if it addressed more issues and solutions related to public speaking. \n\nThe app is more focused on getting you to relax, which if fine, but you also wanted to get over your fear of public speaking. After all that's you sought after the app and bought it in the first place.\n\nLike I said it's a good app, but the price is questionable for what you receive within in app. Just don't expect an end all solution with this app...","score":3,"date":""},{"id":"376258623","text":"Awesome!!!. I have seen very positive results. Could you make an app for stuttering.","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"349383461","text":"Please create one for SELF-DISCIPLINE & PROCRASTINATION!!!!. Discovered the Andrew Johnson apps a few weeks ago. Never tried anything like this before, but I love them! Deep Sleep works like a charm, and Public Speaking was helpful the day of a big presentation. I'd LOVE to see one aimed at increasing self-discipline and overcoming procrastination. I'm a writer who struggles to maintain a daily writing practice and I'd be curious to see if one of these recordings might help with facing the blank page and accomplishing my word count without being defeated by procrastination and its evil twin, perfectionism. Please consider it? I'll bet there are many others who'd be interested as well! Thanks........","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"326442117","text":"Great app. Gives exactly the right encouragement and confidence. I tried it for two weeks before presenting at an international conference and my performance was totally different to past experience. I enjoyed it and have never had such good feedback. Even got offered *** after!","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"284295960","text":"Right Time for this App. The release of this app came at a good time for me. Last Friday I had to teach an audition lesson for a job I am applying for. I downloaded the app on Wednesday and used it twice before Friday.\n\nUsually they say you should use these apps daily for 3 weeks, but since I've been using Andrew Johnson's apps for several months now, I was able to benefit immediately. I was already well practiced in the self-hypnosis techniques and I had already developed a familiarity with, and trust in, Andrew Johnson's voice.\n\nThe audition lesson went well. I think it would have been OK anyway, but I could tell that I was more relaxed, confident and optimistic from having used the app. Some of the concrete directions from the app, such as making eye contact, breathing out and relaxing, etc., came to my mind before and during the audition.\n\nSince I am already familiar with other Andrew Johnson apps, such as Deep Sleep, Relax and others, I was pleased to find some new techniques being tried in this one. For example, I appreciated that the directions to relax muscles happened twice during the session, rather than only once at the beginning as in the other apps. That felt particularly good and right.","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"283852283","text":"Well done. Very helpful. I have quite a few of Andrews apps and like all the others this one is very good. I gave another public speaking fear app and they are both helpful but Andrews is much better. His voice just puts me at ease. Thank you mr Johnson.","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"281395436","text":"Nice. Sweet stuff yo","score":5,"date":""}],"sentiment":{"overallSentiment":"positive","painPoints":[{"issue":"App pricing is high relative to the scope of features offered","frequency":"low","severity":"minor","sampleQuotes":["This is a pretty decent app but it's kind of pricey","It would be well worth the money if it addressed more issues and solutions related to public speaking"]}],"featureRequests":[{"feature":"Bundled app combining public speaking, confidence, and positivity content","demand":"medium","sampleQuotes":["I wish you had a 3 apps in 1 where it helps with public speaking, confidence and positivity"]},{"feature":"Additional apps for stuttering and speech disorders","demand":"low","sampleQuotes":["Could you make an app for stuttering"]}],"praisedAspects":["Andrew Johnson's voice is calming, soothing, and highly effective","App produces measurable improvements in confidence and performance","Combines relaxation techniques with practical speaking advice","Teacher-approved and effective for professionals","Well-designed progressive muscle relaxation twice during sessions","Effective for reducing anxiety and improving clarity","Quick results even with minimal use before presentations"],"summary":"Public Speaking with AJ receives overwhelmingly positive feedback from users who report genuine improvements in their speaking abilities and confidence. Users consistently praise Andrew Johnson's calming voice and the app's self-hypnosis techniques. Many report concrete improvements after just one or two sessions, including reduced anxiety, better eye contact, and improved performance during presentations and auditions. The main criticism is that the premium pricing is somewhat high for an app focused primarily on relaxation rather than comprehensive public speaking training techniques."},"score":{"marketSize":14,"dissatisfaction":25,"feasibility":72,"compositeScore":36},"scanId":"fceeb718-5c98-4761-b59a-4f7d7f1fc08b","createdAt":"2026-03-08T15:47:43.229Z","gapAnalysis":null,"blueOcean":null}}

