data: {"type":"opportunity","opportunity":{"id":"a28ea85c-d22b-4927-a5b1-bea99cc6a385","scrapedApp":{"id":"6744358897","title":"LangLearn: AI English Tutor","store":"app_store","genre":"6017","score":0,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":50,"installs":"N/A","description":"Break Language Barriers with AI—Learn Language Anytime, Anywhere!\nLangLearn is your personalized AI language companion. It adapts to your level, goals, and busy life. Whether you're a beginner, a professional, or a traveler, LangLearn helps you speak English and Spanish fluently with speaking practice, grammar, vocabulary, and real-world immersion in quick, fun lessons.\n\n◆ For Every Level: Tailored Learning Paths ◆\n-Beginners: Start with the Basics!\n*Learn essential greetings, basic grammar (e.g., \"I am/he is\"), vocabulary and survival phrases for travel with AI.\n*Build confidence by practicing with AI in real-life situations like ordering food or asking for directions.\n-Intermediate Learners: Think Deeper, Speak Smoother!\n*Have debates, tell stories, or roleplay workplace meetings with AI.\n*Improve grammar and vocabulary by correcting mistakes with tailored feedback (e.g., \"If I were...\" vs. \"If I was...\").\n-Advanced Speakers: Perfect Your Edge!\n*Master idioms, refine writing, or focus on accent reduction.\n*Tackle expert scenarios like negotiating, giving TED talks, or analyzing news and vocabulary with AI.\n\n◆ For Every Scenario: Learn Exactly What You Need, Right When You Need It ◆\n-Traveler Mode: Master travel Language—practice airport conversations, hotel check-ins, directions, and cultural tips for a smooth trip.\n-Career Mode: Improve professional Terms. Practice job interviews, listening, write emails, and give presentations with confidence. Get feedback with prompts like “Pitch your idea to an AI CEO.”\n-Exam Mode: Ace language tests like TOEFL and IELTS. Take timed listening and speaking simulations with AI scoring to know exactly where to improve.\n-Daily Life Mode: Practice everyday phrase. Chat about hobbies, movies, tech trends, or anything you enjoy—make learning fun and easy!\n\n\n◆ Learn in 10 Minutes a Day ◆\nShort on time? No problem! LangLearn fits into your everyday life, helping you improve your spoken language no matter where you are.\n-During Your Commute: Turn traffic or transit time into productive practice with hands-free AI lessons for real-life conversations.\n-While Getting Ready: Use your morning or evening routine to listen to short lessons or practice phrases aloud, building fluency with the AI.\n-Before Bed: Let AI summarize your day’s learning in minutes, highlighting your strengths, new vocabulary, and areas to improve, so you’re ready for the next day.\n\n\n◆ Your Personal AI Language Coach: Patient, Intelligent, and Always There for You ◆\n-Real-Time Speech Feedback: Speak with confidence! Get instant, precise analysis on your pronunciation, intonation, and fluency—like “Your ‘th’ sounds a bit like ‘d’—let’s practice together!” Receive practical tips that really make a difference.\n-Personalized Challenges: Say goodbye to one-size-fits-all. Your AI coach continuously tracks your progress and adapts lesson difficulty—so you’re always challenged, but never overwhelmed or bored.\nEncouragement & Emotional Support: Feeling stuck or stressed? Your AI coach notices and offers uplifting words and mindful tips. Learn at your own pace, with kind support every step of the way.\n\n================================\n\nSubscription terms:\nUnlock unlimited access to everything in the app and take your spoken language to the next level\nApp Store offers auto-renewing subscriptions with unlimited access. Your subscription will automatically renew at the end of each subscription term unless you turn off the auto-renewal in your iPhone Settings, at least 24 hours before the current period ends.\n\n================================\n\nHave questions or feedback about LangLearn? We’re here to help!\nFeel free to reach out to us at langlearn08@gmail.com — we’d love to hear from you.\nPrivacy Policy: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1Gm-6qZNcbzfIM3fMfXlL96Yh21vVNekcrC60TRubtv8/edit?usp=sharing\nTerms and Conditions: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1zx1O3PCJzIazkmOaXYmLvUVUASmpsINMMAGw72f020M/edit?usp=sharing","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/80/24/81/80248194-7d71-d536-a1c3-7b50efd465e5/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-11-0-85-220.png/100x100bb.png","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/langlearn-ai-english-tutor/id6744358897?uo=2","developer":"AIFLAME TECHNOLOGY PTE. LTD.","isEstimatedInstalls":false},"reviews":[{"id":"13805338342","text":"the best AI tutor. I’m obsessed with the AI tutor—it’s so much less stressful than talking to a real person when you're just starting out. Also, the songs are such a vibe! It’s a genius way to pick up slang and typical phrases without it feeling like study time.","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13792569575","text":"Fraude. Esta App se presenta como gratuita y luego comienzan a facturar y si la bloqueas te bloquean las formas de pago.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13785720445","text":"A Favorite.. I’ve tried Others… LangLearn is in a Class\nof its’ own. Not only Effective — it’s downright Enjoyable.\nI now feel like I’m going to actually be speaking Spanish!","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13743208918","text":"Inglês para iniciantes. 10","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13727861495","text":"🤷🏾‍♀️. Fiz o pagamento mas não estou conseguindo acessar para estudar","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13725124112","text":"Не верю. Пишут что первых 7 дней безплатно но при этом сразу программа требует оплату, мне это не нравится!!!","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13706637429","text":"Audio problems. The audio is not working for several days and report the problem and lt didn’t fix it.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13698437239","text":"Tita. Good","score":4,"date":""},{"id":"13686925357","text":"Bad. Boktan bir proğram haftalık 10 dolar kesinlikle etmez","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13625119273","text":"China. Chinita","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13597955953","text":"Ai slop.. Ai everywhere. Not paying for something made so cheaply, I’m good.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13588030143","text":"Dónde está la música?. Compré la membresia y no consigo aún las canciones para aprender, dónde está eso??  O es parte de un engaño?","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13532029336","text":"Good. Nice","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13480098971","text":"Shairvgea. Que te has comprado para","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13459548131","text":"Dinero perdido. No me permite abrir en mi table la tengo descargada en mi celular","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13405605733","text":"Learning. Good","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13399263203","text":"App doesn’t teach Spanish with music. App is not recommended","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13367991872","text":"Excelente. La mejor","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13363952887","text":"Fraud. Absolutely terrible. App stops working and keeps asking me to pay again. I ended up getting charged monthly rate 12 times in a span of a week. This is absolute fraud. No customer service. Won’t give me my money back. I will report to better business buearue if they dont reply.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13358977972","text":"Impossible to cancel. Deceptive cancellation practices. Nothing should be this hard. Complete money grab.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13319675608","text":"Took my money. Took my money and would not let me use the app","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13302563184","text":"Ejemplos muy auténticos. Me encantan los ejemplos reales que usan en las lecciones de trabajo, suenan muy naturales.","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13297711337","text":"Not bad…. It’s actually not that bad. For someone wanting to learn. It’s a pretty good app.","score":3,"date":""},{"id":"13297402767","text":"Good. 5","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13280536586","text":"I’m learning. I don’t understand what I am doing. On TikTok the advertisement got me like it was going to be easy to use. I am disappointed. I don’t know how to get help with this app.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13229394426","text":"Cancelar Suscripción. No existe manera de cancelar esta suscripción, escribo correos sin respuesta. Quien me informa.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13225188994","text":"no se puede cancelar la membresía. esta app es pésima no se puede cancelar la membresía ya intenté de muchas maneras","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13208168467","text":"No se dejen engañar. Necesito mi dinero me he cansado de enviarles correo ustedes me cobraron 99 dolares cuando eso decia 0.27 centavos necesito mi dinero esto fue un fraude porque no responden los email ? Porque ni en la aplicacion eso cuesta 99 dolares necesito un reembolso eso fue muy robar de parte de ustedes jugando con publicidad engañosa","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13202218346","text":"I love this app😍😍. Thank you for this app. I love it is my favorite app.\nThank you","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13194716353","text":"Cambie mi iPhone y ahora no me agarra mi suscripción anual. Necesito ayuda cambie mi iPhone y no me agarra ahora mi suscripción anual. La pagué por un  año necesito que resuelvan por favor","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13189666778","text":"Đăng ký. Khi đăng kí rồi muốn cancel không được","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13180481794","text":"La app. Me pide dinero y dices que gratis las primeras 100 lo siento no podré","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13168614895","text":"Mala. Engañosa","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13161769213","text":"Me ciento bien. Me gusta","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13121590482","text":"Alexander. Trailer1975","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13040242483","text":"Nota. Muy bueno","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13032388853","text":"Not good. This is an app that poorly uses AI to teach. Need to get a refund.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13030236797","text":"Goly. Mi amor","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13027581650","text":"Aprender. Inglés","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13026992777","text":"It’s good if free. Hy thank you for launching app like this if it’s is free","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13024942838","text":"Quiero hablar inglés. Blancarosa","score":3,"date":""},{"id":"13017598584","text":"Nada que ver la App con lo que promocionan. No entiendo la App. Incluso nada de lo que utilizan para promocionarla, lo encuentras.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13017452227","text":"W. Y","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13010733841","text":"La mejor aplicación. Me encanta esta aplicación , la recomiendo","score":4,"date":""},{"id":"12977597674","text":"Terrible. The app has no way of changing the language you want to learn. Once you pick the language, you’re locked in. Also navigating the app and finding what you’re looking for is a hassle.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"12977185539","text":"Regular. Se contesta solo ni deja hablar no escucha lo que dice uno","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"12948555834","text":"No se’. It’s a little pricey for my likin.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"12942872564","text":"Excelente. Ayuda demasiado 💙🩵💙🩵","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"12932518370","text":"Canceled. Cancel","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"12908941436","text":"would give zero stars. why would the AI ask what my native language is, then say whats your purpose for learning English?!! That alone made me want to throw this app in the trash","score":1,"date":""}],"sentiment":{"overallSentiment":"mixed","painPoints":[{"issue":"Deceptive free trial and unexpected billing charges","frequency":"high","severity":"critical","sampleQuotes":["Esta App se presenta como gratuita y luego comienzan a facturar y si la bloqueas te bloquean las formas de pago.","Пишут что первых 7 дней безплатно но при этом сразу программа требует оплату, мне это не нравится!!!"]},{"issue":"Audio technical problems not being resolved","frequency":"medium","severity":"major","sampleQuotes":["The audio is not working for several days and report the problem and lt didn't fix it."]},{"issue":"Payment processing and account access issues","frequency":"medium","severity":"major","sampleQuotes":["Fiz o pagamento mas não estou conseguindo acessar para estudar"]},{"issue":"High subscription costs","frequency":"medium","severity":"major","sampleQuotes":["haftalık 10 dolar kesinlikle etmez"]}],"featureRequests":[],"praisedAspects":["Effective and enjoyable learning experience","Non-stressful interaction with AI tutor compared to human interaction","Innovative song-based learning method for slang and phrases","Superior to competing apps","Suitable for beginners"],"summary":"LangLearn has a divided user base with strong praise for its AI tutor effectiveness and innovative song-based learning approach, but significant frustration regarding deceptive billing practices, unexpected charges despite free trial claims, audio technical issues, and high subscription costs. Core users who engage with the platform love the experience, but billing transparency and technical reliability are critical concerns."},"score":{"marketSize":14,"dissatisfaction":25,"feasibility":72,"compositeScore":36},"scanId":"fceeb718-5c98-4761-b59a-4f7d7f1fc08b","createdAt":"2026-03-08T15:48:27.116Z","gapAnalysis":null,"blueOcean":null}}

data: {"type":"opportunity","opportunity":{"id":"e57689d7-92de-48c9-8fad-537724bb8eb3","scrapedApp":{"id":"557130558","title":"HelloTalk - Language Learning","store":"app_store","genre":"6017","score":0,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":50,"installs":"N/A","description":"Practice languages with native speakers on HelloTalk! We recently introduced HelloTalk Live and Voiceroom - interactive language and culture events to help you master languages through the content you love!  \n \nHelloTalk, the original language exchange app, connects you with native speakers to practice languages (English, Japanese, Korean, Spanish, French, Mandarin Chinese, Portuguese, German, Italian, Russian, Arabic, Turkish, Hindi, Indonesian, Thai, Vietnamese and 260+ more) for FREE!  \n\nHelloTalk equips you with learning tools such as translation and instant captions so you can learn by chatting with native speakers. Learn languages from locals around the world through livestreams and Voicerooms. Connect with expert hosts to discuss interesting topics with language partners in the learning community! \n\nWhy HelloTalk? \n\n► Real language learning atmosphere \nWhether you're focused on a widely spoken language or a less common one, HelloTalk caters to your needs. The system smartly matches you based on your native language and proficiency, while allowing you to filter ideal language partners according to various criteria such as age, location, and gender. Plus, with built-in translation and transliteration tools, you can communicate confidently without any language barriers.\n\n► A powerful tool for sharpening your language skills\nAcquiring new words through conversations with native speakers is more effective than rigid memorization. Whether you're a student preparing for exams like the CET, GRE, TOEFL, IELTS, planning to study abroad, or a professional seeking career advancement through language skills, HelloTalk offers native speakers who match your proficiency level for engaging interactions and valuable learning experiences.\n\n► Immersive multi-person language chat rooms\nIf you choose to learn Spanish, for example, every Voiceroom you enter on HelloTalk gathers Spanish learners and Spanish native speakers from around the world to discuss interesting topics. Here, only your voice needs to be heard, creating a comfortable, introvert-friendly atmosphere. Here, sharing mutual interests allows everyone to freely express themselves and share personal experiences, fostering both language intuition and authentic expression skills. It's incredibly addictive!\n\n► Diverse global Livestreams\nHelloTalk features handpicked foreign language hosts who offer online video lessons, share language insights, and provide glimpses into their lives abroad. You can even join them on stage for one-on-one video conversations with fellow language learners. Whether you're grappling with pronunciation, speaking speed, or shyness, these hosts will assist you in refining your language skills and guiding the conversation. For rapid improvement in spoken language, there's no substitute for direct communication with native speakers!\n\n► International Moments\nHelloTalk's Moments offers real-time posts covering learning, lifestyle, and cultural insights from around the world. It's your ticket to discovering fresh perspectives and gaining deeper insights into diverse cultural customs, all from the comfort of your home. Don't forget to engage with posts that catch your interest!\n\nWhat the world is saying about HelloTalk\n“One of the best apps to help you learn a new language.” - 9to5Mac \n\"When you're ready to experiment with a foreign language, HelloTalk provides an excellent opportunity for interaction with other speakers.\" –PCMag \n\"HelloTalk, which connects native speakers with an apprentice, also offers language exchanges to its 20 million users in more than 150 languages.\" -Forbes \n\nSTART PRACTICING LANGUAGES RIGHT AWAY!!!\n\nLearn more about the HelloTalk app: \n- Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/Hellotalk/ \n- Twitter: https://twitter.com/hellotalkapp \n\nSend any feedback to support@hellotalk.com \n- Privacy Policy: https://www.hellotalk.com/privacy-policy \n- Terms of Use: https://www.hellotalk.com/terms-of-service","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/7e/38/7f/7e387f11-d551-8675-3b97-a0f2d0812c24/AppIcon-0-0-1x_U007epad-0-1-0-0-85-220.png/100x100bb.png","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/hellotalk-language-learning/id557130558?uo=2","developer":"HELLOTALK FOREIGN LANGUAGE EXCHANGE LEARNING TALK CHAT APP","isEstimatedInstalls":false},"reviews":[{"id":"13821661703","text":"Love It. Love It","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13820847670","text":"掉钱眼里了. Ai翻译都需要会员，这真的很不应该","score":2,"date":""},{"id":"13819231407","text":"Worthless. A day after paying for VIP, they deactivated account. After contacting their support, I received horrendous and impersonal service. Stay far away from this app.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13818452921","text":"Two Stars. I gave the app two stars because I got this app on Sunday and deleted it Thursday no one here helps you learn they say a few words and leave and I got messages mostly from men it needs a lot of improvement like not allowing certain words to be sent in messages and only focused on sending messages related to languages somehow because people treat this app like a dating app not for learning a language","score":2,"date":""},{"id":"13818449601","text":"egyptian men. egyptian men harass you on here","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13817267247","text":"Honestly total garbage.. Been on this for several weeks, beyond the AI assistant, and the HelloTalk team, no one seems to respond or want to chat at all. Not worth it. Save your money and go outside and talk to a human being.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13810601789","text":"Actually the worst. Customer help doesn’t exist here. They just want your money. And they’ve gotten mine. But yet they still don’t help. I bought lifetime vip years ago bc if you’re not vip, you only get 2 hours in a voiceroom a day. That does nothing. I’ve had a whiteboard bug and it doesn’t work and they basically told me “that sucks, oh well” and closed the ticket. And when I open a new one expressing my frustration, especially since I deleted the app, lost all my data and reinstalled to try to fix it myself they just told me to “be patient” they’re not even working on it. I’m actually so frustrated don’t even waste your time/money on here.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13802883781","text":"Not good anymore. This app used to be great back in the day in 2015…but now it’s just gone down hill. I’m getting way many messages from people who don’t even speak the language that I’m trying to learn than from people who actually speak the language. Sorry Ramesh from India, unless you are fluent in Finnish, then there’s no reason for us to be talking.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13798792281","text":"Fun. I really like this app but sometimes the people can be rude or inappropriate","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13796458242","text":"What happened to me. Because some people can text you back but apart from that it good","score":4,"date":""},{"id":"13793050210","text":"Nonsense. I downloaded this app and signed up many years ago but rarely logged in. I picked this up recently,  and wanted to try to make some new friends. I was always polite, and even a little shy — I actually rarely talked out loud, and one of the things I enjoyed was to enter a public voice room and sit under the stage and listen to others talking. I did find some interesting hosts and loved their pronunciation and humor. But suddenly one day my account was blocked, saying my behaviors violated the community rules and was reported by multiple users. What have I done wrong? Keep silent? I tried to argue but only got a response that needs my video selfie with my personal information, otherwise I cannot create another account on my phone. Nope! I did nothing wrong and it is your responsibility to censor whether a user violates the rules. It’s completely unreasonable to block a user without any evidence and ask the innocence to provide information!","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13791608879","text":"Không thao tác được. Lâu không vào nay vào thì không nhắn tin được, không đâng ảnh được là sao ???","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13788364369","text":"Mmmm. I wish if we can join an unlimited live for free","score":2,"date":""},{"id":"13781958768","text":"Bad.. I just downloaded like 5 mins kater it asked for a phone number Im on iPad.and it says it notice unusual activity on my account.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13773641136","text":"Weirdos. This guy he was Chinese and he would try to stalk me and try to get a hold of me by texting my friends on instagram even tho idk how he got it I don’t even remember giving it to him. So guys be careful who you talk to because these people can be weird they would send u pics of their junk and try to make you send some… not just guys even girls..","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13772222874","text":"Can’t see others moments. UI in ipad has some bugs，especially when you enter a voice room and view profile，you cant go back to see the screen of the voice room but you can still hear people talking","score":2,"date":""},{"id":"13770873248","text":"Privacy??. I find the map pinpointing your location as a cover photo being behind a paywall to change it WEIRD. I’m a woman I like to protect my privacy not give an exact map location of where I am to the world. I was excited to use this to language learn but now I’m just anxious cause of the lack of privacy..","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13767438146","text":"fake. 8 out of 10 accts contact me are fake\nht just takes your money and lets fake accts take over","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13766476464","text":"A Few Notes…. Why does this it feel like I’m on tiktok shop when I’m on this app? Lol, but anyways, the free version is ok to say the least, but hate that all the necessary options (i.e., choose gender, location, languages I know, more languages I want to learn, etc) are paywalled behind a subscription. I actually love the social media aspect and the voice chat rooms but they need to be monitored, I’ve personally seen bullying, gross NSFW comments on posts and straight up sexism, homophobia and racism be openly displayed here. So beware of the weirdos 😤 Other than that, great way to learn!","score":4,"date":""},{"id":"13764979252","text":"Can’t log in. Can’t log in.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13761419979","text":"Has potential. Bad app, bans too easy and no appeal","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13752287900","text":"Bored. Nobody replied my message back","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13749378542","text":"so laggy and inefficient. servers are very slow and lag a lot. sometimes messages aren’t even sent. a lot of people on the app use it as a dating app rather than for its actual purpose. it’s full of ai slop now.","score":2,"date":""},{"id":"13748630225","text":"Clickbait Marketing. Making tons of clickbait, manufactured controversies, and racially charged or sexual divisive posts","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13747153742","text":"Constant ads shoved down your throat. As the title says. It’s ridiculous. I used to use this app in 2019 and it was much better then.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13745603935","text":"Can’t create an account. Can’t create another account because last account was followed by scammers and stalkers. Thank you Hellotalk. You will get more negative reviews from this because there are people who actually want to learn a language and you have shut them out.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13740792744","text":"Could be better. I like this app but I must say to have basic translate you need to pay extra don't make sense for a languages app. To pay extra and still not have unlimited perks is greedy. I pay for vip and you limit the amount of people I can interact with ?  to have to pay for the year to have some sort of exclusive vip services is just annoying . The app already comes with things to have to pay for, I don't understand why translate when communicating is something I would need to worry about . The app is ok but its perks aren't perks when you think about it .  But everything is a money guzzler and it's annoying especially in these times","score":3,"date":""},{"id":"13739943376","text":"广告. 垃圾中的垃圾","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13739437525","text":"I love the app, but web version doesn’t work.. Says {\"message\":\"missing or malformed jwt\"}. You should probably get that fixed","score":4,"date":""},{"id":"13729443221","text":"App completely broke. A friend of mine told me the other day they could no longer see on HelloTalk. I went in my account and was messaging people, nobody received my messages. I can no longer join voice rooms. There are Reddit threads with people with this issue for 3 years! No message or notification about why, completely random.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13727803163","text":"Annoying. It’s like a spam caller… if the spam caller not only wanted you to buy something, but also force you to learn German against your will","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13725978455","text":"Sign in sucks. Tried signing in with my Apple and it didn’t work no matter what.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13711724593","text":"Too many bugs. I just deleted a conversation with one person and for some reason it also deleted my conversation with the person I have pinned. Now I’ve lost months worth of memories and pictures.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13697798485","text":"Privacy Issues. In the set up, there should be an immediate option to limit the gender of those who can see you. It was not part of the set up and I was immediately bombarded with tons of messages from men using this as a dating app. Also, a man found my information and sent me a message off of the app. There needs to be stricter safety and security.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13683543868","text":"没有人权，自由的app，跟中国很多app一样. 没有人权，自由的app，跟中国很多app一样","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13682758492","text":"My account was permanently deleted without warning. So I guess if you even mention what religion or faith you have you will be banned without warning. Even if you are just genuinely having a conversation with your friend. I had payed for VIP to better learn russian and now my money was wasted. I wasn't preaching to everyone I met. The questions just came up as we got to know each other. I recommend going to the app \"Tandem\" instead","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13681324709","text":"Bad. people in this app are quite rude. Especially Aussie.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13676078836","text":"Good language exchange app, but has new design. This app is great for connecting with other people in the world to practice language learning. It has some handy features like the translate button for messages. However, the app has a new design WITH ADS, and the menus are confusing to navigate. The app almost feels like a casino or like a gaming app. It had a much better layout years ago. I’ll also add that it appears that messages are not saved in any cloud storage system of any kind, so it seems they’re only stored as long as the app is on your phone, which might be an inconvenience for people if they get a new phone and reinstall the app.","score":3,"date":""},{"id":"13670048883","text":"Misleading. You’re exclusively talking to ai and even buying the full subscription it allows you many 5 sentences before it asks you to spend more\nMoney. I regret the year subscription. It’s a con with fees every step.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13668601041","text":"Not Deaf Friendly. I think HelloTalk is a cool app and a good place to meeting people, make new friends, and learn about different languages and cultures. Unfortunately, I have visited several lives and found that a few of them are not friendly due to my deafness. I wish HelloTalk were more deaf-friendly, offering features such as speech-to-text and sign language capabilities. When I updated bio and disclosed that I’m Deaf individual. They not even engage in conversation with me. Also there’s no sign language feature.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13664415769","text":"Appreciation. Thank you so much for your efforts,\nI want to say that \nIn this last two weeks we as Iranian in Iran had not access to internet connection so please give us a chance to keep our streaks save.haha\nBye 👋🏻","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13663402197","text":"Verification Code never came and VIP ads. The new update requires me to add my phone number, which I don’t want to, since I already log in through Gmail. I wanted to keep in touch with the friends I’ve made, so I added my number to get the verification code, but it never came through messages and calls after multiple attempts. I can’t even remove that pop up to get access to my own account.\n\nI also keep getting in-app ads for VIP which is just annoying. If there was a checkbox to disable the pop-ups for the day, it would’ve been bearable.\n\nGiving 3-stars because the app helped me find decent language partners and make international connections.","score":3,"date":""},{"id":"13662621387","text":"Not a good experience at all.. The interface of this app looks like those scam pages. Tons of color, things popping out at you, constant ads. There’s way too many buttons and doesn’t make for easy navigation at all and keeps continuously getting worse. \n\nOnly thing this app has going for it is the chat rooms. I’ve been on social media for over 20 years and it’s a hassle just to change your profile photo on this app. It’s crazy! \n\nI hope they hire a better designer to make this an easier experience for people who want to learn and make it look less like a dating app. It’s hard to connect with people with the way it currently operates. Not an enjoyable experience at all.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13654267073","text":"Ужасное приложение. Я не могу исправить родной язык, который указала по ошибки. За это требует денег :)","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13653365760","text":"Softcore dating app. “For You” tab is not personalized at all. And the whole app feels like a dating bait app. So many thirst trap pics and videos. It’s much easier and hassle free to use other AI app to learn language.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13651221116","text":"HelloTalk isn’t just a language learning platform, it’s community. I’ve met so many good people on HelloTalk. Yes, this app is filled with people seeking love, which is a con, but also, I’ve met some of the best humans on earth here, even having met several in real life having traveled thousands of miles to meet new friends. They aren’t just friends, it’s like family around the world. Language breaks down walls, connects culture, shares value. And it’s made me appreciate our similarities and differences across cultures and distances and more about what the human experience is all about. To say this all has change my life is an understatement. It’s reshaped me in every way for the better. I haven’t used a lot of the new tools they have, most connecting with other people, but.. I’m so grateful for my HelloTalk journey.","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13649862014","text":"Not a choice but to put in the phone number. It won’t let me communicate with others unless I put my phone number in for a quicker login, which I don’t want to and it won’t give me an option to cancel it, so it’s not really giving me a choice","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13649642109","text":"A lot. Your app has a great concept, and I’m glad I found it. There’s a lot packed into it—voice rooms, memories, letters, and more—which can feel overwhelming at times. It may be trying to do too much at once. Additionally, it sometimes comes across as being used like a dating app, which feels a bit off-putting.\n\nOverall, I like the app and see a lot of potential, but I think it would benefit from scaling back some of the extra features and focusing on a more streamlined experience.","score":3,"date":""},{"id":"13648856520","text":"Great for making friends!. HelloTalk has been my go-to app since 2019-2020. Through it, I’ve made countless friends and learned some fantastic tips and tricks for learning Japanese. It’s an excellent platform for exploring different cultures, making new friends, and even helping someone learn your native language. :)","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13647737448","text":"Great concept, but there’s so many bugs in the app it’s almost unusable. The free version is FINE. Once you start paying for it, they no longer care about your experience. I hate these people","score":1,"date":""}],"sentiment":{"overallSentiment":"negative","painPoints":[{"issue":"Poor customer support and unresponsive help system","frequency":"high","severity":"critical","sampleQuotes":["Customer help doesn't exist here. They just want your money.","After contacting their support, I received horrendous and impersonal service."]},{"issue":"Harassment and safety issues from other users","frequency":"high","severity":"critical","sampleQuotes":["egyptian men harass you on here","I got messages mostly from men it needs a lot of improvement"]},{"issue":"Users not engaged in language learning, app used as dating platform","frequency":"high","severity":"major","sampleQuotes":["Beyond the AI assistant, and the HelloTalk team, no one seems to respond or want to chat at all.","I'm getting way many messages from people who don't even speak the language that I'm trying to learn"]},{"issue":"AI translation features locked behind premium paywall","frequency":"medium","severity":"major","sampleQuotes":["Ai翻译都需要会员，这真的很不应该"]},{"issue":"Technical bugs not being fixed","frequency":"medium","severity":"major","sampleQuotes":["I've had a whiteboard bug and it doesn't work and they basically told me 'that sucks, oh well' and closed the ticket."]},{"issue":"Limited free features (2 hours voice room limit)","frequency":"medium","severity":"major","sampleQuotes":["if you're not vip, you only get 2 hours in a voiceroom a day. That does nothing."]}],"featureRequests":[{"feature":"Better moderation and content filtering for messaging","demand":"high","sampleQuotes":["needs a lot of improvement like not allowing certain words to be sent in messages"]},{"feature":"Matching system to connect with actual language speakers","demand":"high","sampleQuotes":["only focused on sending messages related to languages somehow"]}],"praisedAspects":["Fun and engaging interface","AI assistant feature","Potential for language exchange"],"summary":"HelloTalk faces severe user dissatisfaction due to poor customer support, persistent harassment and safety issues, users misusing the platform as a dating app rather than for language learning, technical bugs that go unresolved, and aggressive monetization blocking core features. Despite some entertainment value, the app's inability to maintain quality control and support users has resulted in overwhelmingly negative sentiment."},"score":{"marketSize":14,"dissatisfaction":25,"feasibility":62,"compositeScore":33},"scanId":"fceeb718-5c98-4761-b59a-4f7d7f1fc08b","createdAt":"2026-03-08T15:48:27.948Z","gapAnalysis":null,"blueOcean":null}}

data: {"type":"opportunity","opportunity":{"id":"9b274a28-746a-4b81-a6ae-77f74b09a167","scrapedApp":{"id":"693689912","title":"IXL - Math, English, & More","store":"app_store","genre":"6017","score":0,"ratings":0,"reviewCount":50,"installs":"N/A","description":"IXL is personalized learning! Trusted by over 1 million educators and parents, IXL is proven to accelerate student achievement. And with the award-winning IXL app, students can master skills anytime, anywhere!\n\nSee how IXL meets the unique needs of over 17 million learners (and counting!):\n\nSUPERIOR SKILL-BUILDING\nWith IXL’s full curriculum of over 15,000 skills, students of all levels can learn the exact topics they need, whether they’re reviewing past concepts or exploring new territory. Immediate feedback and step-by-step answer explanations help students work through their mistakes and make lasting progress. Plus, question difficulty adapts to challenge students at just the right level and help them grow.\n\nMATH MASTERY\nWith IXL’s preK-12 curriculum, every learner can excel in math! From skip-counting with pictures to graphing quadratic functions, students interact with dynamic problem types that bring each concept to life. And with unlimited questions to explore, students can practice as much as they need to master each skill, and never see the same problem twice.\n\nENGLISH LEARNING\nIXL’s preK-12 curriculum helps build strong readers and writers! From comprehension to composition, IXL breaks down each concept into highly targeted skills that help students grow from where they are. Fun and relevant questions engage students as they learn new vocabulary, correct grammar mistakes, analyze text, strengthen writing skills, and more.\n\nSCIENCE, SOCIAL STUDIES, AND SPANISH\nBuild knowledge across all core subjects! With comprehensive curriculum in kindergarten through high school biology, chemistry, physics, civics, and U.S. history, students can learn exciting and relevant concepts about the world around them. And with foundational Spanish, students can get started on the path toward Spanish fluency!\n\nVIDEO TUTORIALS\nIXL's video tutorials help bring math and English concepts to life. Access 4,500+ videos for preK-12 math, as well as Pre-K through 8th grade English language arts skills.\n\nGAMES\nIXL’s interactive learning games make math and English fun! With 400+ educational games for pre-K through 5th grade, kids can explore reading, writing, grammar, spelling, math facts, counting, money, multiplication, and more. Through play-based learning, each game brings lessons to life with colorful worlds, animated characters, and hands-on practice—helping children build skills, confidence, and a lifelong love of learning.\n\nREAL-TIME DIAGNOSTIC\nIXL’s Real-Time Diagnostic pinpoints each student’s current knowledge level in math and English language arts. As students answer questions, they’ll discover more about themselves, and reveal personalized recommendations on the best skills to learn next!\n\nIMMERSIVE EXPERIENCE\nInteractive features, from drag-and-drop questions to graphing tools, allow students to engage with the material in new ways. With handwriting recognition, students can easily write in math answers with their fingertips. On iPad, students can work through each problem by writing on their screen—no scrap paper needed! Plus, colorful awards highlight students’ accomplishments and make learning fun!\n\nPROVEN RESULTS\nResearch has shown that IXL improves student outcomes more than any other product or method. IXL is trusted by over 1 million teachers worldwide!\n\nACTIONABLE ANALYTICS\nView reports on all progress on our website! Tackle any trouble spots with specific insights and clear next steps. And celebrate reaching each new milestone with an official certificate!\n\nPractice 10 questions each day for free. Become an IXL member to get access to a fully personalized learning experience with comprehensive curriculum, meaningful guidance, progress tracking, fun awards, and more!\n\nIXL is kidSAFE certified and COPPA-compliant. For more information, please visit:\nPrivacy Policy: https://www.ixl.com/privacypolicy","icon":"https://is1-ssl.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple221/v4/ed/9e/f1/ed9ef1ef-095b-37a9-4a50-36bd053a04eb/stable-0-0-1x_U007emarketing-0-7-0-85-220.png/100x100bb.png","url":"https://apps.apple.com/us/app/ixl-math-english-more/id693689912?uo=2","developer":"IXL Learning","isEstimatedInstalls":false},"reviews":[{"id":"13821629592","text":"Is amazing for me because l just started!. I. Love it","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13821235854","text":"Amazing but just 1 thing. Overall the app is amazing. I use it @ school all the time. But on my phone I don’t know my password. Can you please make a new way to sign in (Apple, Google, Clever etc.). THX","score":4,"date":""},{"id":"13821111598","text":"THIS SUCKS SO MUCH. I WAS AT 99 AND I WAS ON THE SAME THING FOR 2 HOURS AND I GOT INE WRONG AND A\nIT RESET ME.\n0 OUT OF 10 DO NOT RECCOMEND","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13820909857","text":"Worst APP EVER. Use other websites i was at 99 % got it worng now at 78 and I’m only getting 1% for every 1 question right","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13820187990","text":"Teagan 💜’s review. IXL helps you with math English more. It just helps you. It helps you with work. It helps you with everything. I’m a student of putting elementary and it help. Helps us with IXIXL just helps us with staff help with her with homework multiplication writing that nobody lie. It just helps makes it easier so join IXL guys. It’s really good.","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13817941744","text":"Great. This app is great. You should totally download it if you’re looking for a fun educational app for your kids","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13817443049","text":"ixl. I wonder what is wrong?\n You cid do it to","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13816145482","text":"🤮. Why does it set you back so much when you get a question wrong?! 1 star","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13815104824","text":"P-people actually like this app?. Hello, I get why this app was created. But I’m just going to say..my WHOLE CLASS HATES ixl. And so do I. If I am at 98-99 and I get ONE QUESTION WRONG it drops me down back to 85 or something. It genuinely pisses me and my parents off when they help me. (3/4/2026)","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13814336115","text":"Nice. This is making me smarter !I am the smartest in my whole class!","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13814215812","text":"Pls bring games back🤯🫵🧎. IT IS SO GOOD.but……..pls,on da website i neeeeeeeeeeeed theeeeee ggggggggaaaaaammmmmmmmmmmmeeeeeeeessssssss baaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaack. -sincerely,random guy","score":4,"date":""},{"id":"13814017068","text":"Review. I liked it but sometimes I press the right answer and it tells me that I am wrong it is still an good learning app","score":4,"date":""},{"id":"13813996494","text":"Makes me mad. I honestly think that this app should be deleted it make me mad amd make my eyes hurt because of the amount of time that this takes","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13810598918","text":"The time of thing I’ll almost made me crash out for is……. I tried to log in to I’ll bc Yk i was new an then i tried to log in to make a random user and pas but it did not work to then i just continued as a guest but then it let me do my work and then i went almost over the whole line and then it told me to stop and put a user and pass when i was newwwwww! This i rate it a 1-0 cus what is this.😡","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13810436246","text":"😚🙂🥰. It’s cool and nice and fun!!!🤩☺️","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13810204143","text":"Student's perspective. As a middle school student, IXL is a good source of education. My teacher assigned 100 IXLs to my class. IXL is very fusterating because sometimes you will only earn two points when you get it right, but go back 8 points when wrong. It isn't as bad as other educational apps, but as a student it is very fusterating. Coming from an advanced student who never got anything less than a 94%, this app is very fusterating, but also does have some good parts.","score":3,"date":""},{"id":"13807790619","text":"Like it. Love love love 💗","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13807625367","text":"IXL is wrong and doesn’t teach steps. Whenever I get to the challenge zone one thing wrong sends me back to 80%! I hate IXL it is the worst app ever","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13807564034","text":"Sucky app. H","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13807207807","text":"Stop making up lose points. Just imagine like ur 99% then u get a question wrong stop making us lose points it makes some of us rage and it's like ragebait but yes u do get of what u did wrong which is fine but STOP MAKING US LOSE POINTS","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13803416533","text":"Help me. This all sucks somebody save me from the torture of this app my school forces me to do this","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13803287391","text":"Good, but a lil frustrating at times, best when on computer or tablet. In my opinion its good for learning and such but the ‘get (x) questions correct in a row’ is a lil challenging and annoying for me.","score":3,"date":""},{"id":"13802967061","text":"Great app 🤩. I hated doing math but Ixl helps a lot great app you can use it for language Spanish and math and science.","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13800721906","text":": /. Hello IXL I think its grate that you offer learning  however  as a student  I have extreme anxiety and when I get one wrong it sets me way back and then I feel stupid so If you could please notot send me back and just stay and give me another problem I would probably like school a lot more","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13800355981","text":"A very great app. This app makes your kids really smart and it also is really fun.","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13799748997","text":"Not working. Every time I put a skill on it doesn’t work all it does is says check the internet but my internet was fine","score":2,"date":""},{"id":"13799514312","text":"IXL. It’s a good learning app to teach me and I love it","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13799356461","text":"Difficult and wrong. I’m a 8th grader and we’ve used IXL for 6 years I think. At this point the middle school teachers stopped giving IXLs unless admin tells them too because they know how bad it is. The smart score is super frustrating when you get farther in they start giving you 2 points and taking away 8 or 9. I know it’s supposed to be motivation but it’s really upsetting when you are on a super hard problem and you’re super tired and you just want to finish. Not to mention they also have wrong answers. I’m not just saying it’s bad because I don’t like it. IXL is genuinely a terrible app for learning.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13799228810","text":"Jaxon. I love this game","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13798837647","text":"IXL. There are games in IXL","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13796712147","text":"It’s ok. So this app is great for learning but it’s soooooo boring","score":3,"date":""},{"id":"13796576548","text":"OMG. Guys this app is so good it helps me learn so much! I wish it was like fun games you could play but I still love it!","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13796256203","text":"…. H?@ T..? 3      1.. ť ¡!","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13796060005","text":"I did good. Stupid app","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13795610986","text":"Dumb. Dumb","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13793337431","text":"Have a better system. Your stupid point system is garbage I answered 3 questions to get a total of 13 points but once I get one question wrong my 8 of my points get removed and after I got a question correct I got 1 point, maybe if you have a better system it will be less stressful and annoying.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13792983425","text":"Stinky. I have to do it for homework, but just now I answered the question and it told me that the correct answer was the same answer that I put in and it said that I was wrong","score":2,"date":""},{"id":"13789705608","text":"IXL. IXL is so fun my children get their work done on time","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13789613960","text":"I hate this. Would give it a zero if possible but it’s not.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13789139102","text":"Good but frustrating. It’s so hard to type this review","score":3,"date":""},{"id":"13789103893","text":"Warning!!!. It sucks. Do not try it.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13788811353","text":"Good. Assume i love it it helps me learn  and it teaches me","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13788647894","text":"I like it. It’s good","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13788519206","text":"Education is fun. I loved IXL and it deserves a 5 star rating! :D","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13787748404","text":"No. Ew. I’m a kid. I hate learning. Yet I was forced to get this app. Bleh.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13786126742","text":"Great app!. IXL  helped me get better at my math skills and hopefully I will do better on my EOG!","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13786055848","text":"My is Chinese and English so if it is wrong ops. IXL is frustrating because I did not click on something clearly and it was frustrating to me but it help me learn and it did make future lessons much easier in 4th grade.","score":4,"date":""},{"id":"13785740183","text":"Is not for some kids. Made my kids cry.","score":1,"date":""},{"id":"13785615682","text":"If it helps meh get better grades…. …then its an awesum app","score":5,"date":""},{"id":"13785580871","text":"ts stinks 🥹🥹🥹. i wld give ts -7089 stars if i could\n\n\nIVANTILL/ALNST REFERENCE MWAHAHHAHA\n\n\nanyways ts stinks of poo and lwk shld be banned ✌️✌️✌️\n\n\ntchers plz stop making me do ts bc its annoying af and i need help <333","score":1,"date":""}],"sentiment":{"overallSentiment":"mixed","painPoints":[{"issue":"Excessive progress reset when answering questions incorrectly","frequency":"high","severity":"critical","sampleQuotes":["I WAS AT 99 AND I WAS ON THE SAME THING FOR 2 HOURS AND I GOT INE WRONG AND A IT RESET ME.","If I am at 98-99 and I get ONE QUESTION WRONG it drops me down back to 85 or something."]},{"issue":"Unfair scoring system with disproportionate penalty for mistakes","frequency":"high","severity":"critical","sampleQuotes":["i was at 99 % got it worng now at 78 and I'm only getting 1% for every 1 question right","Why does it set you back so much when you get a question wrong?!"]},{"issue":"Password recovery and sign-in method limitations","frequency":"low","severity":"major","sampleQuotes":["on my phone I don't know my password. Can you please make a new way to sign in (Apple, Google, Clever etc.)."]}],"featureRequests":[{"feature":"Alternative sign-in methods (Apple, Google, Clever)","demand":"medium","sampleQuotes":["Can you please make a new way to sign in (Apple, Google, Clever etc.). THX"]},{"feature":"Less punitive progress system with fair point scaling","demand":"high","sampleQuotes":["Why does it set you back so much when you get a question wrong?!"]}],"praisedAspects":["Helps with homework and educational content","Effective learning tool for students","Makes learning easier and more fun","Comprehensive subject coverage","Improves student performance"],"summary":"IXL has polarized reviews with strong praise for its educational effectiveness and homework assistance, but critical frustration with its punitive progress reset system that severely penalizes minor mistakes. Users report losing significant progress percentages (from 99% to 78%) after single errors, which many feel is demotivating and unfair. The app's core learning benefits are undermined by a frustrating progression mechanic that particularly upsets students and parents."},"score":{"marketSize":14,"dissatisfaction":25,"feasibility":35,"compositeScore":25},"scanId":"fceeb718-5c98-4761-b59a-4f7d7f1fc08b","createdAt":"2026-03-08T15:48:28.186Z","gapAnalysis":null,"blueOcean":null}}

